title: Phir Hera Pheri
description: The movie story deals with Raju a tenant of Baburao Ganpatrao Apte aka Babu Bhaiyya and has not paid his rent for a long time. Raju does not believe in hard work and wants to earn easy money. He cons everybody, even his mother, who thinks that her son works in Calcutta. Baburao, a bespectacled long-sighted man, runs the "Star Garage". He has a familial debt with many money-lenders and has hard time with them. Shyam aka Ghanshyam has come to Mumbai from Gurgaon seeking a job in his late father's bank. Apparently his father died in a fire that broke out in the bank and he claims that the bank owes him the job. He badly needs the money for his friend Khadak Singh's sister's marriage. A young woman, Anuradha Panniker , is also in the running for the job, her father having died two minutes before Shyam's. Shyam meets Raju and a misunderstanding causes Shyam to think that Raju is a pickpocket. A fight ensues between the two, and Raju escapes, leaving his wallet with Shyam. After Raju leaves, Shyam discovers that he had his own wallet on him all the time. Unfortunately, this realisation comes just as Raju returns with two policemen, insisting that Shyam has robbed him.

After a series of meticulous investigations and judgments, Yufan and others started with Li Yong, the leader of the drug dealer in charge of distribution, and after paying the price of lost lives, they finally outlined a complete drug trafficking network, and successfully locked onto and hid within the network.

title: The Tai Chi Master
description: At the end of the Southern Song Dynasty, the country was troubled by domestic and foreign aggression, and foreign countries were eyeing the dynasty, trying to invade the Central Plains. One day, when the foreign enemies attacked the city, Zhang Junbao, a disciple of the Wuji faction, turned the tide and helped Wei Linchuan, the general of the Song Dynasty, successfully defend the border. Zhang Junbao returned to the sect to participate in the selection ceremony of the sect leader. He was rebellious and had no intention on fighting for the sect leader, but was it plotted against him during the ceremony.

title: SUPER BODYGUARD
description: This film is about a security company's bodyguard, Ye Kai, who is entrusted by medical professor Lin Guohua with the task of protecting Lin Guohua's daughter, Eno, in order to keep his scientific research from falling into the hands of the shady businessman Peter. After experiencing several threats of life and death, they do not give up hope and fight back, and finally overcome the culprit with their firm belief and succeed in preserving Lin's scientific research.

title: Pasanga 2
description: Kavin (Nishesh) and Naina (Vaishnavi) are two children who get pushed out of schools because of their hyperactive activities. Their parents are not able to bear the attitude of their children and transfer them through many schools. Accidentally, they end up with a child psychiatrist Thamizh Nadan (Suriya) and his wife Venba (Amala Paul). The two children were sent to a hostel, where they miss their parents dearly. They escape from the hostel and follow Thamizh and Venba’s children to their home. Thamizh suggests that Kavin and Naina join a school where Venba is a teacher, where they let children be themselves.

title: Dashing Detective
description: Kaniyan, a detective from Visakhapatnam, is approached by a child to investigate the mystery behind his pet dog's death. However, it leads Kaniyan to a larger conspiracy involving a deadly assassin.

title: Tekken
description: Starring: - Kelly Overton, Jon Foo, Cary-Hiroyuki Tagawa and Candice Hillebrand

title: Parole
description: Alex, who is released on parole after eight years of imprisonment, sets out to reconcile with his son and settle some old scores.

title: Skull Island Monster
description: Chinese monster horror movie

title: Beauty and the Beast

As villagers are being brutally murdered and the Beast is hunted down as the one responsible for the mayhem, Belle and Beast team up to defeat the real killer the power-hungry witch's malevolent troll.

title: Ape X

title: Curse of the Nun

title: The Black Swan

When one of them apparently abducts the previous governor's pretty daughter and joins up with the rebels, things are set for a fight.

title: The undefeated
description: After the Civil War, ex-Union Colonel John Henry Thomas and ex-Confederate Colonel James Langdon are leading two disparate groups of people through strife-torn Mexico. John Henry and company are bringing horses to the unpopular Mexican government for $35 a head while Langdon is leading a contingent of displaced southerners, who are looking for a new life in Mexico after losing their property to carpetbaggers. The two men are eventually forced to mend their differences in order to fight off both bandits and revolutionaries, as they try to lead their friends and kin to safety. Written by Alfred Jingle

title: Apache Woman

When his son meets a couple of local kids, together they discover a mysterious note that might change everything if they can unravel the mystery in time.

With the 10th annual Hunger Games fast approaching, the young Snow becomes alarmed when he's assigned to mentor Lucy Gray Baird from District 12. Uniting their instincts for showmanship and political savvy, they race against time to ultimately reveal who's a songbird and who's a snake.

description: Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Anurag Kashyap Movie

The movie features veteran actors Suresh Heblikar, Lakshmi along with Achyuth Kumar, Sudha Rani, Sadhu Kokila, Marutesh and Rajveer in prominent roles

title: Thammar Boyfriend
description: Nandini Mitra, an elderly widow, lives alone in a luxurious mansion. One day, she writes a letter to her family and informs them about her decision to marry a young man, Partho.

title: Indrajith
description: Indrajith heads to the forests of north eastern India in search of a precious stone.

title: Treasure Map
description: A Cherokee boy called Edward White Eyes receives a less-than-warm welcome when he meets another boy at Thornridge Manor; the become friendly after they discover a treasure map and end up part of a thief's scheme that forcing them to follow it.

title: Shree 420
description: Raj falls prey to an unethical lifestyle when a rich businessman, Sonachand, lures him into it. However, when Raj realises Sonachand's unscrupulous ways, he decides to make amends.

title: Angarki
description: Bindumadhav and Shabnam meet at a time when the country's sociopolitical situation is bad. As they both get affected, they come closer and try to end the differences between their communities.

title: Ashke
description: Pamma, a bhangra dancer, quits performing when unexpected events force his college team to split. Years later, his nephew learns about his talent and encourages him to relive his long-lost passion.

title: Shatamanam Bhavati
description: An old couple living with their grandson, yearn for the love of their children, who live abroad and hardly visit them. The frustrated couple hatch a plan to make their children come home.

title: PolyTechnic
description: Pauly, a benevolent politician, falls in love with the daughter of his political opponent, Sukumaran. The rest of the story is about the game of political one-upmanship between Pauly and Sukumaran.

title: Mahira
description: A woman's idyllic life is thrown into chaos when her past catches up to her and she must go to extreme lengths to protect her daughter from assassins.

title: Dham Dhama Dham
description: Cast- Rupam chakrabarty, Kalpana kalita, Arun hazarika, Rajib Barthakur, Jeet Baruah, Chetona das, Jharna bishaya, failung basumatary, Pompi Rani, kumkum, bankim rabha, Satyen Sarma, snigdha gogoi( guest appearance),Shankar kalita, jyutishman , Manas, Arun Bordoloi

title: Chhaya Manush
description: A devastated writer meets a man at his friend's place who is aware of his life. However, the author is warned to stay away from him.

title: Evanukku Engeyo Macham Irukku
description: Hari and Giri work together at a pharmacy but at night they steal things to earn their livelihood. Things take a turn when they are caught and chased by a policewoman, a gangster and an NRI.

title: Joseph
description: The thrilling Biblical story of Joseph is told in this high quality 3-D animated feature film for children ages 5 and up. Young Joseph is a dreamer, indulged by his father and resented by his older brothers who soon sell him into slavery without their father's knowledge. Now captive in Egypt, Joseph experiences humiliation, hardship and imprisonment. But his faith and his gift for interpreting dreams soon lead him to an exalted position in the kingdom. When his brothers come calling for help, Joseph responds in a surprising way. The program sets Joseph's story in the context of God's plan for Israel and the promised coming of the Messiah. It powerfully demonstrates God's sovereign hand in all things.

title: Pink
description: After being molested, Minal, along with her friends, tries to file an FIR against a politician's nephew. When the subsequent case gets rigged, Deepak, a retired lawyer, helps them to fight the case.

title: કરસનદાસ પે એન્ડ યુઝ
description: Karsandas Pay and Use... Tilok, a public restroom incharge, and Jaya fall in love with each other. However, things take a turn when Jaya's family disapproves of their relationship.

title: Aate Di Chidi
description: A Punjabi family who resides in Canada, decides to return to India, which makes the elder members happy. However, the different approaches of the young and the old generations turn things chaotic.

title: Sitamma Vakitlo Sirimalle Chettu
description: Two brothers face ridicule due to unemployment and their family's poor financial background. Consequently, their bond with each other and their love lives are deeply affected.

title: Durjon
description: Casting - Utpal Das , Dr Gunin Basamatari , Ananya Parasar , Pakiza Begum , Bina Borah , Kongki Bordoloi , Kinjal Basumatari , Mahesh Bora ,Mahendra Das , Saju

title: Velipadinte Pusthakam
description: Michael Idikkula, a professor in a college, tries to develop a healthy relationship between the students and teachers and raise money for building hostels by making a short film in honour of Vishwan.

title: Sugarless
description: Lovers Venkatesh and Mahalakshmi lead a happy life and are about to get married. But chaos ensues when Venkatesh is diagnosed with type 2 diabetes and decides to hide it from Mahalakshmi.

title: Cross Connection 2
description: Two young couples facing several problems cross each other's paths to make a difference. They each have a unique connection that substitutes for what is missing in their relationship.

title: Guru Sishyan
description: When Mahalakshmi shows up suddenly, her ex-husband Guru Moorthy, a money-lender by profession, tries to shatter her peaceful life, until he learns that his friend Eeti is her younger brother.

title: She Has A Name
description: An American lawyer attempts to build a case against a pimp sending girls to Bangkok. First, he must gain the trust of a young prostitute known only as Number 18.

title: Benny and Babloo
description: When their restaurant is shut down, Benny and Babloo move to Mumbai in search of jobs Their lives change when one of them gets a job at a five-star hotel while the other gets employed at a dance bar.

title: Hrudayaat Something Something
description: When Ramesh, a sales manager, falls in love with Priya, his superior offers to help him impress her, on the condition that he becomes more sincere towards his job.

title: આ છે આપણી દોસ્તી અનલિમિટેડ યાર
description: Aa Chhe Aapni Dosti Unlimited Yaar... When Abhi fulfils his father's dream by becoming an IAS officer, he inadvertently hurts his close friends and girlfriend. So he endeavours to make it up to them using various methods.

title: Ardaas
description: Gurmukh Singh, who firmly believes in God, works as a teacher at a city school. However, when he moves to the village, he learns about the problems of the locals and decides to help them.

title: Ramayya Vasthavayya
description: In a small village, three evil men kill a lot of innocent people to grab their lands. A young man loses all his loved ones in the process and sets out to seek revenge.

title: Ezra
description: Priya and Ranjan have paranormal experiences after she buys an antique box from a dealer. Soon, they learn that the box is a dybbuk and take the help of a rabbi to learn about its history.

title: Anjani Puthra
description: A businessman saves a policeman from a group of thugs. As a result, he incurs the wrath of a ruthless local gangster who is also an assassin.

title: Mister Bhaduri
description: Aniruddha, the boss of a company, goes to a bungalow every weekend with a bunch of roses and pretends to stay with someone he loves.

description: Paari is a kind-hearted man who goes about doing good deeds and tries to help everyone he meets. He moves to Chennai in order to earn a good living and also ends up falling in love with Madhi.

description: Iqbal, a boy hard of hearing and without speech, dreams of playing in the Indian cricket team. When his condition hinders his selection, he asks a retired coach to train him.

description: Lucky lives a carefree life along with his three friends until he meets and falls in love with Seerat. However, a series of unfortunate circumstances keep them from getting married.

description: Just out of prison, Tommy has trouble with the outside world. His sister is too controlling, he has to lie to his mother and deal with his ex-girlfriend. Soon, he falls in love with a parole officer.

title: હવે ક્યારે મળીશું
description: Have Kyare Malishu... Starcast: Jignesh Barot, Rajdip Barot, Prinal Oberoi, Shreya Dave, Prem Kandoliya

title: Mr & Mrs 420
description: Deputy aspires to be an actor but is unable to land a good role while his friend Jass needs a good job to be able to marry his girlfriend. They move to another town in search of better opportunities.

title: Red Wing
description: Maddie adopts Francis, a young orphan, after his caretaker dies. They face various challenges after Maddie's husband, Carl, suspects her affection towards the boy and he is forced to leave town.

description: Bhairu's father, who is a wrestling champion, wants the same glory for his son. However, he does not have any interest in the sport but things change after his father's death.

title: ચિત્કાર
description: Chitkar... Markand Shah, a doctor, attempts to treat his patient Ratna, who is suffering from a mental illness, and provide her with a normal life.

description: When a newly-wed couple, Manjinder and Guddi, return to Manjinder's hometown, they find that his extended family consisting of four maternal uncles have split and gone their separate ways.

title: Bakula Namdev Ghotale
description: After Namdev gets married to a beautiful woman named Bakula, he returns to his village with his wife and meets the sarpanch, Ghotale. Hilarity ensues when Ghotale finds himself attracted to Bakula.

title: હેપ્પી ફેમિલી પીવીટી એલટીડી
description: Happy Family Pvt Ltd... What happens when a rich, dysfunctional family, that is very much caught up in their Mumbai lifestyle, is forced to go live the village-life? That's exactly what happens when Uttam Mehta is almost shot at gunpoint. Fearing that their lives are in danger, the Mehta family is off to hide out at in a location that can't even be located on Google Maps - called Antillapur. Just then, things get even weirder. Little does Uttam and the family know, that this village is unlike any other village...it functions off a Barter System!

title: God's Compass
description: On the night Suzanne Waters celebrates her retirement, she is faced with a series of unimaginable crises

title: Khalnayak
description: Inspector Ram succeeds in nabbing notorious criminal Ballu. When Ballu's escape taints Ram's name, his fiancee, Ganga, decides to trap Ballu. But, things get complicated when Ballu starts liking her.

title: Bhootacha Honeymoon
description: Shankar moves to a village, unaware that it is haunted by a ghost who prevents all marriages. When Shankar decides to marry the woman he loves, the ghost makes an odd demand.

title: ભાનવાર
description: Bhanwar... A young puppeteer finds immense joy in folk puppeteering but to do something worthwhile, he goes to a city. He meets different people and makes new experiences, which reinvigorates his passion.

title: Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon
description: A man marries three different women who live in the same building and are unaware that they have the same husband. To make matters worse, all his wives get invited to his fourth wedding.

description: A son tries to revive his parents' lifeless marriage by travelling back in time to the '70s when their romance was budding. But to his surprise, it turns out to be more complex than he had expected.

title: Mere Baap Pehle Aap

title: The Bad Guys: Reign of Chaos
description: After a group of criminals manage to escape while being transported, a skilled task force is assembled to help track and return them to prison.

title: Los Secretos De Jonathan Sperry
description: Los mejores amigos Dustin, Albert y Mark son niños de doce años que esperan pasar un verano de diversión en 1970. Cuando Dustin corta el césped de Jonathan Sperry, de setenta y cinco años, un hombre al que ha visto en la iglesia, se desarrolla una amistad única. ¡Lo que sucederá el resto de este verano es algo que Dustin y sus amigos nunca olvidarán!

description: Deepak tries to start a transportation service after his father receives a bus upon his retirement. However, his honest endeavour is haunted by mishaps, lack of experience and corruption.

title: Sivaji The Boss
description: A software engineer arrives in India to serve the nation and invest in the country's welfare. A few corrupt officials and politicians try to stop him while he tries to overcome the obstacles.

title: Special Female Force
description: Madam Fong gathers a group of girls and trains them to become special agents with a mission to capture an international terrorist who killed her comrades in a bombing 25 years ago.

title: Storm Rider
description: Dani Fielding's carefree days come to a sudden end when her father is imprisoned. Being spoilt, the repercussions prove difficult for her as she starts to live with her uncle while caring for a mule.

title: The Christmas Project
description: During the Christmas season, the Buckley brothers decide to teach the Hagbarts boys, the bullies at school, a lesson. However, their mother decides to send the Hagbart family gifts

title: Beautiful Beast
description: Isabelle, a spoilt rich girl, goes on a trip with her friend but they have an argument and he leaves her wandering alone in the cold. She later encounters a reclusive man and gets intrigued by him.

title: Love Surreal
description: While growing up, Abby Morrison had an imaginary friend, whom she considers her current boyfriend. Things change when she's attracted to her friend's cousin, Quinn, and must decide whom to give up.

title: Maine Dil Tujhko Diya

title: Slambook
description: When Aparna's family moves into Hruday's neighbourhood, the latter falls in love with the young girl. His maternal grandfather helps the teenage boy by giving him tips on how to woo her.

title: Baankey ki Crazy Baraat
description: Baankey, a 35-year-old unemployed man, sets a motive to get married against his horoscope. A priest offers the solution of a proxy wedding wherein the groom would replace him.

title: The Dirty Picture

title: Nadiya Ke Paar
description: Chandan, a farmer's nephew, is in love with Gunja, his sister-in-law's sibling. However, when her sister dies in an accident, Gunja is expected to marry Chandan's brother

title: Lucky: No Time for Love
description: Lucky is molested by a Russian boy on her way to school but she escapes and hides in Aditya's car. When a terrorist attack breaks out, the two manage to escape and hide in an isolated graveyard.

title: Arya Ek Deewana
description: Two orphan childhood friends go down contrasting career paths after they are separated from one another. Later, fate pits them against each other when both fall in love with the same girl.

title: Fidaa
description: Varun, an NRI medical student, and Bhanu, a vivacious, young woman, fall in love with each other. However, they face many personal differences that create complications in their relationship.

title: Raja Rani
description: John and Regina, who dislike each other, are forced to get married and lead troubled lives. However, things take a turn when the couple suffers a sudden tragedy.

title: 1920: The Evil Returns
description: A famous poet, Jaidev, meets a woman who has lost her memories. He brings her to his house and tries to help her, but things take an ugly turn when she gets possessed by an evil spirit

title: Standing Firm
description: A man struggling to support his family in almost all ways decides to leave his sorrows behind and fight back.

title: Princess Cut
description: Grace's dream date does not go as planned as her boyfriend messes things up. Later, Grace, with the help of her father, tries to understand what it means to love another person truly.

title: Morning Glory
description: To popularise a national morning news programme, Becky, an upstart TV producer, hires famous anchorman Mike Pomeroy. His clashes with his co-host worsen the show's quality and Becky's personal life

title: Amazing Love: The Story of Hosea
description: Stuart, leader of the youth group of the church, takes the youth group on a weekend campaign. When a disagreement takes place, Stuart decides to narrate a story of the Old Testament prophet Hosea.

title: Mujhse Shaadi Karogi
description: A hot-headed man, Sameer, moves to Goa, where he meets and falls for Rani. However, Sunny, his roommate, also loves her and tries his best to ruin Sameer's chances with Rani.

title: Hey Babby
description: Three compulsive womanisers find a baby left at their doorstep. However, chaos ensues as they try to contact their former girlfriends to determine who is the father amongst them.

title: આઈ એમ અ ગુજ્જુ
description: I M A Gujju... Jay, the son of a wealthy businessman, gets into an argument with his father over joining the army. However, he soon finds himself racing against time to save four innocent people from terrorists.

title: Identical Love
description: After being left at the altar, Dr. Charlotte Hudson signs up to volunteer in a health clinic in a tropical country, but her plans of escaping are thrown off when she comes across her former fiancé's twin brother, Seth.

title: Taal
description: Mansi becomes famous with Vikrant's help after her former boyfriend's family members insult her and her father. Problems arise when her ex-lover apologises to her and tries to win her back.

title: Vaah! Life Ho Toh Aisi!
description: A man, who has a lot of family responsibilities, meets an untimely death. However, he is granted a week to return to Earth in order to wrap up all his unfinished business.

title: If You're Gone
description: On the night of the graduation, Lillian's life changes forever when her boyfriend, Brad, disappears. Unable to find him, Lillian is forced to question their relationship and her faith.

title: Sanam Bewafa
description: Two families that are traditional rivals are shocked when their children fall in love with each other. After great difficulty, the households agree to the marriage, but things do not go as planned.

title: Fun2shh... Dudes in the 10th Century
description: Three men are accused of stealing a crown and whilst on the run, they are transported to the 10th century. Amidst several adventures, they must try to bring the crown back to prove their innocence.

title: Christmas Grace
description: Gary and Mr Tollman own toy shops and compete with each other in order to make a profit. However, they are unaware of that fact that God has a different plan for them.

title: The Farmer and The Belle : Saving Santaland
description: When city girl Belle returns to her hometown, she reunites with her former best friend, a farmer. Love blooms between them when they work together to save the town's annual Christmas festival.

title: Everyday Miracles
description: A reluctant faith healer's dreams for a new life as a ranch hand are shattered when his predatory mother tracks him down and makes plans to drag him back to the revival circuit.

title: Chalk and Duster
description: Jyoti, a teacher who is passionate about teaching, stands up for a fellow teacher, Vidya, and fights against her unjustified dismissal by the school's new principal, Kamini Gupta

title: 12th Fail
description: IPS officer Manoj Kumar Sharma fearlessly embraces the idea of restarting his academic journey and reclaiming his destiny at a place where millions of students attempt the world's toughest competitive exam: UPSC.

title: Ranna
description: Sharat assures his despondent grandfather that he will reunite him with his estranged daughter. To fulfil his promise, he goes to work for the woman's family as a driver.

title: Maanikya
description: Vijay and Manasa's families have been at each other's throat's since the past 25 years. However, things take a turn when they fall in love with each other.

title: Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas
description: Saher, a video blogger, embarks on a solo trip to expose Karan, the owner of a tourism company she believes is a fraud. They both start off on a bitter note but gradually fall in love with each other.

title: Ajab Prem Ki Ghazab Kahani
description: Prem falls in love with Jenny, a woman who is already in love with a man named Rahul. Despite this, he agrees to help her marry him and even gets into several comical situations as a result.

title: Force

title: Dragon Tiger Gate
description: Two stepbrothers, who are polar opposites and martial artists, get separated in their childhood. Years later, when a common enemy threatens their existence, they join forces

While working under cover at the New York City branch office, he falls in love with the employee he came to investigate. Alex must choose between saving his company from impending collapse or following his heart.

title: Home Sweet Home
description: A charming barista helps a devout man build a home for a family in need, all while hoping that he notices her.

title: Amavas
description: Karan and Ahana's weekend vacation at an ancient palatial house turns into a nightmare when they are forced to fend themselves from the dark forces residing in the house.

title: Athiran
description: Dr Nair, a psychiatrist, visits a mental asylum located in a remote location in Kerala. He meets a patient, Nithya, who is kept in isolation, and soon uncovers mysteries from her past.

title: The Perfect Gift
description: A wicked girl receives an uplifting message about friendship, commitment and gets to know the real meaning of Christmas from a mysterious drifter.

title: Kaalo
description: Kaalo, a ruthless witch, is resurrected after many years to kill a young girl, Shona, who is travelling alone to her grandmother's place. It is up to Sameer, a youth, to protect Shona from Kaalo.

title: Dhadkan

title: Krishna Cottage
description: A group of college students are forced to take shelter in the mysterious Krishna Cottage for the night. Little do they know that a spirit haunts the cottage.

title: Gayab
description: Vishu, a shy guy who's insulted by all, has no guts to confess to the girl he loves. Fed up of his life, he begs god to make him disappear. He soon turns invisible, which leads him into more trouble.

title: Aladin
description: A young orphan, Aladin, who gets bullied by his peers, finds a magic lamp that changes his life. Thereafter, he sets off on a series of adventures and uses the lamp to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Ghost
description: Karan Khanna, a young politician, is accused of murdering his wife, Barkha. When his new lawyer, Simran, decides to defend him, she comes across a spirit who might be involved.

title: Aabra Ka Dabra
description: A young student sets out on a quest for a magic potion that can bring back his missing father. He faces several hardships while trying to find and rescue his father.

title: My Friend Ganesha
description: Ashu, an eight-year-old boy, feels lonely since his parents do not have time for him and he does not have any friends. However, Ganesha befriends him and helps him become confident.

title: For the Glory
description: When Kurt's life completely shatters because of a family tragedy and other factors, he turns to God, where he finds his true calling.

title: Pyare Mohan

title: The Healing Garden
description: A former military chaplain and a girl from a broken home work together to plant a garden that's been touched by God.

title: Heaven Sent
description: Howard, a bumbling guardian angel, tries to help sort out the lives of a teenager and his mother.

title: The Magic Door
description: A troll takes the help of a boy and an elf to defeat a black witch that poses as an obstacle in his quest to reach home.

title: A Life to Choose
description: A young man uncovers a dark secret that his family have kept hidden.

title: Ek Thi Daayan
description: Bobo, a famous magician, plans to marry his girlfriend. However, he is secretly scarred by persistent hallucinations of his dead sister and is forced to seek psychiatric help.

title: Clancy
description: Clancy, an abused 12-year-old, elopes to avoid being taken by social workers. She bumps into a grumpy, homeless veteran Nick, and considers him for protection. But is Nick a safe refuge for her?

title: Shattering The Silence
description: Deeply buried memories of sexual abuse by her father resurface, when Veronica suffers from postpartum depression. The new mother decides confront her parent and take him to court, which has wide-ranging consequences for her family.

title: 100 Days

title: Judwaa

title: Genesis Impact
description: After attending a lecture on human evolution at a natural history museum, Christina, a young creationist, questions the lecturer and argues against the theory of evolution.

title: The Christmas Spirit
description: Charlotte lands in coma but realises that her spirit is awake. This prompts her to communicate with the people of her town and convince them to not make a deal with a greedy real-estate developer.

title: Akele Hum Akele Tum
description: Two aspiring singers, Rohit and Kiran, fall in love and get married. Soon, the burden of responsibilities cripples the marriage and Kiran decides to part ways with Rohit.

title: Rehna Hai Tere Dil Mein
description: Maddy impersonates Rajeev, the person his love interest, Reena, is about to marry and attempts to woo her. However, he is unprepared for the moment when the truth will be revealed.

title: Dil Vil Pyaar Vyaar
description: Dev, Vishal and Hrithik enter a singing competition. However, life is complicated for them as they face numerous obstacles in their personal lives which slowly bring out the best in them.

title: Mr Ya Miss
description: Casanova Sanjay Patel lands himself in trouble when he is killed by his girlfriend for his flirtatious actions. Mayhem ensues when he returns to Earth as a girl this time.

title: Toh Baat Pakki

title: Nayee Padosan
description: Three men try different methods to woo their neighbour. However, her father wants her to get married to someone from his community.

title: Jaan-E-Mann
description: Suhaan, an aspiring actor, is in a fix when Piya files for divorce and forces him to pay a large amount as alimony. To avoid paying her, Suhaan uses Agastya's love for Piya and helps him woo her.

title: Love Breakups Zindagi
description: Two strangers, Jai and Naina, and their friends find their lives changing after attending a wedding as they struggle to find their true love.

title: Kidnap
description: Out to seek revenge against a businessman named Raina for falsely accusing him and getting him arrested, Kabir kidnaps his daughter Sonia.

title: Aitraaz
description: Raj, a married man, is falsely accused of rape by his ex-girlfriend who is also his employer's wife. This motivates him to sue her for sexual harassment despite societal pressures.

title: The Magnificent Seven

title: Deewangee
description: Sargam approaches Raj, a lawyer, to defend her friend Tarang, who is accused of murder. Raj proves that Tarang suffers from split personality but later, he learns that he might be the actual murderer.

title: Corporate
description: An ambitious career woman unknowingly becomes a pawn in a corporate war between two rival companies and gets caught in a web that shatters her professional and personal life.

title: Dead Before Dawn
description: Linda leads a seemingly perfect life with her husband and two children but, in reality, is a victim of domestic abuse. She soon files for divorce but her husband hires an assassin to kill her.

title: 36 China Town
description: Inspector Karan investigates the murder of Sonia Chang, a wealthy casino owner in China Town. However, the mystery gets harder to solve when none of the suspects seem to have an alibi.

title: Carry On Balle Balle
