description: Devendra Kumar's family life is disrupted when he discovers he has an illegitimate child from a past affair. He brings the young boy, Rahul, home, but his wife, Indu, fails to accept the child.

title: Kuch Kuch Hota Hai
description: A tomboyish Anjali loves Rahul, her best college pal, but is anguished when he decides to wed Tina, a fellow collegian. Eight years later, widower Rahul's daughter is told to reunite him with Anjali.

title: Phobia
description: Mehak, a talented artist, develops agoraphobia after a taxi driver assaults her. However, when she moves into a new apartment, she feels a malevolent force has possessed her owing to her visions.

title: Baaghi
description: Ronny, a rebellious man, falls in love with Sia but circumstances separate them. Years later, Ronny learns that Sia is abducted by the martial arts champion Raghav.

title: ABCD (Any Body Can Dance)
description: After being forced to quit his own academy, Vishnu, a choreographer, comes across a group of talented dancers. He decides to take them under his wing and train them to be the best in the business.

title: Jodhaa Akbar
description: Jodhaa is a fiery Rajput princess who is obliged to marry Mughal Emperor Akbar for political reasons. Eventually, mutual respect and admiration between the duo leads to true love.

title: The Good Student
description: An unpopular high school teacher's life is turned upside down when he is suspected of kidnapping a pretty young girl.

title: Lake City
description: On the run from a dangerous drug dealer, a young man in returns to his childhood home, the one place he does not want to be.

title: Adda
description: Priya asks Abhi, who works to create rifts between lovers for money, to end an affair between her sister and her boyfriend. In the process, Abhi and Priya, engaged to someone else, fall in love.

title: Kotha Bangaru Lokam
description: Balu falls in love with his classmate Swapna, the daughter of a rich business tycoon. Trouble brews when Swapna's parents see a picture of the couple in a newspaper and stop her from studying further.

title: Iddarammayilatho
description: Aakansha happens to come across the love story of Sanju and Komali in a diary. Finding that the story is incomplete she goes to meet Sanju. Matters take a turn when Aakansha falls in love with Sanju.

title: Bunny
description: A millionaire's daughter goes against his wishes to marry her boyfriend. However, when her father finally gives them his blessing, her fiance suddenly demands her father's entire fortune in dowry.

title: Fida
description: Jai falls in love with Neha, unaware of her and her boyfriend Vikram's evil intentions. He easily gets trapped in their conspiracy but decides to exact revenge while being on the run from the police.

title: Qayamat Se Qayamat Tak
description: Despite knowing that their respective families are bitter enemies, Raj and Rashmi fall in love with each other and decide to elope.

title: Qayamat: City Under Threat
description: CBI officer Akram recruits Rachit, a convict, to help save 213 tourists held hostage by three terrorists, Ali, Abbas and Laila, as he was their former associate.

title: Hum Hain Rahi Pyar Ke
description: Rahul looks after his spoilt nephews, Sunny and Vicky, and niece, Munni. When they go to a funfair, they meet Vyjayanti, who has run away from home, and decide to shelter her without Rahul's consent.

title: Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar
description: Sanjay, a carefree young man, experiences mental and physical transformation to compete in an inter-collegiate bicycle race after his elder brother is unable to participate due to an injury.

title: Thodi Khatti Thodi Hatti
description: Ira reclaims her late father's bungalow from a young man who claims to have its ownership. She decides to stay therein until the man leaves. But, as the time goes by, they begin to like each other.

title: Anand
description: Anand, a terminally ill man, sets out to live his last days to the fullest. His doctor, Bhaskar, undergoes metamorphosis due to his optimism and decides to write a book on Anand.

title: Knock Out
description: Businessman Bachubhai's life turns upside down when he is held hostage at a phone booth by an unidentified caller who threatens to kill him if he hangs up the phone.

title: Tuzya Mazyat
description: Shashank and Asmita are a divorced couple with two children, Nisha and Shubham. The children stay with their mother and visit their father, who is married to Radhika, during the weekend.

title: Janma
description: Vandana Sarpotdar is a 50 year old single mother who wants to go for a test tube in order to save the life of her only daughter Nisha who is suffering from Leukemia and needs a Bone Marrow Transplant.

title: લવ નો ભવાડો
description: Love No Bhavado... Cast : Bechar Thakor-Govind Thakor(Rakesh Pandey)-Ishika Toriya-Krishna Zala-Jaimini Trivedi-Ratan Gagvani-Naresh Prajapati-DevThakkar-Ravi Solanki-Vishal Jethava

title: પરિચય
description: Parichay... Story of a girl Roshni who is working as an honest police officer in Gujarat state. She is famous police officer because she always do her work with an honesty and purity. She have one man who always give her information about criminal and crime place. But when criminal knows about that man he kills him. She took revenge of his death but when she feels that she completed her work and clear crime in city, she gets transfer in another city near port. Roshni knows the reason of her transfer after sometime. She has trapped in big political drama where she hunted by one politician. Roshni takes stand against them and give them punishment of their sins by using law of police.

title: Apne
description: A wrecked boxer turns to his sons to win the glory that eluded him in the ring. But when his younger son is injured in the ring, the elder one decides to fulfil his father's dream.

title: Love Sex Aur Dhokha
description: Hidden cameras capture the honour killing of a couple in love, an MMS scandal wreaking havoc in a woman's life and a shocking incident where a woman becomes a casting couch victim.

title: Dus
description: Jamwaal, a terrorist, plans to wreak havoc in Canada when the Indian Prime Minister visits the nation. However, a team of special agents from India are sent to catch the terrorist.

title: Crime Case 99(Yutham Sei)
description: JK, a CID officer, is forced to take up a case while on a lookout for his own sister who is missing. While investigating, he realises there is more to the case and goes on to unveil the mystery.

title: દીકરો મારો વ્હાલ નો વારસદાર
description: Dikro Maro Vahal No Varasdar... After Alok returns home from a foreign university, he plays a silly prank on his fragile father. To make amends, he gets actively involved in familial obligations.

title: Solo
description: An anthology of the chronicles of four people, representing earth, fire, wind and water elements of nature, who experience love, heartbreak and failure in their journey of life.

title: Anthony Kaun Hai?
description: Champak changes his name to Anthony Gonzales when he gets out of jail. When an underworld gangster gets hold of him and attempts to kill him, Anthony must convince him about his real identity.

title: Shor In The City
description: In the city of Mumbai, an NRI businessman, a minor criminal and an aspiring cricketer grapple with life-changing choices during the chaotic period of the festival of Ganesh Chaturthi.

title: A Wednesday
description: Prakash Rathod, a retired police commissioner recounts the most memorable case of his career wherein he was informed about a bomb scare in Mumbai by an ordinary commoner.

title: Aarakshan
description: Dr Anand, the principal of STM College, along with his disciples, fights to abide by the OBC reservation verdict of the Supreme Court. However, they have to overcome many obstacles while doing so.

title: Satte Pe Satta
description: Indu, a nurse, loves Ravi and marries him. However, his uncivilised brothers create trouble for her, making her set out to improve their mannerisms.

title: Christmas on My Mind
description: Lucy wakes up with a wedding dress in hand and thinks she's late to her wedding with her ex-boyfriend Zach. However, she has no recollection of the past two years, including the fact that she's engaged to another man.

title: Once Upon A Time in Mumbai Dobaara
description: Shoaib becomes the new mafia leader after killing his mentor, Sultan Mirza. He finds a protege in Aslam, but trouble ensues when they both fall in love with the same woman, Jasmine.

title: Jaan To Pyara
description: Gill and Lakha, two childhood friends, are in love with Maahi, a woman forced to marry Jagga. When one of them takes Maahi away from her wedding, animosity brews between Jagga and Maahi's families.

title: Teri Meri Jodi
description: The fates of two loving couples are confronted with stereotypical cultural barriers that change the course of their relationships.

title: Jind Jaan
description: Ranjha, along with his uncle, travels to Thailand on a special mission, where he meets with Juliet, who belongs to a rich family. He falls for her and faces many obstacles to win her love.

title: Dharam Yudh Morcha
description: A devout man tells his grandson about Sikhs in India from 1947 to 1984, highlighting the fight of the Sikh people to safeguard the fundamental rights of their religion and linguistic minorities in the region.

title: Proud To Be A Sikh
description: A Gursikh professor meets six youth who are ashamed of their religion. He tries to educate them about their rich heritage and encourages them to be proud of an important aspect of their identity.

title: Ik Onkar
description: A man goes on a mission to save the people from the unjust practices of politicians and the government.

title: Comali
description: Ravi awakens from a prolonged coma to learn that he is in his 30s and has missed 16 years of his life. Soon, he struggles to cope with the modern world and its innovations

title: Mard Ka Inteqam (Keshava)
description: Keshava, a law student who suffers from a rare heart disease, breaks down when his entire family is brutally murdered. He then vows to seek revenge and punish the perpetrators.

title: Chanakya
description: Arjun, a highly sought-after RAW agent, is known for his skills at catching some of the most hardened criminals. However, he falls in danger when he goes after Ibrahim Qureshi, a terrorist.
Arjun falls in love with Lisa and abandons his family and faith for her. They move to a manor in Palampur but when Lisa gets possessed by a demonic spirit, Arjun must save her.

title: Eve's Christmas
description: Eve, a successful yet loner businesswoman, gets a magical wish allowing her to go back in time when she chose career over her marriage with Scott, her lover.

title: Premam (Chitralahari)
description: Depressed with the constant failures in his personal and professional life, Vijay is in search of an opportunity to prove himself. While no one believes him, Swecha decides to give him a chance

title: Half Girlfriend
description: Madhav Jha, a student from Bihar, takes admission in a Delhi college and falls in love with Riya Somani. He coaxes her to be his girlfriend, but she is not interested in him romantically.

title: Titanic
description: A young boy dreams of joining the Indian Navy but faces various challenges and obstacles due to his family's financial background.

title: Dil Diya Hai
description: A man sells his girlfriend to a stranger and uses the money to save the life of his mother. However, he realises he loves her and sets out to rescue her.

title: Housefull 3
description: A rich businessman does not want his three daughters to get married because of a superstitious belief. Now, their boyfriends must prove to him that they are perfect for his daughters.

title: Patiala House
description: Gattu loves to play cricket, even though his father hates the sport. After he gets selected to play for an English team, he must choose between his dreams and his father's wishes.

title: Dastaan-E-Miri Piri
description: Shri Guru Hargobind, the sixth Sikh guru armed with Miri-Piri, wages a war against the Mughals after a serious setback faced by his community.

title: Pride and Prejudice: A Latter-Day Comedy
description: In this modern take on the Jane Austen classic, Elizabeth (Kam Heskin), an earnest college student at Brigham Young University, is more focused on her studies than on scoping out prospective husbands. But then two wildly different suitors -- smooth-talking womanizer Jack Wickham (Henry Maguire) and straitlaced businessman Darcy (Orlando Seale) -- attempt to win her over. Aided by her friends, Elizabeth must struggle to find love and choose Mr. Right.

title: Prescription For Love
description: A nurse fights for a chance at love with a new doctor and for a promotion to free herself from the misery her supervisor creates. As her supervisor tries to derail her chance at happiness, she learns to stand up for herself and go after her dreams.

title: Christmas Catch
description: Mackenzie, a detective who loves Christmas, is asked to go undercover to catch Carson, a charming diamond thief. However, she soon starts falling in love with him and believes that he may be framed.

title: Saare Jahaan Se Mehnga
description: A man struggles to survive in the ever-growing inflation of the country. When he comes up with an idea, it backfires and lands him in big trouble.

title: Sab Kushal Mangal
description: Pappu, a reality show creator, and a corrupt politician lock horns over Pappu's sensational work. Complications ensue further when they fall for the same girl.

title: Dagadabaichi Chawl
description: Dagdabai Mhatre, the owner of a chawl in Mumbai, is taken for a ride by the residents who take undue advantage of her simple and kind nature by not paying rent on time.

title: Ek Maratha Lakh Maratha
description: Ek Maratha Lakh Maratha Ek Maratha Lakh Maratha is the pain of Marathi people. This is the story of a young man living in a farming family. He fights alone to solve the abuse of his sister and bring her justice. He doesn't even know how his struggle turns into a big march. Now his only goal in life is to bring justice to his sister.

title: Shrimant Damodar Pant
description: Damu, a simpleton, lives happily with his family. However, everyday in the evening, his late grandfather's spirit enters his body and creates problems for everyone.

title: Ek Kutub Teen Minar
description: Kutub, a civil engineer, aspires to be a property developer. However, his impatience towards achieving his dreams land him in problems every time and crush his dreams.

title: Tata Birla Ani Laila
description: Two con artists, Tata and Birla, are more than willing to do anything for money. When they are tasked with murder, they have a change of heart.

title: Bhoot Returns
description: Tarun and Namrata move into a luxurious bungalow with Taman and Nimmi, their son and daughter respectively. However, strange occurrences start taking place and they must escape in order to survive.

title: Zed Plus
description: Aslam, a villager who runs a small business, accidentally meets the prime minister of India, who grants him special security on his request. Soon, he starts chasing political ambitions.

title: Chatur Singh Two Star
description: A police detective is sent to South Africa to investigate the murder of a politician. Once there, he finds himself in direct confrontation with a gangster.

title: Baghban
description: Raj Malhotra and his wife, Pooja, sacrifice everything to let their four sons have a happy life. However, when Raj retires, his sons become selfish and treat their parents with disrespect.

title: A Dog's Tale
description: Anything is possible when a mysterious professor tells young Tim about a supernova that grants wishes. Unfortunately, when Tim's wish doesn't go as planned, he finds himself in a dog's body.

title: A Doggone Christmas
description: A pair of brothers is overjoyed when they stumble across a puppy with telepathic abilities. However, the CIA has a bone to pick with them as the puppy was once in their possession.

title: Deewar
description: A group of Indian soldiers is captured during the Indo-Pak War. Gaurav, whose father, Major Ranvir, has been held captive by the enemies, decides to go on a rescue mission.

title: Blackboard
description: The current scenario of the corrupt education system with Blackboard. The story traces a common man's struggle to educate his granddaughter. Will he be successful in this fight? Will he be able to bring change to the education system? Will he be able to educate his granddaughter with his limited resources? Blackboard is all about the commercialization of the archaic education system.

title: Raju Ban Gaya Gentleman
description: Renu helps Raju acquire a job in her company and, later, they both fall in love with each other. However, things take a turn when his success makes him arrogant.

title: Ankganit Anandache
description: Anand finds his life turned upside down after the death of his father. As he struggles to cope with this loss, he begins to strengthen his relationship with his son.

title: Manyaa The Wonder Boy
description: Manya is a poor village boy whose life changes when Sudhir Phadnis, his sports teacher, trains him to become a state-level athlete.

title: Karz
description: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Johny Mera Naam
description: When Heeralal, a gangster, gets arrested, he befriends Johny, a petty thief, in prison. He then seeks Johny's help in executing his mission of smuggling a few diamonds.

title: Kidu
description: Five notorious schoolboys change their ways and become well-behaved when Annie, their new teacher, inspires them. However, a shocking incident changes the boys' lives drastically.

title: Dhartiputra
description: Yashpal tries to rape Jeeva and her husband, Shiva, stops him while she manages to escape. However, Yashpal kills him and she vows to avenge his death.

title: Gulebagavali (Gulaebaghavali)
description: A businessperson sends three thieves to find the hidden treasure in a village named Gulaebaghavali. A fourth criminal enters the gang midway, and they plan to divide the loot among themselves.

title: Silver Wolf
description: Jesse, a sixteen-year-old teenager, develops a deep bond with the wolf he rescues from the wilderness and tries to save it from a hunter.

title: The Legend Of Wolf Mountain
description: Three children are kidnapped and taken to the forest by escaped convicts where they are released, but must still stay clear of the evil men. A wolf appears, a Native American Spirit, and helps them in returning to safety.

title: Tinhi sanja
description: Sandeep is an only child and his parents dote on him. The family of three starts to drift apart when Sandeep gets married to Sujata, an ambitious young woman.

title: Badlapur Boys
description: Vijay grows up with a dream of bringing water to his village after his father's sacrifice goes in vain. So, he participates in a kabaddi tournament to attract the attention of the bureaucracy.

title: Bhaigiri 2 (Bhooloham)
description: Deepak, the CEO of a sports channel, manipulates Bhooloham and Arumugam, two boxers, for his personal gain. When Bhooloham's attack during a fight puts Arumugam in a coma, he gives up boxing.

title: Little Lord Fauntleroy
description: Ceddie and his mother Errol live in a lower-class Manhattan home. Suddenly one day, an agent from Cedric's estranged grandfather, the Earl of Dorincourt, visits them and asks them to move to England.

title: Mythri
description: Siddarama is one step away from winning a sum of INR one crore in a game show hosted by his favourite actor Puneeth Rajkumar. However, scientist Mahadev Godke attempts to ruin his plans.

title: Sakharam Binder
description: One of Vijay Tendulkar's most controversial plays, Sakharam Binder was first staged in 1974. It tells the story of the book-binder Sakharam who takes home a series of women after they have been thrown out of their homes by their respective husbands.In return for providing shelter, Sakharam exploits the women by getting them to perform household tasks and occasionally, for sexual favours. The play opens with the seventh woman Laxmi who is docile and timid by nature. After exploiting her for a few days, Sakharam throws her out and brings the next woman Champa who is flamboyant and head-strong. Things get complicated after a few days when Laxmi returns. What follows is a succession of unexpected events which culminate into a dramatic end.

title: 100 Days of Love
description: Despite their strained history as children, a columnist falls in love with his schoolmate when they meet after years. Just as he decides to win her heart, he learns that she is engaged to another man.

title: Doli Saja Ke Rakhna
description: Inder and Pallavi fall for each other but her three possessive brothers hate him. Resultantly, the couple elopes but they soon find themselves missing their families and decide to return.

title: Bhalwan Singh
description: In the pre-independence era, the British steal from the people and terrorise them. However, Bhalwan Singh, a village man, decides to stop them and also win the heart of his lady-love, Veero.

title: 72 Hours: Martyr Who Never Died
description: In a bid to defend the north-east front of India from the Chinese army, Jaswant Singh Rawat, a rifleman, combats the opponents alone for 72 hours.

title: Saath Tujha Bhetla
description: Vedika and Aditya fall in love and desperately want to get married. When Vedika's father learns about Aditya's financial problems, he does not approve of their relationship.

title: Amaanat
description: A young woman sets out to search for her missing husband and comes across Sona, who saves her from some thugs. They soon form a bond but face challenges in their quest.

title: 22G Tussi Ghaint Ho
description: In order to match their family status with the family of the girl he loves, milk vendor Boota Singh's brother, Rupan, forces him to try his hand at politics.

title: Extra Ordinary Man
description: Nithiin, Sreeleela | Vakkantham Vamsi | Harris Jayaraj

title: Roy
description: Ranbir Kapoor | Arjun Rampal | Jacqueline Fernandez

title: Saadi Marzi
description: A couple having varied personalities, father from Punjab and mother from Haryana, want to raise their son individually. The son's life bears disastrous consequences due to their cultural differences.

title: My Friend Ganesha 3
description: Ganya, an orphan, is troubled by his evil uncle and aunt for the huge property that he has inherited from his family. He therefore seeks the help of Lord Ganesha.

title: Jora 10 Numbaria
description: A traumatised young boy grows up to become a notorious gangster and sets out to seek revenge against the corrupt officials who destroyed his family.

title: Aslee Punjab
description: In Punjab, several farmers along with the youths face various issues. The farmers do not have adequate facilities for agriculture whereas the younger generation must tackle many personal problems.

title: Dhol Ratti
description: A Punjabi family moves into their in-laws' home during unfavourable political conditions occurring in the country. However, problems arise when family members from both sides start fighting.
A reputed doctor goes mysteriously missing. Things get complicated when the doctor's psychic patient steps up to help his wife find him.

title: Laali Ki Shaadi Mein Laddo Deewana
description: Laddoo, a middle-class ambitious man, falls in love with beautiful Laali. However, their happiness is short-lived when they discover that Laali is pregnant.

title: Viraam
description: Abhiraj, a widowed businessman, leads a solitary life until he comes across Mathun, who was cheated by her fiance. He decides to help her and soon enough, a bond starts to form between them.

title: Shaandaar
description: Jagjinder Joginder, a wedding planner, brings together the dysfunctional family of businessman Bipin Arora while making arrangements for his daughter's destination wedding in London.

title: Devdas
description: After his wealthy family prohibits him from marrying the woman he is in love with, Devdas's life spirals downward as he takes up alcohol and a life of vice to alleviate the pain.

title: Gulaab Gang
description: Rajjo runs a gang that strives to uplift the downtrodden and combat injustice in the village. When a corrupt politician runs for the local elections, Rajjo decides to compete against her.

title: Saggi Phull
description: Cast: Shivendra Mahal, Neetu Pandher, Amritpal Chhotu, Ravinder Pawar, Amitiz Shergill, Dilawar Sidhu, Navdeep Kalar, Balwinder Bego, Gurpreet Kaur Bhangu, Sukhi Bal, Simranpreet, Raj Dhariwal & others

title: I Am 24
description: Subhendu, a middle-aged writer, falls in love with a much younger woman named Sheela. In order to woo her, he pretends to be a younger man.

title: The Balkan Line
description: A Russian task force, led by Andrei Shatalov, is dispatched to recapture the Slatina Air Base in Kosovo and defend it from terrorists until reinforcements arrive.

title: Aashiqui Not Allowed
description: Bittu is an ambitious man who is under debt. While in the process of earning money using incorrect methods, he comes across Billu Bakra, a criminal, but gets on his wrong side

title: Tere Mere Phere
description: Rahul and Pooja go on a drive through the Himalayas for their honeymoon, but soon begin to quarrel. However, a gun-toting local breaks into their vehicle and forces them to drive him to his wedding.

title: Trigger
description: An amateur set designer visits a dense forest to erect a set for an upcoming movie. However, he realises his mistake when he is informed of the growing tiger attacks in the forest.

title: Punjab Singh
description: Punjab Singh, a young villager, relocates to the city to make a living. But a tragic incident forces him to become a gangster with a motive of eradicating the mafia leader Lally Sarkaria.

title: Konjam Konjam
description: Konjam Konjam is an Indian Tamil-language romantic family drama film written and directed by debutant Uday Sankar and starring Priya Mohan, Gokul Krishnan, and Mersheena Neenu in prominent roles. Produced by Betty C.K and P.R.Mohan under their Mimosa Productions company

title: Hum Tum Shabana
description: Rishi and Karthik fall head over heels for Shabana, a participant in a beauty pageant. However, they are soon horrified to find out that her uncle is a dreaded gangster.

title: Samarthya Vaunshacha Diva
description: The film Samarthya is based on the issue of female feticide. It is an issue which is destroying whole country. A lot of children in India die because of female feticide. Thus the film focuses on this issue being a high level crime and leaves the audience on a message to save girl child.

title: Eka Breakup Chi Goshta
description: Starring - Anurag Dalvi, Aditi Paranje, Purva Yenpure, Amol Redij, Sunny Kambale, Aniruddh Joshi, Prajita Burud, Sujata Kalokhe, Sneha Patil & Manisha Chavhan

title: Korameenu
description: Karuna, a wealthy man, clashes with his driver Koti when they both fall in love with the same woman. Their differences soon cause disasters in their colony.

title: Paathshala
description: A group of friends nearing the end of their graduation decide to visit each other's native places. On their journey, they have adventures and spend moments that lead them towards self-discovery.

title: No Way Home
description: An ex-convict returns to the home of his youth, where a poignant friendship blossoms with the restrained wife of his temperamental and jealous brother.

title: The Name of the Rose
description: After a mysterious death in a Benedictine Abbey, the monks are convinced that the apocalypse is coming. William of Baskerville,is asked to assist in determining the cause of the untimely death.

title: The Mission
description: Jesuits build a mission station and reform a South American tribe in the jungles of Brazil. When Spain sells Brazil to Portugal, the priests and the native must work together to defend their mission.

title: Deya Neya
description: Prasanta, the son of a wealthy businessman, aspires to become a famous singer. However, when he leaves for Kolkata to fulfil his dreams, he falls in love with Sucharita

title: Rupantar
description: Debangi, a vitiligo patient, is constantly harassed due to her medical condition. Tired of being stigmatised, she decides to become a skin doctor in order to educate the villagers.

title: Ebong Kiriti
description: Detective Kiriti Roy investigates an unexpected murder during a party. Later, Roy learns that each guest has secrets of their own and tries to identify the real killer.

title: Bhalo Theko
description: Anandi lives in an extended family along with her parents, siblings and uncle and is in love with Babua, her brother's friend. However, things change drastically in her life when Babua goes abroad.

title: 3 Deewarein
description: Chandrika decides to make a documentary on the three inmates on death row. Gradually, they start reforming themselves while Chandrika, too, finds redemption in her life.

title: Bhavnao Ko Samjho
description: Himmatram disowns Sunderlal, his alcoholic son, and bequeaths everything to Suman, his grandniece. But Sunderlal tries various ways to have his name incorporated into his wealthy father's will.

title: Sankat City
description: Guru and Ganpat, two small-time thieves, steal a Mercedes car with a bag containing INR 1 crore. When Guru tries to sell the car, a customer recognises it and informs the real owner, a gangster.

title: Raajneeti
description: Samar, the son of a political family, has chosen to go to the USA to live with his girlfriend. However, the death of his father makes him put his plans on hold and enter the dirty world of politics.

title: Dongari ka Raja
description: Differences arise between Mansoor Ali, an underworld don, and his right-hand man Raja when the latter falls in love with Shruti and wants to leave the realm of crime.

title: Maatr
description: A politician's son and his friends kidnap and sexually assault a school teacher, Vidya, and her daughter, Tia. After her daughter dies in the incident, the woman decides to take revenge.

title: The 12th Man
description: Jan Baalsrud, a Norwegian resistance fighter, manages to flee after eleven of his fellow fighters are surrounded by the German forces on a beach during the World War II.

title: Yeh Faasley
description: Arunima stumbles upon some clues that point out that her father lied to her about her mother. When she becomes suspicious of him, she sets out to uncover the truth and discovers a dark secret

title: Qaidi No 420 (Veedevadu)
description: A kabbadi player is arrested for the murder of his wife on their wedding night. However, the police officer investigating the case finds other clues that lead him on a different trail.

title: Woodstock Villa
description: Jatin finds his wife Zara missing. He receives a call from her kidnappers who demand a hefty ransom of fifty lakhs. However, things are not how they seem to be.

title: Malamaal Weekly
description: Lilaram, a lottery vendor, learns that a jackpot-winning ticket was sold in his store. Chaos ensues when he discovers that the winner is missing and most likely dead.

title: Mission Mangal
description: A group of scientists at ISRO battle in their personal and professional lives and work tirelessly towards their only motive, the Mars Orbiter Mission.

title: Kaun Hai Villain (Villain)
description: An AGDP on the verge of retirement is tasked with investigating the murders of three men on his last day at work. However, his investigation gradually turns into a dangerous cat-and-mouse game.

title: Coyote Lake
description: Near the US-Mexico border, two unwanted and dangerous guests arrive at a small bed and breakfast and threaten a young woman and her overbearing mother.

title: Kansas City Confidential
description: A master criminal recruits three petty crooks to carry out a bank heist, followed by a distribution of the loot in Mexico. But Joe, their scapegoat, vows to nab the real culprits for ruining his life.

title: Dressed to Kill
description: Holmes investigates why three criminals are killing the owners of three music boxes. It is soon discovered that they are after crucial the Bank of England printing plates that are hidden in the boxes.

title: The Woman in Green
description: Dead bodies of several beautiful young women are found in the streets of London with their forefingers chopped off. Sherlock Holmes, along with Watson, decides to solve the mysterious case.

title: Enigma
description: When KGB agents are sent to the west to assassinate several Soviet dissidents, an American agent must infiltrate Soviet intelligence and obtain information from a Russian computer to stop them.

title: Wilderness Love (Personally Yours)
description: Bridget, her sister Hannah and brother Sam decide to bring their divorced parents back together.

title: The Mystery Of Her
description: After a near-fatal car accident, a popular high school student loses her memory and gets a second chance at a more meaningful life.

title: Nurses on the Line: The Crash of Flight 7
description: An aircraft crash in the jungle of Mexico leads to a frantic race for survival for the lucky souls who escape from the wreckage.

title: Point Last Seen
description: Rachel, a single mother and park ranger, is look for a young girl, who has disappeared in the desert. At the same time, her own children are kidnapped by their emotionally unstable father.

title: In a Stranger's Hand
description: A successful businessman stumbles upon a deadly mystery when he becomes a participant in a search for a missing child.

title: Love Lessons
description: Sunny (Patty Duke) and Mick (Ronny Cox) are a married couple in their 50s looking forward to retiring early and sailing around the world. They must reconsider their plans, however, when Sonya finds out she's pregnant. Unsure how to proceed, they seek advice from various friends and family members. Sonya grows more convinced she should have the baby, while Mick seems inclined to set sail. The two will soon discover if their differences are irreconcilable.

title: Turn The River
description: Kailey, a pool player and gambler, receives an opportunity to win a large sum of money. She plans to utilize this amount to take away her son, Gulley who stays with her ex-husband and move to Canada.

title: Finding Love in Big Sky Montana
description: After being denied the funding needed to refurbish her grandfather's ranch, Paisley is reintroduced to her ex-boyfriend Josh, a big-time marketing executive who decides to help come up with ideas on how to raise money for the farm.

title: Love In Aruba
description: Amber joins single father Connor overseas in Aruba to tutor and watch over his daughter, Macey, while he focuses on work

title: Rear Window
description: Jason Kemp (Christopher Reeve) is a quadriplegic who passes the time spying on his neighbors from his window. By chance he catches one of them, Julian Thorpe (Ritchie Coster), beating his wife and reports it to the police. He later becomes certain that Julian has killed her, but fails to convince his nurse or his friends of any foul play. Meanwhile, Julian has discovered that Jason is privy to his crime, and is conniving to take care of him as well

title: Lights, Camera, Romance
description: As an actress, Emma always acts like she's in love for work but knows little of what true love is. When Emma realizes she has always loved her good friend Gray, she learns how love works.

title: Heaven's Door
description: After the sudden demise of her grandfather, Riley, a young girl discovers a portal that helps her access heaven. She receives miraculous healing powers but with a heavy price.

title: The Protected Wife
description: A woman suspects that her husband has staged his own death and kidnapped their young son. As her quest to uncover the truth about her supposedly dead husband brings her head to head with government agencies, she realises that he was living a double life, and comes to believe that he is still alive.

title: Baby of the Bride
description: Four grown-up children are enough for most people. Newlyweds Margaret and John have enough problems as it is, without another baby on the way.

title: The Perfect Stranger
description: Nikki is a dejected attorney with problems in her married life. One day she receives a mysterious dinner invitation from a man who claims to be Jesus of Nazareth.

title: Love Finds You in Valentine
description: Kennedy Blaine inherits a ranch located in the small Nebraskan town of Valentine. Before selling it, she decides to spend the summer in the house and explore her family history.

title: I'm In Love with a Church Girl
description: Miles, a rich drug dealer, is smitten with Vanessa, a devout Christian woman. He vows to reform himself after marrying her, unaware that a few law-enforcement agents plan to capture him.

title: Love Finds You In Sugarcreek
description: Micah, a baseball player, and his young son flee to an Amish community to avoid the media onslaught after his wife is murdered. As they live and work there under aliases, a policewoman suspects them.

title: The War Within
description: A cartoonist struggles to gain control over his life after a war wages within his soul between Heart, Conscience, Will, Emotion, Mind and Memory.

title: Homeless for the Holidays
description: Jack Baker, a hardworking and self-made executive, lives an upper-middle-class life until he loses his job one day. To make ends meet, he starts working at a burger joint.

title: Polycarp
description: Anna is freed from slavery by a Christian family and the family priest, Polycarp, who guides her. However, she struggles to find a common path between their religion and her beliefs.

title: I Am Potential
description: A child born with no eyesight and with other disabilities fights against all odds to achieve excellence in the field of music with the help of his father.

title: Cream Of The Crop
description: A high school teacher dedicated to saving her family farm falls in love with a real estate tycoon.

title: Valley Of The Lanterns
description: An elderly woman is forced to make a big decision after her stubborn attitude towards the past puts her family's future in danger

title: The Visitor
description: The Visitor, directed by Mehmet Eryilmaz, is 2015 Turkish film. The Visitor is the second feature film of Mehmet Eryilmaz has produced “A Fairground Attraction” as well as some other dramatic documentaries.

title: Jimmy
description: Jimmy, a teenager with autism, does not always understand what he sees or hears but has a fantastic memory. His father uses his memory to free a client from jail, which triggers drastic consequence

title: Pahila Paul Jivnacha
description: A drama film directed by Sanjeev More, starring Amisha Ambekar, Suyesh Janjhunrke and Saroj Patil in the lead roles.

title: Wish You Well
description: Twelve-year-old Lou and her brother had just begun to adjust living with their great-grandmother when a coal company tries to steal their land.

title: The Good Journey
description: Two estranged brothers are sent on a cross country journey by their father in the hope that they can find common ground while offering gratitude and forgiveness to others.

title: A Horse Called Bear
description: Ethan discovers that his late mother owned a horse and he has inherited it. Traveling across the country to live with his grandparents, he finds a gentle and faithful horse named Bear.

title: The Sound of the Spirit
description: A 13-year-old Jewish girl, Rivka, overcomes her sadness over the demise of her parents to shine with the light of her Messiah before her aunt, uncle and the orthodox Jewish synagogue they attend.

title: Kho Kho
description: Maria, a physical education teacher, takes up the chance to train the school's promising girls' team in the sport of kho-kho. While doing so, she aspires to accomplish her own unfulfilled dream.

title: Bluff Master
description: Uttam, a smart con man, targets gullible people to extort money from them. However, the tables turn when he gets involved with a dangerous gang that uses him to do their bidding.

title: Wah Taj
description: Tukaram Marathe, a farmer from Maharashtra, claims that the land where the Taj Mahal stands belongs to him. He and his wife go on a hunger strike to get their voices heard.

title: Dhanak
description: After seeing a poster of Shah Rukh Khan promoting eye donation, Pari takes her brother, a person with visual impairment, to the actor's shooting venue in Rajasthan, hoping for a treatment.

title: Tum Milo Toh Sahi
description: Three couples from different generations struggle with the unrelenting demands of career, money, ambition and stress. A sprawling cafe called Lucky plays a central role in their romance and heartache.

title: Jag Jeondeyan De Mele
description: Abijot and Mitro are childhood friends and fall in love after growing up. But their family's differences come in their way and they reject their decision to marry each other.

title: Treasures of the Snow
description: A Swiss village is the setting for this story of a young boy who is ostracised for causing a tragic accident. Trying to find forgiveness, he seeks refuge with a woodcarver who teaches him to find his way to peace.

title: A Miracle on Christmas Lake
description: After the death of his friend, Bobby keeps going to the lake where they played winter hockey. Soon, he discovers a magical rink that only appears in the night.

title: Robin and Marian
description: An ageing Robin Hood returns from the Crusades after twenty years to woo and win Maid Marian one last time, but she has turned into a nun and does not fully welcome his return

title: Mayberry Man
description: An arrogant movie star is busted for speeding in a small Southern town and sentenced to attend Mayberry Fest: a weeklong festival celebrating The Andy Griffith Show. Immersed in a modern-day Mayberry, he discovers the true meaning of family.

title: Uda Aida
description: A young boy hailing from a poor family gets enrolled in a prestigious school. However, things change when his parents have to face the rich families and their children.

title: Treasure Lies
description: Tired of being overly responsible, Sean wishes to live irresponsibly for the last few weeks of high school. A sudden financial windfall could change his life, but first, he must make a tough decision.

title: Unhinged
description: Rachel gets into a small argument with the stranger on the road. But the man turns out to be mentally unstable and makes her a target of his rage, killing and injuring several people.

title: Angel And The Badman
description: When Penelope Worth, a Quaker girl, nurses Quirt Evans, a notorious gunman back to health, he reflects on his past transgressions. He then decides to learn more about her peaceful ways.

title: Gol Maal
description: Ramprasad works for Bhavani, who discourages his employees from pursuing any hobbies. Things take a hilarious turn when Bhavani catches Ramprasad at a hockey match and he lies about having a twin.

title: The Climb
description: Derrick Williams, the rising star in the world of rock climbing, is paired with Michael Harris, an exceptionally good rock climber known to take every possible safety precaution, for a rescue mission.

title: Mithya
description: A struggling actor gets caught up with a group of criminals due to his uncanny resemblance to an underworld kingpin, Raje.

title: Chal Guru Ho Jaa Shuru
description: In order to earn some quick money, a group of jobless theatre artists start posing as spiritual gurus and start conning innocent and naive people.

title: Ankhon Dekhi
description: Bauji resists his daughter's request to let her marry the man she loves as the villagers incessantly shame him. However, his opinion changes after he meets him and he decides to change his viewpoint.

title: Cinderella: Conspiracy at the Emerald Castle
description: Duke Zaral comes up with an evil plan on Cinderella and Prince Charles's wedding day. He mixes poison in the prince's drink and kidnaps Cinderella, intending to take over the kingdom.

title: Jamaica Inn
description: Mary is sent to live with her aunt and uncle in Cornwall. However, when she discovers that her uncle's property is being used as the base by a gang of ship wreckers, she starts fearing for her life.

title: We Three Kings
description: Amy, Catherine, and Charles Fay can't wait for their Uncle Henry to arrive for Christmas. This is the first year since Mama passed away and the children are working together to fill the void and put together a Christmas play at their church. There are challenges along the way, from a runaway lamb to the stern lady who plays the church organ, but with the help of Uncle Henry's new song, 'We Three Kings,' not only is the Christmas pageant a success, but the children learn truths about Jesus and the gifts that were given to Him by the Magi.

title: Cry in the Wild: The Taking of Peggy Ann
description: When Peggy Ann Bradnick, a young girl, gets kidnapped by William, the Pennsylvania police begin a massive manhunt in the history of the United States.

title: Yesterday's Children
description: A pregnant American woman starts having visions about a distant Irish town called Malahide. She decides to head to Ireland with her husband and son to find out what her visions mean.

title: The Gospel of John
description: A portrayal of the life of Jesus Christ, a first-century Jewish preacher and religious leader, as recounted by John in his Gospel, which is the fourth among the canonical gospels.

title: Let There Be Light
description: After a near-death experience, the world's most famous atheist must reinvent himself to save his family and his soul.

title: One Special Night
description: Builder Robert and doctor Catherine are brought together by fate one snowy night. Taking shelter in an empty cabin, not only do they talk and connect but bond and overcome their initial conflicts.

title: Mi Pobre Angelito
description: Home Alone (Mi Pobre Angelito) Eight-year-old Kevin is accidentally left behind when his family leaves for France. At first, he's happy to be in charge; but when thieves try to break into his home, he puts up a fight like no other.

title: A Christmas Romance
description: Snow strands a young widow (Olivia Newton-John) and her two daughters with a banker (Gregory Harrison) holding their eviction notice.

title: Santa Stole Our Dog: A Merry Doggone Christmas!
description: When Santa steals the beloved family dog, they venture out to the North Pole during the Christmas holidays to look for him and bring him back.

title: North
description: North (Elijah Wood) is a talented and bright kid, but his mom (Julia Louis-Dreyfus) and dad (Jason Alexander) are utterly preoccupied with other things in their lives, leaving him largely ignored. Advised by a mysterious man (Bruce Willis) who pops up on occasion, North decides to legally separate himself from his parents and goes on a search across the globe for the ideal mother and father. Unfortunately for the young boy, most of the people that he meets have very little potential.

title: Konrad
description: The factory tries to recall an instant 8-year-old boy (Huckleberry Fox) in a box, delivered to a woman (Polly Holliday) by mistake.

title: Life with Father
description: A strait-laced and tyrannical stockbroker tries to bend his family to his rules but find that they insist on ignoring him until he begins to change his own ways.

title: The Little Princess
description: Sara Crewe, a rich girl, grows up in a boarding while her father is out at war. However, one day she gets news that he has passed away, but she doesn't lose hope and believes her father will return.

title: Chasing the Star
description: Three Magi priests traverse the desert in harsh conditions only to meet the newly born King and undergo several hardships in the process.

title: Mister Scrooge to See You
description: Ebenezer Scrooge embarks on a journey filled with adventures and explores the life Timothy Cratchit the VI.

title: Heaven Is Waiting
description: Ned is unable to forget his wife, Kate, who died years ago due to cancer. However, his daughter, Liz, tries to divert his attention towards Carol, their neighbour.

title: The Cascadia Treasure
description: Hoping to save her family's land, a spunky teen embarks on a daring quest to find long-lost treasure in an abandoned mine.

title: The Wild Stallion
description: CJ befriends Hanna, who visits her ranch to take photographs of wild horses for her school project. Soon, the two uncover a plot that endangers horses and set out to stop it.

title: The Whole Wide World
description: Novalyne meets Robert and they begin a relationship. However, he is disheartened when she accepts the affections of another man after he spends his time with work and his ailing mother.

title: The Fourth Wise Man
description: A young Magus wants to bring three precious jewels to the baby Messiah, but misses the caravan of the three other wise men

title: Unlikely Angel
description: St Peter challenges selfish Ruby with reuniting the Bartilsons in exchange for her angel-wings. After her return to Earth, she tries to help the grieving family in the guise of a governess.

title: Homestate
description: A down and out brother shows up at his sister's house unannounced, forcing her family to change their routines for him and leading to a series of events that reveal underlying tensions and threaten family cohesion.

title: The Other Side of Hell
description: A patient at a mental institution begins seeing other patients gets abused by the guards so he decides to escape; however, that's easier said than done.

title: Riding on Faith
description: A shattered man, haunted by the loss of his wife and young daughter, finds himself trapped in the grief. When a charismatic new pastor arrives in town, an unexpected friendship takes root, offering the possibility of hope and healing.

title: Heidi
description: The story revolves around a poor old man who travels to the town in search of his beloved granddaughter who is forced to work as a servant there.

title: My Teacher's Wife
description: A high school student enlists the help of an attractive maths tutor to improve his grades. Later, he realises that she is the wife of his obnoxious maths teacher.

title: Wild Prairie Rose
description: After returning home to care for her ailing mother, a woman faces censure over her burgeoning romance with a deaf man.

title: EK The Power Of One
description: Nandu, an assassin who is wrongly accused of murdering a powerful politician, is on the run from the police while CBI Inspector Rane is tasked to nab him.

title: Zinda
description: After being held imprisoned in a room for 14 years, Balajeet Roy is suddenly released. Thereafter, he goes on a quest to look for the people who wronged him.

title: Gang
description: Four friends get together to start their career in crime and extortion and they succeed. However, things take a turn when one of them is arrested and sentenced for five years.

title: Necessary Parties
description: A teen (Mark-Paul Gosselaar) throws a wrench in his parents' divorce by having a lawyer/auto mechanic (Alan Arkin) take them to court.

title: Heroes
description: Two students embark on a trip to film a documentary focussing on why one must not join the Indian Armed Forces. However, by the end of their project, their perspective goes through a paradigm shift.

title: Gallows Road
description: When Bob Collins is devastated because of a crime, he approaches his brother to reconnect him with God but they are interrupted by a bully. They go to Frank to help them seek God's forgiveness.

title: Maqbool
description: Maqbool, an underworld don's henchman, falls in love with his boss's mistress, Nimmi, who instigates him to kill the don and become the next leader.

title: Salaar: Part 1 – Ceasefire
description: A gang leader makes a promise to a dying friend by taking on other criminal gangs.

title: Tahaan
description: A local moneylender takes away an eight-year-old boy's pet donkey in lieu of an unpaid loan. When the boy goes to retrieve it, he meets a terrorist who gives him a grenade to fulfil a task.

title: The Perfect Nanny
description: After being released from a mental hospital, Andrea takes a job as a nanny to look after the kid of a good looking widower. She plans to be his wife someday and kills anyone who stands in the way.

title: Ek Hasina Thi
description: Sarika falls in love with Karan, a mysterious man who frames her for carrying illegal firearms. However, in jail, she transforms into a vindictive woman and sets out to avenge the wrongs done to her.

title: Ek Aur Ek Gyarah
description: Tara and Sitara, two thieves, take shelter in Major Ram Singh's house. They are forced to deceive him when Cobra, a gangster, kidnaps their mother to get his brother, Panther, released from prison.

title: A Murder of Innocence
description: A new pastor learns how important it is to provide stability, healing, and hope after a double homicide shakes his community to its core.

title: Pashbandh
description: A woman is tormented by her husband and ill-treated by her children. Her husband has an affair and even beats her. She silently bears all her sorrows.

title: A Clean Kill
description: Unmarried film editor Katie Griffin (Roxana Zal) meets married suspense writer Richard Mannhart (Perry King) when he saves her during a convenience store robbery. During the confusion, they exchange an erotically charged moment that leads to a rapturous affair. Mannhart promises to leave his wife, Laura (Susan Blakely), but procrastinates right up to the moment that his wife's car is involved in a suspicious accident. When the adulterous couple is accused of murder, they turn on each other.

title: Atrocity
description: Rishabh and Sai are in love but when a politician's son, Manish, becomes obsessed with Sai, the duo's relationship becomes the target of the ugly game of politics.

title: Dead Man Rising
description: After contemplating the horrors of previous executions using new experimental drugs, a death row inmate searching for information on how to best face his upcoming demise finds himself evolving into a stalwart Christian.

title: Legend of the Muse
description: A painter's life is forever changed when a mythical and deadly spirit from Celtic lore becomes his muse and lover.

title: A Mother's Revenge (Desperate Justice)
description: Carol lives happily with her family. Things change when her younger daughter is brutally raped and goes into a comatose state. During the case's trial, Carol kills her daughter's rapist with a gun.

title: Cries Unheard: The Donna Yaklich Story
description: Donna Yaklich marries Dennis, a policeman, and finally feels she has found herself a perfect partner. Her life begins to fall apart when Dennis becomes abusive and she cannot handle it any more.

title: Deadly Whispers
description: Distraught after their daughter's murder, the relationship of Tom and Carol is further afflicted when Tom becomes the prime suspect.

title: Dream Killer
description: An up-and-coming teenage singer is falsely accused of murdering her producer and her mother must find out the truth before her daughter is sent to prison.

title: Lady Killer
description: The story of a woman trapped in a stale marriage who has a brief affair with an attractive younger man. However, when she ends the affair, her lover becomes a violent, vengeful monster.

title: Night of the Living Dead
description: A group of unsuspecting people get trapped in an old farmhouse after the dead unexpectedly rise from the grave and seek the living as food.

title: Notorious
description: This movie features a German expatriate, who sets out on a mission to spy on a group of Nazis.

title: Introspectum Motel
description: Two strangers head down a dark and twisted path as they uncover their hidden connection; together, they are forced to confront their choices, their shared history, and ultimately their humanity.

title: Fair Play | Everything Comes With a Price
description: Freedom tries to keep her relationship with her boyfriend, Malcolm, together despite his weakness for other women. Meanwhile, her sister, Sasha, must stop her gold-digging ways after she begins dating a married man.

title: Instinct to Kill
description: A woman trains with a former mercenary in order to protect herself from her violent husband.

title: A Dangerous Man
description: After years in special ops and wrongful imprisonment, a witness to the murder of a Chinese cop agrees to retrieve a kidnapped girl and a bag of money.

title: He Belongs To Me
description: An over-protective mother will do anything to protect her son even if it means taking a life.

title: Passionate Betrayals
description: Two wealthy wives forge a pact to murder each other's husbands on a weekend getaway, but things go sideways when their sinister plot is uncovered.

title: Unfair Exchange
description: A love story about a book author whose publishing deal is in trouble and does the unthinkable to save his career even if it may cause him to lose his marriage.

title: Deceitful Passions
description: Vito, a young and handsome man, must choose between love and lust when faced with losing everything, including his own life.

title: The House Guest
description: A young married couple allows a female friend move into their home; this house guest, whom the wife has not seen in years, begins seducing everyone around her and people start dying.

title: The Psychic
description: A psychic reads a woman's future, but when the woman doesn't listen, things begin to get ugly, with their lives taking a difficult turn.

title: Dilemma
description: A happy couple's marriage plans get derailed when David reunites with a lost love from the past.

title: Monogamish
description: Zane is living the American dream: a perfect NFL husband, a nice house and a growing business; until the day her husband presents her with a request: he wants to be polyamorous.

title: Forbidden Fruit: First Bite
description: Poker player Ronnie makes a bet with his friend Karey that he can sleep with a popular girl from campus before her. However, things don't go as plan for either of them as the game of Forbidden Fruit doesn't play out as expected.

title: Deceitful Tendencies
description: A happily-married man ends up getting more than he bargained for when he helps a young woman who appears to be having car trouble.

title: Get My Gun
description: After a traumatic assault leaves Amanda pregnant and out of a job, she finds herself on the verge of motherhood and the target of a psychotic stalker who will stop at nothing to get their hands on her unborn child.

title: 10 Eyes
description: A film following a young woman's struggle to find love and sanity after suffering from an abusive childhood and battling mental illness.

title: Induced
description: An expectant couple heads to a remote cabin to have a natural childbirth, but comes under attack from a predatory midwife who will stop at nothing to snatch their unborn child from them.

title: Behind Closed Doors
description: A college freshman begins a romance with a seemingly charming grad student, but he soon starts to show a different side.

title: If You Think You're Lonely Now
description: Everything changes for Angel, a lonely single woman working from home, when she meets and falls in love with a man she will soon come to fear.

title: Imprisoned by Love
description: Tracie, a devoted wife and mother, lives in fear of her abusive husband. She struggles to make a decision to stay for the sake of her children or leave to save herself.

title: True or False
description: Cora Patterson's life is upended when the demons of her past return to wreak havoc on her newfound happiness.

title: No Ordinary Love
description: In No Ordinary Love, vulnerability and strength prove vital to a resilient woman who finds herself in a dangerous situation with her police officer husband. When she exposes his secret to her pastor’s wife, the two women’s lives intersect with shocking results.

title: The Invite
description: Selena trains the weak and vulnerable to defend themselves from the predators that lurk in the shadows. She never imagined that she would have to become one of those very same predators in hopes of saving her husband from a terminal illness.

title: Heaven's Revenge
description: After a professional wrestler breaks her heart, Heaven Bailey vows to make him pay.

title: Wall of Secrets
description: Thrown away at birth, Monica moves in to the Safe-Haven Home, where her stay soon becomes a nightmare.

title: Fixation
description: Husbands have their secrets, but Katherine never suspected what she now fears is true:  the man sleeping beside her is a serial killer

title: Death of a Cheerleader
description: Angela is devastated to be rejected by Stacy, the most popular girl in her school. However, things get worse for her when Stacy gets stabbed and the investigators keep interrogating her.

title: The Killing Secret
description: Kerry Evans is a budding young lawyer who has an important case to work on. During the process, she ends up unearthing some alarming information on her family and her employer

title: The Conspiracy
description: Two young filmmakers select a crazed conspiracy theorist as the subject for their next project, but they soon come to believe that the man isn't as delusional as they originally thought.

title: Rapture
description: After an apocalyptic event, a group has to make a perilous journey to safety.

title: Arctic Void
description: When the power mysteriously fails and almost everyone vanishes from a small tourist vessel in the Arctic, fear becomes the master for the three who remain. Forced ashore, the men deteriorate in body and mind until a dark truth emerges.

title: Solar Impact
description: When solar debris triggers a chain of dramatically tragic events on Earth, a group of friends must find a way to save themselves.

title: American Apocalypse
description: Members of a family struggle to stay alive in the wake of a deadly and catastrophic virus that's brought America to its knees.

title: Lockdown: 2025
description: When martial law is declared, a family seeks shelter in the safety of its own home during a nationwide lockdown for a highly contagious virus.

title: White Sky
description: Chased deep into the forest, survivors of an alien insurrection battle altered humans who want to assimilate them.

title: COVID-21: Lethal Virus
description: A female scientist, along with two members of the special forces, attempts to reach the laboratory to create a cure for the ancient rabies virus that gets released due to climate change.

title: Meteor: First Impact
description: A scientist races the clock in an attempt to save Earth from a series of deadly meteor attacks.

title: E.M.P. 333 Days
description: After an E.M.P. (Electro Magnetic Pulse) weapon is deployed, North America is forced to live in pre industrial conditions. Anything electrical is useless, sending the country into anarchy. An introverted 11 year old girl must fend and fight for herself while trying to find her father.

title: Divination
description: A couple who are expecting their first child are ecstatic but, when the husband is tormented by horrific visions, a spiritual battle begins

title: The Virus
description: A group of film students catch a virus, created years ago at a secret facility they're visiting, and have to find a antidode before it is too late

title: CO2
description: A mysterious deadly vapor suffocates a small American coal town. Based on actual events from around the world, CO2 follows a determined group of survivors as they attempt to survive and escape.

title: Myth: Bigfoot Hunters
description: A band of park rangers discover they're not alone when they encounter the legendary bigfoot while searching for two missing people in the forest.

title: Mega Lightning
description: After a violent thunderstorm scares a house party, the guests flee to a nearby home for shelter, only to discover a more sinister hand is at play. Now, they can't escape the stranger's home due to the thunderstorm, but they can't stay inside.

title: Earthrise
description: Humanity now lives on Mars and each year a small number are sent back to Earth aid in its rehabilitation. Following the journey of three individuals as they go home for the first time.

title: The Omega Code
description: Two men on different missions collide as they seek to obtain the ancient codes hidden within the Torah. One man's quest for the truth stands in the way of another man's lust for power.

title: The Tunnel
description: A film crew learns of a government cover-up about the abandoned train tunnels beneath the heart of Sydney, and decides to go inside to try to find the truth. Very quickly the group begins to realise that perhaps the cover-up was for a good reason.

title: Freshman Fall (She Cried No)
description: Melissa, a college freshman, gets invited to a fraternity party along with her friends. However, things take a turn for the worse when she is date-raped by Scott.

title: The Man In 3B
description: A charismatic new tenant quickly makes his mark on a Queens apartment building, but his popularity soon results in a murder with many suspects.

title: Unsheltered
description: In 2017, five college students set out to escape the path of Mother Nature. When things take a turn, they have to seek shelter and are never seen alive again.

title: Double Mommy
description: Jess, a young student, gets raped by her boyfriend's best friend Brent. However, things get worse for her when she realises that she is pregnant with twins.

title: M.O.M. Mothers of Monsters
description: A distraught woman suspects her teenage son is plotting a school shooting, but when he slips through the cracks of the system, she must take matters into her own hands.

title: El hijo del pueblo
description: Película mexicana del año 1974 interpretada por el canta- autor y actor Vicente Fernández, dirigida por René Cardona

title: Escuela De Vagabundos
description: El vago Luis Alberto llega a la mansión de los Valverde en busca de un teléfono y termina contratado como chófer por doña Emilia, quien tiene la manía de proteger a los vagabundos. Luis Alberto conoce a las hijas del matrimonio: la bella y altiva Susi y la joven y alegre Lala. En poco tiempo, José Antonio se enamora de Susi, quien lo considera un patán... muy atractivo.

title: Chandler Christmas Getaway
description: The Chandlers pack up and head to a cabin for maximum holiday fun. With old feuds, new feuds, and a heap of holiday stress, the Chandler family must pull together to make this the best Christmas ever.

title: El cuatrero
description: El tramposo Álvaro y su cómplice Mariana engañan al poderoso ranchero Lázaro robándole una camioneta y un valioso caballo. Un veterinario delata el escondite de los estafadores y Lázaro llega hasta ellos....

title: Ni Chana, Ni Juana
description: La vendedora ambulante Juana, amiga del vendedor de camotes Rosalío, busca a su madre Pilar y a su gemela, Emilia, que llegaron a la capital cuando ella tenía tres años. Su madre reniega de Juana por que es indígena y su hermana es la cantante española Piquito de oro. Con ayuda de Rosalío, Juana entra en los foros de cine donde ellas trabajan, pero falla en todos sus intentos de hablarles allí y en otros lugares.

title: Los hijos de María Morales
description: Dos hermanos (Pedro Infante y Antonio Badú); parranderos, jugadores y mujeriegos; se pasan la vida de feria en feria; timando a la gente y enamorando a cuantas mujeres se les cruzan por el camino. Un buen día el amor les tender una trampa; y los famosos Morales queriendo ser gavilanes, fueron palomas.

title: Grow House
description: Two stoners who are overwhelmed with debt decide to break into the medical marijuana business. However, they need to learn how to grow it since they're already experts at smoking it.

title: Amor y Frijoles
description: Karen sospecha que su esposo llega tarde a casa, lo que la lleva a un mundo impulsivo y desesperado por descubrir la verdad. Con la influencia de su amiga Nicole, buscan los secretos de Dionisio en esta historia típica de Honduras.Amor y Frijoles muestra la vida y el amor de dos mujeres en Centroamérica.

title: Buffed Up
description: Three friends go through extreme heights to acquire a pair of one of Detroit's hottest accessories: Cartier Buffalo Tusk Glasses.

title: Christmas With The Carters
description: When their Christmas gift budget is destroyed by the theft of an expensive watch, a family must band together to find it and steal it back by surviving the most chaotic Christmas Eve of their lives.

title: ¡El que no corre... vuela!
description: Toda clase de abusos y atropellos sufre la india María en la gran ciudad, sin embargo, ella convierte todo problema en risas y alegría

title: Jingle Bell Ranch
description: Divorced and penniless, a high-powered CEO embarks on a journey with her offbeat assistant to save her grandma's failing ranch before Christmas.

title: La Criada Bien Criada
description: Inocencia es una provinciana que llega a la capital en busca de trabajo y se encuentra con un montòn de aventuras divertidas y personajes pintorescos.

title: Un macho de mujer
description: La divertida historia de una joven pareja dominicana y la influencia del machismo en la cultura de su país caribeño.

title: El camino de los espantos
description: Un grupo de personas, entre las cuales se encuentran los famosos Viruta y Capulina, se dirigen en tren a la ciudad, en el trascurso del camino una tormenta interrumpe su viaje y deberán tomar un camino que se encuentra hechizado.

title: Carabina 30 - 30
description: Carabina 30-30 es una película mexicana filmada en 1958 dirigida por Miguel Delgado.

title: Chicas De Hoy
description: Una profesora criticada por su estilo de vida demuestra a sus alumnos que puede cambiar su futuro.

title: Allá en el Rancho Grande
description: Jorge Negrete en este clásico del cine Mexicano presenta la manera de ser del pueblo, su lucha y el orgullo que siente por su país.

title: la Nana
description: Raquel (Catalina Saavedra), empleada doméstica por más de dos décadas de los Valdés, sufre mareos por la exposición a productos químicos. La señora Valdés (Claudia Celedón) contrata ayuda, desatando la desesperación de Raquel. Resentida, inicia un ataque contra cada nuevo empleado.

title: El Limpiapiscinas
description: Gustav Ortiz, un estudiante universitario, se ve obligado a aceptar un trabajo de verano limpiando piscinas. Al principio odia su trabajo, pero pronto se da cuenta de que le permite acercarse a la chica que ama.

title: Un amor de película
description: Bernardo es un productor de cine cercano a la bancarrota que decide convencer erróneamente a un famoso director de cine de hacer una mala película para poder ganar mucho dinero. Laura, su novia y agente, se convierte en su confidente y musa.

title: American Visa
description: Un profesor boliviano se ve involucrado en serios crímenes tras haber sido negada su entrada a los Estados Unidos.

title: A Christmas Blessing
description: Grandma Grace fakes an illness during the Christmas holiday as a ruse to set up her granddaughter and employee to fall in love with each other.

title: Christmas In Carolina
description: Career-minded Elle nurtures a distaste for Christmas. So, she finds herself in trouble when her boyfriend, Wesley, invites her to spend the holiday in South Carolina with his family.

title: Snow
description: Christmas is nearing and Santa appears in San Ernesto, California, as Nick Snowden, to find his young reindeer who is inadvertently captured in a zoo.

title: Alla en la plaza Garibaldi
description: Un niño huérfano hace autostop hasta la Ciudad de México para buscar a un miembro de su familia y se une a una banda de carteristas juveniles

title: Stalag 17

title: Marry Us for Christmas

title: A New Husband for Christmas

title: Wedding Swingers
description: A TV producer invites his old college friends to a destination wedding.

title: The Wedding Party
description: As their big day arrives, a couple's lavish wedding plans turn into a nightmare that includes exes, fighting parents and uninvited guests.

title: The Perfect Mate
description: Hope, a control freak and a perfectionist, knows nothing would please her more than bringing the perfect future husband home for the weekend to meet her family.

title: A Lot Like Christmas
description: After not seeing his family for over seven years, PJ gets talked into going home for Christmas by his co-workers; when he arrives, he reconnects with his high school sweetheart, Rebecca.

Hoping to rebuild their father's restaurant, the sisters create weekend holiday single mixers that include great food, dancing and unexpected romance.

description: Stars: Jessy Abdo, Ziad Bourji, George Diab

title: عسل إسود
description: Molasses

description: Ramadan Mabrouk Abul-Alamein Hamouda رمضان مبروك، مدرس لغة عربية، ينتقل إلى خارج البلاد للعمل في إحدى المدارس الخاصة. يواجه مواقف محرجة بسبب الطلاب المتميزين الذين يدرسهم.

title: EL ÚLTIMO BESO DEL KÁISER

title: Titanic (1943)

Angesichts der zu hohen Ausgaben für den Bau des größten Luxusschiffs der Welt plant Sir Bruce Ismay (E. F. Fürbringer), Geschäftsführer der White Star Line, die Richtung des sinkenden Aktienwerts seines Unternehmens umzukehren. An Bord der Titanic kämpft der mutige deutsche 1. Offizier Petersen (Hans Nielsen) darum, seine selbstgefälligen britischen Vorgesetzten davon zu überzeugen, die Schiffsmotoren nicht zu überanstrengen.

Seryozha Aleshkov perdió a su familia, fue rescatado por un regimiento del ejército y participó en batallas. El pequeño soldado recibió la Medalla al Mérito Militar. Éste drama de guerra entrelaza los sentimientos de tragedia y amor, el peligro y la esperanza, la amargura de la separación y la alegría de pertenecer.

title: Sirona
description: A young woman with supernatural gifts escapes captivity, only to be hunted down by a group of mercenaries whose lives she will change forever.

La situación se torna violenta y las armas hacen su aparición. una historia muy intensa y llena de drama.

title: El Basukazo 3

EL BAZUKAZO en esta ocasión con las actuaciones estelares de Max Hernandez Jr. Amador Granados el Alacran, Oscar Lopez y la actuación especial de Fabian Lopez. una historia que no te puedes perder

description: Al sufrir un atentado su familia, Luis es adoptado por un capo de la mafia. con el tiempo se convierte en un medico pues no tiene intenciones de dedicarse a la mafia, pero el destino ya estaba escrito para el

description: Fue abandonado siendo un niño por sus propios padres, su escuela fue la calle y para sobrevivir tuvo que unirse al crimen organizado. No te pierdas la película mas esperada de este año.

description: Four women working in the drug business meet in the streets.

description: A woman unknowingly enters into a relationship with the man who was responsible for the death of the love of her life.

Waking up in the hospital and held captive by armed agents, he escapes and encounters a woman who seemingly knows of a larger conspiracy involving alien abductions and the creation of human hybrids.

description: A female sniper on military leave vows to fulfill her fiance's dying wish until an alien invasion.

description: Haley escapes her small-town and builds a life in Los Angeles as a wedding planner. When her sister asks her to plan her wedding, Haley returns to her childhood town and reunites with a childhood flame.

title: Hometown Holiday
description: Krista decides to be selective about her relationships. But when she meets Ryan and they develop feelings for each other, she finds herself taking some tough decisions.

title: Christmas Lucky Charm
description: Every boyfriend Jessica has had found the love of his life right after he dated her. Just as Jessica leans into her unlucky love life and swears off dating for the Christmas season, a handsome gallery owner moves in across the street.

title: أيام السادات
description: The Days of Sadat ينشأ أنور السادات من خلفية متواضعة ويتغلب على العقبات ليصبح ملازمًا بالجيش وبعد ذلك الرئيس الثالث لمصر.

title: حسن ومرقص
description: Hassan and Morcos يتم وضع رجل دين مسيحي تحت الحماية ويطلق عليه اسم حسن لحمايته من المتطرفين. يلتقي بمرقص، رجل الدين المسلم في نفس الظروف، وتشكل بينهما صداقة.

title: كده رضا
description: Can't Complain الإخوة الثلاثة المتطابقون، الذين أطلق عليهم اسم رضا من قبل والدهم، الذي كان محتالًا، يكبرون ويطورون شخصيات مختلفة. يواجهون مشكلة عندما يقع الثلاثة في حب نفس المرأة نادية.

title: ألف مبروك
description: Congratulations يواجه أحمد العديد من العقبات في يوم زفافه قبل أن يستسلم للموت عند منتصف الليل. يشعر بالذعر بعد الاستيقاظ في الصباح لأنه يدرك أنه عالق في حلقة زمنية ويعيش ذلك اليوم من جديد.

title: الباشا
description: The Student Cop يتم تكليف بسيوني، ضابط شرطة، بمهمة اختراق مجموعة من الطلاب للكشف عن منظمة لتهريب المخدرات تقوم بتوزيع المخدرات في إحدى الجامعات الخاصة.

title: Runaway Romance (Fugue Sentimentale)
description: Ann Stanway leaves Hollywood for the countryside where she discovers friendship, love and ultimately herself. However, she has to make a choice between staying on or returning to her old life.

title: Perfect Messy Holiday
description: After losing her job and her boyfriend, an aspiring romance novelist moves from her London flat to a beach house on the Sunshine Coast, where she discovers that love can be both perfect and messy.

title: From The Heart (2020)
description: Kathy Yoder has left her Amish ways and is a successful travel guide writer. When Kathy goes home to settle her dad's affairs, she's reminded of her life before she left the Amish community, including her old love, Isaac. Will Kathy decide to stay or return to her traveling lifestyle?

title: North Face
description: Toni und sein Freund Andi treten aus der Armee aus, um an einem von den Nazis organisierten Bergsteigerwettbewerb teilzunehmen. Sie beginnen ihren mutigen Aufstieg zur Eroberung des Eigergipfels durch die Nordwand.

title: Die Welle
description: The Wave - Das ungewöhnliche Experiment eines High-School-Lehrers, seinen Schülern zu zeigen, wie das Leben unter einer Autokratie aussieht, gerät schrecklich außer Kontrolle, als er eine soziale Einheit mit einem ausgeprägten Eigenleben schmiedet.

title: Coffee Shop
description: Donavan is distraught when her boyfriend leaves her and her coffee shop is in danger of repossession. However, things take a turn when Ben enters her life.

title: Enchanted Christmas
description: Interior designer Laura is sent to her hometown of Sante Fe, N.M., to remodel a landmark hotel in time for a Christmas Eve benefit dance performance. As Laura dives into the renovations, she discovers that a former love is the star of the benefit.

title: For The Love of Christmas
description: A once-loving woman loses touch with peace, love and the gift of giving. When a homeless family appears on her doorstep, her heart becomes reacquainted with the true meaning of Christmas

title: My Perfect Romance
