description: Newly appointed CEO of Robinson Tech, Wes Robinson, is looking for new ideas to boost the company's sales. Vivian Blair, a programme developer, shares a dating algorithm she has been working on called My Perfect Match.

title: A Fall City Christmas
description: Upon returning to his hometown in Washington, a parolee meets a single mother unexpectedly. Soon, he finds happiness in her company and assumes the role of father for her daughter.

title: Kokowääh
description: Henry, ein Drehbuchautor, arbeitet an der Adaption eines berühmten Bestseller-Romans. Die Dinge ändern sich, als er herausfindet, dass er aus einer One-Night-Affäre in Stockholm eine achtjährige Tochter hat

title: Barefoot (Barfuss)
description: Nick Keller, Hausmeister in einer Nervenheilanstalt, rettet Leila, eine besorgte Frau, vor dem Selbstmord. Allmählich kommen sich die beiden näher und verlieben sich.

title: Das Wunder Von Bern
description: The Miracle of Bern- 1954 kehrt Richard (Peter Lohmeyer) nach sieben Jahren Kriegsgefangenschaft in seine deutsche Heimatstadt zurück. Die Jahre haben ihren Tribut gefordert und er hat kein Verständnis für seine Familie – insbesondere für seinen fußballbegeisterten Sohn Matthias (Louis Klamroth). Unterdessen reisen ein Journalist (Lukas Gregorowicz) und seine Frau nach Bern in der Schweiz, um über die Weltmeisterschaft zu schreiben. Die Geschichten dieser Fremden laufen zusammen, als sie in Bern ankommen, wo sie Zeuge einer positiven deutschen Leistung in einem Spiel gegen Ungarn werden.

title: Sophie Scholl: The Final Days
description: Basierend auf einer wahren Geschichte ist Sophie Scholl eine Studentin in München im Jahr 1943, die zusammen mit ihrem Bruder Hans Mitglied der Antikriegsbewegung Weiße Rose ist. Sie wird verhaftet, weil sie Anti-Nazi-Flugblätter verteilt hat. Sie wird von den damals drakonischen Justizgesetzen des Regimes verurteilt und ebenso wie ihr Bruder und Christoph Probst zum Tode durch die Guillotine verurteilt.

title: Chiko
description: Chiko ist ein deutscher Film aus dem Jahr 2008, der von Özgür Yıldırım geschrieben und inszeniert wurde.

title: Running On Empty Dreams
description: A woman's idyllic married life is shattered when she meets a single mother and falls in love. She is faced with the decision of staying with her loving husband or choosing the forbidden love that she craves.

title: It's Christmas Again
description: Jake Young wants to spend his vacation with his girlfriend Abbey Walker, but she's already volunteered for her church's Christmas play. After a skateboarding accident, Jake is transported back in time to Bethlehem on the night Jesus is born and discovers the true meaning of Christmas

title: Charade
description: Regina finds herself followed and harassed by three men who are linked to the death of her husband, Charles. She seeks help from a charming stranger named Peter but gets embroiled in a world of lies.

title: The Feels
description: Andi and Lu are excited to celebrate their upcoming wedding with a joint bachelorette weekend in wine country. On the first night, things get off to a rocky start when one of the brides admits that she's never had an orgasm.

title: Where We Started
description: They know they should not even consider it, but when two unhappily married people find themselves flirting and then developing feelings for one another, they consider risking it all for a forbidden romance.

title: Regresa
description: Regresa es una película de comedia romántica mexicana de 2010 dirigida por Alejandro González Padilla y protagonizada por Jaime Camil y Blanca Soto. Ganó el premio a la mejor película en el Festival de Cine Benéfico de Mónaco de 2010.

title: اللمبي 8 جيجا
description: Ellembi 8 Gega اللمبي، محامٍ فقير، يتزوج نوجا، وهي معلمة فقيرة، ويعيش كلاهما تعيسًا في حياتهما المليئة بالفقر. ولاحقًا يتعرض اللمبي لحادث يغير حياته.

title: بنك الحاز
description: Bank Alhaz بعد طرده من وظيفته، ينضم موظف في البنك إلى زميل سابق في العمل وأحد ألعاب الفيديو للتخطيط لعملية سطو ستحقق كل أحلامهم.

title: ح دبور
description: H Dabbour هيثم دبور ينحدر من عائلة ثرية. عندما يُسجن والده بعد اتهامه زورًا، يقرر إثبات براءة والده

title: أل فرح
description: Al Farah تنظم زينهم حفلات زفاف وهمية لكسب المال من أجل شراء حافلة. تعمل الخطة بشكل مثالي، لكن كل شيء يأخذ منعطفًا عندما تموت والدته خلال إحدى الاحتفالات المزيفة.

title: غش إل زوجية
description: Ghesh El Zawgeya حازم، زير نساء، يجبره والده على الزواج على افتراض أنه سيتغير. تأخذ حياته منعطفاً آخر عندما يلتقي بزوجته التي ستصبح قريباً.

title: More Than Friends
description: Growing up through the years, a woman comes to understand that her close female friend is deeply in love with her.

title: Fire Island
description: A modern take on The Wizard of Oz about a young woman trying to find her way home after tragedy. Mimi's life has flipped upside down. She's gone from happy wife to heartbroken widow and mixed-up mistress, while only in her early thirties. She's determined to find her way back to a happy life. Mimi's journey kicks off on Fire Island.

title: Until We Meet Again
description: For thirty-five years the ghost of Eddie Conway, a passionate young pianist, has haunted an old house in the Hollywood Hills, unable to move on without completing his piano concer.

title: Perfect People
description: After many years of marriage Ken and Barbara decide to change their way of living radically. In order to become more attractive they submit themselves not only under modern diets and physical education but also try plastic surgery.

title: Heavenquest : A Pilgrim's Progress
description: A man is arrested and begins having visions of a woman in white.

title: Cyborg X
description: A group of people needs to save planet Earth after a cyber virus attacks a manufacturing company, which ends up creating an army of machines that wreaks havoc around them.

title: Once Upon a Time in the Apocalypse
description: In the near future of the Wild West, a civil war has ravaged the U.S., leaving countless dead and the rest living in lawlessness.

title: Journey to Promethea
description: A boy leads his people against a tyrannical king and takes them to a promised land.

title: Lost at War
description: Five soldiers who are out on a mission find themselves stuck in a foxhole in an apparently deserted camp.

title: The Man From Earth
description: When a retiring professor reveals to his colleagues that he is thousands of years old, they decide to ask him questions related to their respective fields to find out if he is telling the truth.

title: Jules Verne's Mysterious Island
description: After their failed escape attempt, five prisoners of war find themselves stranded on an island with other survivors. Together, they must battle all odds and escape unscathed before it's too late.

title: A Christmas Carol
description: Ebenezer Scrooge, a spiteful and miserly man, encounters three spirits on Christmas Eve who show him the folly of his ways.

title: The Stepford Wives
description: Joanna, a young woman, moves to a suburban town with her husband and two children. As she tries to settle into her new surroundings, she stumbles upon a sinister conspiracy that terrifies her.

title: Wild Witch
description: Twelve-year-old Clara is scratched by a mysterious cat and starts to develop strange powers, leading her to discover that she is from a family of wild witches.

title: Escape 2120
description: A detached teenage orphan escapes to the future in suspended animation, but when he arrives at a natural utopia, he must evade a lynch mob convinced that he's the prophesied devil's child.

title: Deathstalker
description: A medieval sword fighter tries to free a princess from a wizard's castle by battling ancient creatures and attempting to retrieve an amulet.

title: The Conspiracy of Dark Falls
description: Nicholas Thorn is about to discover why people who ask too many questions in the town of Dark Falls. Together with agent Alex Fletcher, the two embark on a mysterious journey to unravel the conspiracy that has taken over the town.

title: First Signal
description: When Air Force Space Command receives a signal from an alien satellite in Earth's orbit, a government conspiracy is uncovered.

title: Alien Shark
description: When Aleesha's friends throw her a military deployment party on an island, a meteor crashes into the dunes and a massive alien shark targets the beach. Now, Aleesha must fight back to save them and the planet from this predator beyond the stars.

title: Santa Claus
description: The devil wants to prevent Santa from making the children of the world happy. Merlin the magician helps Santa save the world from his evil plans.

title: Portal Runner
description: An evil force pursues a 15-year-old boy after he discovers a secret family legacy and a portal that enables him to travel to parallel worlds.

title: The 5th Dimension
description: Two graduate student physicists run out of time to prove their theory on time travel.

title: The Hideous Sun Demon
description: When a scientist is accidentally exposed to radiation, he finds himself morphing into a deadly, lizard-like creature every time he is out in the sun.

title: Alchemy of the Spirit
description: American artist Oliver Black wakes up to discover that his wife has died in their bed overnight.

title: Chilbolton Incident
description: In 1974, NASA sent a message into deep space, containing information about humanity and earth. 27 years later a response appears in Chilbolton, England. Is it a ingeniously sophisticated joke, or is it something else?

title: Skyquake
description: When reports of strange sounds emanating from the sky flood social media, Adam (Sandy Robson), a recluse, believes that whatever is causing the noise has followed him home.

title: The Hollow World
description: When the solar system is attacked by an overwhelming alien force, astronaut Xander returns to a looted Earth to search for what matters most.

title: Forward
description: After building an experimental machine, an out of work computer engineer must choose to live in a loveless marriage or risk everything by using a machine to spend time with ghosts from the past.

title: Project Metalbeast
description: A bloodthirsty werewolf becomes nearly indestructible after a government scientist uses it to test a metal-based skin.

title: Paradox
description: After travelling sixty minutes through time, a scientist returns to warn his colleagues to shut down the secret project or die within the hour.

title: Blue Monkey (Insect)
description: Detective Jim Bishop and Dr. Rachel Carson must find a way to stop a giant murderous insect that is eating people alive before it procreates and spreads a deadly infection.

title: Aliens: Zone of Silence
description: After her brother vanishes from the Mexican desert, a young woman sets out to uncover the truth about his disappearance. When she discovers an extraterrestrial presence, she must risk her life to expose the desert's otherworldly secret.

title: Lancelot: Guardian of Time
description: Merlin sends Lancelot through a window in time to act as a young Arthur's bodyguard and ensure that he's properly guided before becoming king. Unfortunately, wicked sorcerer Wolvencroft learns of Merlin's plans and obliterates their intended time travel trajectory, sending Arthur and Lancelot to Los Angeles during the end of the 20th century. While coping with the immediate shock of the present-day world, Arthur and Lancelot must find a way to outmaneuver Wolvencroft and return Arthur to Cam.

title: Scared to Death
description: As a terrifying genetic organism travels through the sewers of Los Angeles craving human spinal cords, a brave couple try to capture the beast.

title: Bahama Hustle
description: Two up-and-coming rappers hoping to make it big borrow money from a loan shark, but soon find themselves desperately tracking down the music promoters who stole it.

title: Bridge of the Doomed
description: A group of soldiers is ordered to hold a bridge during a zombie outbreak, but what lives underneath the bridge proves to be even more deadly.

title: Maggie Shayne's Embrace the Twilight
description: A seductive vampire and an ex-soldier must keep the only human-vampire hybrid safe from dangerous mercenaries who are after the secrets of her immortality.

title: Blood Ransom
description: After a man (Alexander Dreymon) kidnaps her away from her immortal master, a woman (Anne Curtis) must decide whether to complete her transformation into a vampire or sacrifice everything for love.

title: The Backpacker
description: A maniacal killer hunts Ben Cross, a retired soldier, on the lonely roads of the Outback. Ben has to draw upon all of his strength to unravel the reasons behind the situation and survive the deadly game of cat and mouse.

title: Krampus: The Return
description: When Lisa and her friends go looking for answers behind her brother's mysterious death, they discover he was a victim of the infamous Christmas demon

title: The Mermaid's Curse
description: While investigating a string of mysterious disappearances in a small beachside town, Jake, a journalist, unknowingly encounters a siren and falls in love with her.

title: El Regreso De La Llorona
description: Un ser sobrenatural busca venganza por la muerte de sus hijas y ataca a un grupo de jóvenes que están de vacaciones en la playa después de que maten accidentalmente a una joven.

title: The Legend of Jack and Jill
description: A group of friends grieving a recent loss meet up with one another only to discover they are being hunted by Jack and Jill.

title: Veerana
description: Mahindra Pratap and his younger brother Sameer kill Nikita, a witch who uses her charm to kill people. After many years, Nikita comes back from the dead and targets Mahindra Pratap's daughter Jasmin.

title: Jilla
description: சக்தி, மதுரையைச் சேர்ந்த ஒரு சக்திவாய்ந்த கும்பல் சிவனின் வளர்ப்பு மகன். சக்தி காவல்துறையை கடுமையாக வெறுத்தாலும், அவன் தந்தையின் விருப்பத்தின் பேரில் காவலனாக வேண்டிய கட்டாயத்தில் இருக்கிறான்

title: Rana Vikrama
description: ನಾಪತ್ತೆಯಾದ ಪತ್ರಕರ್ತನ ಪ್ರಕರಣದ ತನಿಖೆಗೆ ಅಧಿಕಾರಿ ವಿಕ್ರಮ ಮುಂದಾಗುತ್ತಾನೆ. ಆದಾಗ್ಯೂ, ಸತ್ಯದ ತಳಕ್ಕೆ ಹೋಗಲು, ಅವರು ಪ್ರಬಲ ದರೋಡೆಕೋರರ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಹೋರಾಡಬೇಕು.

title: Axcellerator
description: A car thief and a store employee are pursued by a group of people after they come into possession of a teleportation device. With their lives at stake, the duo must do everything to survive.

title: Kayla
description: Sam, the son of a famous polar explorer who is missing, is not thrilled to move to a Canadian wasteland with his mother and her new husband. Meanwhile, he plans to compete in a sled dog race.

title: Arthur and Merlin
description: Arthur, a young warrior, along with Merlin, a hermit wizard, embarks on a quest to thwart a powerful druid who is hell-bent on destroying the Celtic people.

title: Nightbeasts
description: A father and son on a weekend hunting trip in the woods encounter supernatural creatures at night.

title: Fireball
description: Inspector Ava Williams investigates a prison fire to its source, a prisoner seeking revenge against those who put him behind bars.

title: Wasteland
description: A world world ravaged by a deadly virus and within that world is Scott Miller, a man who, against the odds, is trying to carve out some sort of life.

title: The Bone Snatcher
description: Dr Straker and his team are on a mission to find some missing scientists but things take a turn when they learn that a dangerous creature is out to hunt them.

title: Ice Twisters
description: Charlie, an ex-scientist, is in the town of Harrisford, Oregon, to promote one of his books when a deadly tornado hits the city. He teams up with a few scientists and tries to stop the calamity.

title: Assassin 33 A.D
description: While doing research, a group of young geniuses accidentally stumble upon a secret terrorist plot to create a time machine to go back in time and change history. 2021.  Stars: Jordyn Barrera, Christina Birdsong, Donny Boaz

title: Night Zero
description: A dinner party turns deadly when a group of friends are trapped after an alien invasion threatens to take over the world. Things take a turn for the worse when the chemical the military are using to destroy the aliens is turning humans into zombies.

title: Bacterium
description: Several friends come face-to-face with a maniacal scientist and a creature mutated by chemical weapons in an abandoned factory.

title: The Defiled
description: The Defiled: We Are All Meat , After a virus turns most of humanity into flesh-eating mutants, an infected father (Brian Shaw) tries to prevent his newborn son from suffering the same fate.

title: Nightmare Code
description: After a programmer working on a top secret code suddenly turns violent, a new coder is brought in to find out what went wrong. The more he tries to unlock the secret of the code, the more it begins to affect him.

title: A Murderous Affair: The Carolyn Warmus Story
description: When Paul's wife is murdered, he is the primary suspect until attention turns to his lover, a teacher from Westchester County, N.Y.

title: The Eve
description: Friends head to a remote island off from Martha's Vineyard to celebrate New Year's Eve. As tensions rise, an unforeseen presence halts the celebration and turns the holiday into a fight for survival.

title: Six Years Gone
description: Six years ago, Carrie Dawson's young daughter was abducted outside of her school, causing her mother's life to fall into ruin. Now, clues begin to emerge about the truth of her disappearance.

title: October Baby
description: Hannah suffers from asthma, epilepsy and depression. To make things worse, she discovers that she was adopted. Hannah tries to find her biological mother with the help of her best friend, Jason.

title: The Stairs
description: Hikers in the woods stumble upon a mysterious staircase that leads them into a subterranean nightmare.

title: The Long Hot Summer
description: A drifter's arrival in a small Mississippi town has varying effects on the members of a wealthy family.

title: For the Love of Spock
description: For the Love was created by brothers Brendan and Todd Wells, documenting their endless adventure around the globe in search of whitewater and waterfalls. As expedition kayakers at heart, the brothers and their many friends explore rivers around.

title: Starfish
description: Humanity is about to come to an end due to a mysterious signal; trapped at the home of a dead friend, Aubrey tries to turn things around after finding a mysterious cassette tape.

title: Unconditional
description: Samantha is pulled away from a perfect life by a tragic turn of events. She begins to lose faith and descend into hopelessness, but is saved by a chance meeting with two children and an old friend.

title: The Allnighter
description: When an astrophysics student loses priceless research to an auto theft he makes a bargain with a woman at a local pawn shop in order to get it back.

title: The Untold Truth - Diana and Dodi
description: Exploring the mysterious relationship between Princess Diana and Dodi Al-Fayed.

title: 23 Blast
description: Travis Freeman, a footballer, ends up losing his eyesight due to a bacterial meningitis infection. However, he is coaxed by his coach, Farris, to rejoin the team.

title: Evil Lurks
description: Consumed with grief, Kimberly joins a hypnotherapy group and is quickly singled out by a hypnotist possessed by a great evil known as the Shh Man.

title: Preternatural
description: Two amateur film-makers find the movie they thought they were making, is actually making them.

title: Char Man
description: Two friends visit fire-ravaged Ojai, Calif., intent on making a fake documentary about the infamous Ojai vampire. However, things take a bizarre and frightening turn when they learn about a different local legend: The Char Man.

title: Sleep. Walk. Kill.
description: People in a quiet town start walking and killing in their sleep. When the blood dries up, those who are left have to work together to stay alive.

title: Army of the Dead
description: An archaeological dig accidentally unleashes an ancient curse that reanimates an army of skeletal conquistadors who were lost centuries earlier while searching for El Dorado.

title: Beware the Lake
description: A dead high schooler rises from her watery grave to take revenge on the jealous cheerleaders who drugged and murdered her.

title: Chupa
description: When a task force is sent into Cuyahoga Valley National Park to find and capture the mythical chupacabra, the hunters quickly become the hunted.

title: Cannibal Troll
description: A bachelorette weekend in the countryside turns into a nightmare for the bride-to-be and her friends after they encounter a cannibal troll. Subjected to unimaginable horrors, their hope fades with every passing moment.

title: The Haunting of the Murder House
description: In October, four filmmakers disappeared in a haunted house while live streaming on social media. A year later, their footage was found.

title: Retreat to Paradise
description: Ellie tends to injured tennis star Jordan as he heals from a shoulder injury. He's selfish and miserable but with Ellie's help, both start to hope for a brighter future together.

title: Scarlett
description: A young woman must save her father from weapons dealers.

title: My Brother's Wife
description: The black sheep (John Ritter) of a rich Boston family chases his sister-in-law (Mel Harris) for 27 years, starting in 1961.

title: Steel Toes
description: A lawyer and humanist, Danny Dunkleman, is tasked with defending a man, Mike Downey, who is accused of committing a brutal hate crime. Things get tough when their ideologies collide.

title: Alto
description: Frankie questions where her life is going after she meets Nicolette, the daughter of a mob boss, and becomes increasingly attracted to her.

title: Rise of the Tomb Raider
description: Lara Croft continues her late father's research, trekking across Siberia in search of the answers her father couldn't find, facing off against an ancient and ruthless shadow organisation.

title: Welcome to Paradise
description: A woman feels trapped by her life as a housewife, so she convinces her two old friends to go on a vacation to Florida for spring break -- just as they did years earlier.

title: Hearts of Winter
description: Quando a filha de um viúvo o inscreve em um programa de TV de reforma de casas, ele aceita com relutância. À medida que a designer começa a transformar a casa e a expulsar os fantasmas da sua falecida esposa, o viúvo consegue deixar seu passado para trás.

title: Bootleggers
description: In rural Arkansas, two families feud over the rights to a moonshine run and try to get even with one another in the 1920s.

title: Breaking Loose
description: An Australian motorcycle gang follows a surfer (Peter Phelps) north in this sequel to the 1977 "Summer City."

title: Encounter
description: After he loses everything in a car crash, a differently-abled man experiences another major change in his life as his friends discover an unidentifiable object in a field that holds many secrets.

title: Tell Me How I Die
description: A few college students volunteer as test subjects for a new drug. They suffer the after-effects of the drug and begin to hallucinate about their death.

title: K-11
description: A music executive (Goran Visnjic) wakes up in a dangerous section of the Los Angeles County jail normally reserved for LGBT inmates.

title: Across The Hall
description: Julian gets the shock of his life when he gets a call from his best friend Terry about his fiancee being unfaithful. In a fit of rage Julian wants to take a shot at her. Will Terry avert the disaster.

title: Stained
description: Scorning the mediocrity of their mundane lives, two people carry out a plan to make the American dream a reality.

title: If I Can't Have You
description: Dark comedy psychological thriller revolving around a psychotherapist's interactions with deranged men.

title: We Are Boats
description: Francesca looks for her daughter while she navigates through the world of living by encountering strangers at the exact time when she needs to.

title: Dawn
description: A unsuspecting couple get into a ride-share only to find out that they may have to fight for their lives as the deranged driver puts them through life and death situations.

title: As a Prelude to Fear
description: When a young girl called Eve gets kidnapped and imprisoned in a dungeon-like basement, the police believe it is the work of the notorious Pied Piper.

title: Deadly Presence
description: Three friends looking for a night of fun decide to stay in a supposedly haunted house. Several days later Candace finds herself in the midst of strange happenings. When she calls on her friend for help, it's up to her to seek the answers.

title: Miss Bala
description: Gloria gets abducted by a group of criminals when she visits Mexico to meet her friend Suzu. Later, she uses her wit to survive in the cruel world of crime.

title: Quarries
description: Kat joins an expedition to escape her violent boyfriend. But things take a twisted turn when she realises that she is being targeted by a pack of predators.

title: Lockdown
description: Lockdown - An angry mob, fed up with a deadly virus that has wiped out most of the population, attack a school to rid their city of those they suspect are spreading the disease. One man must rescue his sister and fight his way out, against the armed militia.

title: Navy Seals
description: Navy Seals: The Battle For New Orleans,A group of elite Navy SEAL soldiers travel to New Orleans, Louisiana, to rescue the vice president, only to discover that zombies have overrun the city, which forces them to fight for their lives.

title: While She Was Out
description: On Christmas eve, Della, a submissive housewife with an abusive husband, gets into a threatening duel with a bunch of hooligans. As she's cornered, all she has is her red toolbox from her crashed car.

title: Fire with Fire
description: While vacationing away from the city, recent college graduates face the dangers of white supremacists lurking in the rural territories of the United States

title: Revelator
description: While a disgraced psychic investigates the mysterious death of a wealthy family's last heir and with a sceptical journalist recording his progress, he finds himself the only suspect when the death is ruled a murder.

title: Testament
description: One regular man named Simon is swept up by a popular movement in a dying world. When the charismatic leader of that movement is brutally executed, everyone looks to Simon to keep the movement alive.

title: The Hyperions
description: In 1960, professor Ruckus Mandelbaum invents the Titan badge, which offers humans superpowers and creates an unusual family of superheroes. However, by 1979, a new line of superheroes has taken up the badges and two of the originals want them back.

title: Wild Justice
description: Daniel, an ex-soldier, gave up a violent life to live peacefully with his new wife. But when he steps in during a terrible incident at the local pub he sparks a gang war that can only end in an explosive battle in the Australian outback.

title: Puncture
description: Mike, a drug-addicted lawyer, is approached by a nurse with a case involving a health supply corporation. As Mike takes on the case, he tries to battle against his own obsession with narcotics.

title: Big Trouble in Seattle
description: The lawyer of a gangster who is on trial for murder uses his skills to frame an innocent young woman and thereby save his client.

title: Act Your Age
description: An out of work young actor with no respect for the elderly makes himself into an old man to get a part in a play. When research requires him to spend a week at a nursing home, he is forced to review his life choices.

title: 100 Feet
description: Marnie is placed under house arrest with an electronic ankle bracelet to serve her sentence for killing her husband. However, a malevolent entity soon turns her incarceration into a living hell.

title: Winds of Silence
description: The lives of two brothers are shattered when one of them has a devastating tragedy.

title: Firenado
description: Four scientists develop a ground-breaking technology capable of controlling weather, which malfunctions and creates a fire tornado that destroys everything in its path. It's a race against time for them to stop the out-of-control science experiment.

title: The 2nd
description: When a man gets delayed while picking up his son from his college, he witnesses a gang of terrorists trying to kidnap a prominent personality's daughter, Erin.

title: Revelation Blue
description: Revelation Blue: Restoration The continuing story of ex-preacher Devon Blue, turned Philadelphia police detective searching for the killer of his childhood friend while dealing with a corrupt police department and restoring his faith in God. In the continuing story, Devon Blue tracks down the killer of his childhood friend and the murder of two fellow detectives in a city with a corrupt police department.

title: As The Village Sleeps
description: A smart yet naive college girl organizes a birthday celebration at her stepfather's cabin, bringing together a volatile group of friends and family. While playing a mysterious party game, nightmares blend with reality and the friends struggle to survive as the living game attacks and turns them against each other.

title: Night Shift
description: Des and Bobby are just two mid twenties brothers trying to get by, but when they are delivered a final demand letter from the bank, they do whatever they can to save their family's home.

title: Reed's Point
description: An RV crash near the New Jersey Pine Barrens leaves two survivors, Sarah and Alex, who investigate the crash site a year later. They find themselves stuck in the woods unsure of whom they can trust and questioning if monsters really do exist.

title: Black Pumpkin
description: On October 31st, two small town preteens accidentally awaken an evil entity that has been dormant for decades; they are forced to survive against a monster known as 'Bloody Bobby'.

title: Silent Retreat
description: When Janey realises that the men behind her meditation centre are brainwashing women, she decides to expose them. However, the owner tries to blackmail her when she is about to break the rules.

title: Ab Negative
description: A blood infection has decimated the world population, every blood type is affected except the rarest one.

title: The Wake
description: After accidentally killing a boy with their car, five friends attend his wake. Once there, they find themselves stalked by a masked assailant.

title: Shadows
description: Alma and Alex live in an abandoned hotel deep inside the woods. Their mother, a strict, over-protective woman, shelters them from ominous presences - known as the Shadows. But as the sisters grow older, they become.

title: Cut Her Out
description: Darcy Baker can't purge her mind of the animalistic abuse she suffered as a child at the hands of her mother. Darcy's therapist Ryan discovers that her family homestead has been abandoned. He is eager to get her back there and pull the suppressed memories to the surface. Their stay becomes deadly.

title: The Summoning
description: A group of friends set out on a road trip to "the party of the century" in the middle of nowhere, but on the way, they break down and find themselves being hunted for a satanic ritual.

title: Harvey
description: Small town life is about to become a lot more interesting, when one man realizes he may be a killer.

title: 47 Hours to Live
description: Two teenage girls, are bored one night and turn to the internet for scary stories. They find a game on a creepy website that claims you can use your phone to summon the supernatural...and if you lose the game...you lose your life.

title: ReSet
description: A college student passes out at a party and wakes in the bedroom of Edgar, who seems nice but has sinister intentions. As she tries to escape, she finds an heirloom that may help her gain the upper hand against her captor.

title: Blackwater
description: A Feature western genre film, 60 minutes in length shot on green screen, and locations actors placed into worlds created by 3D models.

title: Non, ou a Vã Glória de Mandar
description: No, or the Vain Glory of Command : Não, ou a Vã Glória do Comando (português: Não, ou a Vã Glória do Comando) é um filme português de 1990 dirigido por Manoel de Oliveira. O filme, estrelado por Luís Miguel Cintra e Miguel Guilherme, retrata uma série de derrotas de toda a história militar de Portugal

title: Sefarad
description: No Portugal do século XIX, onde os judeus foram banidos durante séculos, um oficial convertido embarca numa missão heróica para reavivar a comunidade judaica.

title: Capitães de Abril
description: April Captains : Em 1974, o exército liderado por dois jovens capitães dá um golpe contra a ditadura portuguesa que governou o país durante 40 anos.

title: Diamantino
description: Diamantino (Carloto Cotta) é uma estrela do futebol mundial, até que, de repente, perde todo o seu talento e se aposenta como um fracasso aos olhos da opinião pública. Com isso, o ex-ídolo passa a procurar um novo propósito, confrontando o neofascismo, em seguida se envolvendo com a crise dos refugiados, chegando na questão da modificação genética até a busca pela origem do genial.

title: Viriato
description: Há milhares de anos existiu um guerreiro que lutou e deu a vida por um território que mais tarde se tornou a Lusitânia. Contra os avanços do Império Romano, que possuía uma imensa armada, optou por dedicar a sua vida à proteção do seu povo e das suas terras. Chamava-se... Viriato.

title: Belarmino
description: O ex-campeão de boxe Belarmino responde um psicológico encarando a câmera em close. Em seguida, a câmera o acompanha em seu dia a dia, em casa com a família, cobiçando as mulheres e trabalhando como porteiro de uma boate, além dos treinos e sessões de boxe.

title: Fatima
description: Com base em acontecimentos históricos, três jovens pastores em Fátima, Portugal, relatam a visão da Virgem Maria, inspirando os fiéis

title: Jogo de Xadrez
description: Chess Game : Mina acabou atrás das grades após um crime de corrupção. Mas o mentor, o senador Franco, usa sua influência para mantê-la presa e abafar o caso.

title: 1492 Conquest of paradise
description: Colombo obtém a aprovação da Rainha Isabel para descobrir uma nova rota marítima para a Índia. Depois de semanas navegando, a tripulação tem um vislumbre do Novo Mundo e se alegra quando os nativos lhes mostram pepitas de ouro.

title: Alice
description: Alice is a Portuguese film directed by Marco Martins, released in 2005. Alice stars Nuno Lopes as Mário, the father, and Beatriz Batarda as Luísa, his wife, as well as Miguel Guilherme, Ana Bustorff, Gonçalo Waddington, Carla Maciel, Laura Soveral and José Wallenstein. Alice was produced by Paulo Branco

title: O Sangue
description: Um adolescente e seu irmão são abandonados pelo pai e deixados sozinhos desde muito cedo.

title: Ein Sommer in Portugal
description: A summer in Portugal : O arquiteto de hotéis viciado em trabalho efetivamente se afastou de sua família. Interrompe o último projecto marroquino de passar férias com a mulher Liane em Lisboa, mas atrasa-se. O simpático decorador de interiores local João, viúvo, gosta de recebê-la. Ao descobrir que ela se sente solitária, ele a seduz com sucesso com sua personalidade e a propriedade para a qual nunca se mudou devido à morte de sua falecida esposa por câncer. Quando Ben finalmente percebe a tensão, fica claro que já tem um longo caso com Antilla, irmã de João.

title: A Canção de Lisboa
description: A Song of Lisbon  : A Canção de Lisboa is a 1933 Portuguese musical comedy film, directed by José Cottinelli Telmo, and starring Vasco Santana, Beatriz Costa, António Silva, Alfredo Silva, Ana Maria, Artur Rodrigues

title: O Leão da Estrela
description: A história gira em torno de Anastácio, torcedor dos Leões de Alcochete e do Sr. Barata, torcedor do Inferno Futebol Clube. Um dia, as duas equipes se enfrentam. Qual time vencerá?

title: Parque Mayer
description: Após a aprovação da Constituição do Estado Novo em 1933, que limita a liberdade de expressão, um teatro no Parque Mayer luta contra a censura para continuar apresentando sátiras artísticas.

title: Un Dorado de Pancho Villa
description: A Faithful Soldier of Pancho Villa : Un fiel soldado de Pancho Villa es una película dramática mexicana de 1967 escrita, dirigida y protagonizada por Emilio Fernández. Fue inscrito en el V Festival Internacional de Cine de Moscú.

title: El Bruto
description: The Brute : Un trabajador musculoso apodado El Bruto es contratado por Carmelo, un propietario, para despedir a los inquilinos. Más tarde, El Bruto se enamora de la hija de Carmelo, pero enfrenta problemas por parte de una celosa Paloma, la esposa de Carmelo.

title: Two is A Magic Number
description: Nach dem Tag von Andrej, Nadia und Claudius am See, an dem sich eine Reihe dunkler Geheimnisse und Verrat entfalten.

title: Reveille
description: Reveille – Im November 1943 müssen sich eine Gruppe amerikanischer Soldaten und ihre verwundeten deutschen Gefangenen mit ihrer gegenseitigen Menschlichkeit auseinandersetzen, nachdem sie nach einem Gefecht in Mittelitalien gemeinsam in Deckung gegangen sind.

title: Qué Bonito Amor
description: La terrateniente Gertrudis interrumpe su propia boda con Antonio, porque no quiere ceder su poder a un hombre, como declara el cura. Los que alguna vez fueron amantes iniciarán una gran disputa por la Presidencia Municipal. Actores Lola Beltrán, Antonio Aguilar, Joaquín Cordero, Luz María Aguilar Director Mauricio de la Serna

title: El Libro de la Selva
description: Después de que una amenaza del tigre Shere Khan lo obliga a huir de la jungla, un cachorro llamado Mowgli se embarca en un viaje de autodescubrimiento con la ayuda de la pantera Bagheera y el oso de espíritu libre Baloo.

title: La Terre Etrangère
description: Ne pouvant repartir, portée par l'énergie du désespoir, Aline arrive à Mogador en compagnie de sa tante, Flora Masson, de son cousin, Yvon, et des trois enfants de Paul, François, Virginie et Toine.

title: Silent Witness
description: 检察官童涛在涉及林萌萌的谋杀案中与辩护律师赵丽对峙。她被指控谋杀了她富有的父亲的未婚妻，审判最终得出了一个意想不到的结论。

title: Baby and Me
description: 반항적인 10대(장근석)는 부모가 없는 동안 아기를 돌봐야 한다.

title: 2 Mundos
description: 2 mundos é o melhor filme angolano dirigido por Hochi-fu o diretor de videoclipe por trás de Windeck do Cabo Snoop, Os Lambas - Comboio, o filme mostra uma história de amor africana

title: The Radicals
description: A dramática história do movimento Anabatista e de dois de seus primeiros líderes, Michael e Margaretha Sattler

title: A Floresta do Escalpe
description: Em 1820, um caçador de peles do Texas viaja para a misteriosa floresta de Buckskin para salvar um menino perdido, mas deve enfrentar demônios do passado.

title: Almanya - Willkommen in Deutschland
description: Cenk, ein sechsjähriger deutscher Junge mit gemischter türkischer und deutscher Abstammung, hinterfragt seine Identität in seiner Schule. Seine türkischen Verwandten, stolz auf ihre deutsche Identität, sehnen sich danach, das Land ihrer türkischen Vorfahren wiederzusehen.

title: Wo ist mein Zuhause
description: Where is my home  : Eine wahre, berührende Geschichte. Als Wenya zwei Jahre alt war, trennten sich ihre Eltern und sie lebte danach bei ihrem Vater und ihrer Stiefmutter. Ihre Stiefmutter mochte sie nicht und stritt sich ständig mit ihrem Vater. Er hatte keine Wahl – er musste Wenya zu ihrer Mutter schicken, aber ihre Mutter war völlig auf die Führung ihres Geschäfts konzentriert und hatte keine Zeit, sich um Wenya zu kümmern. Deshalb wurde sie oft zu ihren Verwandten und Freunden geschickt, wo sie aufwuchs.

title: Rapunzel oder Der Zauber der Tränen
description: Rapunzel lebt allein im Wald, in einem Turm ohne Türen. Dann kommt eines Tages ein mysteriöser Fremder zu Besuch.

title: مسعود صيدا و سعدة
description: Masood Saida and Saada (مسعود صيدا و سعدة) : عندما يخرج مسعود من السجن بعد 15 عامًا، يقرر العودة إلى حيه القديم، ليصدم عندما يلاحظ التغييرات التي حدثت.

title: ساره
description: Sarah(ساره) : بعد أن أصبح عباس وسارة متشردين يحاولان البقاء على قيد الحياة قدر استطاعتهما. وفي أحد الأيام، التقوا بسيدة الأعمال الجميلة سناء. وسرعان ما يرى عباس في الشابة الأم المثالية لسارة الصغيرة.

title: Simon Blanco
description: Después de la Revolución Mexicana, el héroe de guerra Simón Blanco regresa a casa para proteger a su esposa de los asesinos.

title: Macario
description: Tres deidades misteriosas visitan al campesino empobrecido Macario (Ignacio López Tarso) cuando su esposa (Pina Pellicer) le prepara su comida favorita, un pavo entero. Después de negar el suculento pájaro tanto a Dios (José Luis Jiménez) como al Diablo (José Gálvez), Macario finalmente ofrece la mitad a la Muerte (Enrique Lucero), con la esperanza de que el gesto evite su propia muerte. Como recompensa, la Muerte le ofrece a Macario agua curativa que funcionará sólo a discreción de la propia Muerte.

title: El cumpleaños de Carla',
description: Dos hombres casados ​​están solos en una cabaña de campo, terminando los preparativos para el cumpleaños de una de sus esposas, que se celebrará al día siguiente, cuando de repente, tres jóvenes y atractivas mujeres que se encuentran huyendo, les piden que los ayuden.

title: Genghis Khan
description: 铁木真，一个年轻的成年人，深深地爱着他儿时的朋友博尔特。然而，随着父亲的去世，他的生活发生了翻天覆地的变化，他失去了他的爱和他的部落。

title: Rendez-vous
description: Un drame érotique provocateur interprété par André Techine qui a remporté le prix du meilleur réalisateur au Festival de Cannes pour cette enquête fascinante sur l'intersection de la passion sexuelle et artistique.

title: The Assailant Besouro (Beetle)
description: Besouro, um lendário lutador de capoeira brasileiro, embarca na missão de vingar o brutal assassinato de seu mentor, cujo fantasma o obriga a derrotar os poderosos e libertar os escravos.

title: Age Of The Living Dead
description: Humans are obliged to donate their blood to vampires as part of a peace treaty between the races. But as soon as humans manage to acquire weapons, they start a rebellion.

title: Verônica
description: Uma professora enfrenta assaltos, comerciantes de drogas e homicídios em seu dia a dia escolar. Agora, ela precisa proteger um menino de oito anos de idade que teve seus pais assassinados pelos traficantes.

title: Psychos
description: Three young women seek revenge against a sadistic predator.

title: Ice Quake
description: A colossal methane explosion in Alaska threatens to put an end to life on Earth and military geologist Michael Webster enlists the help of an Army Colonel in finding a way to contain its effects.

title: Amor entre o jogo do poder
description: É uma narração histórica baseada em fatos reais que, pela política de sobrevivência, faz com que Elisa, de 20 anos, abandone o poder da palavra amor, preferindo casar-se com a lei do poder, do dinheiro, da forma, da fama e da transparência. Trazendo com você a expressão; Aquele que nunca recusa a miséria ainda será miserável

title: Mutterliebe
description: Mother's Love ist ein christlicher Familienfilm, der sich mit dem Thema Kindererziehung beschäftigt. „Wissen kann das Schicksal verändern“ und „Aus meinem Kind soll etwas werden“ – das sind alles Hoffnungen, die fast alle Eltern für ihre Kinder haben. Um sicherzustellen, dass ihre Tochter Jiarui eine gute Universität besucht und die Aufnahmeprüfung besteht, beschließt Xu Wenhui, ihren Job als Vertriebsleiterin zu kündigen und ihrer Tochter beim Lernen für die Wiederholungsprüfung zu helfen

title: Kind, komm zurück nach Hause!
description: Li Xinguang, ein einst braver Gymnasiast, erlag der Internetspielsucht. Seine verzweifelten Eltern wandten sich hilfesuchend an Gott und baten um göttliches Eingreifen. Durch Gebet und Glauben befreite sich Xinguang schließlich von seiner Sucht und kehrte nach Hause zurück, nachdem er sich in der virtuellen Welt verirrt hatte.

title: لحنش
description: Lhench : يحكي الفيلم قصة شاب عاطل عن العمل ينتحل شخصية ضابط شرطة من أجل كسب المال والانتقام من ماضي القمع الذي تعرضت له والدته بسبب إساءة رجال السلطة لها. ويسعى الفيلم من خلال الضابط المزيف إلى تسليط الضوء على مجموعة من المواضيع المتعلقة ببعض الظواهر الاجتماعية والأحوال الإنسانية المرتبطة بعوالم العمل في قوة الشرطة. .

title: الوكيل فينود
description: Agent Vinod : ينطلق العميل فينود في مهمة سرية للعثور على سبب وفاة زميله راجان. يضرب الإرهاب عندما يتكشف مؤامرة أكبر.

title: Despiser
description: A down-on-his-luck guy learns things can always get worse when he dies in a car accident and learns he must battle forces of darkness in purgatory.

title: Hot Rod Horror
description: A woman searches for her brother in a haunted junkyard.

title: The 12 Disasters of Christmas
description: When a dark star ominously appears in the sky, natural disasters occur across the globe. Soon, a group of heroes led by Jacey set out to stop the end of the world by analysing a Christmas song.

title: Game Of Death
description: Marcus Jones, a CIA agent, is sent to Detroit by his mentor, Dietrich. Here, he is required to gather intelligence for the possible prosecution of Frank Smith, an arms dealer.

title: The Mutation
description: After a deadly experiment on a rat goes wrong, the mutated rat has been let loose in a city and a group of detectives are on the hunt for the beast. As the body count rises, no one is safe, and the rat is growing at a rapid pace.

title: Solar Attack
description: When the sun's increasing rays of plasma begin to kindle the methane in the earth's atmosphere, the scientists race against time and try to come up with a solution to avoid the disaster.

title: البطة السفرا
description: El Batta El Safra : في إطار عمله الذي قد يحصل على ترقية كبيرة، يجد أحمد وفيق، الباحث الأكاديمي في علم النفس، نفسه مضطرًا إلى مراقبة رشا التي تتعرض للخطر.

title: قصتي وقصتنا
description: My Story and Our Story : يواجه زعيم الكنيسة "يانغ يي" عقدًا من الزمن في سجن الحزب الشيوعي الصيني، ويعاني من ظروف قاسية. لقد تم تزويده بكلمات الله سرًا من قبل زملائه المؤمنين، وهو يشارك الإلهام والدعم وسط الاضطهاد المتزايد. وعلى الرغم من الاكتشاف والمراقبة المكثفة، إلا أنهم يصرون على المشاركة وإيجاد العزاء في تعاليم الله.

title: ذكريات شبابي
description: Memories of my youth : "ذكريات شبابي" يروي القصة الحقيقية لشاب مسيحي يبلغ من العمر 20 عامًا يدعى تشاو شين ليانغ يواجه اضطهادًا وحشيًا على يد السلطات الصينية. تم اعتقاله وتعذيبه، ويعاني من الحروق والمياه الحارقة في كفاحه للحفاظ على إيمانه. يسترشد تشاو شين ليانغ بكلمات الله يجد الشجاعة لتحمل الضغط المتواصل من الشرطة الشيوعية الصينية

title: El Ruiseñor de las Cumbres
description: Joselito, un pastor, visita periódicamente a sus padres que viven en un pueblo cercano. Cuando se da cuenta de que su padre gasta el dinero que tanto le costó ganar en alcohol, deja su trabajo.

title: En las buenas y en las malas
description: Después de proponerle matrimonio a su novia embarazada, Sebastián conoce a Pamela, una joven que está decidida a seducirlo.

title: Das Leben Jesu
description: Eine Gruppe gelangweilter, frustrierter Teenager verbringt ihre Zeit damit, mit dem Motorrad durch eine triste Stadt im Norden Frankreichs zu fahren. Sie beschimpfen arabische Einwanderer, schikanieren die Schwachen und kassieren lustlos Sozialhilfe. Bandenführer Freddy (David Douche) hat eine grobe sexuelle Affäre mit dem einheimischen Mädchen Marie (Marjorie Cottreel). Als ein junger Araber namens Kader (Kader Chaatouf) Interesse an Marie bekundet und sie ihm daraufhin reagiert, ist Freddys Bande empört und löst eine tragische Kette von Ereignissen aus.

title: Wolf creek 2
description: Im australischen Outback bietet Paul, ein englischer Tourist, der verletzten und verängstigten Katarina, einer deutschen Touristin, eine Mitfahrgelegenheit an, die von einem skrupellosen Mörder verfolgt wird.

title: Nicos Weg
description: Hier kommt Nico! Mit ihm könnt ihr ab heute Deutsch lernen. Nico ist Spanier und kommt nach Deutschland. Er kann aber kaum Deutsch sprechen. Was sucht er in Deutschland? Was will er machen? Begleitet ihn auf seinem spannenden Weg!

title: Universal Squadrons
description: An ex-soldier (Riley Smith) and his fiancee (Willa Ford) face a deadly threat from his former comrades.

title: Cinderela Pop
description: Com o coração partido após o divórcio dos pais, uma adolescente desiludida vai morar com a tia e trabalha para traçar seu próprio caminho como DJ. Ela decide virar as costas ao amor até que um belo cantor se apaixona por sua música.

title: Invader
description: A crashed UFO and its reverse-engineered computer system take over the minds of soldiers at an air force base. The alien entity (in the guise of A.S.M.O.D.S., (Asmodeus), a strategic flight defense systems program for fighter jets) is discovered by tabloid reporter Frank McCall and D.O.D. Captain Harry Anders. They escape the base in a stolen F-19 and are taken to the Pentagon, where their story is met with understandable scepticism. An attempt by Asmodeus' minions to capture Frank & Harry for brainwashing convinces General Anheiser of their sincerity, and they return to the base and eventually face Asmodeus and its army of brainwashed soldiers.

title: Rosewood Lane
description: Sonny, a psychiatrist relocates to her hometown after her father's murder. Forewarned about the local eerie paper boy, she starts suspecting him as the killer. Will she be able to unravel the mystery?

title: Fei Cheng
description: Ghost Town... 《鬼城》讲述了中国西南部偏远村庄知子罗的故事，讲述了其文化历史和中国新经济的严酷现实之间的斗争。这部纪录片由赵大勇执导，亲密地描绘了留下的人物，从一对牧师父子，到面临经济困难的年轻恋人，再到一个为生存而捡破烂的十二岁男孩。

title: Tales From the Other Side
description: Three kids sought out to have the most legendary Halloween night ever. Their Trick-or-treat adventure brings them to the home of the local town legend "Scary Mary". Legends say that she is a woman of pure evil, but one thing is for certain - She knows just the right spooky tales to give these three kids the scare of their life. Sharing six unique stories that will lead the children down a mysterious path to the unexpected.

title: Trespass Into Terror
description: Five friends go on a weekend hunting trip that they will never forget... if they come out alive. They wander onto the wrong side of property lines, and the folks in these parts don't take kindly to strangers intruding onto their land.

title: Falling Flowers
description: 天才作家萧红怀孕、被遗弃、一贫如洗，面对父权制、贫困和战争，她开始了大胆的文学生涯。

title: Amor a balazo limpio
description: Amor a tiro limpio El comisario Rogelio persigue a la cantinera Chabela pero ella lo desprecia. Marcos reta a Rogelio a duelo por el amor de Chabela. Se desata una trama de desafíos y odio a muerte

title: Las Señoritas Vivanco
description: Two spinster sisters believe that committing a robbery is no longer considered a sin after going to confession. Sara García, Prudencia Grifell, Manuel Fábregas, Pedro Armendáriz, Ana Luisa Peluffo

title: São Jorge
description: Saint George : Diante de tempos difíceis, um boxeador desempregado deve assumir um trabalho perigoso como cobrador de dívidas para poder sustentar sua família.

title: O Leão da Estrela
description: O Leão da Estrela é um filme de comédia português de 1947, estrelado por António Silva, Milú, Maria Eugénia, Curado Ribeiro, Laura Alves, Érico Braga, Maria Olguim e Artur Agostinho, e realizado por Arthur Duarte. É um clássico do cinema português

title: do Desassossego
description: Disquiet : Directed by: João Botelho. Cast: Cláudio da Silva, Pedro Lamares, Ricardo Aibéo, Suzie Peterson, Manuel João Vieira, Sérgio Grilo, among others

title: El-Maslaha
description: يطلب الضابط حمزة نقله إلى إدارة مكافحة المخدرات انتقاماً لمقتل شقيقه على يد تاجر المخدرات سليمان المسلمي.

title: Waafet Reggala
description: يجتمع الأصدقاء بعد سنوات من الفراق لمواساة صديقهم ومساعدته على الخروج من الأزمة النفسية التي سببتها وفاة زوجته.

title: 13 Minutes
description: Nach einem gescheiterten Attentatsversuch auf Adolf Hitler wird Georg Elser von den deutschen Streitkräften gefangen genommen. Sie foltern ihn körperlich und emotional und zwingen ihn, die Einzelheiten seines Plans preiszugeben.

title: Fuga Mortal
description: "Un detective (George Segal) de la policía de Los Ángeles persigue a un fugitivo (Dolph Lundgren) que esconde a una diputada (Kristian Alfonso) secuestrada. Fecha de estreno: 27 de marzo de 1993 (Japón)"

title: Las Caras del Diablo 2
description: Cuando una compleja investigación implica a un ex ministro de Justicia, sus hijos y su esposa, el detective Guzmán no tiene otra opción que sacar de la prisión a su compañero, el inspector Pedro Ramírez, para resolver el caso. Ahora, Ramírez está de vuelta con una nueva misión, y una vez más se convertirá en un desafío personal para él.

title: Cangrejo II
description: Basada en hechos reales, cuenta la historia y recrea los acontecimientos del asesinato de una joven en el que luego su hermano sacerdote resultó ser el principal sospechoso.

title: Speedy Rescue
description: 本片讲述了缉毒组织剑小队，在队长秦风的带领下，面对邪恶的贩毒集团，冒着艰险营救缉毒富商张百雄的故事。

title: La Boum 2
description: Vic, seize ans, part en vacances en Autriche avec sa famille. Elle rencontre Philippe et se laisse emporter par son charme, sans savoir que son amie Pénélope a elle aussi des sentiments pour lui.

title: يد إلهية
description: Divine Intervention : يرتب العشاق الفلسطينيون من القدس والضفة الغربية، الذين يفصلهم حاجز تفتيش، لقاءات سرية في هذا العمل الساخر الشهير عن الحياة على جانبي الحدود الفلسطينية الإسرائيلية.

title: توائم روحي
description: Tawa'am Rouhy : بعد وفاة زوجته في شهر العسل، يبحث أرمل متأثر بشدة عن مساعدة معالج يقترح طريقة غير تقليدية لعلاجه.

title: Pixote
description: O adolescente sem-teto Pixote (Fernando Ramos Da Silva) é jogado em uma prisão juvenil durante uma batida policial em crianças de rua de São Paulo. A prisão é um mundo de pesadelo onde guardas sádicos torturam e assassinam os jovens presidiários. Fugindo com uma colega presidiária transgênero chamada Lilica (Jorge Julião) e seu namorado, Dito (Gilberto Moura), Pixote viaja pelas ruas do Rio de Janeiro e se envolve em um submundo de drogas e violência.

title: Perdida
description: Uma mulher moderna é transportada para o Brasil do século 19 e encontra o amor com Lord Ian Clarke.” Katherine Chediak Putnam, Dean W. Law, Tubaldini Shelling. Ficção científica e fantasia2023115 min

title: Carandiru
description: Drauzio Varella, um médico, está tratando presos em uma prisão superlotada no Brasil. Ao fazer isso, ele aprende sobre suas histórias, incluindo como chegaram lá.

title: Er ist wieder da
description: Look Who's Back : Adolf Hitler wacht auf und findet sich im 21. Jahrhundert dort wieder, wo sich einst sein Bunker befand, ohne Erinnerung an irgendetwas nach 1945. Indem er moderne Situationen aus der Nazi-Perspektive interpretiert, findet er als Komiker Ruhm und Erfolg.

title: Survive or Die
description: A young refugee girl escaping civil war wrongly lands in a remote uninhabited part of Australia. She must reach civilisation whilst fighting starvation, harsh terrain and a hunter who hunts her in vengeance for the death of his son.

title: Danger Zone
description: American mining engineer gets involved in civil war and international conspiracy in an African country.

title: USS Seaviper
description: The German U-Boat, U-234, from the Port of Kiel is trading cargo with the Japanese. USS Seaviper must locate and stop this dangerous exchange. The Captain of USS Seaviper must go ashore to conduct reconnaissance on an island near Sumatra, but the ship is left in the hands of Mister Cutter, after the Executive Officer is injured in battle. A conflict between Cutter and the Chief of the Boat puts the submarine in jeopardy. Seaviper is trapped below the surface, with decreasing oxygen, and a Japanese destroyer hunting them from above. Damage to the boat also leave her survival in question. They must fight the Japanese destroyer and get the information about U-235 back to Pearl Harbor.

title: Angry Ranger
description: 概要。一名男子刑满出狱后回到原来的社区，发现原来和他一起出去玩的朋友现在变成了街头暴力团伙，正在恐吓社区。 《愤怒的游侠》由王龙伟执导。

title: Dédales
description: À la demande d'un collègue, un psychologue est chargé d'examiner une femme jugée pour plusieurs meurtres.

title: Circle of Atonement
description: 이상원 형사와 그의 딸 앞에 의문의 남자가 나타나 10년 전의 살인 사건에 얽힌 숨겨진 이야기를 파헤친다.

title: La herencia
description: En ocasiones, la única manera de salvar a la familia es llegar al punto de perderla.

title: Pobres Millonarios
description: La familia Morales estaba acostumbrada a una vida extravagante. Cuando la herencia de su patriarca se seca, se ven obligados a mudarse a un vecindario más humilde, conectarse con nuevos amigos, hacer gastos frugales y lidiar con un avellador avaricioso.

title: Rota Comando
description: Filme baseado em fatos do livro Matar ou Morrer do ex-capitão da ROTA e hoje vereador da cidade de São Paulo Conte Lopes. O filme se passa na cidade de São Paulo e conta a história da Ronda Ostensiva Tobias de Aguiar (ROTA). Rota ComandoDirigido por Elias Júnior.

title: Bartok the Magnificent
description: Bartok, o morcego albino, junto com seu melhor amigo Zozi, o urso, abrem caminho para entreter as pessoas através de apresentações de rua. Eles são atraídos pelo Príncipe Ivan, que é sequestrado por uma bruxa.

title: Run Lola Run
description: Lola hat 20 Minuten Zeit, ihrem Freund 100.000 DM zu bringen, sonst raubt er einen Laden aus. Sollte das Geld nicht zurückgezahlt werden, hat das Konsequenzen. Abhängig von Lolas Begegnungen sehen wir drei mögliche Szenarien.

title: Sonnenallee
description: Eine Gruppe Kinder wächst auf der Ostseite der Sonnenallee in Berlin neben einem für deutsche Staatsbürger reservierten Grenzübergang auf. Die Possen und Interaktionen der Kinder veranschaulichen den Alltag auf der Sonnenallee.

title: Wolfsburg
description: In A Love Undone schlägt Philipp versehentlich einen kleinen Jungen, während er mit seiner Verlobten streitet. Er flüchtet vom Tatort und lässt das schwer verletzte Kind zurück. Die Mutter des Jungen, Laura, trifft später unwissentlich auf Philipp und es kommt zu einer Beziehung. Die verheerende Wahrheit kommt ans Licht, was für beide katastrophale Folgen hat.

title: المسيرة: السوق الأخضر
description: Al Massira: la Marche Verte : في عام 1975، نظمت جماهير من المغاربة مسيرة ضد احتلال الصحراء الغربية للدفاع عن أراضيهم الصحراوية.

title: على تزاد تفا داو
description: Lights Went Out on His Birthday... فيلم كوميدي لجميع أفراد الأسرة. فيلم لمحمد كراط كوميديا ​​رائعة

title: مول البندر
description: Moul Al-Bandir : "شركة خدمات إنتاج الأفلام والأفلام التجارية والوثائقية واللقطات مقرها في المغرب مع خدمات ما بعد الإنتاج الداخلية."

title: SEAL Team VI
description: Inspired by true events, special forces agents face harrowing circumstances when their covert mission becomes compromised.

title: Check Point
description: When a beggar warns the townspeople about a silent invasion, nobody believes him until a series of murders take place. It is up to them to find the infiltrators among them.

title: Containment
description: What happens when an epidemic breaks out, but you're kept in the dark? Anything can happen. Slowly the residents realize that they will all die unless they come together.

title: Brush with Danger
description: A runaway fighter and his sister, a painter, arrive in Seattle and start pursuing their dreams. However, troubles begin after they get tricked into selling a fake Van Gogh painting to a criminal.

title: Ultimate Justice
description: Gus decides to get back his team of elite soldiers to save the abducted daughter of a former member and take revenge for his wife's murder.

title: Avenging the Throne
description: In the late 1300s, five warriors returning home from battle encounter a fort which turns into an epic fight for survival.

title: Bunker: Project 12
description: Soviet officials pull the plug on a dangerous experiment and seal the evidence in a remote bunker. Years later, a reckless scientist hires some mercenaries to infiltrate the bunker and recover whatever they can.

title: Una Fe Sin Miedo
description: Un ayudante del sheriff comienza a cuestionar su fe después de ver a un agresor desconocido dispararle a su compañero.

title: Lotoman 003
description: Los hermanos ponen a prueba su integridad mientras investigan a los miembros de una pandilla.

title: I Love Bachata
description: Marcos (Roberto Ángel Salcedo), Tommy (Fausto Mata) and Carlitos (Raeldo López) form a bachata group and have problems becoming famous.

title: Killer's Nocturne
description: 严烈山先生是一位心狠手辣的夜总会老板，他对赌王罗天白怀恨在心。

title: Executor
description: A priest gives assassination assignments to a young man staying at his orphanage. When one of the missions goes wrong, the assassin begins to question his beliefs.

title: The Sensei
description: In 1985 Colorado, a long-absent woman, proficient as a black belt in martial arts, returns home where she agrees, secretly, to train a bullied gay teen.

title: Range 15
description: Five soldiers wake up after a night of drinking to realise that a zombie apocalypse has begun. They must restore the freedom of the US by fighting the zombies.

title: Death Fighter
description: A police officer decides to join forces with a mercenary in order to hunt down his mentor's killers and bring them to justice.

title: Point Man
description: Set in Vietnam in April 1968 - three months after the tide-turning Tet Offensive and one month after the assassination of Martin Luther King Jr. - Point Man is the story of a U.S. Army fire team fractured by racial tensions, moral crises, and the crushing pressures of combat in a war nobody wants to fight. Andre "Casper" Allen, a rough-edged ideologue, finds his radical politics put him at odds with the squad's machine gunner, Silas Meeks. When their search-and-destroy mission in the Mekong Delta goes terribly wrong, both men find themselves pitted against each other and their recalcitrant platoon commander, Lieutenant Sutter. Point men die like flies in the bush, and as loyalties dissolve every step forward comes with a price.

title: هي فوضى
description: Chaos : حاتم، ضابط شرطة، يسيء استخدام منصبه لتحقيق مكاسب شخصية. يضايق الفتاة البريئة نور عندما ترفض الموافقة على مطالبه.

title: Contract Killers
description: Arrogant assassin Lee-Seng (Rob Young) has one night to kill a squad of vigilantes hunting down drug dealers. Everything goes according to plan until Marshall survives the attack and goes on the run with a beautiful young woman.

title: Outlawed
description: Jake O'Neil, a military commando, does everything in his power to take down a corrupt businessman and rescue Jade, his childhood sweetheart.

title: Enemies Among Us
description: Louisiana Governor Chip Majors is all set to be North Carolina Senator's Vice Presidential nominee but things change when he discovers his past that returns to haunt him.

title: Kill Cavalry
description: A portrayal of Gen. Hudson Kilpatrick's role in the Battle of Aiken and a precarious strategy that shows his utter disregard for the lives of his own soldiers.

title: No Chance
description: The world's greatest commando sets out for revenge when a group of international criminals from his past kidnap his daughter.

title: Raven
description: Jerome "Raven" Katz (Burt Reynolds) is a veteran mercenary assigned to lead a top-secret mission into Bosnia to retrieve an important device. When the situation quickly deteriorates and much of his unit is killed, Raven realizes that he's been sent into a trap and marked for death. Barely escaping alive, Raven goes into hiding, but he emerges years later to hunt down and eliminate Martin Grant (Matt Battaglia), the former team member who double-crossed him.

title: The Curse
description: A tough woman struggles to adapt to civilian life after leaving the Marines. Her relationship with her best friend and a new romance with a kind, considerate man help her to discover her feminine side.

title: Blackwater
description: Four young women tourists are hunted by ruthless woodsmen in the Florida Everglades.

title: Street
description: An amateur MMA fighter decides to participate in an underground circuit after he angers a Russian mafia leader, who wants to hire him.

title: Attack In LA
description: Three friends find themselves lost on Skid Row and are captured by an angry homeless gang.

title: Slaughter Is the Best Medicine
description: Vet leads his team of disbanded mercenaries into the treacherous Gallows Wood on one last mission to capture the elusive Professor Black. What was meant to be a simple extraction mission soon becomes a terrifying journey into madness.

title: Bad Company
description: A group of troubled teenagers stumble upon a secret terrorist plot to attack a rural nuclear power plant. With no immediate help available, they decide to take it upon themselves to stop the rogues.

title: Machine
description: A pair of con artists run a scam where they pose as policemen in order to steal drugs from drug dealers.

title: Confessions of an Action Star
description: Frank Sledge, a member of a touring dance troupe, ends up becoming one of the world's most sought-after action superstars. But fame and money make him lose touch with his roots.

title: Dicen que soy comunista
description: Un obrero agobiado por la crisis económica y el encarecimiento de la vida encuentra accidentalmente la propaganda de un partido político, aparentemente de izquierda, que le convence para incorporarse a sus filas ya que defiende a la clase trabajadora.

title: Fallaste corazón
description: El albañil Lupe vive con su esposa Lidia y su hija Toñita.

title: Er Relajo Der Loro
description: Después de que un loro queda atrapado por traficantes de animales, lo vende a diferentes personas a lo largo de los años. En el proceso, es testigo de la transformación de Venezuela.

title: Prova de Coragem
description: Hermano, um renomado médico e ávido alpinista, planeja escalar um pico traiçoeiro na Terra do Fogo. Ao saber que sua esposa Adri está grávida, ele não está pronto para a nova responsabilidade.

title: Vidas Partidas
description: Por trás do casamento aparentemente perfeito de Graça e Raul está um relacionamento violento e volátil, que leva Graça a se posicionar contra o abuso que está sofrendo.

title: O Exercício do Caos
description: The Exercise Of Chaos : Um pai austero e suas filhas adolescentes trabalham em um engenho. Nutrindo uma relação guiada pelo domínio autoritário da figura paterna, eles tentam lidar com a ausência da mãe e o comando de um sinistro capataz. Primeiro longa metragem de Frederico Machado

title: The Color Out of Space
description: Die Farbe außerhalb des Weltraums – Ein Junge, der nach seinem vermissten Vater sucht, reist nach Deutschland und entdeckt ein eindringliches Erbe, das ein Meteorit in der Gegend hinterlassen hat. Basierend auf H.P. Lovecrafts Kurzroman „Die Farbe außerhalb des Weltraums“.

title: Aguirre, the Wrath of God
description: Don Lope de Aguirre, ein rücksichtsloser spanischer Herrscher, macht sich auf die Suche nach der mythischen peruanischen Stadt El Dorado. Die Expedition fordert jedoch bald einen Tribut von seiner geistigen Gesundheit.

title: The Blue Angel
description: Professor Immanuel Rath trifft Lola, die Headlinerin des Kabaretts „Der Blaue Engel“, nachdem er seine Schüler von der Show verjagt hat. Als er sich in sie verliebt, beginnt sein Leben aus den Fugen zu geraten.

title: اللى بالى بالك
description: Elly baly balak... يتعرض الضابط المنفلوطي واللمبي لحادث مروع أثناء محاولة اللمبي الهروب من السجن. تنشأ التوترات عندما يتم تبادل أدمغتهم عن طريق الخطأ أثناء الجراحة.

title: بوشكاش
description: Boshkash... بوشكش، حارس مرمى متقاعد، يصبح وكيلًا رياضيًا ناجحًا ويعتقد أن القلادة التي يرتديها تجلب له الحظ. تتغير الأمور عندما يفقد القلادة ويلتقي بصحفي.

title: ابراهيم لبيض
description: Ibrahim Labyad... الطفل الصغير إبراهيم يشهد مقتل والده على يد تجار المخدرات. عندما يكبر، يقرر الانتقام منهم.

title: الليمبي
description: El limby... ألمبيك، شاب متحدي، يحلم بالزواج من المرأة التي يحبها. يواجه مشكلة أثناء بحثه عن عمل، وفي كل مرة يحاول الربح من مشروع صغير يفشل بشكل كوميدي.

title: إل دادا دودي
description: El Dada Doody... فتاة تعمل في سرقة الموبايلات مع شريك لها ويتعرضان للتفتيش في احدي نقاط الشرطة علي الطريق فتقوم بالتتضحية به ووضع المسروقات معه ويقبض عليه وتتورط في جريمة قتل فتهرب لتعيش في الإسكندرية، وتضطر إلى العمل كمربية أطفال لدى لواء شرطة تقابل ياسمين شخصاً آخر يغير حياتها كلها وتبدأ طريق الالتزام والتوبة ثم يظهر محمد شرف مرة أخري في حياتها بعد الإفراج عنه ويبدأ في مساومتها

title: إمارات يعقوبيان
description: Emaret Yacoubian... يحاول الأفراد من مختلف مناحي الحياة التغلب على مختلف القضايا الشخصية والاجتماعية أثناء إقامتهم في قلب القاهرة، مصر.

title: Tacos Al Carbón
description: Constantino Rojas se gana la vida vendiendo tacos y sueña con abrir un gran restaurante de tacos. Cuando gana un coche de lujo en la lotería, decide venderlo para cumplir sus sueños.

title: Dios Los Junta y Ellos Se Separan
description: La vida cotidiana de una familia colombiana de clase media.

title: Hasta el Viento Tiene Miedo
description: En un internado, el alma maldita de un antiguo estudiante posee el cuerpo de una joven.

title: The Dragon Nine
description: 衰落的龙族血脉的最后传人，风一帆，意外吞下祖传秘宝龙九丹，神奇生下了天赋异禀的龙九子。九子一出生就能够说话，传说九子的血肉能够自行炼化、聚合，从而获得永生。这导致九子受到诸多邪恶势力的觊觎，于是一家人踏上了逃亡之旅。带着濒死经历的疯狂逃亡之旅让家庭整体成长，也让才华横溢的九子明白了每个人存在的责任和作用。最终，他凭借团队的配合，保护了大家。

title: Le Ballon Rouge
description: The Red Balloon... Un jeune garçon trouve un gros ballon sphérique rouge rempli d'hélium et apprend qu'il a son propre esprit lorsqu'il commence à le suivre partout

title: Das weisse Rauschen
description: The White Sound“ ist das Regiedebüt des österreichischen Regisseurs Hans Weingartner mit Co-Regisseur und Drehbuchautor Tobias Amann. Der Film war die Idee beider Studenten im Rahmen eines separaten Projekts an der Kunsthochschule für Medien Köln.

title: Funny Games
description: In „Funny Games“ wird ein friedlicher Urlaub zum Schrecken, als verstörte Männer eine Familie terrorisieren. Mit gewalttätigen Begegnungen und psychischen Qualen verwickelt der Film das Publikum in den sich entfaltenden Horror.

title: The Cabinet Of Dr. Caligari
description: Ein Schlafwandler macht tödliche Vorhersagen, die erschreckend sind. Später durchleben ein Mann und seine Verlobte aufgrund einer seiner Vorhersagen eine schreckliche Tortur.

title: Linhas de Wellington
description: A história de um tenente, um sargento, uma jovem, um comerciante e uma prostituta que estão presos na guerra travada entre as forças do General Wellington e as tropas de Napoleão em 1810.

title: Horse Money
description: Uma odisseia hipnotizante pelas memórias reais, imaginadas e de pesadelo de um idoso imigrante cabo-verdiano que vive em Lisboa.

title: Curral De Moinas
description: As aventuras de Quim e Zé da fictícia aldeia portuguesa Curral de Moinas continuam com o choque cultural destes caipiras que chegam a Lisboa. Curral de Moinas já é a comédia bancário-romântico-financeira do ano!

title: El Supersheriff
description: Para evitar que el ejército estadounidense capture a su amigo alienígena, Bud y su amigo se mudan de ciudad en ciudad antes de establecerse en Monroe. Aquí aprenden sobre una base alienígena que planea apoderarse de la Tierra.

title: Puños de la Venganza
description: Un campeón retirado de artes marciales mixtas regresa para una última pelea para desentrañar una conspiración.

title: Promoción fantasma
description: Modesto, un maestro que posee habilidades paranormales, ayuda a algunos espíritus perdidos a completar sus graduaciones y deshacerse de ellos de la escuela para siempre.

title: إل رجل إل غامد بسلامته
description: El Ragol El Ghamed Besalamtoh... تدور أحداث الفيلم حول "الشاب" (هاني رمزي) الذي يضطر إلى الكذب في بداية حياته نتيجة الظروف الصعبة التي يعيشها. ومع مرور الوقت، يصدق الجميع كذبته، ولا يستطيع التراجع عنها. ورغم عمله موظفاً في القطاع الخاص إلا أنه يراسل عدداً من الجهات الحكومية ويطالبهم بحل عدد من الأزمات. عامة مثل «الرغيف» و«البطالة» و«أزمة السكن»، وبعد فترة تحدث المفاجأة وتشتهر.

title: الاسم طلعت
description: Nom el-Talat... يعاني موظف حكومي من شكل نادر من مرض الخدار، مما يجبره على النوم من الاثنين إلى الأربعاء من كل أسبوع. ومع ذلك، في أحد أيام الثلاثاء، أثناء غيابه، تضرب أزمة - حيث يتم سرقة أصول قيمة من مكتبه. الآن، بمساعدة زملائه في العمل، يجب عليه محاولة مطاردة اللصوص واستعادة ممتلكات الحكومة.

title: ٣٦٥ يوم سادة
description: 365 yom saada... هادي، المليونير المستهتر، يواعد النساء لفترة وجيزة ولا يتصل بهن مرة أخرى. يعتقد أن حياته مثالية حتى يقع في حب امرأة جميلة.

title: Lost On Journey
description: 玩具公司老板到陈沙过年。

title: The Basement
description: 한국의 실리콘밸리가 핵폭탄의 공격을 받았다. 벤처기업을 운영하는 가족은 2주 동안 집 지하실에 숨어 지내기로 결정했습니다. 가족은 지하실에서 하루하루 생존을 위해 몸부림치기 시작했습니다.

title: Pourri gâtés
description: Trois frères et sœurs gâtés sont obligés de gagner leur vie après que leur père riche et bien intentionné prétende qu'il a tout perdu pour leur donner une leçon.

title: O Cerco
description: Uma portuguesa (Maria Cabral) enfrenta problemas quando abandona o marido para ir em busca da sua identidade interior

title: Uma Abelha na Chuva
description: Um casal de nobres ricos e deprimidos destrói a vida de seus servos por despeito.

title: Schwarzer Panther
description: Nach vielen Jahren trifft Emilie ihren Bruder Jakob wieder. Sie teilt mit ihm nicht nur ihre Trauer über den Verlust ihrer Eltern, sondern auch ein Geheimnis.

title: El Gran Dictador
description: Un barbero judío pierde la memoria tras un accidente aéreo. Cuando finalmente intenta darle sentido a lo que le rodea, se encuentra sometido a la tiranía de un dictador.

title: Cinco De Mayo: The Battle
description: Miles de soldados mexicanos arriesgan sus vidas mientras se enfrentan al ejército más poderoso del mundo para traer la libertad a su país.

title: El pequeño coronel
description: El coronel José de Alvear muere durante la guerra española, dejando atrás a su único hijo. Pronto llega Don Martín afirmando ser el hermano del coronel y el guardián legal de la riqueza de la familia.

title: Dreams of Getting Rich
description: 故事讲述了20世纪90年代初，贫困男孩小宝跟随弟弟二哥从东北的一个贫困村庄来到经济飞速发展的深圳的故事。

title: Call Centers
description: Mathieu Polivennes, jeune et brillant banquier d'affaires, est envoyé en Haute-Loire pour une mission d'urgence afin de remettre de l'ordre dans les centres d'appels de Cecredico, société de crédit à la consommation et filiale de la banque qui l'emploie. A quelques semaines des élections, la faillite du centre d'appels du fin fond de l'Auvergne porterait gravement préjudice aux aspirations électorales de Segondas, le grand patron de la banque.

title: The Kid from the Big Apple
description: 莎拉是一名在纽约长大的马来西亚人，她回到自己的祖国，了解到她的祖父和母亲之间发生了一场大争吵。

title: Pendatang
description: Pendatang은 Ng Ken Kin이 감독하고 Lim Boon Siang이 각본을 맡은 2023년 말레이시아 디스토피아 드라마 스릴러 영화입니다.

title: Une Femme fidèle
description: " Un noble du XIXe siècle (Jon Finch) tente de séduire une femme mariée (Sylvia Kristel)."

title: Les Dalton
description: Les frères bandits Dalton sont condamnés à la prison et font tout ce qu'ils peuvent pour s'échapper afin de mettre la main sur un sombrero magique, laissant derrière eux une traînée chaotique. Peuvent-ils s'en sortir ?

title: Little Heroes: Legend of Yuefei
description: 北宋时期，岳村开设了自己的学校。德高望重的校长周东喜欢岳飞，收他为徒。周董与女儿周瑶一起训练岳飞武术。

title: The Reading Boy
description: 一个 9 岁的男孩和他的爷爷和神一起生活，而他的父母在城里工作。他每天给爷爷读书而不是看电视。有一天，狗开始吠叫，把他拉到爷爷的房间。

title: Assassination
description: 일본의 침략에 저항한 한국의 전사들은 강제로 중국으로 망명하게 된다. 그들은 일본인을 몰아내려고 하지만 반역자가 그들의 계획을 좌절시키려 합니다.

title: Zurdo
description: Un policía corrupto (Alejandro Camacho) intenta hacer que un joven jugador de canicas (Álex Perea) pierda un próximo partido contra un oponente de gran prestigio.

title: El último cazador
description: Auténticos tramperos como los de antaño, como David Crockett, Jack London o Jeremiah Jonson, hoy ya no existen. Aún queda, sin embargo, una última alma que sigue viviendo según la antigua filosofía de los tramperos, viviendo en armonía con la naturaleza.

title: La Guarida Del Lobo
description: Vicente ha sido herido y Toco lo acoge en su cabaña. El cambio en la pacífica relación que mantenían es provocado por un personaje que quiere las tierras de Toco. Pronto se desata el conflicto y se revelan secretos inesperados.

title: أميرة الروم
description: Princess of Rome... مليكة، أميرة روما، تنتقل من بيزنطة لتجنب الزواج. تذهب إلى بغداد حيث تصبح والدة الإمام المهدي.

title: مملكة سليمان
description: The Kingdom of Solomon... مملكة سليمان هي سلسلة أفلام دينية/تاريخية إيرانية من إنتاج مجتبى فراورده وإخراج شهريار بحراني الذي قام بتصوير القديسة مريم من قبل

title: Den kæmpestore bjørn
description: The Great Bear... Sophie begleitet ihren Bruder Jonathan, um mit ihm Urlaub am Rande eines riesigen Waldes zu machen, in dem mythische Tiere leben. Doch die Dinge ändern sich dramatisch, als ein 1000 Jahre alter Bär sie entführt.

title: What is the Ghost Up To?
description: 천동은 8년 전 첫사랑 무림에게 버림받았다. 지루한 일상에 질려갈 위기에 처한 그의 앞에 무림이 유령으로 나타난다. 무림의 죽음을 받아들이기도 전에 무림은 그에게 부탁을 한다. 그의 남자친구를 찾기 위해서다. 천동은 처음엔 화를 내지만 결국 남자친구를 찾아 나선다.

title: Amor Incondicional
description: Un pastor de jóvenes lleva a adolescentes a un campamento que enfrentan conflictos. Para resolverlo, comparte la historia de Oseas, destacando el compromiso y el amor incondicional. La película ofrece inspiración y un poderoso mensaje del evangelio.

title: Siempre a tu lado, Hachiko
description: Un profesor encuentra un perro abandonado y lo lleva a casa. Con el tiempo, forma un vínculo inquebrantable con el perro.

title: Hallie
description: "Halie" presenta la historia de una familia tras la muerte de su madre desde la perspectiva de una pequeña niña con un enorme corazón. Escenas divertidas dan paso a acontecimientos emotivos en este drama familiar que muestra cómo superar la desgracia y redescubrir lo preciosa que es la vida.

title: لقد كان توهيبا
description: Teita Rahiba... يصر رؤوف على الهروب من جدته المسيطرة والزواج من صديقته منار. يتم تخريب خطته عندما تعود جدته إلى البلاد وتتدخل في حياته الشخصية

title: يوم مالوش لازمة
description: Youm Maloush Lazma... يكافح مها ويحيى من أجل الانسجام أثناء الاستعدادات لحفل زفافهما. ويزداد التوتر بينهما عندما تهدد صديقة يحيى السابقة بإفساد يومهما الكبير.

title: إل حرب إل الأمية إل تالتة
description: El Harb El Alameya El Talta... أثناء لعب كرة القدم مع أصدقائه، يركل خميس الكرة ويكسر بالخطأ نافذة متحف مهجور. يذهب لاستعادة الكرة ويكتشف أن التماثيل قد عادت إلى الحياة.

title: Anjo Da Guarda
description: SCHUTZENGEL... Um adolescente presencia um crime e passa a ser protegido pela polícia, que contrata um ex-soldado e veterano da Guerra do Afeganistão para proteger a menina. Mas o criminoso é um figurão de Berlim e já comprou todo mundo do Judiciário e da Polícia.

title: 2 Duros de Roer
description: Uma improvável equipe de policiais e um estudante vivem um dia louco, conhecem os personagens mais ridículos e desmascaram uma operação de tráfico de drogas com consequências desastrosas não apenas para a cidade, mas para o mundo inteiro.

title: El Hombre que Copiaba
description: André, de dezenove anos, quer ganhar dinheiro para cortejar sua vizinha Silvia. Ele começa a falsificar notas, participa de uma loteria e finalmente planeja um assalto a banco com seu amigo.

title: Auto da compadecida
description: João Grilo, um mentiroso patológico, e seu amigo Chico, um covarde, lutam para ganhar a vida, e é quando bolam um plano astuto para resolver seus problemas.

title: NOÉ
