Cuando la madre de Esperanza muere, aunque regresa a casa, está reticente a reunirse con sus dos hermanas, Caridad y Faith, después de tantos años de separación.

title: Miradas que Matan
description: Max, a quien la vida le resulta difícil debido a su apariencia peligrosamente fascinante, se encuentra con Alex, que sufre una rara enfermedad cardíaca. Ayuda a un Max suicida a redescubrir la vida y la felicidad.

title: Educacion Sexual En Breves Lecciones
description: Alejandra y Ana son amigas de la universidad, ambas son vírgenes y esperan encontrar pronto el amor de su vida. Ana conoce a Miguel, pero aceptan ser solo amigos. Alejandra conoce a Esteban, un conocido mujeriego.

title: Alivio
description: Tres madres solteras de diferentes regiones de México intentan sanar recuerdos dolorosos de abuso a través de una profesión compartida por la que han luchado muy duro: ser enfermeras.

title: Heroes Verdaderos
description: Un criollo, tres nativos y un mestizo se encuentran luchando por la independencia de México junto a Miguel Hidalgo.

title: Un frère
description: A Brother... Tom, 15 ans, va passer un autre été calme avec ses parents et sa sœur cadette dans leur maison d'été. Mais par hasard, une autre famille vient passer du temps avec eux, avec leur fils Félix, 17 ans.

title: 96 Heures
description: Kancel échappe à la police en enlevant le policier qui l'a arrêté. Il a 96 heures pour découvrir qui l'a trahi et prouver son innocence.

title: Dans Paris
description: Après qu'une histoire d'amour se termine mal, un jeune parisien nommé Paul (Romain Duris) sombre dans le même genre de profonde dépression qui a poussé sa sœur au suicide. Il rentre chez lui avec son père (Guy Marchand) et son frère sans but Jonathan (Louis Garrel) mais refuse de sortir du lit.

title: Forces Spéciales
description: Ahmed Zaief, un chef taliban, kidnappe Elsa, une journaliste française qui couvre un reportage en Afghanistan. C'est désormais à une équipe des forces spéciales françaises de sauver Elsa d'une forteresse au Pakistan.

title: Les Hommes libres
description: Free Men... Dans le Paris occupé par les nazis, Younès, un Algérien, est chargé par la police d'espionner une mosquée dont le recteur est soupçonné d'aider les Juifs. Mais il finit par se lier d'amitié avec l'homme et rejoint la Résistance française.

title: Insolação
description: Numa cidade vazia e chamuscada pelo sol, jovens e velhos confundem a febre da insolação com o delicado nascimento da paixão. Como fantasmas, eles pairam em torno de edifícios e planícies sem fim em busca do amor sempre evasivo. Inspirado em contos russos do século XIX

title: O Diário de Tati
description: A adolescente Tati conta, de forma divertida, todos os problemas de sua juventude ao seu diário. Desde ficar em recuperação em matemática até os esforços para conseguir fisgar Zeca, sua paixão atual.

title: Feliz Natal
description: Caio tem 40 anos e mora no interior do Rio de Janeiro, onde é dono de um ferro-velho. Na noite de Natal vai à capital visitar a família e os amigos. Finalmente ele poderá encontrar um homem que não via há muito tempo: ele mesmo.

title: Safe heaven
description: Katie Feldman zieht an die Küste von North Carolina, um ein neues Leben zu beginnen. Dort lernt sie den Witwer Alex kennen und verliebt sich in ihn. Doch das Glück schwindet, als ihre dunkle Vergangenheit ihr Leben heimsucht.

title: Verblendung
description: Mikael Blomkvist, ein Journalist, beauftragt Lisbeth Salander, eine Computerhackerin, das Geheimnis einer Frau zu lösen, die seit vierzig Jahren vermisst wird. Die beiden entdecken bald mehr, als sie erwartet hatten.

title: In der Falle
description: Simone, eine reiche verheiratete Frau, hat eine Affäre mit einem jüngeren Mann, der sie erpresst, nachdem er gesteht, dass er Opfer einer Erpressung geworden ist. Aber sie befürchtet, dass etwas Größeres im Spiel sein könnte.

title: Falling Rocks
description: Sechs Freunde treffen sich zu ihrer jährlichen Wanderreise und machen sich auf den Weg in einen abgelegenen südafrikanischen Dschungel. Sie gehen davon aus, dass sie die einzigen in der gesamten Gegend sind, doch sie könnten nicht falscher liegen.

title: Born to Win
description: Leon Terblanche will ein guter Ehemann und Vater sein. Doch ohne es zu wollen zerstört er die Menschen, die ihm am nächsten stehen. Er findet Orientierung im Glauben, bis ihn ein schwerer Schicksalsschlag wieder an Gott zweifeln lässt

title: Jumanji: The Next Level
description: Lorsque Spencer disparaît, son groupe d'amis retourne à Jumanji pour parcourir des territoires inexplorés et l'aider à échapper au jeu le plus dangereux du monde.

title: El Rey de los kickboxers
description: Un policía de Nueva York (Loren Avedon) se hace pasar por actor para exponer la realización de películas de muerte sobre artes marciales en Tailandia.

title: Cruces
description: Al otro lado de las montañas en un pueblo donde  los hombres y mujeres que lo habitan enfrentan problemas singulares, de amor, de desencuentros y rechazos que los obligan a tomar decisiones creyendo que son suyas, pero Ruth, una niña de ocho años, sabe que todo en esta vida es según la voluntad de Dios: La vida y principalmente la muerte.

title: Caleb
description: Rebecca busca a su hermana, una joven periodista que desapareció mientras investigaba una serie de acontecimientos desafortunados, y conoce a un hombre encantador de mirada oscura en un lugar remoto del mundo.

title: الجن
description: Djinn... زوجان إماراتيان يواجهان بعض الأنشطة غير الطبيعية في شقتهما بعد عودتهما من الرحلة. لاحقًا، اكتشفوا أن شقتهم مسكونة بمخلوقات غامضة.

title: الطريق إلى كابول
description: Road to Kabul... الطريق إلى كابول هو فيلم أكشن مغربي صدر عام 2012، من إخراج إبراهيم الشكيري. مع أكثر من 400000 مشاهدة، حقق الفيلم نجاحًا كبيرًا في شباك التذاكر

title: رعاية الأم
description: Khayal Ma'ata... يكن ومجموعة من اللصوص المحترفين يسرقون قطعاً ثمينة من المجوهرات. بعد عدة سنوات، يطلب ياكان المساعدة من حفيده عندما يجد نفسه مطاردًا من قبل المجموعة لمنحهم المجوهرات.

title: لقطة كبيرة جدًا
description: Very Big Shot...

title: ابن اصول
description: Ibn Osool... هشام، شاب ثري، يعمل تاجرًا للألماس مع والده. تأخذ الأمور منعطفًا عندما يعاني من هلوسة مستمرة بقتل شخص ما له.

title: بانانيا آدم
description: Banny Adam... يجد آدم نفسه متورطًا في موقف معقد عندما يُتهم بارتكاب عدد من الجرائم في نفس الوقت الذي تطلب فيه الشرطة مساعدته.

title: ل أخر نفس
description: Le Akher Nafas... فيلم آخر نفس كامل بطولة ياسمين عبد العزيز. تدور أحداث مسلسل آخر نفس المقتبس من المسلسل، حول سلمى (ياسمين عبد العزيز)، وهي سيدة قُتل زوجها الضابط حازم (فتحي عبد الوهاب) في ظروف غامضة، ثم انكشف أمر أولادها.

title: خطاب اعتقال
description: Arrest Letter... رجل ينضم إلى منظمة إرهابية لخوض حرب مقدسة. ومع ذلك، عندما يُقتل شقيقه، الذي يريد أن يصبح جزءًا من الحركة، يدير ظهره لمجموعته ويسعى للانتقام.

title: إل كنز أ
description: El Kenz 2... ينطلق حسن، عالم المصريات، للبحث عن الكنز الذي دفنه والده في قصر بشير الكتاتني. ومع ذلك، فهو يعاني من مشاكله الشخصية على طول الطريق.

title: حرب كرموز
description: Harb Karmouz... أثناء الثورة المصرية عام 1952، تم القبض على جندي بريطاني على يد الضابط يوسف المصري بعد أن اعتدى على امرأة مصرية. تأخذ الأمور منعطفاً عندما يحاول البريطانيون إطلاق سراحه

title: عقدت الخواجه
description: Uqdat el-Khawagah... بعد حادث سيارة، تتطاير الشرر بين رجل يعاني ماليًا وابنة رجل أعمال، مما يكشف أسرارًا غامضة وأطرافًا فضفاضة.

title: فاس ماله و دقه
description: Fas Malh We Dakh... يقع المسرح تحت لعنة، وعندما يعلم بكري بالأمر يحاول إبطاله

title: يا ثدي يا تادي
description: Ya Thadi Ya Taadi... شاب يبحث عن معلم ليعطي والدته دروسا في القيادة. يجد معلمة تبدأ الفصول الدراسية ولكن ينتهي بها الأمر بالوقوع في حبها.

title: Yodha
description: योद्धा 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की एक्शन थ्रिलर फिल्म है, जो सागर अंब्रे और पुष्कर ओझा द्वारा निर्देशित है, और हीरू यश जौहर, करण जौहर और अपूर्व मेहता द्वारा निर्मित है।

title: Murder Mubarak
description: एक हत्या की जांच के दौरान, एक गैर-पारंपरिक पुलिस अधिकारी कई संदिग्धों पर ध्यान केंद्रित करता है। वह एक बाहरी व्यक्ति के रूप में उनकी दुनिया में कदम रखता है, लेकिन पाता है कि वहां जो दिखता है उससे कहीं अधिक है।

title: Carry On Jatta 3
description: ढिल्लों का बेटा जस मीत से प्यार करता है। हालाँकि, मीत के भाइयों की ढिल्लन के साथ तीखी बहस हो जाती है, जिसके बाद ढिल्लन अपने बेटे की मीत से शादी करने की इच्छा को अस्वीकार कर देता है। जैस अपने पिता का मन बदलने के लिए एक पागलपन भरी योजना बनाता है।

title: O Filme dos Espíritos
description: O Filme dos Espíritos é um filme de drama brasileiro de 2011 dirigido por Michel Dubret e André Marouço, baseado no livro O Livro dos Espíritos de Allan Kardec. O filme foi lançado no Brasil no dia 7 de outubro de 2011 em comemoração ao mês de aniversário de Kardec.

title: Contramão
description: Ethan é arrancado de sua terra natal e confrontado com um mundo desconhecido, onde o pecado reina e um líder opressor domina. Neste ambiente, a moralidade é relativa e a liberdade parece inexistente.

title: My One True Love
description: A fortune teller tells us that Ali will find true love with a man named John. Together with her friends, Ali starts a fanatical search for John. Meanwhile, she develops feelings for firefighter Sean.

title: Quest For Love
description: Mackenzie travels to Costa Rica with her best friend Ethan to secure cacao for her work at a chocolate company. She hopes that Ethan will finally see her through new eyes. When a tourist meets Mackenzie, his interest in her makes Ethan wake up.

title: Finding Love in Sisters
description: It follows Esperanza, a lawyer whose dream life is showing some cracks. When her mother dies, she returns to Sisters, Oregon and reunites with her sisters.

title: Brand New Old Love
description: Former high school friends run into each other and decide to make good on a promise they made to one another to get married if they were both single at age 30.

title: Buckskin
description: In 1820, a Texas fur trapper journeys into the mysterious Buckskin woods to save a lost young boy, but must confront past demons.

title: Komodo vs. Cobra
description: A group of people sail to an island for an investigation. They meet a doctor who tells them the place is filled with animals that want to devour everything after being infected by a powerful compound.

title: Sacrifice
description: An undercover police officer gets tangled in a dangerous heroin scheme when one of their young defectors leaves him in charge of his five-year-old sister.

title: Sub Zero
description: Things take an ugly turn when a deadly weapon is stolen by a terrorist. The terrorist is shot down but the weapon lands on the K2. Now a dedicated team must climb the K2 to find it.

title: Magdala Rose
description: In 1244, the pacifist Cathars seek refuge in the Castle of Montsegur, where a group of defending knights protects them from a crusading army.

title: The Devil's Tomb
description: An elite bunch of soldiers, who are on a clandestine mission to retrieve a scientist from a subterranean lab, face an ancient demonic force in the facility.

title: Maximum Impact
description: After terrorists fail to assassinate the US Secretary of State, they kidnap his granddaughter. In order to stop a war, the CIA and FSB must save the girl before it is too late.

title: Polar Storm
description: The comet Copernicus approaches earth. This phenomenon disturbs the magnetic field by causing deadly electromagnetic pressure waves. Soon, the US government announces national emergency.

title: Open Graves
description: Jason and his pals start playing a bizarre board game. The losers begin to get killed due to the game's lethal curse. It then dawns on Jason and his girlfriend that the winner can fulfil his wish

title: Conjure X
description: An anthology of short films about supernatural creatures from another world that terrorise people who must fight and beat the former.

title: Invoking 5
description: When a housewife hears strange noises from the walls of her house, she must get to the bottom of the haunted mystery and survive the night.

title: Married to a Murderer
description: After the death of their mother, Ted and Frank go their separate ways. However, during Ted's marriage to Emma, Frank shows up and threatens to reveal a dark secret.

title: Bloody Mary Returns
description: A group of vloggers are looking for the ultimate urban legend and soon discover the legend of Bloody Mary is very much real. Now, the group is stuck under her curse and will have to learn how to stop Bloody Mary once and for all before it's too late.1.A group of vloggers are looking for the ultimate urban legend and soon discover the legend of Bloody Mary is very much real. Now, the group is stuck under her curse and will have to learn how to stop Bloody Mary once and for all before it's too late.

title: Mr. What
description: An inspirational drama about Mattiesko Wuopio, a man who has spent twenty-two years in prison for a crime he did not commit. Upon apprehension of the real criminal, Mattiesko is released, only to face the stigma of jail time as he re-enters society in tiny Tecumseh, Michigan.

title: Tiger Nageshwar Rao
description: Ravi Teja

title: Harry Potter
description: Hola, soy Only McQueen, mi pasión es crear los mejores videos para el entretenimiento. Hago videos desde 2015, gameplays originales, de alta calidad y con contenido útil para una audiencia general. Por cosas que pasaron en mi vida tuve que dejar de hacer videos en el canal pero ahora puedo regresar. Mi pasión creció y ahora en 2022 quiero hacer nuevos videos en diferentes idiomas agregándoles mi propio valor único de una manera original y creativa como lo hice en el pasado. Reproduzco, grabo y edito todos mis videos y es mucho trabajo duro, así que espero que les guste y por favor no lo vuelvan a resubir.

title: A Grande Caçada
description: Um caçador de veados foi levado por algo na floresta do Alabama. Apenas seu rifle, sangue e uma pegada de 16" foram deixados para trás... Cinco anos depois, seu filho busca vingança.

title: A Caça
description: Lucas (Mads Mikkelsen) trabalha em uma creche. Boa praça e amigo de todos, ele tenta reconstruir a vida após um divórcio complicado, no qual perdeu a guarda do filho. Tudo corre bem até que, um dia, a pequena Klara (Annika Wedderkopp), de apenas cinco anos, diz à diretora da creche que Lucas lhe mostrou suas partes íntimas.

title: A Lição
description: Fin (Evan Bendall) e Joel (Rory Coltart) são dois adolescentes que desperdiçam suas vidas pelas paisagens rurais áridas da cidade em que vivem, porém, a má educação deles está prestes a mudar. Atormentado por jovens problemáticos que fazem sua ira, um professor no fim das suas forças decide ensinar uma lição que eles nunca mais esquecerão.

title: Magal e os Formigas
description: João é um aposentado que está chateado com a vida. Viciado em loterias, ele nunca conseguiu ganhar dinheiro com isso. Um dia, porém, ele começa a receber visitas sobrenaturais do cantor Sidney Magal.

title: Spirit of Fear
description: Trying to regain his memory, a man must evade a demonic presence while following the clues left for him to discover his past.

title: Alternate Ground
description: After disappearing overnight, a teenage boy's unexplained behaviour causes concern. A lack of medical answers leads to a revelation of extraterrestrial abduction.

title: Swap Out
description: Two couples have a drug and alcohol-fueled night of fun, games, and partner swapping, but things turn dark the morning after they sober up

title: The Employer
description: Five applicants give interviews for a coveted position at Carcharias Corporation. Things take a turn to the dark side when just before the final round, they are drugged and locked in a room.

title: Recreator
description: Three friends tumble into trouble, when an accident in a science lab brings them face-to-face with their own clones. Faster, stronger and much better than them, how will the three escape their clones?

title: The Evil Within
description: A lonely and mentally disabled boy who lives with his older brother is urged by a reflection in an antique mirror to go on a murderous rampage.

title: The Shadow People
description: A newlywed (Kat Steffens) is plagued by voices and strange visions shortly after she and her husband (Bug Hall) move into their dream home.

title: The Night Visitor 2: Heather's Story
description: A special girl has to protect her family and the planet from an other-worldly being.

title: Señorita Arizona
description: La ex-señorita Arizona se convirtió en una ama de casa en un matrimonio infeliz. Pero su vida va a cambiar repentinamente al conocer a un grupo de mujeres empoderadas en un grupo de apoyo.

title: La Decisión De Alison
description: Narra la historia de una adolescente que se enfrenta a la realidad de un embarazo. Sin ningún lugar a donde ir y en medio de su soledad, se encuentra en una «clínica» a punto de terminar con la vida de su bebé.

title: الانسة مامي
description: Ms. Mammy  : نبيلة سيدة أعمال ناجحة ترفض الزواج. تتغير حياتها عندما تحلم بأنها متزوجة ولديها طفلين.

title: احكي يا شهرزاد
description: Ehky Ya Sharhazad : عندما يعلم كريم الذي يعمل في إحدى الصحف أن البرنامج الحواري السياسي الذي تقدمه زوجته قد يكون عائقًا أمام ترقيته، يقنعها بالتركيز على مواضيع غير مثيرة للجدل

title: عماليات خاصة
description: Amaleyat Khasa : يقوم الضابط أدهم بتجنيد مجموعة من الأشخاص لتنفيذ مجموعة من المهام الخاصة. يقوم بتوظيف وتدريب مهندسي السيارات، شريف وعمر، ومتخصص سوق الأوراق المالية، يوسف.

title: Un Amor Más Grande
description: Basada en una historia real, la película presenta los acontecimientos en la vida de Kurt Kuykendall, (Jason Burkey, «Bebé de octubre», «El poder del amor»). El chico de oro lo tiene todo: buen parecer, un lugar en el equipo de basquetbol en la universidad y la esperanza de llegar a las Olimpiadas

title: Cicatrices
description: Los Conflictos dentro del matrimonio, la Pugna por el trono del hogar.Las cosas que se dicen con el afán de ofender y que se quedan en el recuerdo por mucho tiempo.

title: Solución Final
description: Basada en una historia real, esta película cuenta sobre el adoctrinamiento de Gerrit Wolfaardt: sus tradiciones familiares, historia, cultura, incluso su iglesia, le han enseñado que los sudafricanos negros son un cáncer en la tierra.

title: Who Killed Soul Glow?
description: Soul Glow is murdered. No suspect, no witness, no way to identify the case.

title: Venus & Vegas
description: When three Vegas buddies attempt the score of a lifetime, they have to walk a fine line between their girlfriends who want their heads, and the mobsters who want them dead.

title: Asteroid
description: An out of touch family man leaves the big city for a dream house in a small town with his wife and daughter just before the end of the world.

title: Outlaw's Buckle
description: During a terrible storm, a serial killer wreaks havoc inside of a Texas prison.

title: The Driver
description: A criminal getaway driver plays by his code and set of rules for years. When he is forced to break his rules, it starts a domino effect of chaos in an already dangerous world of treacherous players.

title: Return to the Hiding Place
description: Piet Hartog and his friends form a resistance and fight to save innocent lives when the Nazi forces begin persecuting the Jews in Holland.

title: A Wave of Kindness
description: A young journalist embarks on a quest to find happy stories of resilience and compassion amid his own personal struggles.

title: Tulsa
description: An alcoholic biker must confront his demons when the nine-year-old daughter he never knew existed enters his life.

title: King's Faith
description: Brendan (Crawford Wilson) tries to leave his violent gang life behind, but his past continues to threaten his new faith, family and future.

title: Seventy Times Seven
description: After his wife is murdered, David Andersen sets out to find her killer. Along the way, he struggles with the scripture verse that asks one to love his enemies.

title: The Kitchen
description: In a dystopian future London where all social housing has been eliminated, Izi and Benji fight to navigate the world as residents of The Kitchen, a community that refuses to abandon their home.

title: Night Swim
description: Forced into early retirement by a degenerative illness, former baseball player Ray Waller moves into a new house with his wife and two children. He hopes that the backyard swimming pool will be fun for the kids and provide physical therapy for himself.

title: Wish
description: Young Asha makes a wish so powerful that it's answered by a cosmic force, a little ball of boundless energy called Star. With Star's help, Asha must save her kingdom from King Magnifico and prove that when the will of one courageous human connects with the magic of the stars, wondrous things can happen.

title: Princess Cut 3: Beauty From Ashes
description: A down-on-her-luck waitress witnesses a domestic disturbance and develops an unexpected relationship with the policeman investigating the case.

title: Gibsonburg
description: In Ohio, a high-school athlete (Louis Bonfante) struggles with family problems and romance while his baseball team struggles with a losing record.

title: Triunfo en la Adversidad
description: Travis, un joven deportista y estrella del equipo estudiantil de su escuela en el poblado de Corbin. Debido a una fuerte infección, el chico queda totalmente ciego. Travis debe decidir si vivirá el resto de su vida encerrado en la seguridad de su hogar o si se atreverá a salir y retomar su vida con la ayuda y el apoyo de sus padres y amigos.

title: Cautivado
description: Presenta la apreciación de expertos, al igual que testimonios personales de individuos y familias que han logrado escapar de la adicción a la tecnología y han aprendido a tomar decisiones inteligentes que honran a Dios en el uso de la comunicación del Siglo XXI.

title: Siempre un Ganador
description: Emily Hilton se transfiere a una nueva escuela secundaria cristiana para su último año decidida a repetir como campeona estatal de golf. Cuando comienza esa búsqueda, su nuevo entrenador de golf y sus compañeros de equipo la afectan mucho.

title: Gracia Navideña
description: Una juguetería propiedad de un cristiano tiene que lidiar con un competidor malvado que abre una tienda más grande al otro lado de la calle con el propósito de cerrar la tienda más pequeña. Esta es una historia conmovedora con un mensaje navideño muy evangelístico.

title: El Medallón Perdido
description: Con la participación de Alex Kendrick, El Medallón Perdido es la historia de Billie y Allie, dos amigos de 13 años encuentran un medallón que había estado perdido por cientos de años y accidentalmente los transporta al pasado a una isla remota gobernada por Cobra, un guerrero del mal.

title: Interceptor Force 2
description: Dans un futur proche, le gouvernement a créé une équipe d’élite composée de soldats spécialement entraînés en cas de rencontre avec des extraterrestres hostiles.

title: KM31
description: Agata fait sortir sa voiture de la route en évitant un enfant nu ; laissée dans le coma, sa sœur jumelle Catalina commence à enquêter et découvre une ancienne histoire d'une jeune Indienne trompée par son amant espagnol lors de la conquête du pays.

title: Peguei o último trem
description: Filme gospel completo dublado "Peguei o último trem" Entre na arca dos últimos dia

title: Minha história, nossa história
description: ang Yi, um líder de igreja, é preso em uma das campanhas de prisão em massa do Partido Comunista Chinês e condenado a dez anos na prisão. Sob o monitoramento estrito e as exigências de trabalho escravo dos guardas da prisão, ele se sente péssimo e atormentado e anseia pelo suprimento das palavras de Deus.

title: O fogo do ourives
description: Filme Testemunho de Fé "O fogo do ourives" O Milagre da Vida Florescendo na Prisão dos Demônios

title: Batismo de fogo
description: Filme gospel "Batismo de fogo" A única senda para entrar no reino dos céus

title: O povo do reino dos céus
description: Filme gospel "O povo do reino dos céus" Somente pessoas honestas podem entrar no reino dos céus

title: Crew
description: क्रू 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की कॉमेडी फिल्म है, जो राजेश ए कृष्णन द्वारा निर्देशित है और इसमें तब्बू, करीना कपूर खान और कृति सेनन ने एयर होस्टेस की भूमिका निभाई है। दिलजीत दोसांझ और कपिल शर्मा सहायक भूमिकाएँ निभाते हैं।

title: Surkhi Bindi
description: ਕੈਨੇਡਾ ਪਰਵਾਸ ਕਰਨ ਦਾ ਸੁਪਨਾ ਪਾਲਦੀ ਰਾਣੋ ਨੂੰ ਸੁੱਖਾ ਨਾਲ ਵਿਆਹ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਮਜਬੂਰ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾਂਦਾ ਹੈ। ਆਪਣੇ ਪਤੀ ਦੇ ਸਹਿਯੋਗ ਨਾਲ, ਉਹ ਲੋੜੀਂਦੇ ਪੈਸੇ ਬਚਾਉਣ ਲਈ ਇੱਕ ਬਿਊਟੀ ਪਾਰਲਰ ਖੋਲ੍ਹਦੀ ਹੈ, ਇਸ ਗੱਲ ਤੋਂ ਅਣਜਾਣ ਕਿ ਅੱਗੇ ਕੀ ਹੈ।

title: Por Esta Razón
description: POR ESTA RAZÓN presenta un viaje rápido a través del libro más vendido en la historia—la Biblia (las Escrituras de los profetas).

title: Road House
description: Ex-UFC fighter Dalton takes a job as a bouncer at a Florida Keys roadhouse, only to discover that this paradise is not all it seems.

title: Patna Shukla
description: एक आम महिला की, असामान्य लड़ाई और धैर्य।

title: Shaitaan
description: शैतान 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की अलौकिक हॉरर फिल्म है, जो विकास बहल द्वारा निर्देशित और देवगन फिल्म्स, जियो स्टूडियो और पैनोरमा स्टूडियो द्वारा निर्मित है। फिल्म में अजय देवगन, आर.माधवन, ज्योतिका, जानकी बोदीवाला और अंगद राज हैं।

title: Woh Bhi Din The
description: एक प्रसिद्ध फोटो जर्नलिस्ट एक अतिथि वक्ता के रूप में अपने अल्मा मेटर में लौटता है, अपने लापरवाह स्कूल के दिनों और पहले प्यार के बारे में याद करता है

title: Swatantra Veer Savarkar
description: स्वातंत्र्य वीर सावरकर विनायक दामोदर सावरकर के जीवन पर 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की जीवनी पर आधारित फिल्म है। इसका निर्देशन, सह-लेखन और सह-निर्माता रणदीप हुडा द्वारा किया गया है, जो सावरकर की मुख्य भूमिका भी निभाते हैं।

title: Ae Watan Mere Watan
description: 1942 में भारत के स्वतंत्रता संग्राम के बीच, एक बहादुर युवा लड़की ने एकता का संदेश फैलाने के लिए एक भूमिगत रेडियो स्टेशन शुरू किया, और भारत छोड़ो आंदोलन के दौरान ब्रिटिश अधिकारियों के साथ एक रोमांचक लड़ाई शुरू की।

title: Madame Web
description: कैसेंड्रा वेब न्यूयॉर्क शहर की एक अर्धचिकित्सक है जिसमें दूरदर्शिता के लक्षण दिखाई देने लगते हैं। अपने अतीत के बारे में रहस्योद्घाटन का सामना करने के लिए मजबूर होकर, उसे तीन युवा महिलाओं को एक रहस्यमय प्रतिद्वंद्वी से बचाना होगा जो उन्हें मरना चाहता है।

title: Fighter
description: शमशेर पठानिया ने अपने आजीवन सपने को पूरा किया और भारतीय वायु सेना के सदस्य बने। कड़ी चुनौतियों का सामना करते हुए, पैटी को एक सच्चा हीरो बनने के लिए अपनी सीमाओं से ऊपर उठना होगा।

title: Article 370
description: आतंकवाद और भ्रष्टाचार पर नकेल कसने के लिए एक शीर्ष-गुप्त मिशन के लिए प्रधान मंत्री कार्यालय से एक युवा फील्ड एजेंट को चुना जाता है।

title: House of Ninjas
description: अपने दुर्जेय निंजा जीवन से सेवानिवृत्त होने के वर्षों बाद, एक बेकार परिवार को उभरते खतरों का मुकाबला करने के लिए रहस्यमय मिशनों में वापस लौटना होगा।

title: Love Storiyaan
description: छह जोड़ों के साथ सीमाओं पर काबू पाने की उनकी असाधारण कहानियाँ

title: Sabina K
description: Una madre divorciada con dos hijos se enamora de un viejo amigo hasta que las cosas van terriblemente mal en sus familias.

title: Kung Fu Panda 4
description: Po must train a new warrior when he's chosen to become the spiritual leader of the Valley of Peace. However, when a powerful shape-shifting sorceress sets her eyes on his Staff of Wisdom, he suddenly realizes he's going to need some help. Teaming up with a quick-witted corsac fox, Po soon discovers that heroes can be found in the most unexpected places.

title: ગુલામ ચોર
description: Gulaam Chor... રોકડ જીતવા માટે અશ્વિનના ઘરે પોકર ગેમ રમવા માટે બાર વ્યક્તિઓ ભેગા થાય છે. જો કે, જ્યારે મધ્યરાત્રિએ લાઇટ બંધ થાય છે ત્યારે વસ્તુઓ વળાંક લે છે.

title: વ્હાલમ જાઓ ને
description: Vaahlam Jaao Ne... સુમિત એક વિચિત્ર માણસ છે જે તેને પ્રેમ કરતી રીના સાથે લગ્ન કરવામાં અચકાય છે. જો કે, તેણીના પિતાને મળવાની તેણીની દરખાસ્તને નકારવામાં તેની અસમર્થતા શ્રેણીબદ્ધ દુર્ઘટનાઓ શરૂ કરે છે.

title: Coma
description: After an accident, Viktor, an architect, finds himself in a strange new world. He must learn the laws of the land while trying to navigate his way into the real world.

title: King Lear
description: Cordelia, the youngest daughter of King Lear, is left to survive on her own after the end of her father's reign, as she is denied a share of his kingdom.

title: Lawless
description: Set in the prohibition-era Virginia, the loyalty of three bootleggers, the Bondurant Brothers, is put to the test when they refuse to pay the required bribe to the corrupt authorities.

title: Death of Me
description: A hungover couple makes a horrific discovery about the events of the previous night. They try to deconstruct the night to the best of their memories while waiting for a typhoon to pass.

title: Room 203
description: The lives of childhood friends Kim and Izzy change when they move into Room 203, a quirky apartment with large stained-glass windows depicting medieval sacrifices and a sinister past.

title: Borrego
description: After witnessing a drug mule's plane crash in the Borrego desert, Elly is kidnapped and forced on a dangerous journey to a remote drop-off point. With limited essentials and alone in the desert with her captor, desperation for survival takes hold as Elly risks her life to escape from his clutches before the trip turns deadly.

title: Dangerous
description: Dylan, a sociopath, escapes from prison to attend his brother Sean's funeral. Once there, he must not only struggle with his own mental health issues but also contend with a group of mercenaries.

title: Bad Samaritan
description: Aya, a spa owner, welcomes Taryn, a former college friend, into her home. Little does she know that her guest will go to any lengths to create the family bond she has wanted all her life.

title: Kung Fu Panda 4
description: Po must train a new warrior when he's chosen to become the spiritual leader of the Valley of Peace. However, when a powerful shape-shifting sorceress sets her eyes on his Staff of Wisdom, he suddenly realizes he's going to need some help. Teaming up with a quick-witted corsac fox, Po soon discovers that heroes can be found in the most unexpected places.

title: The Least Of These: A Christmas Story
description: A single mother and her daughter find hope in a small town. The mother, eventually, meets an art collector who could change her course of life.

title: Translated
description: Saint Paul is mysteriously transported from ancient Rome to present day America. As time passes, he starts to question contemporary Christianity.

title: A Heart That Forgives
description: Brought up together, two foster brothers choose different paths. While Malcolm decides to pastor a small church, Silk takes a dark road.

title: Lost Heart
description: Hannah, a burnt out, mega-music star, returns to her small Northern Michigan hometown of Lost Heart, for her estranged father's funeral. There she will confront the ghosts of her past and perhaps find her peace and balance once again.

title: Steps of Faith
description: Mocked by her family for following a directive from God to work on a hippotherapy farm for children, Faith questions the message she received when a child is nearly injured and the work, including the horse manure shovelling, is overwhelming.

title: Hoovey
description: Mientras practica, cuando Eric 'Hoovey' Elliot se desploma en el suelo, se entera de que tiene un tumor en el cerebro. Después de una peligrosa y arriesgada cirugía, comienza a reaprender todo.

title: Pablo el último Apóstol
description: Cuenta la historia de la conversión y ministerio del apóstol Pablo, quien fue perseguidor de los cristianos antes de su encuentro con Jesucristo. La trama se desarrolla en la Roma del siglo I, mostrando los desafíos y peligros que enfrentaron los primeros cristianos.

title: Camino A Emaus
description: Dos viajeros que lloran la muerte de Jesucristo se encuentran con un extraño que les revela varios misterios escondidos en las antiguas escrituras sobre la vida de Jesús.

title: 77 Oportunidades
description: Un aspirante a fotógrafo sufre una confusión interior mientras sigue reviviendo un día trágico una y otra vez.

title: Abedules
description: Un reconocido escritor y conferencista se encuentra repentinamente dudando de su propia fe y dispuesto a abandonar su carrera, al verse enfrentado a la muerte inesperada de su amada esposa.

title: Lucy Shimmers e o Príncipe da Paz
description: Uma menina precoce forma uma amizade improvável com um criminoso empedernido enquanto ambos estão confinados no mesmo hospital.

title: O banquete do reino dos céus
description: O Banquete do Reino dos Céus” A verdadeira história de um padre que acolheu o Senhor Cheng Mingde é um padre católico. Ele vê que a Igreja Católica está se tornando cada vez mais desolada e sombria e que até mesmo os bispos e outros padres cederam ao governo ao aderirem à Igreja das Três Autonomias.

title: Reflexões sobre a Salvação
description: Yang Mingyuan é presbítero numa igreja doméstica. Um dia, ele fica sabendo que o presbítero Xu, que é altamente respeitado na igreja, aceitou a Relâmpago do Oriente. Ele fica muito comovido e decide buscar e investigar a Relâmpago do Oriente.

title: Fé em Deus 3
description: Meng Changlin, obreiro da Igreja das Três Autonomias, inicialmente achava que crer no Senhor na Igreja das Três Autonomias o pouparia da perseguição do Partido Comunista Chinês. Porém, depois que Xi Jinping assumiu o poder, o Partido reforçou sua perseguição contra a fé religiosa, e até a Igreja das Três Autonomias, comandada pelo governo, começou a sofrer opressão e perseguição.

title: A tão aguardada felicidade
description: A fim de ganhar bastante dinheiro para viver uma vida boa, Ding Ruilin e seu marido investiram muito trabalho duro para abrir e administrar uma empresa. Mas, graças ao abuso e exploração pelo governo do Partido Comunista Chinês, eles continuam com dívidas pesadas e não têm escolha senão ir para o exterior para trabalhar.

title: Mammoth
description: Leo and Ellen are a busy New York couple who dedicate more time to their jobs than their daughter Jackie. She eventually gets more attached to her nanny, who has left her own kids back in Philippines.

title: Sinister Minister
description: When Trish, a single mother, is smitten with DJ, a minister, she feels that she and her teenaged daughter Siena will have a sound familial life. But Trish is unaware of DJ's dark past.

title: Clare And Francis
description: Both born in Assisi, St. Clare and St. Francis decide to leave behind their lives of luxury to follow Jesus Christ. This drama follows their attempts to live out the Gospel by working with the poor and establishing their own religious orders

title: يا أنا يا خالتي
description: Ya Ana Ya Khalty : تيمور مصمم على الزواج من نوال، لكن والدتها ترفض مباركة زواجهما. وفي محاولة للحصول على موافقتها، يتنكر في هيئة وسيطة قديمة تدعى خالة نوسة.

title: إذاعة حب
description: Love Station : ليلى وفريدة، صديقتان مقرّبتان، تعملان معًا في محطة إذاعية. تتغير حياتهم عندما تقع ليلى في حب زميل العمل حسن وتخفي هويتها الحقيقية عنه.

title: بيبو وبشير
description: Bebo we Basheer : بشير، مدرب كرة السلة، وبيبو، عازف الطبول، يقيمان في نفس الشقة ولكنهما لا يعلمان بوجود بعضهما البعض. يلتقيان بالصدفة ويقعان في الحب دون أن يعلما أنهما يعيشان في نفس المكان.

title: The Second Coming of Christ
description: The journey of a woman scientist who, at the end of times, discovers that true faith can bring miracles.

title: Wildflower
description: Chloe, a college student, turns to art to escape from traumatic childhood memories. However, she is soon haunted by recurring nightmares of a sinister incident that she cannot clearly remember.

title: Waiting for the Miracle to Come
description: An aspiring trapeze artist discovers a cryptic letter her father wrote, directing her to a remote gold mine. Upon her arrival, she meets two retired vaudeville stars who help her discover a greater reward.

title: To Save a Life
description: After his friend's accidental death, Jake Taylor changes his dangerous lifestyle and sacrifices his dreams in a tryst to save the lives of others.

title: Random Encounters
description: What seems to be a chance encounter one day at a coffee shop leads to a full-fledged romance. However, the couple must fight for their relationship to survive.

title: Las mentiras del comunismo
description: Zhang Mingdao es un cristiano de la Iglesia de Dios Todopoderoso que ha experimentado la obra de Dios Todopoderoso en los últimos días durante varios años, comprende algunas verdades y entiende el verdadero significado de la vida humana

title: Salvar Una Vida
description: Después de la muerte de un amigo de la infancia, un adolescente popular (Randy Wayne) arriesga su propia posición social al acercarse a compañeros de clase que normalmente son rechazados.

title: Cuestion de Principios
description: Queriendo demostrar que todo el mundo tiene un precio, un jefe se dirige a un nuevo empleado que tiene una ética inquebrantable.

title: El ataque del tiburón de cinco cabezas
description: Un tiburón monstruo de cinco cabezas patrulla alrededor de una isla devorando todo lo que sea de carne y hueso. La policía y el equipo del acuario entran en acción y hacen todo lo posible para matar al monstruo.

title: En tu cabeza
description: Un atraco, un asesinato, una cárcel y una historia de amor. La tercera edición de Cinergía llega con cuatro historias con un final conjunto, una película de eficiencia ficción con la que, en cada parte, aprenderás consejos sobre eficiencia energética mientras lo pasas de cine.

title: O mensageiro do evangelho
description: A cristã Chen Yixin tem acreditado no Senhor por muitos anos e teve a felicidade de saudar o retorno do Senhor Jesus – Deus Todo-Poderoso! Ela veio a entender a vontade urgente de Deus de salvar a humanidade a partir das palavras de Deus Todo-Poderoso e a missão e responsabilidade que um ser criado deve assumir

title: As mentiras do comunismo
description: "As mentiras do Comunismo", um filme cristão, é um reflexo preciso da lavagem cerebral que o governo do Partido Comunista da China usa contra os cristãos. Após a prisão de Zhang Mingdao e de sete outros cristãos, a polícia do Partido Comunista da China emprega tortura brutal e desumana contra eles.

title: Ignorância fatal
description: Zheng Mu'en é colaborador de uma igreja cristã chinesa nos EUA. Ele crê no Senhor há muitos anos, trabalha com paixão e se gasta pelo Senhor. Um dia, sua tia testemunhou para ele que o Senhor Jesus voltou para expressar a verdade e realizar a obra de julgar e purificar o homem nos últimos dias.

title: O caminho para o reino dos céus é perigoso
description: O cristão Zhong Xin é pregador numa igreja doméstica na China continental. Ele leva seus irmãos e irmãs a investigarem o caminho verdadeiro e determina que Deus Todo-Poderoso é o retorno do Senhor Jesus

title: Esperando
description: Yang Hou'en era pastor de uma igreja doméstica na China. Ele tinha esperado vigilantemente o Senhor Jesus descer das nuvens e levá-lo para o reino do céu. Com esse objetivo, ele trabalhou diligentemente para o Senhor, perseverou em Seu nome e acreditava que qualquer um que não fosse o Senhor Jesus descendo das nuvens seria um Cristo falso.

title: Te Ata
description: Basierend auf der wahren Geschichte von Mary Thompson Fisher (Q'orianka Kilcher), weithin bekannt als Te Ata, die kulturelle Barrieren überwindet, um als Schauspielerin und Geschichtenerzählerin der amerikanischen Ureinwohner berühmt zu werden.

title: Oskar - Gehen, wenn's am Schönsten ist
description: Buchhändler Oskar erhält eine schlechte Nachricht: Er hat nur noch vier Wochen zu leben. Jetzt muss er entscheiden, wofür er sie ausgeben möchte

title: Oro La Cité perdue
description: Un groupe de soldats espagnols part à la recherche de Teziutlan, une ville légendaire créée avec de l'or. Cependant, ils sont consumés par la rivalité et la haine entre eux.

title: عمر وسلمى 2
description: Omar & Salma 2... بعد قصة حب عاصفة، تزوج عمر وسلمى وأنجبا فتاتين جميلتين. ومع ذلك، يبدأ عمر في القلق بشأن الأيام الخوالي ويبدأ في فقدان الاهتمام بزواجه.

title: عمر وسلمى 3
description: Omar & Salma 3... يترك عمر وظيفة محترمة ليصبح مغنيًا، مما يجعل زوجته سلمى تطلب الطلاق. يخطط للانتقام منها، لكن خططه تدمر عندما يقرر والده التدخل.

title: نور عيني
description: Noor Eieny... أحمد، الشاب الذي يدرس ليصبح فنانًا، يقع في حب سارة، الشابة التي تعاني من إعاقة بصرية. تنشأ التوترات عندما تسافر للعلاج وتعود مخطوبة لصديقه.

title: تيمور و شفيقة
description: Taymour and Shafika... تيمور وشفيقة صديقان منذ الطفولة. يتم اختبار حبهما عندما تكبر شفيقة لتصبح وزيرة وتيمور حارسها الشخصي.

title: Kali Jotta
description: Kali Jotta Punjabi Vijay Kumar Arora, Harinder Kour ,Satinder Sartaaj, Neeru Bajwa and Wamiqa Gabbi.The Punjabi movie "Kali Jotta has an intriguing narrative where the plot takes an unexpected turn when the happy-go-lucky character of Neeru Bajwa - Rabiya secures a government position as a primary school teacher where she faces extreme harassment at the hands of her male colleagues.

title: Amar Singh Chamkila
description: एक विनम्र गायक के तेज बोल पूरे पंजाब में प्रसिद्धि और रोष पैदा करते हैं क्योंकि वह अपनी असामयिक मृत्यु से पहले भारी सफलता और क्रूर आलोचना से जूझ रहा है।

title: Bade Miyan Chote Miyan
description: संभ्रांत सैनिकों ने एक नकाबपोश पागल से चोरी किए गए हथियार को बरामद करने के लिए टीम बनाई जो भारत को नष्ट करना चाहता है।

title: Maidaan
description: मैदान 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की जीवनी पर आधारित स्पोर्ट्स ड्रामा फिल्म है, जो अमित रविंदरनाथ शर्मा द्वारा सह-लिखित और निर्देशित है और आकाश चावला, अरुणव जॉय सेनगुप्ता, बोनी कपूर और ज़ी स्टूडियो द्वारा निर्मित है। रोब मिलर और रीलस्पोर्ट्स द्वारा खेल कार्रवाई।

title: Madgaon Express
description: बचपन के दोस्त डोडो, आयुष और पिंकू गोवा की यात्रा पर निकलते हैं जो कई भयानक फैसलों के कारण पूरी तरह से पटरी से उतर जाती है।

title: Kaam Chalu Hai
description: एक पिता अपनी बेटी गुड़िया और पत्नी राधा के साथ अपनी छोटी सी खुशहाल दुनिया को संजोते हुए अपने दर्द को एक क्रांतिकारी आंदोलन में बदल देता है। उनका मिशन गुड़िया के क्रिकेटर बनने के सपने को पूरा करना है।

title: Siren
description: एक दोषी एंबुलेंस ड्राइवर बेसब्री से जेल से अपनी रिहाई का इंतजार कर रहा है, लेकिन इसमें 14 साल लगेंगे।

title: Jee Ve Sohneya Jee
description: ਜੀਵੇ ਸੋਹਣਿਆ ਜੀ 2024 ਦੀ ਇੱਕ ਭਾਰਤੀ ਪੰਜਾਬੀ ਫਿਲਮ ਹੈ ਜੋ ਥਾਪਰ ਦੁਆਰਾ ਨਿਰਦੇਸ਼ਤ ਹੈ। ਇਸ ਵਿੱਚ ਸਿਮੀ ਚਾਹਲ ਅਤੇ ਇਮਰਾਨ ਅੱਬਾਸ ਮੁੱਖ ਭੂਮਿਕਾਵਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਹਨ ਅਤੇ ਮਿੰਟੂ ਕਪਾ, ਉਦੈ ਵਕਤੀ ਸੂਰਿਆਨਾਰਾਇਣ, ਕੇਤਾਬਚੀ ਐਸ਼, ਅਲੈਗਜ਼ੈਂਡਰ ਗਾਰਸੀਆ, ਲੀ ਨਿਕੋਲਸ ਹੈਰਿਸ ਅਤੇ ਚੇਤਨ ਮੋਹਤੂਰੇ ਸਹਾਇਕ ਭੂਮਿਕਾਵਾਂ ਵਿੱਚ ਹਨ।

title: Premalu
description: ഗിരീഷ് എ.ഡി സംവിധാനം ചെയ്ത് ഫഹദ് ഫാസിലും ഫ്രണ്ട്സും വർക്കിംഗ് ക്ലാസ് ഹീറോയും ചേർന്ന് ഭാവന സ്റ്റുഡിയോസ് നിർമ്മിച്ച 2024 ലെ ഇന്ത്യൻ മലയാളം-ഭാഷാ റൊമാൻ്റിക് കോമഡി ചിത്രമാണ് പ്രേമലു.

title: The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It
description: Arne Cheyenne Johnson stabs and murders his landlord, claiming to be under demonic possession while Ed and Lorraine Warren investigate the case and try to prove his innocence

title: Sniper: G.R.I.T. - Global Response & Intelligence Team
description: When an international terrorist cult threatens global political stability and kidnaps a fellow agent, ace sniper Brandon Beckett and the newly-formed Global Response & Intelligence Team -- or G.R.I.T. -- led by Colonel Stone, must travel across the world to Malta, infiltrate the cult, and take out its leader to free Lady Death and stop the global threat.

title: Arcadian
description: In the near future on a decimated Earth, Paul and his twin sons find tranquility by day but terror by night when ferocious creatures awaken and consume all living souls in their path. When Paul is nearly killed, the boys come up with a desperate plan for survival, using everything their father taught them to keep him alive.

title: Sting
description: Charlotte is a rebellious 12-year-old girl who finds a tiny spider in her rundown apartment building. She keeps it in a jar, but it soon starts to grow at a monstrous rate and develop an insatiable appetite for blood.

title: The Wages of Fear
description: Pour éviter une explosion mortelle, une équipe de crack clandestine a 24 heures pour conduire deux camions remplis de nitroglycérine à travers un désert plein de dangers.

title: Abigail
description: A group of would-be criminals kidnaps the 12-year-old daughter of a powerful underworld figure. Holding her for ransom in an isolated mansion, their plan starts to unravel when they discover their young captive is actually a bloodthirsty vampire.

title: The Ministry of Ungentlemanly Warfare
description: British Prime Minister Winston Churchill and a group of military officials hatch a daring plan to neutralize Hitler's fleet of German U-boats during World War II. Made up of a motley crew of rogues and mavericks, the top-secret combat unit uses unconventional techniques to battle the Nazis and change the course of the war.

title: The First Omen
description: A woman starts to question her own faith when she uncovers a terrifying conspiracy to bring about the birth of evil incarnate in Rome.

title: Monkey Man
description: A young man ekes out a meager living in an underground fight club where, night after night, wearing a gorilla mask, he's beaten bloody by more popular fighters for cash. After years of suppressed rage, he discovers a way to infiltrate the enclave of the city's sinister elite.

title: Migration
description: A family of ducks decides to leave the safety of a New England pond for an adventurous trip to Jamaica. However, their well-laid plans quickly go awry when they get lost and wind up in New York City.

title: Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets Of Dumbledore
description: डंबलडोर ने गेलर्ट ग्रिंडेलवाल्ड के उदय का विरोध करने के लिए जादूगरों, चुड़ैलों और मुगल बेकर की एक टीम को इकट्ठा किया। वे ग्रिंडेलवाल्ड को भ्रमित करने और उसे राजनीतिक शक्ति प्राप्त करने से रोकने की योजना बनाते हैं।

title: Queenpins
description: A housewife and her friend come up with a scheme to scam millions from big conglomerates through coupons. A loss prevention officer teams up with a postal inspector to track them.

title: Stillwater
description: Bill Baker heads to France to see his daughter Allison who was imprisoned for murdering her cheating lover, Lina. However, Allison claims she is innocent, which compels Bill to investigate further.

title: Forever Strong
description: An extremely talented rugby player is pitted against his fathers' team at a leading tournament.

title: Shake Off The World
description: Austin, a rising high school football star, gets rejected by his coach, forcing him to join a new school. However, when challenges arise in life, he has to overcome them by following his faith.

title: Redeeming The Time
description: Paul Vincent, who is a star athlete during his high school, faces many obstacles in life after an unexpected calamity strikes his family.

title: Sparks: The Ken Sparks Story
description: The life of NCAA football coach Ken Sparks, who for 46 years devoted his life, despite the sacrifices it demanded of him, to coaching the game of football in such a way that made him a legend.

title: Pitching Love and Catching Faith
description: Heather is an attractive softball player who finds it difficult to date boys. However, things change after she meets Tyler, a competitive baseball player, who also seems to like her.

title: The Legend of Tarzan
description: When Jane is abducted by the Belgian envoy Leon Rom while investigating the government's activities in the Congo, John must revert to his former self as Tarzan if he is to save his beloved wife.

title: Point Blank
description: Abe Guevara, a criminal, and Paul Booker, an ER nurse, form an unlikely alliance when the two decide to expose a group of corrupt policemen.

title: Cross Purposes
description: A driven young man headed to medical school reluctantly takes a temp job as a nurse’s assistant where a gravely ill teen teaches him about purpose.

title: Cowboy & Indiana
description: A former world champion bull rider struggles with his past as he takes on a court-mandated role of mentor to ten-year-old Indiana.

title: Win By Fall
description: A teenage wrestler is confident that he'll win a college scholarship until his coach unexpectedly moves him up two weight classes.

title: Uma Vida com Propósito
description: Rachel, uma estudante, ajuda as pessoas a resolverem seus problemas familiares, ajudando-as a abraçar a espiritualidade. No entanto, ela é assassinada por dois de seus colegas que pretendem mudar suas crenças.

title: Liberta das garras da morte
description: Liu Zhen, 78 anos, é uma típica dona de casa da zona rural. Depois de crer em Deus, ela sentiu uma alegria incomparável ao ler Sua palavra e cantar louvores a Ele todos os dias, reunindo-se frequentemente com seus irmãos e irmãs para comungarem a verdade… Entretanto, as coisas boas não duram para sempre.

title: A conversa
description: Jiang Xinyi e outros cristãos foram presos pelo governo do Partido Comunista da China; seus funcionários torturam brutalmente os cristãos a fim de confiscar os fundos da igreja e prender outros líderes da igreja

title: Rompendo Armadilhas
description: Há 2.000 anos, quando o Senhor Jesus realizou a obra da redenção, sofreu calúnias e condenações da comunidade religiosa judaica. Os líderes judeus uniram forças com o governo romano e O pregaram na cruz. Nos últimos dias, Deus Todo-Poderoso — o Senhor Jesus retornou em carne e osso — chegou à China para realizar a obra de julgamento.

title: Cântico da Vitória
description: A obra de julgamento de Deus Todo-Poderoso nos últimos dias tem reverberado por toda religiões e grupo. Sucedendo a propagação do evangelho do reino, as palavras de Deus Todo-Poderoso são aceitas e propagadas por mais e mais pessoas.

title: Filho, volte para casa
description: Li Xinguang é um aluno do 3º ano do ensino médio. Desde pequeno, ele sempre foi um garoto sensível e bem comportado. Seus pais e seus professores gostavam muito dele. Enquanto frequentava a escola secundária, ele ficou enfeitiçado por jogos de computador da internet.

title: Mindcage
description: When a copycat murderer strikes, Detectives Jake Doyle and Mary Kelly seek help from an incarcerated serial killer called the Artist. As Mary delves deep into the Artist's brilliant but twisted psyche, she and Jake get lured into a diabolical game of cat and mouse, racing against time to stay one step ahead of both criminals.

title: The Favourite
description: Queen Anne of England falls sick while her close aide Sarah Churchill oversees the country's important matters. Soon, things take a turn when Sarah's cousin Abigail starts serving the queen.

title: The Matrix Resurrections
description: Thomas Anderson's seemingly ordinary life ends when he accepts Morpheus's offer, only to wake up to a new, more secure and much more dangerous Matrix.

title: Starfish
description: While working at a dredging company, a diver seeks out the truth behind a tragic loss, but an unexpected romance could help or hinder her search.

title: Thanksgiving
description: A mysterious masked maniac terrorizes residents of Plymouth, Mass., one year after a Black Friday riot ended in tragedy. Picking off victims one by one, the seemingly random revenge killings soon become part of a larger, sinister plan.

title: The Nun II
description: 1956 में फ़्रांस में एक पादरी की हत्या हो जाती है और ऐसा लगता है कि एक बुराई फैल रही है। सिस्टर आइरीन का एक बार फिर शैतानी ताकत से आमना-सामना होता है।

title: Cobweb
description: Young Peter is plagued by a mysterious, constant noise from inside his bedroom wall -- a tapping that his parents insist is in his imagination. As his fear intensifies, he starts to believe that his parents are hiding a terrible and dangerous secret.

title: Squared Love Everlasting
description: Enzo proposes to Monica. However, before they can say 'I do' to each other, he has to face his past, while she has to deal with the problems of taking on a new position at school.

title: Flight of the Living Dead
description: A group of scientists smuggles a fellow expert, who is infected with a virus which revives the dead, on a plane. Gradually, the virus spreads to a few people who must fight for their survival.

title: The Hours
description: As Virginia Woolf begins writing her novel 'Mrs Dalloway', in the future, Laura Brown reads the novel to escape her monotonous life. Meanwhile, Clarissa Vaughan readies herself to host a party.

title: Your Place or Mine
description: Debbie and Peter are best friends and total opposites. She craves routine with her son in LA, but he thrives on change in NY. When they swap houses and lives for a week they discover what they think they want might not be what they really need.

title: Insidious: The Red Door
description: Josh Lambert heads east to drop his son, Dalton, off at school. However, Dalton's college dream soon becomes a living nightmare when the repressed demons of his past suddenly return to haunt them both.

title: Barbie
description: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.

title: Resident Evil: Death Island
description: Agent Chris Redfield and his team investigate a zombie outbreak in San Francisco. They follow a clue that leads them to Alcatraz Island, where a new horror awaits them.

title: Paradise
description: एक कंपनी एक ऐसी तकनीक विकसित करती है जो लोगों के बीच जीवनकाल को स्थानांतरित करना संभव बनाती है। जब उसकी पत्नी उसके कर्ज़ को चुकाने के लिए अपने जीवन के 40 वर्ष गँवा देती है, तो एक आदमी को उसे वापस पाने का एक रास्ता खोजना होगा।

title: Inside Job
description: The global financial meltdown that took place in Fall 2008 caused millions of job and home losses and plunged the United States into a deep economic recession. Matt Damon narrates a documentary that provides a detailed examination of the elements that led to the collapse and identifies keys financial and political players.

title: Bird Box
description: Years after an unseen entity wreaks havoc on humankind by compelling people to commit suicide, Malorie and her two children, blindfolded, undertake a dangerous journey in a bid to survive.

title: The Perfect Find
description: Everything is at stake for a 40-year-old woman: her career, her ticking biological clock, and her bank account. She risks it all for an intense, secret romance with the one person who could destroy her comeback.

title: Air
description: Sonny Vaccaro and Nike pursue basketball rookie Michael Jordan, creating a partnership that revolutionizes the world of sports and contemporary culture.

title: BlackBerry
description: Explores the incredible growth and tragic collapse of the world's first smartphone and how it smashed huge enterprises before surrendering to Silicon Valley's fiercely competitive companies.

title: Riddles Of The Sphinx
description: Robert Parr and his ex-lover Jessica must undo his father's mistake of releasing an ancient beast, the Sphinx, by seeking four mysterious stones which have the power to trap the beast.

title: Warbirds
description: A group of elite female aviators crash-lands on an eerie island during World War II and must fight enemy soldiers, repair their plane, and fend off flying dinosaurs if they hope to survive.

title: Drown the Clown
description: Claire Sable, who recently lost her daughter, Lily, in a drowning accident, struggles to cope and insists on preserving her belongings. However, when Lily's clown doll begins popping up in several places, Claire is spooked.

title: Blood Harvest
description: A small town with a dark past welcomes a visiting family, but the longer the family stays, the more danger they find themselves in.

title: Fire Serpent
description: A massive fireball from the sun strikes Earth and unleashes an invincible fire demon that starts possessing humans.

title: Trial by Fire
description: A lone female firefighter in a squad is blamed for her father's accidental death in a fire. Later, she sets out to prove her worthiness to a male-dominated crew and trains to become a smokejumper.

title: 9 Ball
description: Gail, a young talented woman, desires to become a professional 9-ball player. However, her uncle forces her to use her skills for pool hustling.

title: Judicial Indiscretion
description: Upon her nomination to the United States Supreme Court, respected judge Monica Barrett meets Jack Sullivan, an Irishman who claims to be a writer. What she discovers about Jack, however, is far worse.

title: Await the Dawn
description: An otherworldly evil terrorizes members of a troubled family and their captor.

title: The Descent
description: A group of friends set out on an expedition to a cave. Their adventure turns into a nightmare when they get trapped inside the cave and are pursued by bloodthirsty predators.

title: Chokehold
description: After the Russian mob kills her father, Zoey returns home from Las Vegas to join an underground fighting club, in an attempt to find the people responsible for her father's death.

title: Sumuru
description: In a future colony, women rule and men are used for insemination and manual labour.

title: Life Ain't Like The Movies
description: A quirky 16-year-old boy must learn to deal with his problems and survive an erratic high school life.

title: The Forgettable Life of Liam White
description: Liam White finds himself squashed under the burden of fame, fortune and writer's block. So, when he discovers that his cancer has relapsed, the author sets off on a journey of introspection.

title: The Legend Of Hawes
description: After a homestead is attacked by ravenous marauders, the lone survivor hires a dangerous gunman to help her track them down and get revenge.

title: Break Even
description: The lives of four friends change drastically after they find $50 million in cash that belongs to a ruthless kingpin during a weekend trip to a remote island.

title: Guardian
description: A Gulf War veteran, now a detective for the LAPD, battles a supernatural foe who was unleashed during an excavation in Iraq and is now searching for a child known as `the chosen one'. The detective must also tackle the rise of a new street drug, being sold by an evil disco-owner who is linked to the events in Iraq.

title: Caved In: Prehistoric Terror
description: While leading a team on a seemingly innocuous mission into a mine in Switzerland, John Palmer encounters evil beings and orders his men back to safety but the team leader pushes them to go on.

title: Acceleration
description: When Vladik, a notorious gangster, kidnaps her son, Rhona fights to fulfil his horrific demands and bring her child home.

title: Dark Storm
description: Scientists linked to a clandestine military base invent a device which supercharges dark matter. When the device breaks down, one scientist is plastered with dark matter, giving him superhuman powers.

title: Fixer
description: Thomas Chalk, Member of Parliament, will stop at nothing to ensure that his path back to political power is clear, enlisting the help of his "FIXER". The Fixer then takes Chalk’s son under his own wing, leading him on an urban socio-political odyssey of horror and twisted conspiracies and double-crosses.

title: Built to Kill
description: A selection of poignant yet disturbing stories of people who must resort to some less ideal means either for survival or to find their place in an arguably hopeless world.

title: Mercy For Angels
description: The daughter of an LA detective is abducted and tortured by thugs, who will sell her into sex slavery, if her mother cannot set her free in time.

title: Lost Padre Mine
description: For over two centuries the folklore surrounding the mysterious mother lode of gold hidden somewhere in the mountains north of El Paso del Norte has enflamed the imaginations of treasure hunters and truth seekers alike.

title: Mount Joy
description: An upcoming national tour could be the big break for small town rock sensations. However, the disappearance of the lead singer's girlfriend, who is also the band's manager, and the devastating secret she harbours could mean the end to it all.

title: Mile 19
description: Linda experiences the unexpected after she decides to go to the aid of a troubled stranger.

title: Civil War Saint
description: A wounded Civil War soldier wakes up to find the war has ended and his rescuer is an unexpected friend: a Saint Bernard who saves him and shows him the path home.

title: Pocket Full Of Game
description: Female hustler Porsha Garcia earned money, beauty and respect by being loyal and respecting the codes of the street game. Porsha is more than satisfied with her life until a chance encounter with a stickup kid named Fresh.

title: The Sighting
description: Two high school friends, Travis and Nate, are on a road trip to Canada when they're attacked by mysterious and vicious creatures. Nate is stolen into the woods and Travis will stop at nothing to get him back.

title: Amber's Descent
description: Strange events plague a renowned pianist when she relocates to an isolated farmhouse to complete her latest symphony.

title: Alta Vista
description: A screenwriter struggles to cope with the loss of his father and becomes entangled in the Hollywood underworld.

title: Angels Unaware
description: God sends the archangel, Eden, to Earth where she is purposely placed with people who are about to make a life decision that could negatively impact them and others around them.

title: Intermedio
description: Four unlucky friends encounter deadly creatures in tunnels on the Mexican border.

title: Monster X
description: Two friends hide in an old theater to escape ravenous hordes of vampires, zombies and werewolves.

title: The Paper Boat
description: A tragic incident connects the stories of some Los Angeles-based individuals who are fighting different battles in their respective lives.

title: Samurai Cop
description: A bitter samurai cop and his sidekick intend to get their revenge and bravely try to go after the Yakuza.

title: Gangster Exchange
description: Hiro and Marco are caught in a mob war in New York when they are asked to smuggle a 50-pound toilet made of pure heroin. Will they succeed in their attempts?

title: The Crossroads of Hunter Wilde
description: Following and EMP attack, Hunter Wilde and a group of Christian survivalists must defend the town of Crossroads from hordes of demons.

title: After Masks
description: People face fear, isolation, loneliness and financial hardships during the COVID-19 pandemic.

title: Intersection
description: A con man learns that his son has been abducted and takes to the streets of Sydney to complete a series of trials and appease the kidnapper.

title: A Story Worth Living
description: Allison Foster and her childhood best friend, Melissa, find themselves attending the same college in a small Midwestern town. Wanting to end her junior year strong, overachiever Allison receives a class assignment that goes beyond the classroom and encourages her to perceive life in a more positive light.

title: The Suffering
description: When a man gets trapped on a rural farm, he begins to encounter a sinister presence and finds himself fighting for his sanity.

title: Conversando Com Os Mortos
description: Seis meses após o suicídio de sua irmã Sofie, Megan ainda lamenta sua morte, mas se depara com pistas que levam a fatos muito perturbadores sobre a morte de Sofie, revelando segredos obscuros.

title: A Cabana
description: Após o desaparecimento de seu filho mais novo, Mack Phillips está gravemente deprimido. Sua vida toma um rumo improvável quando ele recebe uma carta misteriosa pedindo-lhe para visitar uma cabana.

title: Proyecto tiempo
description: “Proyecto Tiempo”, dirigida por Isabel Coixet, es la segunda película de Gas Natural Fenosa. Una trepidante historia protagonizada por Carmen Machi, Lluís Homar o Úrsula Corberó, entre otros artistas de nuestro cine para explicar la historia de Pablo Andrade, un científico que logrará cambiará el mundo pero no a su familia.

title: Una entrevista con dios
description: An Interview with God... La fe de un periodista prometedor se ve desafiada cuando se encuentra entrevistando a un hombre que dice ser Dios.

title: A Ti Te Queria Encontrar
description: A ti te quería encontrar is a 2018 Mexican romantic comedy film directed by Javier Colinas and written by Tamara Argamasilla. The film stars Eréndira Ibarra, Erick Elias, Luis Arrieta, and Paulette Hernández

title: Todo por Grace
description: Running for Grace... Un huérfano usa su vertiginosa velocidad para entregar medicinas a los recolectores de café en las montañas de Hawaii. El amor joven pronto florece cuando comienza un romance prohibido con la hija del dueño de una plantación.

title: Persiguiendo la Estrella
description: Chasing the Star... Tres sacerdotes magos atraviesan el desierto en duras condiciones sólo para encontrarse con el Rey recién nacido y pasar por varias dificultades en el proceso.

title: El truco del manco
description: Cuajo tiene 28 años, tiene parálisis cerebral y por ello enfrenta dificultades para moverse. Vive en los barrios marginales de Barcelona y es un talentoso cantante de rap que lucha junto con amigos para construir un estudio de música.

title: La teta asustada
description: Fausta padece una rara enfermedad por la que se encuentra en constante miedo y confusión. Ante la repentina muerte de su madre decide tomar medidas drásticas para no seguir los pasos de su madre.

title: Che El argentino
description: Ernesto Guevara, conocido como 'Che', lidera un grupo de exiliados cubanos bajo el mando de Fidel Castro en una revolución para derrocar a Fulgencio Batista, el dictador de Cuba.

title: Al final del camino
description: Nacho y Pilar se detestan. Para su decepción, se les encarga cubrir la historia de un gurú que resuelve problemas matrimoniales. Mientras fingen ser pareja, se enfrentan a situaciones inesperadas.

title: Babysitting
description: Franck est obligé de garder le fils de 12 ans de son patron Marc Schaudel après qu'il n'ait pas trouvé de gardien pour une nuit. Les choses tournent mal lorsque les amis de Franck visitent sa maison et lui font une surprise.

title: Tanguy
description: Malgré une vie réussie, Tanguy, 28 ans, vit toujours avec ses parents. Pour tenter de le faire déménager, ses parents tentent de lui rendre la vie misérable à la maison.

title: Le coup du siècle
description: Deux escrocs venus d'horizons très différents se rencontrent en route vers la Côte d'Azur et décident d'unir leurs forces et d'escroquer Thomas Westerburg, un milliardaire.

title: Click
description: Un architecte bourreau de travail découvre une télécommande universelle qui lui permet d'avancer et de reculer rapidement vers diverses parties de sa vie. Des complexités apparaissent lorsque la télécommande commence à outrepasser ses préférences.

title: Tulpen aus Amsterdam
description: Anna Lechner liebt ihre Arbeit als Blumengroßhändlerin in Amsterdam und hat ihren Traummann Ed Verkerk gefunden, einen ehrgeizigen Tulpenzüchter. Doch als ihr Vater stirbt, nimmt er ihr das Versprechen ab, sich um ihre jüngere Schwester Lilli zu kümmern.

title: Ein Sommer in der Provence
description: Drei junge Geschwister und ihr Vater machen einen Familienurlaub, um Kontakt zu ihrem Großvater Paul aufzunehmen, den sie nie getroffen haben. Doch als der Vater der Kinder geht, wird der Urlaub zum Albtraum.

title: Die letzten Tage des Parvis K
description: Parvis möchte sich mit seiner Tochter versöhnen, bevor seine Krankheit sein Leben kostet; Er reist mit dem Boot nach Spanien, wo sie seiner Meinung nach lebt, und schließt sich einer bunt zusammengewürfelten Gruppe anderer Einwanderer an, um die schwierige Suche auf sich zu nehmen.

title: Mutter Wider Willen
description: Die ehrgeizige Investmentmanagerin Sonja hat eine glänzende Karriere vor sich. Ihr Leben verändert sich plötzlich, als ihre Schwester bei einem Unfall ums Leben kommt. Ihre Kinder müssen bei Sonja einziehen. Die beiden sorgen überall für Chaos und bringen Sonjas Zeitplan durcheinander.

title: ظرف طارق
description: Zarf Tarek : يطلب فادي من طارق، الموظف في إحدى شركات الهاتف المحمول، الحصول على تفاصيل شخصية عن الشابة سارة. لكن بدلاً من نقل المعلومات، يلتقي طارق بسارة ويقعان في الحب.

title: الديلر
description: The Dealer : علي ويوسف يحتقران بعضهما البعض منذ الصغر. تنشأ التوترات عندما يلتقيان بعد دخولهما عالم تجارة المخدرات.

title: أل رهينة
description: Al Rahina : يصل مصطفى إلى أوكرانيا، حيث يشهد اختطاف عالم مصري. لاحقًا، ينطلق لإنقاذه في مكان لا يعرف عنه شيئًا.

title: شيكامارا
description: Shikamara : شيكامارا امرأة شابة متزوجة من زوج متهور. تعمل كسائقة ميكروباص لإعالة أطفالها. تلتقي بشبيهتها جايدا، وهي فتاة غنية تعيش بلا مبالاة لكنها تحاول تحسين نفسها من أجل حبيبها شريف.

title: سمير وشهير وباهر
description: Sameer & Shaheer & Baheer : سمير وشهير وبهير، ثلاثة إخوة غير أشقاء، يسرقون آلة الزمن التي صنعها رجل. إنهم يستخدمون الآلة التي تعيدهم في الوقت المناسب.

title: ابو شنب
description: Abu Shanab : ضابطة تحارب الأشخاص المسؤولين عن التحرش بالنساء وتسيء إليهم في الأماكن العامة. ولكن عندما تذهب لإلقاء القبض عليهم، تشهد عملية سطو.

title: عشان خارجين
description: Ashan Kharjeen : رمزي، شاب يخشى الالتزام، يلتقي بليلى ابنة مدير أعماله، ويقع في حبها. وفي إحدى الليالي، يعثرون على حقيبة مليئة بالنقود ويشرعون في مغامرات خطيرة للعثور على المالك.

title: Ebola Rex
description: Chaos strikes in Los Angeles when a diseased Tyrannosaurus rex escapes from a laboratory. As residents run for their lives, a general and a renegade soldier must deal with the monster on the loose.

title: Big Kill
description: Two gamblers on the run, a deadly preacher and a tenderfoot end up in a boomtown that is going through chaos.

title: Gossip Nation
description: Blacktown, in Sydney's West, is the home to a growing African community. Jealousy and tragedy haunt the characters as their lives are tainted with gossip, but always hold a hope for redemption, forgiveness and understanding.

title: Whisper
description: A young Nurse is assigned to look after a patient in a remote location in the English countryside. As the night continues she finds herself terrorized by an unseen force that is connected with her patient.

title: Of Dice And Men
description: Six role-playing game aficionados see their previously carefree lives shaken when one decides to enlist in the military to fight in Iraq. With one member of the group choosing to change things up, the rest begin to assess their lives, too.

title: The Adventures of Paula Peril
description: A sexy and determined reporter investigates brutal mobsters and supernatural villains.

title: Unchained
description: Kidnapped and forced into an underground fighting ring, a determined woman plans to overthrow her captors and save the lives of others doomed to the same endless cycle.

title: Trouble Is My Business
description: Detective Roland Drake falls for two sisters from the Montemar family. One woman is dead and the other wants to kill him. Passion, murder, and betrayal. Just another day at the office.

title: Couch Survivor
description: An executive of a failing cable network hosts a reality show in hopes of reviving the business. Seven people participate in the show where they compete to see who can stay on one couch the longest.

title: Love Me Till Monday
description: A Spell on You : A young woman, fresh from university, finds herself working a dead-end office job at the same time that she is trying to find love, a task that proves harder than it seems since she isn't quite sure who she is.

title: Battle B-Boy
description: A group of talented but financially struggling B-Boys join an underground fighting ring in Downtown Los Angeles that uses Hip-Hop music and Break dancing to battle for money. To save the life of one of their friend's father, the B-Boys form a strong bond. They fight for each other, for their families and for a better future.

title: Con Man
description: Barry Minkow is sentenced to prison for 25 years for running a fraudulent business. However, he makes an agreement with the FBI to apprehend criminals in exchange for an early release.

title: Breathe
description: A group of divers embarks on a trip to capture and explore the beauty of the ocean. However, on their latest dive, their oxygen tanks run low, putting their lives at risk as they encounter sharks and other marine wildlife.

title: Mermaid Down
description: A mermaid gets confined to a mental institution after her tail is cut off and she is captured. Later, a doctor tries to understand her behaviour and her past.

title: Me Familia 2
description: The story of Phillip Molinari Senior and his legacy of corruption, organised crime, and political influence, which continues to this day.

title: Cain And Abel
description: The traumas of childhood differences and disappointments leads two brothers on totally different paths. Finding their way back to one another, will the childhood traumas they've endured be too much and drive them even further apart?

title: Mysterious Circumstance: The Death of Meriwether Lewis
description: When explorer Meriwether Lewis suffers a mysterious and untimely death, the president sends a messenger to investigate. In a tense encounter with the only witness to his final night alive, the seemingly closed case of suicide begins to unravel.

title: Bitcon
description: A reformed criminal is forced back into the underground when a hard drive containing crypto goes missing and its value begins to skyrocket.

title: The Gift Of Grace
description: William and Cynthia work through a number of problems over 10 years of marriage and lavish their two daughters with love. However, when the going gets tougher, only time can tell if they will prevail or break apart.

title: S.O.S. Survive or Sacrifice
description: A group of individuals decides to take a ride in a hot air balloon. However, things go sideways when the balloon is carried far out in the sea without a pilot.

title: The Little Things
description: Dee (Kathryn Beck) thinks she has the ability to alter people's destinies as long as she never leaves her home. Facing eviction and the loss of her powers, Dee asks for help from Mitch (Chris Hillier), her first love and the first life she changed.

title: Diamond in the Rough
description: Michelle, a young teen in Colorado, loses her faith amidst extreme hardships and brief homelessness. With a mother battling drug and alcohol addiction since she was little, and war veteran father battling extreme PTSD, violence and dysfunction are.

title: The Way We Weren't
description: After ending their previous relationships, two people meet and try to impress each other by exaggerating and fibbing about themselves. However, once they move in together, their lies are revealed.

title: Astro Loco
description: An inquisitive ship computer tasked with overseeing safe, interplanetary voyage of the crew must cultivate a deeper sense of humanity to be effective amid the maniacal spread of cabin fever.

title: Fractional
description: A psychiatrist, John Hatchett, wakes up tied to a chair in an abandoned warehouse. Left with no food, water or chance of escape, John's only weapons are his mind and he must use them to full effect.

title: Killer Concept
description: Mark, a talented photographer, decides to have some fun by getting involved in a project that is fraught with the risk of exposing his biggest secret.

title: The Misadventures of Mistress Maneater
description: With only 30 days to repay a massive loan, a disgraced art historian is forced into a scandalous scheme to win the heart of, and then extort, an Episcopal priest.

title: Sold Out
description: A music-based drama about a female talent scout who takes a down-on-his-luck construction worker under her wing and helps him rise to his potential as a singer/songwriter.

title: Sweet Sunshine
description: A singer-songwriter hits the big time after a family tragedy, trying to put their past behind them and focus on their passion.

title: Awaken The Shadowman
description: Two estranged brothers, Adam and Jake, set out to search their mother who disappears mysteriously. Things change when they discover that a supernatural force targeting their family.

title: Bet On Ben
description: Ben tries to rekindle with a former love after a prison stint, but an old nemesis in the middle of an illegal arms deal puts him and his love in danger.

title: Band of Rebels
description: A band of Confederate soldiers use their unique set of skills to travel behind enemy lines and wreak havoc on the Union army.

title: Hamlet's Ghost
description: A Shakespearean actor travels back in time to confront forces from the past and future.

title: The Shattering
description: Claire has everything - money, a loving husband and a desired child. But suddenly her life changes. Doubts and lies bring her to the edge of insanity.

title: Blame
description: While on vacation in rural Wisconsin, five friends seek refuge in a lone building after their vehicle crashes in a vicious snowstorm. With no cell service, the group splits up to find help but when they reunite, one of them is found dead.

title: Ape Canyon
description: A mixed-up guy in the midst of a quarter-life crisis drags his big sister along on a Bigfoot-hunting expedition.

title: Painted Horses
description: Burdened with the responsibility of teaching an uninterested class, Pam Hoog devises an ingenious method of teaching the troublesome students.

title: El libro de la vida
description: Aqui tienen la pelicula ganadora la resubi por fallas tecnicas en el sistema, una disculpa. Saludos. Aqui abajo les dejo mis redes sociales oficiales para seguirme.

title: Escanaba in da Moonlight
description: A family of hunters in Michigan deals with the eldest son (Jeff Daniels) who has never shot his own deer.

title: These Streets We Haunt
description: Marcus, a corporate artist who's lost his zeal for life, rents out his spare bedroom to a girl he begins to suspect is a real life comic book villain.

title: The Internship Games
description: When six students across different universities are selected for an internship program, they must compete against each other to get that position.

title: Malibu Crush
description: Two best friends from Pasadena pretend to be celebrated film students in order to profess their love for an ex-girlfriend who lives in Sydney, Australia.

title: A Bad Idea Gone Wrong
description: Two thieves get trapped with a house-sitter after they accidentally set off the alarm. Later, things get heated up as the thieves slowly start turning on each other.

title: Doctor Mabuse
description: Inspector Carl Lohemann (Nathan Wilson) tries to stop criminal mastermind Dr. Mabuse (Jerry Lacy) when he returns from exile.

title: Crazy
description: Born in Nashville, Hank Garland grows to become a legendary guitar player in the 1950s. However, a car accident brings an end to the future of this promising musician.

title: Hawks Ridge
description: A black, grieving ex-pastor saves the life of the white man that killed his wife.

title: Maysville
description: Thirteen-year-old Teddy is taken from his family and forced into a life of hard labour after a tragic accident, but his past follows him after he escapes to the town of Maysville.

title: Mexican Moon
description: A Vietnam vet is forced to lose his job at a local garage after the drug cartels put a financial stranglehold on a small Texas town.

title: Emerald Run
description: A man who's desperate to save his daughter agrees to smuggle emeralds across the Mexican border; when things don't go as planned, he's left for dead.

title: The Haunted Hotel
