description: Eight tales of ghostly encounters through the decades, manifesting amid the ruins of a once grand English hotel.

title: A Holiday Heist
description: College students staying at school over Christmas break are taken hostage by three bumbling thugs. As they try to rob a fine art exhibit, the students are forced to find the spirit of Christmas as they make plans to fight back.

title: Rollers
description: Rufus Paisley is a closet alcoholic and everything he loves is smashed together into one place: Rollers. To keep it alive, he's drained every ounce of personal capital he's got. Now the historic venue, once owned by his parents, is in trouble and he's running out of ways to save it, and himself. His friends urge him to move on, but can he?

title: Still Here
description: A journalist is tasked to cover the story of a young girl who had gone missing in New York City. He is struck by the story and takes it upon himself to solve the case.

title: Running for Grace
description: An orphan uses his blazing speed to deliver medicine to the coffee pickers in the mountains of Hawaii. Young love soon blossoms when he begins a forbidden romance with the daughter of a plantation owner.

title: Big Bear
description: Despite being dumped by his fiance, Joe decides to enjoy his bachelor party with his three friends. But things get worse when his friends kidnap the man his fiance ran with.

title: Halloween Party
description: When a Halloween-themed meme ends up killing her best friend, Grace takes it upon herself to resolve the mystery. She enlists the help of Spencer, a computer genius, in her mission.

title: Mount Hideaway Mysteries: Exes and Oh No's
description: A spy moves back home and solves mysteries with her home-schooled childhood friends. To investigate murders that threaten her hometown and the nearby secret government facility, she must confront the enemies of the town, her own past, and her ex-boyfriend.

title: Halloween Party
description: A woman (Elle Newlands) mistakes a homeless man for a costumed partygoer and drags him (Frank Gangarossa) to an annual Halloween party.

title: Trauma Therapy
description: At a remote wooded retreat, a group of lost souls attends a self-help seminar lead by famous influencer Tobin Vance. As the guests get pushed further and further by Vance's extreme program, which includes lie detectors, firearms, and experimental drugs, they question his methods and begin to fear for their lives.

title: NetherBeast Incorporated
description: A seemingly ordinary telephone company employs vampires and manages to avoid any suspicion. However, things take a terrifying turn when the company starts hiring humans.

title: Feedback
description: While working in his studio for a late-night show, a radio host is attacked by two masked men who threaten him to read their script which contains the truth about a scandal.

title: The Kitchen
description: Jennifer wants her thirtieth birthday to be special. But what should be an epic milestone soon turns into a day she never wants to remember.

title: Lloyd the Conqueror
description: A tyrannical professor (Mike Smith) coerces three slacker students into joining his LARP league in exchange for a passing grade.

title: The Secret Scripture
description: Fifty years after being confined in a mental hospital, Roseanne McNulty must relocate to another institution. A psychiatrist takes an interest in her and reveals her joyful yet sorrowful past life.

title: Sanctuary Population One
description: A young idealist searches for his family while fighting the infected, militias, bloodthirsty marauders and the ghosts of his past.

title: Dark Tourist
description: Obsessed with the idea of grief tourism, Jim Tanha, a security guard, travels to California to meet Carl Marznap, a serial killer, and builds an uncanny friendship with him.

title: Acts of Desperation
description: A desperate cop stalks his cheating wife at the same time a polite bank robber tries to save a suicidal woman.

title: Companion
description: Malicious spirits haunt a guilt-stricken woman as she journeys across an apocalyptic landscape to save the man she left behind.

title: Refuge: American Apocalypse
description: A family struggles to survive after a catastrophic event. As food and supplies dwindle and the threat of marauders becomes more apparent, the family must decide either to stay in hiding or search for an elusive mansion.

title: شباب البومب
description: Shabab El Bomb

title: 400 Contra 1
description: A verdadeira história por trás da criação do Comando Vermelho, poderosa organização criminosa que aterrorizou o Rio de Janeiro por várias décadas.

title: As Melhores Coisas do Mundo
description: Mano é um adolescente que precisa enfrentar os altos e baixos vividos por pessoas de sua idade. Ele enfrenta outra crise pessoal em casa quando seu pai abandona a família.

title: Chico Xavier
description: Francisco Candido Xavier, a man born to a humble Portuguese family, grows up to become one of the most renowned mediums and philanthropists.

title: Elite Squad: The Enemy Within
description: Nascimento is called in to stop a prison riot started by Beirada, who is eventually killed. Now a high ranking officer, he finds himself in a conflict between the government and paramilitary groups.

title: O Bem Amado
description: Odorico é eleito prefeito da cidade de Sucupira e deve inaugurar um cemitério. Ele é acusado de ser corrupto e luta para salvar sua reputação.

title: Reflexões de Um Liquidificador
description: Uma taxidermista (Ana Lúcia Torre) conversa com seu liquidificador enquanto a polícia investiga o desaparecimento de seu marido (Germaino Haiut).

title: Uma Noite em 67
description: Um documentário que mostra a grandeza do Festival de Música Popular Brasileira de 1967.

title: Viajo Porque Preciso, Volto Porque Te Amo
description: Um geólogo (Irandhir Santos) pondera o efeito que um canal tem sobre uma comunidade.

title: De Pernas pro Ar
description: Uma mulher workaholic passa por um momento difícil depois que seu marido a abandona e ela é demitida da empresa. Isso faz com que ela busque uma mudança de carreira e assim se torne sócia de um sex shop.

title: Achados e Perdidos
description: Um delegado aposentado torna-se o principal suspeito do assassinato de uma prostituta.

title: Árido Movie
description: Um meteorologista da TV se envolve em uma vingança familiar quando vai ao vale da Rocha para enterrar seu pai.

title: 2 Filhos de Francisco
description: Francisco José de Camargo, um homem pobre do Brasil, faz tudo ao seu alcance para garantir que seus filhos se tornem os melhores músicos do país.

title: O Homem Que Desafiou o Diabo
description: Zé Araújo é um viajante recém-chegado em Jardim dos Caiacós. Ele seduz a filha de um comerciante e é obrigado a se casar com ela. Araújo torna-se um escravo do sogro e da mulher. Percebendo que vira motivo de piada na cidade, ele resolve mudar de vida e começar uma nova.

title: O Casamento de Romeu e Julieta
description: Julieta é filha de Alfredo, torcedor fanático do Palmeiras. Quando Julieta conhece Romeu, chefe da torcida corintiana, eles se apaixonam. Romeu finge torcer pelo Palmeiras para conseguir o aval de Alfredo, mas isso pode levar ao desastre.

title: Xuxinha e Guto contra os Monstros do Espaço
description: Xuxinha e Guto contra os Monstros Espaciais Contando com a ajuda inestimável de um anjo da guarda chamado Xuxinha, Guto terá que enfrentar terríveis monstros comedores de lixo que vêm do planeta XYZ para a Terra querendo destruir a humanidade.

title: Anjos do Sol
description: Um pescador pobre vende sua filha de 12 anos para um recrutador de prostitutas. Ele a leva para um bordel de classe baixa na região amazônica. Embora sofra inúmeros abusos, ela só pensa em escapar das condições horríveis.

title: Um Ato de Coragem
description: John Q Archibald mora com sua esposa, Denise, e seu filho Michael. Mas quando Michael precisa de um transplante de coração de emergência que John não pode pagar, ele promete fazer qualquer coisa para manter seu filho vivo.

title: Sangue Jovem
description: Condenado por um pequeno crime, JR torna-se aliado de Brendan Lynch, ajudando-o mais tarde a escapar da prisão. Eles trabalham juntos para executar um assalto, mas o desenrolar dos acontecimentos os converte em inimigos.

title: The Runners
description: A man races against time to save his teenage sister from human traffickers who want to sell her to a Mexican cartel.

title: Extramundane
description: A new property manager tries to figure out his way when he takes over an apartment building during a pandemic.

title: Watching Amber
description: After the death of Amber's boyfriend Paul, she's determined to move on and continue with her new love, Chad. She tries to put her past behind her but is stalked by a mental neighbor who is determined to eliminate all competition.

title: A Night Without Armor
description: A married policeman goes to a lake to watch a meteor shower. While watching the sky, he meets a single nurse, and the two start falling in love.

title: Remember Me
description: Rose awakes in an unknown house following a serious car accident with memory loss and no ability to walk. Her Mother and boyfriend are there to help her. Rose wants to piece together her life before the accident. All is not what it seems.

title: Big Nothing
description: A frustrated Charlie teams up with his former colleague Gus and his girlfriend Josie to blackmail Reverend Smalls, a priest who is a porn addict, and extort money to provide for his family.

title: One Church
description: When a national tragedy turns into a personal vendetta for aspiring politician Cornelius Barlow, religion comes to the forefront of public debate. A national debate, like so many that disguise the real agenda by using words like: Uniting, Inclusion, and Co-Existing. 'ONE CHURCH' is a political thriller that tells the story of two prominent families that create a spiritual revolution.

title: Who Killed Soul Glow?
description: The investigation begins to find the killer of celebrity Soul Glow.

title: The Bill Collector
description: Lorenzo Adams, who works at a bill collection agency in Norfolk, is in serious trouble as he has only three weeks to repay his debt of $150,000.

title: Everlasting
description: A high school student tries to find out the truth of his girlfriend's murder by going to Los Angeles to confront the killer.

title: Laugh Killer Laugh
description: A deeply troubled jewel thief shows absolutely no signs of emotions. It takes him a strange sense of awakening to completely change his personality.

title: Haunting Of Whaley House
description: A tour guide at a notorious haunted house gets more than she bargained for during an unauthorised ghost hunt with her friends.

title: The Maltese Holiday
description: Two single travellers travel to Malta in search of adventure, and end up finding find love along the way.

title: Cleaver Family Reunion
description: A dysfunctional family reunite to celebrate the birthday of a family member. But when old secrets are revived, the family members find it difficult to control the situation.

title: Honor Amongst Men
description: John Halmo is a veteran police officer that tries to juggle the daily stresses in his life and defuse an impending biker war that's about to engulf his hometown.

title: Last Ones Out
description: A skeptical American is stranded in the middle of a zombie-infected Africa and must rely on the help of three mysterious strangers to make it out alive.

title: Get Rich Free
description: Three young door to door salesmen from Los Angeles get in some financial troubles and decide finding a treasure is the best way to solve them.

title: Hatton Garden: The Heist
description: As the Easter bank holiday and Passover coincide in April 2015, four elderly men burgle the Hatton Garden Safe Deposit Company, an underground safe deposit facility in London, stunning the Britons.

title: Red Pill
description: In the run-up to the 2020 elections, some progressives head deep into a red state to canvas homes for votes but find terror instead.

title: Pinching Penny
description: A British hypochondriac gets obsessed with owning the latest and the best things in the world. His obsession leads him to kidnap a girl and hold her for ransom.

title: The Next Dance
description: Selena is a dancer, while Tristian works at his father's accounting firm. When a dance competition is announced, Tristian decides to compete with Selena. However, things do not turn out as expected.

title: Even Trade
description: Power and money come between childhood friends when one wants to become legitimate.

title: Prey for Death
description: Baron Emerson explores the world hunting the best warriors in every region. He arrives in the American frontier to track down an outlaw gunslinger, and arranges for him to be freed so he can hunt him through the wild west.

title: The Don Of Dons
description: The Don of Dons is a forced love story with murderous pulp action. Mr. Brown, a man that is pushed beyond his limits must find a mythical figure only known as the Mad Sam.

title: Gold Fools
description: Out of a job, a man takes his two friends along on a treasure hunt that will bring them in contact with a mysterious threat.

title: Magic Boys (Diamond Heist)
description: After two misfits witness a murder, they try to save their lives by disguising themselves as male strippers. Unfortunately, they fall into a deeper trouble.

title: Grayhound Attack
description: As the USA enters World War II, American fighter pilots conduct a high-risk mission during a crucial battle and attempt to bring down a German airbase.

title: Witness Insecurity
description: Johnny Graham is reared by the Torino crime family after his parents' death. Graham is distressed by the fact that he has to decide whether to be faithful to his adoptive family or his conscience

title: Measure of Faith
description: A family comes together after the death of the matriarch and is shocked by the secrets she took to the grave

title: Mutant Virus
description: You have nothing to fear but fear itself… And Mutants, of course. Prepare to be drawn by terror and quartered by grizzly horror. Experience some of the most disturbing short films ever assembled in this anthology that will leave you gasping for more. Blood, guts and tears will flow as man meets mutant. Are you game for the ride?

title: House on the Hill
description: A woman who got away from serial killers Leonard Lake and Charles Ng joins a private investigator to learn the ultimate destiny of one of the killers' targets.

title: Coffin
description: Pursuing a lead from an anonymous source, Jack Samms embarks on a race against time to rescue his ex-wife and her lover from an underground wooden box within 75 minutes.

title: Don't Get Caught
description: When Dre and Ice rob a marijuana farm during a road trip and quickly sell their ill-gotten stash, they never anticipated that the owner would offer a $100,000 reward to get his crop back.

title: Loon Lake
description: Louis Olsen tries to escape his grief by going to a lake in southwest Minnesota; while there, he accidentally disturbs a witch's grave, which starts a haunting nightmare.

title: Billy the Kid: Showdown in Lincoln County
description: A bloody conflict erupts between ranchers and store owners in Lincoln County.

title: Asylum of Darkness
description: An asylum patient escapes from the facility and encounters a supernatural world after he leaves that continues to taunt him.

title: Hex
description: During the English Civil War, two opposing soldiers find themselves trapped in a forest controlled by a Witch.

title: It's Not A Date
description: Milo and Carly go out on a date. But things take a turn for the worse when Carly, who has been on too many bad dates, decides that Milo is the worst one of them all.

title: The Rodeo Thief
description: An injured bull rider who's rodeo career is nearly over agrees to steal roping horses for an unforgiving loan shark.

title: Octopus Pot
description: A man is left broken after he's left by the woman he loves. While he can't bring her back, he can cover the ground with the blood of his enemy.

title: Drops of Happiness
description: A modern-day story of graduate unemployment and how young people are going beyond their normal life in search of greener pastures.

title: Agent
description: Friends find themselves caught up in a government conspiracy after unleashing an ancient power in the desert.

title: L.A. Slasher
description: Disgusted with tabloid culture, a killer abducts reality TV stars -- while the media and the public debate whether society is better off without them.

title: Texas Cotton
description: Residents of LaCoste, Texas, believe that a mysterious outsider is responsible for an endless plague of dying crops. The stranger's arrest leads to an investigation that turns the whole town against an ageing lawman who's searching for the truth.

title: Away Bus
description: Two sisters orchestrate a highway bus robbery to raise money to save their dying mother, but a twist forces them to make quick decisions.

title: Bad Impulse
description: A new high-tech security system forces members of a family to confront their innermost fears and desires.

title: Know Your Enemy
description: A Middle Eastern man invades the home of a young, affluent couple as a result of a road rage incident, and the results are a tense exploration of their preconceptions and misconceptions.

title: Making Time
description: When a divorced man goes back in time, he must be careful not to change anything, including proposing to his ex-wife.

title: The Aviation Cocktail
description: Three World War II veterans return to their small rural town in Nebraska only to face terrible personal battles.

title: The Droving
description: A man returns from the military in search for his lost sister, who mysteriously went missing around the time of a strange traditional festival called `The Droving'.

title: Evil Down The Street
description: A family move into their new dream home, but unbeknownst to them the house is hiding a malevolent presence. Soon, one of their own is afflicted by a terrifying demonic force, and she starts to turn on her family.

title: S'ids Lake
description: After Sid accidentally kills a teenage girl in his sleep, he invents an alter-ego to protect himself from accusations.

title: Edge Of Isolation
description: Stranded deep in the woods, a young married couple are taken in by an isolationist family, one that lives off the blood and plunder from lost hikers, and the family wants the couple to stay for the rest of their lives.

title: Blood From Stone
description: Bodies start to pile up when a self-destructive vampire follows his fed-up bride to a desert town full of gamblers and drunks.

title: Eve
description: A distraught actress terrorizes the woman who beat her out for the much-coveted movie role in "Paradise Lost."

title: Club Utopia
description: A bored housewife wants to make something of herself and becomes an exotic dancer. Her newfound confidence spills over into the rest of her life.

title: Abandoned Dead
description: Rachel is a security guard at a run-down, nearly abandoned clinic; when she begins to experience terrifying visions of murder victims, she rallies a psychiatrist and detective to help uncover the truth.

title: Luciferous
description: A family is manipulated by a malicious force.

title: 200 Degrees
description: Ryan finds himself inside a sealed industrial kiln, with a mysterious voice manipulating him. Armed with only his cell phone, he must meet the verbal demands or risk being burnt alive.

title: Endure
description: After a shocking photo of a young woman is found inside the wreckage of a fatal car crash, detective Emory Lloyd must find the woman before it's too late.

title: The one
description: Starring: Jet Li (李连杰), Jason Statham, Delroy Lindo, Carla Gugino, and James Morrison. Director: James Wong.

title: Comeback Season
description: When Walter's wife asks him to leave the house for cheating on her, he comes across Skylar, an American football legend. The two live together as neighbours and try to resolve their past mistakes.

title: Grace and Goliath
description: Hollywood big shot Josh Jenkins sweeps into Belfast to make a movie, but before long his world crashes and he loses everything. Hotel cleaner Lily invites him to stay with her crazy family and gradually the people of this `strange' city touch his heart forever.

title: Half Light
description: When her son dies accidentally, Rachel Carson, a crime novelist, experiences guilt. To overcome this, she relocates to a Scottish village to start a new life. But bizarre occurrences destabilise her.

title: My Son, My Son, What Have Ye Done
description: Brad kills his mother and barricades himself in his house with two hostages. Detective Havenhurst speaks to his girlfriend and his neighbour in an effort to understand his psyche.

title: Calloused Hands
description: Although neglected by his mother and abused by her boyfriend, Josh manages to forge his own path in life when his grandfather Solomon returns to help him study for his bar mitzvah.

title: Beast No More
description: A young biologist dealing with the loss of a child leaves suburbia and heads into the Australian bush where she gets a chance to be a mother again, but at a cost.

title: Nightblade
description: A reunion of three friends after years turns ghastly when dancers at a strip club owned by one of them are killed by a mysterious killer. To help their friend, the other two hunt for the assassin.

title: Art of Obsession
description: A novelist's life begins a downward spiral after his family dies in a car accident and his new novel tanks. He finds solace and renewed inspiration thanks to his neighbour's wife, but the paranoia of losing another loved one leads him to abduct her.

title: 53206: Milwaukee
description: After her cousin's murder, an aspiring singer must decide whether to follow her dreams or stay in Milwaukee and help her community end the cycle of violence.

title: Beyond the Night
description: A war of attrition breaks out when a soldier's son reveals damning information about a local gangster's daughter.

title: Day Zero
description: Three young friends receive an induction notice, and have 30 days to report for duty. They battle with their conflicts and amongst themselves to figure what it means to serve with honour.

title: Killing Poe
description: Five students enrolled in a class on Edgar Allen Poe take law into their own hands to punish their abusive professor. However, their plan goes awry when they realise that the truth is hard to digest.

title: Shadows and Lies
description: When he falls for a New York gangster's favorite call girl, Vincent is forced to flee the city, threatened with death if he should ever come back. But after four years in exile, Vincent secretly returns intent on rescuing the woman he loves.

title: Twenty Million People
description: When Brian's new girlfriend, a stand-up comedian, suddenly disappears, he enlists the help of his broken-hearted best friend and imaginary characters from a cliché romantic comedy to find her.

title: Lost in Love
description: While visiting ancient ruins in Turkey, tourists Hope and Jeb are left behind by their tour bus. The strangers must work together to get back to Istanbul and grow close along the way.

title: The Dunes
description: When a journalist moves to his hometown, he does not have the slightest idea that the strings of his unresolved past are lying there in wait to entangle him in a psychological Gordian knot.

title: Surrogate
description: A ghost horror about single mother and nurse Natalie who falls mysteriously ill and struggles to stop her family from being destroyed.

title: Infiltrators
description: With a valuable relic up for grabs in an office tower that is condemned and awaiting demolition, an urban explorer and his partner undertake a search. However, they are not the only ones looking to claim the prize.

title: Eight Days Carlo
description: Carlo, a steel worker, has been laid off from his job. He's married to his high school sweetheart, a cancer survivor. They have a special needs teenage son. Carlo has lost his medical insurance; the bank is going to foreclose on their house in 8 days. Carlo will do ANYTHING to protect his family in this compelling story.

title: The Mad Whale
description: When her husband commits her to a mental asylum, Isabel becomes part of a new program by Dr Benjamin Calhoun, who makes his patients participate in a theatrical production of 'Moby Dick'.

title: The Donner Party
description: Snow traps a California-bound wagon train of travelers (Crispin Glover, Clayne Crawford, Christian Kane) in the Sierra Nevada Mountains.

title: Beeper
description: When Richard Avery's son is kidnapped by a drug dealer, he becomes a desperate man. He must now follow the dealer's instructions through a beeper if he wants to rescue his son.

title: Crack In The Floor
description: A group of friends on a hiking trip find themselves in a perilous situation when they interrupt the self-imposed exile of a deranged hermit.

title: Happy Log
description: While on a camping trip, two boys (Caleb Meadows, Brock Patrick Kaufman) cross paths with a ruthless hit man who is looking to collect on a local gambling dept.

title: Black Noise
description: An elderly man wakes up in his home and discovers his wife is missing. He struggles to piece together the bizarre events as his daughter sends him to a long term care facility.

title: Restricted Area
description: Four blue-collar friends, recently laid off from the steel mill, go on a camping trip and discover a backwoods cult with a cataclysmic agenda.

title: Refuge
description: Refuge - An actress on the brink of self-destruction, forms an unlikely friendship with a young refugee and former child soldier.

title: Taught in Cold Blood
description: A troubled teen is torn between the girl he loves and a man who encourages him to kill.

title: Twisted Pieces
description: A vengeful ex-soldier hunts a demonic surgeon who abducts people and creates human trophies to sell to the highest bidder.

title: The Stranger Game
description: Joanna Otis, a hard-working mother, hires a male babysitter to take care of her son. However, she soon learns that the babysitter is a psychopath who wants to destroy her family.

title: Iron Ridge
description: A young man becomes lost without gear in the back country of Montana and tries to survive while a man-eating bear stalks him.

title: Laura Gets A Cat
description: An unemployed writer juggles a dull boyfriend and an affair with a performance artist while living a vivid imaginary life.

title: A Miami Love Story
description: Romance threatens to destroy the delicate balance between two rival crime families.

title: Chasing Robert Barker
description: A photographer turned paparazzi is caught in the downward spiral of a fabricated tabloid story.

title: Canadian Muscle
description: A high-school senior searches for his first car while his friends make plans for the first night of summer vacation.

title: 21 Brothers
description: Sgt. Reid prepares his men for the battle of Courcelette during World War I. As he preps his battalion, he deals with the day-to-day difficulties of life in the trenches.

title: Point Defiance
description: While under house arrest, a stockbroker's world is turned upside down after his troubled brother returns from military duty in Afghanistan, forcing them to face a forgotten past harbouring a dark secret.

title: The Leprechaun's Curse
description: After a bunch of thieves are sent out to hunt for urban legends by a wealthy man intending to open a museum full of mythical creatures, they learn the legend of a leprechaun.

title: We Go In At Dawn
description: A senior war planner gets captured by the Nazis and is held as a prisoner of war at a special war camp. Soon, a team of experts sets out on a mission to rescue him and bring him back safely.

title: Corazones de acero  (Fury)
description: Al final de la Segunda Guerra Mundial, los aliados en el teatro europeo están en su enfrentamiento final. Las cosas se ponen difíciles para Don Collier, un comandante de tanque alemán, mientras contraataca al enemigo.

title: Nacidas para sufrir
description: Un grupo de mujeres es tan generoso que cada una compite para ver quién puede ser más útil.

title: El Turno Nocturno
description: Diego trabaja en una gasolinera. Un día, cuando hace su turno de noche, se encuentra con unas cuantas personas espeluznantes. Se siente incómodo y se da cuenta de que no pertenece allí.

title: las viudas de los jueves
description: Una comunidad cerrada alberga familias adineradas acostumbradas a las cosas buenas de la vida. Cuando tres hombres son encontrados muertos en una piscina, oscuros secretos comienzan a salir a la luz.

title: Tension Sexual No Resuelta
description: Juanjo, un profesor universitario, busca la ayuda de su alumno para recuperar a su novia. Sin embargo, las cosas se complican cuando descubren un secreto.

title: La Isla Minima
description: Pedro y Juan, dos detectives que comparten ideologías diferentes, deben dejar de lado sus diferencias y dar caza a un asesino en serie que mata mujeres sin piedad.

title: En un lugar de Africa
description: Debido a la amenaza de Hitler, Walter Redlich, un abogado judío, emigra a Kenia con su esposa Jettel y su hija Regina. Las cosas cambian cuando los oficiales británicos ordenan a la familia que se mude.

title: El diario de Carlota
description: Carlota, una chica de 17 años, se disfraza de chico para acercarse a Lucas. Sin embargo, su mejor amiga pretende seducir al enamorado de Carlota, un deportista llamado Oriol.

title: Todo lo que tú quieras
description: Después de la muerte de su esposa, Leo lucha como padre soltero. Sin embargo, cuando ve que su hija de cuatro años se desconecta, cede a su ingenua petición de disfrazarse de su madre.

title: El gran Vázquez
description: Manuel Vázquez, un destacado caricaturista español, vive una vida de lujo e indulgencia. Sin embargo, no pasa mucho tiempo antes de que los acreedores lo persigan y se vea obligado a enmendarse.

title: Os 12 Trabalhos
description: A história de um jovem negro, Héracles, que após ser liberado de uma instituição juvenil, tenta se candidatar ao seu primeiro emprego honesto como entregador de motocicletas. Para conseguir o emprego, ele terá que realizar 12 árduas tarefas em São Paulo.

title: A Distância Entre Nós
description: Stella e Will, ambos pacientes com fibrose cística, desenvolvem uma relação improvável, apesar da ameaça de infecção cruzada. No entanto, eles eliminam suas restrições para vivenciar a união.

title: Ainda Orangotangos
description: Dezesseis pessoas vivem o dia mais quente do ano.

title: El Penalti Mas Largo Del Mundo
description: Fernando, un hombre que trabaja en el supermercado del barrio y juega como portero suplente del equipo de fútbol, ​​descubre que su aburrida vida da un giro emocionante cuando finalmente juega un partido.

title: Para Sempre Alice
description: A vida de uma professora de linguística começa a desmoronar quando ela é diagnosticada com a doença de Alzheimer de início precoce. Quando ela perde o emprego, sua família faz o possível para mantê-la unida.

title: Lejos de La Habana
description: A tres artistas cubanos no se les permite regresar a su patria.

title: Un rey en la Habana
description: Un actor (Alexis Valdés) intenta ayudar a la mujer (Yoima Valdés) que ama después de que su rico prometido muere en la cama.

title: Perder es cuestión de método
description: Cuando se encuentra un cuerpo empalado en una estaca cerca de un lago, un periodista se propone resolver el crimen. Descubre una intrincada red que involucra fraude inmobiliario, políticos corruptos y cazadores de esmeraldas.

title: Perro salvaje
description: Martín, ex campeón de boxeo, participa en torneos carcelarios y los gana. Sin embargo, cuando decide regresar a casa, le arrebatan todo lo que le importa, lo que le obliga a buscar venganza.

title: El sueño de una noche de San Juan
description: Elena decide buscar la ayuda de la reina de las hadas para tratar a su padre enfermo. ¿Salvarán sus esfuerzos la vida de su padre?

title: Ninette
description: Un hombre (Carlos Hipólito) conoce a una belleza seductora (Elsa Pataky) mientras visita a un viejo amigo (Enrique Villén) en París.

title: Hermanos
description: Mientras estaba de gira en Afganistán, el helicóptero de Sam es derribado y se presume que está muerto. En casa, es su hermano el que se ocupa de la familia. Sam regresa, pero con mucho exceso de equipaje.

title: Campanita
description: Cuando Tinker Bell descubre que para visitar el continente necesita tener talento para la naturaleza, se propone adquirirlo con la ayuda de sus amigos.

title: El Método
description: Siete candidatos ambiciosos compiten entre sí para conseguir el puesto de ejecutivo en una misteriosa corporación. Realizan varias pruebas para demostrar su valía.

title: Volando voy
description: Un joven (Borja Navas) se convierte en conductor de fuga de una banda de delincuentes en Madrid, España.

title: Iluminados por el fuego
description: La Guerra de las Malvinas dejó una huella imborrable en un periodista argentino. Impulsado por el intento de suicidio de un amigo, el periodista regresa a las Malvinas y revive las experiencias que vivió allí.

title: Gisaku
description: Gracias a sus poderes mágicos, el samurái Yohei despierta en la actual España tras dormir casi 400 años. Ha llegado el momento de cumplir la misión que emprendió por primera vez en el siglo XVII.

title: Azul Oscuro Casi Negro
description: Cuando Antonio se da cuenta de que es infértil, le pide a su hermano Jorge que deje embarazada a Paula. Sin embargo, las cosas se complican cuando Natalia, la novia de la infancia de Jorge, regresa después de muchos años.

title: Contra Corrente
description: After Santiago drowns at sea, his ghost haunts his former lover, Miguel, to have his body buried. However, Miguel's wife soon learns about his past affair with Santiago, complicating their marriage.

title: Trampas de Tu Lado Oscuro
description: Trampas De Tu Lado Oscuro: Directed by Oscar Liza Alauie. With Ruben Barrera, Rosa Alauie, Diana Rojas, Jean Pear Guerrero.

title: La caja Kovak
description: Un escritor de ciencia ficción que ha sido invitado a una isla para una conferencia descubre que ha sido atraído a una trampa cruel. Las cosas empeoran cuando las personas que lo rodean comienzan a suicidarse inexplicablemente.

title: Parque Central
description: Cuatro parejas muy especiales luchan con la vida para conseguir sus deseos. Algunos buscan respeto y el derecho a amarse unos a otros. Otros se enfrentan a la traición y a verdades ocultas. Cuatro historias llenas de humor, drama y pasión. Los une un espacio común: son habitantes del "Parque Central".

title: Ekipo Ja
description: Los Ekipo Ja, un grupo de gitanos cuerdos liderados por el gitano Juan De Dios, están en posesión, sin saberlo, de un sello sagrado capaz de pedir deseos a quien lo posee. Y quien quiere poseer por encima de todo es la Marquesa.

title: La Cuba Mia
description: película documental con la participación de grandes artistas cubanos, en la que sus protagonistas son Celia Cruz y Miliki.

title: كلب بلدي
description: Kalb Balady : تركت والدته روكي عندما كان طفلاً وقام بتربيته على يد كلب فريسكا، مما جعله يكتسب سمات خاصة. تكتشف الشرطة قدراته وتجنده لتعقب مجرم شائن.

title: ويش سجون
description: Wesh Sogoon : تدور أحداث الفيلم حول رجل محكوم عليه بالإعدام شنقًا، وتفاصيل حياته داخل السجن وعلاقاته مع رفاقه.

title: إل حكاية فيها من
description: El Hekaya Fiha Mena : شاب طموح يأمل الالتحاق بكلية الاقتصاد والعلوم السياسية، لكن حلمه في أن يصبح سياسيًا مؤثرًا قد يعيقه عمل والده كحلاق.

title: EUC
description: بعد التخرج من المدرسة الثانوية بدرجات مخيبة للآمال، قررت مجموعة من الأصدقاء إنشاء جامعتهم الخاصة. حتما، لن يمر وقت طويل قبل أن يجدوا أنفسهم في موقف مضحك.

title: شابه محارف
description: Shabah Monharef : شاب يغني في فرقة يديرها عمه. لقاء صدفة يقوده إلى مقابلة فتاة أحلامه. يلجأ إلى كل شخص يعرفه للمساعدة في كسب حبها.

title: حمادة يعلب
description: Hamada Yal'ab : حمادة، رجل فقير، يدمن المشاركة في عروض الألعاب ليصبح ثريًا. يواجه عقبات مختلفة عندما يفوز بمليون دولار.

title: خالتي فرنسا
description: Khalty Faransa : تضطر فرانسا إلى رعاية ابنتي أختها، باتا وويزا، بعد وفاة أختها. تتغير حياتهم عندما يبدأ باتا العمل مع الشرطة.

title: الدادا دودي
description: Aldada Dodi : فتاة لصة تتظاهر بأنها مربية أطفال حتى تتمكن من سرقة منزل رجل ثري لكن أطفاله الستة جعلوها تفقد عقلها.

title: ساب البرمبه
description: Wannabe Courageous : عندما تصاب زوجته الجديدة بالإحباط بسبب فشله في حمايتها من الخطر، يطلب عمر المساعدة من طبيب نفسي غريب لاستعادتها.

title: أهواك
description: Ahwak : الدكتور شريف، جراح التجميل، يقع في معضلة غريبة. يلتقي بشابة ويقع في حبها، ولكن عندما يلتقي بأمها العازبة، يجد نفسه منجذبًا إليها أيضًا.

title: للات هنا و سرور
description: Lelet Hana Wa Sror : بعد أن يتزوج من فتاة أحلامه، يجد محتال نفسه ملاحقًا من قبل عصابة تهدد بكشف غطائه وإفساد علاقته بالمرأة التي يحبها.

title: Días de pesca
description: Marco Tucci conduce hasta Puerto Deseado para pescar tiburones y visitar a su hija separada.

title: Teresa: El cuerpo de Cristo
description: Teresa, la hija de un noble, ingresa al convento después de tener visiones de Jesucristo. Decepcionada con lo que ve a su alrededor, decide reformar la orden religiosa de la que forma parte.

title: Tuya siempre
description: The past comes back to haunt a petty criminal (Flora Martínez) who works at a jazz club.

title: La soledad de los números primos
description: Mattia y Alice son compañeros de clase que se hacen amigos por casualidad. Ambos tienen una infancia traumatizante. Sin embargo, se separan cuando Mattia se va a trabajar a Alemania. ¿Se reunirán?

title: Bezerra de Menezes - O Diário de um Espírito
description: De Menezes, carinhosamente conhecido como o "Médico dos Pobres", deixa o interior do Nordeste do Brasil e vai para o Rio de Janeiro para estudar medicina.

title: Os Últimos na Terra
description: Um homem e uma mulher são os únicos sobreviventes depois que um desastre destrói o mundo. Eles pensam em começar uma vida juntos, mas as coisas mudam depois que outro homem entra em suas vidas.

title: Cleópatra
description: Cleópatra é um filme épico de drama histórico brasileiro de 2007, dirigido por Júlio Bressane. É estrelado por Alessandra Negrini no papel homônimo.

title: Concursante
description: Después de que un profesor de economía gana una gran suma en un programa de juegos, necesita ayuda para administrar el dinero.

title: خير و بركة
description: Khair And Baraka : يكافح شقيقان عاطلان عن العمل للعثور على عمل. ينتهي بهم الأمر في مواقف مسلية للغاية بعد أن يتولوا وظائف غريبة.

title: جيران السعد
description: Giran el-Sa'd : يجد مجموعة من الأشخاص الذين يعيشون في نفس الحي أنفسهم في مواقف غير مريحة بسبب أطفالهم. يتحدون معًا من أجل الخروج من المشاكل.

title: كتكوت
description: Katkout : كتكوت، ملاكم ماهر، يغادر قريته عندما يتآمر عليه معارفه. علاوة على ذلك، فقد وقع في مأزق عندما ظنت السلطات أنه إرهابي سيئ السمعة.

title: إل خلبس
description: El khalbous : هي كوميدي فيلم الخلبص سترينج محمد رجب عند عمان الأسي حد

title: حياتي مبهدل
description: Hayaty Mebahdela : تتغير حياة طاطه عندما يقتل قطة بالخطأ ويصاب باللعنة. ينقل اللعنة دون قصد إلى المرأة التي يحبها من خلال القلادة التي يقدمها لها.

title: فول السين العظيم
description: Fool el Seen El Azeem : محيي مرفوض من قبل جده وأعمامه لكونه جبانًا. يستعين بوالدته، لكن زوج والدته يرسله إلى الصين للمشاركة في مسابقة للطبخ.

title: سامي أوكسيد الكربون
description: Samy Oxed El Karbon : سامي طيار متهور لا يهتم إلا بنفسه. لكن حياته تتغير عندما تأتي امرأة شابة على باب منزله مدعية أنها ابنته من زوجته السابقة.

title: Traummann im zweiten Anlauf
description: In einem toskanischen Dorf entwickeln Maggie, eine verklemmte alleinerziehende Mutter und Professorin, und Luca, ihr Ex-Freund, Gefühle füreinander, als ihre Tochter und seine alte Mutter sein Auto stehlen und nach Rom rennen

title: Vier Tage Toskana
description: Da der verstorbene Berliner Künstler Dorn jahrelang seine Steuern nicht zahlte und die Familie nicht informierte, müssen seine Witwe Erika und seine Töchter dringend das prächtige Anwesen in der Toskana verkaufen, das sie seit seinem Tod ohnehin kaum besucht hatten.

title: BloodRayne
description: Rayne, eine halb Mensch, halb Vampir aus Rumänien des 18. Jahrhunderts, neigt zu blinden Wutanfällen und schwört, die Vergewaltigung ihrer Mutter durch Kagan, den König ihrer Rasse, zu rächen.

title: die luftbrücke – nur der himmel war frei
description: Zweiteiliges Historiendrama über eine schwierige Liebesbeziehung zwischen einer Deutschen und einem amerikanischen Soldaten während der Berliner Luftbrücke. Nachdem ihr Mann Axel für tot erklärt wird, muss Luise Kielberg als alleinerziehende Mutter eines 12-jährigen Jungen im Nachkriegs-Berlin überleben.

title: Frischer Wind
description: Sechs Monate sind seit dem Tod seiner geliebten Frau vergangen und Kurt Tobaben (Günther Maria Halmer) kann den Verlust immer noch nicht verarbeiten. Der wohlhabende Handschuhfabrikant aus Hamburg vernachlässigt sein Unternehmen, versteckt sich in seiner Villa und trauert der Vergangenheit nach

title: Der Liebling des Himmels
description: Die Karriere des berühmten Psychiaters Dr. Magnus ist bedroht, nachdem er von einer unbekannten Person erpresst wird, die sein persönliches Tagebuch gestohlen hat.

title: Dein Reich komme
description: Piet Hartog und seine Freunde bilden einen Widerstand und kämpfen für die Rettung unschuldiger Leben, als die Nazis in Holland mit der Verfolgung der Juden beginnen.

title: Liebe ohne Minze
description: Saskia, eine Modedesignerin, heiratet Robert, einen Architekten. Saskias jugendliche Tochter Mira mag Robert jedoch nicht und weigert sich, mit ihm zusammenzuleben. Auf der Suche nach ihrem Vater Amine begibt sie sich nach Marrakesch.

title: Wie ein Licht in der Nacht
description: Wie ein Licht in der Nacht ist ein Fernsehfilm aus dem Jahr 2010, der sich dem Thema Alkoholismus widmet. Florian Baxmeyer leitete die Regie und Thorsten Näter schrieb das Drehbuch.

title: Kirikou et les Bêtes Sauvages
description: Kirikou, un jeune garçon, déjoue une sorcière qui menace son village. Son grand-père juge cependant cette histoire trop brève et continue en racontant ses autres réalisations.

title: M.Popper et ses pingouins
description: Lorsque le père de Tom Popper meurt en Antarctique, il hérite de six pingouins. Tom décide dans un premier temps de les offrir, mais ses enfants pensent que c'est un cadeau d'anniversaire et il est obligé de les garder.

title: La Nouvelle Guerre des boutons
description: Lebrac et sa bande d'amis qui se battent avec des enfants d'un village voisin doivent protéger Violette, une jeune fille juive, après qu'elle ait été découverte par quelques partisans nazis.

title: La Passion du Christ
description: Le sauveur de l'humanité, Jésus-Christ, est trahi par l'un de ses disciples et crucifié. Malgré la mort douloureuse, Jésus maintient la pureté de son âme et déjoue les desseins de Satan.

title: Le Monde de Nemo
description: Après que son fils ait été enlevé de la Grande Barrière de corail et envoyé à Sydney, Marlin, un doux poisson-clown, demande l'aide d'un poisson oublieux et entreprend un voyage pour le ramener à la maison.

title: Days of Glory
description: Quatre hommes indigènes d'Afrique du Nord rejoignent la Première Armée française pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale pour libérer les régions du sud de la France des forces nazies.

title: Lincoln
description: Abraham Lincoln utilise ses pouvoirs de président des États-Unis d'Amérique pour abolir l'esclavage et réunifier son pays pendant la guerre civile.

title: David et Goliath
description: Un simple berger, David, combat un puissant guerrier, Goliath, dans une bataille légendaire entre deux grands empires antiques.

title: L'affaire
description: Basé sur l'histoire vraie d'une enseignante bien-aimée pour les aveugles qui découvre qu'elle-même perd la vue.

title: sheitan
description: Bart, Ladj, Thai et Yasmine se rendent dans la maison de campagne d'Eve après l'avoir rencontrée dans une discothèque. Mais les choses deviennent étranges lorsqu'ils rencontrent Joseph, la gouvernante excentrique d'Eve et adorateur du diable.

title: Quantos dias. Quantas noites
description: “Quantos dias. Quantas noites”, novo documentário da Maria Farinha Filmes (“Aruanas”, “Começo da Vida”) dirigido por Cacau Rhoden (“Nunca Me Sonharam”, “Tarja Branca”), realiza um profundo mergulho nos propósitos da nossa existência no planeta. Especialistas e pensadores nos convidam a enxergar as oportunidades e as desigualdades nesse tema, além da nossa própria conexão com o tempo e com a idade.

title: É Proibido Fumar
description: Baby, um professor de violão viciado em cigarro, se apaixona pela vizinha. Ela o faz parar de fumar, mas logo ele sofre de sintomas de abstinência e começa a sentir falta da ex-mulher.

title: Saneamento Básico
description: Depois de os moradores da Linha Cristal terem sido negados dinheiro para melhorar as instalações sanitárias e serem solicitados a usar os fundos para fazer um filme, eles decidem fazer um filme para destacar seus problemas.

title: Falsa Loura
description: Silmara, operária industrial e mulher de beleza exuberante, apoia o pai incendiário e se envolve com duas estrelas pop diferentes, com quem aprende lições de vida traumáticas.

title: Durval Discos
description: Durval (Ary França) e sua mãe, Carmita (Etty Fraser), vivem uma existência monótona nos fundos da Durval Records, a loja de música de sua propriedade. A rotina deles vira de cabeça para baixo quando uma mulher desaparece, deixando-os com uma criança de 5 anos, Kiki (Isabela Guasco), e um bilhete prometendo voltar em alguns dias.

title: A Partilha
description: No Rio de Janeiro moderno, quatro irmãs muito diferentes se reúnem pela primeira vez em anos, após a morte da mãe. Entre outros itens da agenda está a divisão (o título - "A Partilha") da herança da mãe entre as quatro irmãs

title: O Invasor
description: Complications arise after two crooked entrepreneurs (Marco Ricca, Alexandre Borges) hire a hit man to kill their business partner.
يواجه زوجان كارثة داخل ما يبدو أنه مستشفى بعد تعرضهما لحادث مروع، ويجب عليهما الهروب لإنقاذ حياتهما.

title: الفيل الأزرق 2
description: The Blue Elephant 2 : نزيل جديد في مستشفى الأمراض النفسية يقلب حياة الدكتور يحيى رأسًا على عقب عندما يتنبأ بوفاة عائلته بأكملها.

title: وردة
description: Warda : يعود وليد، المخرج الشاب، إلى قريته الصغيرة مع صديقته الهولندية. عندما يلاحظ حدوث أشياء غريبة في المنزل، يقوم بتركيب كاميرات للوصول إلى الجزء السفلي منه.

title: القرد بيت كلام
description: El-Qird Beyitkallem : يقوم شقيقان ساحران بإعداد حيلة سحرية غير متوقعة على أمل تحرير والدهما

title: مرعي البريمو
description: Marei El Brimo : قصة مرعي البريمو الذي يعمل في تجارة البطيخ، حيث يواجه من خلال عمله العديد من المواقف والمفارقات الكوميدية المثيرة.

title: سمير أبو النيل
description: Sameer Abu Alneel : سمير، شاب، مكروه من جيرانه بسبب سلوكه وبخله. لاحقًا، يرث المال من ابن عمه ويقرر إنشاء قناة فضائية لمناقشة حياته الاجتماعية.

title: جوازا ميري
description: Jawaza Miri : يحاول بيري جاهداً العثور على الرجل المثالي لكنه يفشل دائمًا. تتغير حياتها عندما يقع رجلان في حبها في نفس الوقت، وتحاول استغلال الموقف.

title: Atomised
description: Die Brüder Michael und Bruno haben ständig Probleme, wenn es um Liebe und Sex geht. Ihre turbulente Kindheit und ihre nachlässige Mutter spielen eine wichtige Rolle bei den Problemen, mit denen sie als Erwachsene konfrontiert sind.

title: Eden
description: Ein erfolgreicher Koch (Josef Ostendorf) entwickelt wachsende Gefühle für eine verheiratete Kellnerin (Charlotte Roche).

title: Ostwind 2
description: Als Mika und ihr Pferd Ostwind sich auf ein Turnier vorbereiten, wird Ostwind abgelenkt und rennt in den Wald. Mika folgt ihm und ist verblüfft, ihn mit einer Stute zu sehen.

title: From the Depths
description: A young woman survives a shark attack, following which she is plagued by a nightmare, wherein she is chased by a predator.

title: Inoperable
description: Upon waking up, a woman finds herself trapped in an abandoned hospital. She must find a way to escape before a hurricane passes or she will be a prisioner inside it for life.

title: Two Jacks
description: Jack Hussar Sr. is a legendary Hollywood director, whose persona commands respect from his fans; now his son is interested in assuming that role.

title: Ice House
description: Ice House follows the story of two friends, Grant and Wayne, on one night's excursion to a fish house on a frozen Minnesota lake for an evening of camaraderie. What seems to be a harmless outing between two friends slowly evolves into a murderous plot between two men, both with hidden secrets and mysterious agendas.

title: Beach House
description: Terror strikes when a woman encounters a mysterious artist from her mother's past while staying at a beach house.

title: Path to the Dream
description: Two brothers who are experts in martial arts take different paths after a fight in which one of them is badly injured, but years later, they are reunited in a world where organized crime controls everything.

title: Once Upon a Time in Tombstone
description: A retelling of the story of what happened before, during and after the deadly 30-second Gunfight at the O.K. Corral between lawmen led by Virgil Earp and outlaws in Tombstone, Arizona Territory, October 26, 1881.

title: Bird
description: After witnessing a brutal murder, a woman who flees for her life must team up with a reluctant criminal to save herself.

title: All I Ever Wanted
description: Frustrated by the repetitious grind of the drug dealing life and part time mime street performer "Ace" (Mason Troy) tries to escape the life he once choose out of desperation while fighting subconsciously with his haunting past and dealing with his not so life motivated friends.

title: Sleeping Beauty
description: When Tambria, a witch, is not invited for Princess Dawn's birthday, she curses her to an eternal slumber. When Prince Jayson and his aide learn about it, they decide to rescue the princess.

title: The Margarita Man
description: A young man, who fears he will grow up to be like his working class father, goes to college where his love for the party gets him cut off financially and forces him to sell margaritas in order to stay in school.

title: Creature in the Dark
description: After strange creatures arrive, a husband waiting for the return of his wife must take on the role of a father figure to his young daughter.

title: Mary Loss of Soul
description: When part of 15-year-old Mary's soul is ripped from her body, her family find themselves haunted by a wrathful spirit and desperate to find her soul before time runs out.

title: The Best People
description: Anna, a free-spirited woman, learns that her sister is engaged. She feels insecure and plans to sabotage her wedding with help from the groom's best man.

title: Desert Son
description: Phillip's stepfather abandons him in the desert, and the boy survives with two orphans named Jack and Lucy in an old mining town. Jack grows jealous of the bond between Phillip and Lucy and leads them back to civilization by committing increasingly dangerous crimes, until the unthinkable happens and the group violently unravels

title: Crackie
description: Mitsy lives with her grandmother after being abandoned by her mother. Her life takes a turn when she brings home Sparky, a dog, and tries to create a loving home for it. But, her joy is short-lived.

title: The Henchman's War
description: A henchman's mistake sets him on a deadly crusade against a mid-level crime boss.

title: Premeditated
description: Independent filmmakers in route to a meeting that they hope will finally give them their big break get sidetracked on the way, and in a matter of hours, they become the prime suspects in a woman's disappearance.

title: Sum of Existence
description: After being violently assaulted, a woman is hypnotized to forget what happened. However, her attacker has other disturbing plans in mind.

title: The Curse of Lilith Ratchet
description: A mysterious shrunken head brings sudden death to anyone who encounters it.

title: Life Gets In The Way
description: A woman living in Los Angeles tries to come to terms with her past and deal with her present struggles as she tries to find a partner in a city where serious relationships are a rarity.

title: The Glass Window
description: A young man struggles with balancing success and relationships until he travels to a mysterious island in the Bahamas and discovers the secret of The Glass Window

title: Outsourced
description: An American salesman whose job has been outsourced must travel to India to train his replacement. However, everything is not as easy as it seems.

title: Honor Among Thieves
description: After being injured in the Civil War, a veteran returns home to Texas to find he's been enlisted in a new battle, one for his life.

title: Blissful Lies
description: The bonds among five lifelong friends are tested when secrets and lies arise -- leaving them all wondering if it is too much to move forward as the family they once were.

title: Ouija Room
description: An agoraphobic woman with autism begins summoning spirits to be her friends while her caretaker/brother is gone during the day.

title: Hellphone
description: Le film tourne autour de l'histoire de Sid, de la fille de ses rêves, Angie, et de la façon dont le téléphone portable les aide à tomber amoureux à la fin.

title: La traversée
description: Alex et Stéphanie, agents communautaires, emmènent cinq adolescents décrocheurs dans un voyage éducatif à travers la Méditerranée. Mais leur capitaine se trouve être un ancien flic voué à une haine puissante envers les jeunes du quartier.

title: Water Lilies
description: Se déroulant au cours d'un été étouffant dans une banlieue française, Marie cherche désespérément à rejoindre l'équipe de natation synchronisée de la piscine locale, mais son intérêt est-il uniquement pour le sport ou pour avoir une chance de se rapprocher de Floriane, la mauvaise fille de l'équipe ?

title: Full Metal Village
description: Bewohner eines kleinen deutschen Dorfes bereiten sich auf den Zustrom von Heavy-Metal-Fans vor, die das jährliche Open-Air-Konzert des Dorfes besuchen.

title: Wer früher stirbt ist länger tot
description: Der elfjährige Sebastian erfährt, dass seine Mutter an seinem Geburtstag gestorben ist und gibt sich selbst die Schuld daran. Er bekommt Albträume von der Hölle und hat das Gefühl, dass es nur zwei Möglichkeiten gibt, sich selbst zu retten.

title: Das Gluck Kommt Unverhofft
description: Lotte Wagner ist eine alleinerziehende Mutter von zwei Kindern, die finanziell und beruflich Probleme hat. Matthias, Vorstandsmitglied der Firma, in der Lotte arbeitet, verliebt sich in sie.

title: Rindvieh A La Carte
description: Der arrogante Fernsehkoch Felix Hauser betreibt außerdem ein schickes Sternerestaurant und sein Agent Dennis steht kurz vor dem Abschluss eines japanischen Deals zur Gründung einer internationalen Kette.

title: Nichts als Ärger mit den Männern
description: Mit „Nichts als Ärger mit den Männern“ hat Matthias Steurer eine pfiffige Romantikkomödie inszeniert. Originelle Charaktere und gewitzte Dialoge machen die Geschichte einer jungen Frau, die lernen muss, ihr Leben endlich in den Griff zu bekommen, zu einem ebenso unterhaltsamen wie geistreichen Vergnügen.

title: Silent As The Grave
description: A relentless documentary filmmaker struggles to unravel the mystery of his uncle's death, but an unknown enemy is intent on keeping the truth buried.

title: The Fighter's Ballad
description: A confused, angry man breaks into a church. The priest inside offers him a chance at redemption.

title: The Wishing Forest
description: A desperate widow goes on a dangerous quest to find a mythical wish-granting unicorn that lies deep within a cannibal-infested forest.

title: A Psycho's Path
description: Captain Peters and his crew undertake a mission to track down a blood-hunter serial killer who is on a spree to murder the residents of a desert town in California.

title: Sugar
description: Private detective John Sugar investigates the disappearance of Olivia Siegel, the beloved granddaughter of Hollywood producer Jonathan Siegel. As Sugar tries to determine what happened to Olivia, he unearths Siegel family secrets, old and new.

title: Daily Dose of Sunshine
description: 정신과에서 일하는 친절한 간호사는 자신에게 닥칠 어려움에도 불구하고 자신이 돌보는 사람들에게 매일 햇빛이 되기 위해 최선을 다합니다.

title: Minha história
description: ang Yi, um líder de igreja, é preso em uma das campanhas de prisão em massa do Partido Comunista Chinês e condenado a dez anos na prisão. Sob o monitoramento estrito e as exigências de trabalho escravo dos guardas da prisão, ele se sente péssimo e atormentado e anseia pelo suprimento das palavras de Deus.

title: Dois Irmãos
description: Dois Irmãos: Uma Jornada Fantástica 2020 Ian Lightfoot & Barley Lightfoot Melhores Momentos

title: Simplesmente Acontece
description: Você não precisa ir tão longe para encontrar aquilo que mais procura. Alex (Sam Claflin) e Rosie (Lily Collins) são amigos inseparáveis que cresceram juntos em Londres, compartilhando entre si suas melhores experiências. Tudo muda quando Alex ganha uma bolsa de estudos e passa a morar nos EUA. Separados, seus caminhos agora são outros. Mas nos tempos de hoje é impossível não permanecer conectado. E em se tratando de amor, o difícil é fazer as escolhas certas.

title: Luna Llena
description: Un pistolero del salvaje oeste regresa de la tumba para evitar que una banda de hombres lobo sedientos de sangre aterrorice a un pequeño pueblo.

title: Online Binline
description: Sid, an Internet addict, loves Kimaya but is unsure of approaching her without the facade of the virtual world. When his friend also falls in love with her, he competes against him to win her heart.

title: Send It!
description: Billy Johnson's coach and friends help him participate in the world's most prestigious kiteboarding championship. He meets a girl who challenges and inspires him to be a better athlete.

title: Beverly H
description: A Beverly Hills CEO must address her cheating husband, protect her company from a corporate raider, and decide if the world is ready for a new life-extension drug, all within 24 hours.

title: Salt
description: CIA agent Evelyn Salt's life takes an ugly turn when she is accused of planning the assassination of the Russian president. However, she flees and sets out to prove her innocence.

title: Circles
description: Vol. 1 :- Mya, a teenage girl growing up in the inner city, faces the challenges of young adulthood.

title: Fighting Olympus
description: When a retired police officer learns his brother has been captured by a secret society, he must infiltrate the cult to expose their crimes and rescue his brother. In this unique action/crime drama, a man must choose between family and the call of duty..

title: Hillwalkers
description: When a group of young hikers accidentally trespass on the wrong private property, they find themselves human prey of its masked, gun-toting owner.

title: Vendetta Road
description: A highly surveilled cabin compound on a campground plays host to a fugitive who's on the run from a mafia gang manhunt.

title: When Jack Came Back
description: Jack, a down-on-his-luck actor, begrudgingly comes home after the death of his father and discovers that his mum is in the grip of Alzheimer's disease. Now, the two of them must find some common ground before Nancy's time runs out.

title: Super Hybrid
description: With a mind of its own, a mysterious car goes on an unstoppable killing spree.

title: Awakening The Nun
description: Bad Nun: Deadly Vows :- Catherine and her family move into a converted church and are harassed by a religious stalker. Catherine's grandmother begins to reveal that she has secrets that she keeps hidden from the local church and that the nun returns every night.

title: Whiteblood
description: Rico leaves back the vicious circle of the drug world and becomes an illegal immigrant with his mother. However, soon he finds himself returning to his past to pay for her cancer treatment.

title: Hobo Heyseus
description: A strange man attempts to help folks of a small town change by using words, deeds, and logic.

title: White Night
description: Five people go through various art installations as they deal with the issues of love, loss and getting old.

title: Broken
description: Desperate to escape her broken past, a woman (Morjana Alaoui) settles in England and becomes the caregiver of a tetraplegic patient (Mel Raido).

title: American Gothic
description: After their prison bus crashes, two convicts escape and break into in an isolated farmhouse. The quiet couple living there prove to be anything but victims.

title: Bittersweet Monday
description: An emotional goodbye between two friends morphs into an unexpected love affair, which puts two marriages and several friendships in jeopardy.

title: Thug Love
description: Going through a difficult divorce at 40, Destiny begins a passionate affair with a young man. As her obsession with him grows, her career will be in danger unless she can handle it all.

title: Wake Up
description: As a psychiatrist tries to break down the motives that led one of his patients to kill her entire family, it begins to take a toll on his own mental health.

title: Woodstock Or Bust
description: Meryl and Lorian, two ambitious singers tired of their local performances, set out on a trip filled with misadventures to debut their original album at the Woodstock music festival.

title: Should've Put A Ring On It
description: Thea (Tiara Gathright) is tired of waiting for her boyfriend to pop the question so she creates an elaborate proposal that he spoils with his reluctance.

title: Nagahan Derakht
description: فرهاد زندگی خود را از کودکی تا 50 سالگی برای روانکاو تعریف می‌کند.

title: The Midnight Man
description: A couple travels to a remote cabin on a mountain for a romantic getaway. However, things soon turn dark when they realise that a manic killer is on the loose.

title: Get Happy!
description: A miserable man finds happiness when he dates a manic young woman.

title: Scandalous
description: Three couples get together after the death of a key figure in their lives, and they encounter a web of infidelity and deceit.

title: Finding Desmond
description: Finding Desmond follows the struggles of Desmond Jackson. Since Desmond's mother was the only person who knew his past died, he had no choice but to disappear into the streets to hide.

title: Just Say Goodbye
description: A woman is looking forward to a vacation until she learns her best friend is planning to kill himself while she is away.

title: Street
description: An amateur MMA fighter decides to participate in an underground circuit after he angers a Russian mafia leader, who wants to hire him.

title: Double Duty
description: A tough woman struggles to adapt to civilian life after leaving the Marines. Her relationship with her best friend and a new romance with a kind, considerate man help her to discover her feminine side.

title: You Can't Have It
description: Bill, along with his wife and friends, decides to spend time in a bar the night it is supposed to shut down, unaware of the mayhem that is going to ensue.

title: Dead Weight
description: A woman finds herself lost in the desert with an impaled leg, amnesia, and a strange bag she can't let go of. As she finds her way out, the items in the bag - and a meeting with a Baby Shaman - help her remember and confront memories she may have killed her brother.

title: Black Fly
description: A troubled teenager and his older brother reconnect, setting off a powder keg of buried secrets, paranoia and murder. Inspired by true events.

title: The Body Tree
description: A group of friends visiting Siberia to honour the memory of their friend sets a demon free during a ceremony. Later, they must learn to trust each other to save their lives.

title: 3 Holes and a Smoking Gun
description: An ex-Hollywood screenwriter turned teacher has an evening class in New York City. He soon becomes locked in a battle of wits with a devious student who has designs on the same masterful script.

title: The Dog Walker
description: After a traumatic assignment, an investigative journalist decides to retire. However, a killer forces her to solve one last mystery.

title: Milwood
description: An orphan assigned to Milwood Orphanage and Boarding School for Boys becomes a victim of terror.

title: Primrose Lane
description: Chris and Robin visit their friend's home and are surprised to find it is empty. They soon realize they are in some sort of alternate reality and not as alone as they think.

title: Seventy-Nine
description: Doctors carry out secret experiments in a supposedly abandoned asylum, testing new methods of brainwashing on subjects who have been taken from their everyday lives.

title: Hong Kong Rebels
description: A 16-year-old aspiring writer is lured into the Hong Kong underworld after his brother's questionable suicide

title: Flying By
description: This musically driven drama follows a successful Real Estate developer who puts his marriage and business on the line when given the opportunity to follow his ultimate, life-long dream: music.

title: Dark Nemesis
description: In a post-apocalyptic world ruled by feuding leaders, a group of soldiers attempt to steal a warlord's treasure. To escape capture, they step into a desolate and dangerous land.

title: Natural Selection
description: After Tyler and his mother move to a different town, he faces problems while adjusting to his new school. But after he meets Indrid, a rebel, and Paige, a sweet girl, he gets torn between the two.

title: Prairie Dog
description: A lone sheriff and a visiting environmental consultant race to solve the mystery that haunts the valleys of Brada County.

title: Misfortune
description: A young man learns that his father's killer's will soon be released on parole, which sparks a chase through the desert, searching for a hidden family inheritance.

title: Purgatorium
description: Five strangers wake up in an abandoned house and realize if they want to escape, they will have to work together to solve a puzzle of murder and mayhem.

title: Palmdale
description: A drifter with a violent past comes to the city to kill somebody for money. On his way to do it, a young woman crashes into his life, giving him the choice - to continue on this path of self destruction or leave it all behind him.

title: The Cure
description: A pharma laboratory decides to promote a cancer antidote without researching about its side effects. When the laboratory director finds out, he questions the research head.

title: Paranormal Abduction
description: Rebekah Lakin suffers a memory loss after she escapes a brutal assault by Frank. She tries to recollect the incident and finds it similar to a series of recent murders.

title: The Slider
description: Michael works as a hospital attendant and lives with his wife, Ester, who falls into depression after their son dies. Michael is willing to do everything possible to save her, even things that no healthy mind could ever have imagined.

title: Kidnapped In Romania
description: A couple of Italian-American journalists head to Romania to create a tourism guide. Things take an unexpected turn when they are kidnapped and held for ransom.

title: No Witnesses
description: A man, still traumatized by witnessing the killing of his mother as a child, decides to seek his own brand of justice by carrying out a home invasion after learning that a wealthy businessman may have gotten away with murder.

title: Pastor Shirley
description: Jason is distraught after his community starts depleting post a series of unfortunate events. He turns to pastor Shirley for help in his time on need.

title: Point of no Return
description: Peter, a young aircraft engineer is deceived by his manager Jason into substituting faulty aircraft parts. When a part explodes killing a passenger, Air accident investigation find Peter responsible. Jason is found murdered.

title: Concealed
description: A struggling South African actor travels to Australia for a life-changing audition. However, his trip descends into chaos when his girlfriend suddenly goes missing.

title: The Phoenix Project
description: The Phoenix Project - Four scientists craft a machine to reanimate deceased organisms.

title: The Burning of Atlanta
description: After a major battle, federal troops take control of Atlanta, only to have the Confederates try to burn it to the ground.

title: Firetrail
description: When a Confederate cavalry captain is transferred from the Virginia front to defend his home state, he discovers that his fiancée has left him for a profiteering draft-dodger.

title: Terror Talk
description: When a virus outbreak causes widespread panic, a doomsday prepper retreats into his new house; believing that he's safe from the dangers outside, he quickly discovers that his house is haunted by terrifying ghosts.

title: Miracles Are For Real
description: A famous television star meets her abusive ex-husband for dinner and notes that he has changed considerably since their separation. Later, she must decide whether to trust him again or not.

title: Switchin' the Script
description: During a weekend corporate retreat, Lonnie's best friends convince her to take control when dealing with men. Lonnie's new attitude impresses every man she meets, especially her boss's good-looking son, David.

title: Regarding the Case of Joan of Arc
description: Joan, an alt-right Christian terrorist, claims that she is sent by God and follows the commands of a voice that tells her to attack the federal buildings in the USA.

title: Pagan Warrior
description: After a savage gang of Vikings invade a Saxon castle, murdering all in their path and claiming it as their own, one vengeful surviving man uses a coven of witches to summon a demon to enact revenge

title: Body Keepers
description: Seeking a part for a school project, a group of teenagers break into a shed housing a corpse kept on dry ice. As a result of this, they unleash an evil entity that soon targets them.

title: Shiner
description: Matt Bradford, a naive, aspiring MMA fighter suffers the misfortune of teaming with Happy McBride, a flash-in-the-pan (but flashy) ex-champ. Despite huge differences in their agendas, Matt and Happy force each other to overcome deep issues - with Happy's daughter, who becomes Matt's girlfriend - as referee.

title: Los crímenes de Oxford
description: Un profesor de la Universidad de Oxford y un estudiante intentan descifrar símbolos y algoritmos matemáticos asociados a una misteriosa serie de asesinatos.

title: Fuera de carta
description: Maxi, un conocido chef gay, se encuentra en un aprieto cuando sus hijos de su anterior matrimonio aparecen al mismo tiempo que un futbolista argentino por el que desarrolla sentimientos.

title: Enloquecidas
description: Después de que el amor de su vida desaparece misteriosamente, una joven emprende con su tía un viaje por la ciudad para descubrir qué pasó.

title: Cobardes
description: Cobardes es una película dramática española de 2008 con temática de acoso escolar escrita y dirigida por José Corbacho y Juan Cruz, protagonizada por Eduardo Garé y Eduardo Espinilla.

title: Besouro
description: Besouro, um lendário lutador de capoeira brasileiro, embarca na missão de vingar o brutal assassinato de seu mentor, cujo fantasma o obriga a derrotar os poderosos e libertar os escravos.

title: Lula o filho do Brasil
description: Um menino da classe trabalhadora muda-se ainda jovem para a capital financeira do Brasil e cresce para se tornar um dos políticos mais influentes da história do país.

title: Xuxa em Sonho de Menina
description: Xuxa em Sonho de Menina is a 2007 Brazilian fantasy children's film, written by Flávio de Souza and directed by Rudi Lagemann. It was the first film with the actress Xuxa to be directed by Conspiração Filmes, and was distributed by Warner Bros. and Globo Filmes.

title: O Guerreiro Didi e a Ninja Lili
description: Um guardião (Renato Aragão) deve proteger a filha de um soldado europeu desaparecido.

title: Meu Nome Não É Johnny
description: João, um menino de família de classe média alta, entra no mundo do tráfico de drogas após o divórcio dos pais. Tudo vai bem até que ele é capturado e apresentado ao tribunal.

title: EL CONJURO 2
description: Peggy, madre soltera de cuatro hijos, busca la ayuda de los investigadores de lo oculto Ed y Lorraine Warren cuando ella y sus hijos presencian sucesos extraños y paranormales en su casa.

title: Mothman
description: Amanda Mason and her boyfriend Tim set out to film a documentary on the case surrounding her missing brother, Dakota. Through a series of interviews, they uncover that Dakota was disturbed and troubled by an event months before his disappearance.

title: Skipping Stones
description: After the tragic death of her brother, a young girl tries to fight the guilt of being left behind while grieving her brother's death.

title: Wild Boys
description: When her belated father challenges her to a treasure hunt with her inheritance as the price, Kate, a reclusive young woman, must venture into the wild unknown to protect her solitary way of life. Ill-equipped for an outdoor adventure, Kate gets lost and joins forces with a pair of feral young men she encounters in the wilderness

title: The Summerland Project (Amelia 2.0)
description: After his wife Amelia suffers an aneurysm that leaves her bedridden and slowly dying, police officer Carter Summerland searches for a way to revive her. He's approached by Wesley Enterprises about allowing Amelia to be the test subject for an experimental program that will place her mind in an artificial body.

title: Adam & Eve
description: A young man searches for his path to God only to find it in sin.

title: Morgen, ihr Luschen! Der Ausbilder-Schmidt
description: Schmidt, ein Militärausbilder, versucht, seine Jungen abzuhärten, indem er ihnen Disziplin beibringt. Die Dinge werden jedoch hässlich, als seine Chefin anfängt, seine Methoden in Frage zu stellen.

title: Margarete Steiff
description: Basierend auf dem Leben der deutschen Spielzeugmacherin Margarete Steiff zeigt der Film ihren langen Weg von einem 10-jährigen Mädchen, das an den Rollstuhl gefesselt ist, zu einer der ersten und erfolgreichsten Schöpferinnen von Stofftieren.

title: Au delà des apparences
description: Après que sa petite amie ait été assassinée par des mafieux européens, Sam s'enfuit à Paris pour se cacher. Des années plus tard, il voit une femme dans un film hollywoodien dont il est certain qu'elle est Georgia. À Los Angeles pour enquêter, il rencontre Kat, qui décide impulsivement de l'aider.

title: LOL
description: Lola, une adolescente, apprend à gérer les aléas de la vie adolescente, les relations, les malentendus, les amis et sa mère célibataire, qui est choquée lorsqu'elle découvre son mode de vie.

title: Martyrs
description: Lucie et Anna, victimes de maltraitance sur enfants, se lancent dans un voyage pour se venger de leurs agresseurs.

title: خمس جولات
description: 5 Rounds (Khamas Gawlat)... فارس، مقاتل مصري شاب من القرية، لديه فرصة واحدة ضد بطل اللزوجة إدغار. الفوز هو حلمه، لكن الطريق صعب للغاية بالنسبة لهذا الفتى الصغير في البلدة... وكل من حوله يخذلونه أو يستغلونه.....

title: اولاد رزق
description: Welad Rizk... يواجه الإخوة المجرمين الخيانة بعد فشل صفقة مع تاجر مخدرات.

title: الحفلة
description: Al Hafla... شاب يستعين بأحد محققي الشرطة للعثور على زوجته التي اختفت في ظروف غامضة من أحد المتاجر الكبرى. وعندما يحقق المحقق في القضية، يجد بعض الاكتشافات المذهلة.

title: هامليت فريزر
description: Hamlit Fraizer... عندما يضرب التغير المناخي مصر ويجمد البلاد، تتظاهر مجموعة من الضباط غريبي الأطوار بشخصية طاقم تصوير في إيطاليا وينطلقون للبحث عن جهاز يمكنه إنقاذ أمتهم.

title: A Return to Grace: Luther's Life and Legacy
description: Telling the story of the monk who took on the Catholic Church, tracing his life before and after the contentious 95 Theses.

title: Being Trump
description: President Donald Trump's Space Force program has quickly become a reality, and he insists on being the first man to walk the red planet. However, the framers of the constitution never imagined a sitting president leaving the planet.

title: Nun Nancy
description: A passionate minister disguises herself as a bartender at a Baltimore watering hole so she can more effectively share God's love with the clientele.

title: Camp Cool Kids
description: With encouragement from his eccentric grandfather, an outcast tries to overcome his fears and stand up against bullies at a summer camp.

title: Paranormal
description: Paranormal follows best-selling, self-made novelist Greg Evans struggling through the worst case of writer's block in his award-winning career. In a desperate search for inspiration, Greg quickly finds himself immersed in a world he is not prepared to face.

title: Chain of Life: The Rick Boyle Story
description: Chain of Life tells the inspirational story of Rick Boyle, a man who overcame extraordinary obstacles-learning disabilities, childhood abuse and neglect, obesity, and a four-pack-a-day cigarette habit-to become an avid long distance bicyclist, mentor of young people, and a teacher in his church.

title: Saint Nicholas
description: Everybody knows the story of Santa Claus, the red–suited figure who lives at the North Pole and distributes gifts to good children every Christmas eve. But is there any historical evidence on which this jolly old character is based? Was there a real Santa Claus? To answer that question, host Mark Wilson, a distinguished historian and archeologist travels not to the North Pole but to modern day Turkey and Italy. There he uncovers clues that lead to the truth about the man behind the legend.

title: Jack London's Son of the Wolf
description: After winning gold in a bet, young Jack London embarks on a spirited journey that takes him to a native village where he finds love

title: Bigfoot: Grip of the Monster
description: Author Max Lee writes a bestseller about his terrifying encounter with a Bigfoot in the woods of Maine. Twenty years later, he returns to the scene of the life-changing event to search for answers.

title: House in Time
description: After being discharged from a psychiatric institution, Dez returns to her childhood home to assume the role of caregiver for her estranged mother. Her homecoming soon takes a surreal turn when she stumbles upon portals that lead her back to significant moments from the past.

title: No Small Matter
description: High-quality care and education has far-reaching impacts. Discovering the tragic cost of getting this wrong and the huge payoff for kids, families, and country of getting it right.

title: Chuck Berry
description: Noted for his talent and charisma, the prolific craftsman of word and chords, Chuck Berry, gets explored with a look at his enduring legacy as the absolute instigator of rock and roll.

title: Hee Haw Farm
description: Struggling to fund her veterinarian dream, a teen takes a job at a quirky donkey farm, where unforeseen challenges and eccentric characters await.

title: Calber Island
