description: A young woman goes in a coma and needs a kidney replacement to stay alive. The situation gets complicated as she is adopted, and her mother must find her biological parents to save her life.

title: Wake The Dead
description: After a near death incident leaves Kristin scarred with a terrifying connection to the Spirit World, her family attempts to break her free of an Evil Spirit's hold.

title: The Congressman
description: Charlie Winship, a congressman, gets embroiled in controversy and visits a remote island to clear his head and get his life under control.

title: As Dreamers Do
description: The story of how Walt Disney created a film empire through his love of animation and vast imagination and talent.

title: A Year and Change
description: Owen undergoes a self-awakening process and decides to turn his life around. He gives up drinking and falls in love with Vera.

title: Adormidera
description: In the late 1300s, five warriors returning home from battle encounter a fort which turns into an epic fight for survival.

title: Les fusillés
description: Louis, militaire de 27 ans, perd son régiment lors d'une attaque de l'ennemi. Il est accusé de désertion alors qu'il rentre dans son camp après avoir recherché sa troupe.

title: La Résurrection
description: Un psychologue du lycée (Mischa Barton) tente d'aider un étudiant qui croit que son frère revient de la tombe pour punir ses assassins.

title: Les Dangereux
description: La jeune et talentueuse chanteuse Roxanne LaBelle a été kidnappée contre une rançon d'un million de dollars et la seule personne qui sait pourquoi est son père et manager canaille.

title: La Loi Du Cochon
description: Stéphane Brousseau, 27 ans, est un joueur compulsif. Alors que la banque s'apprête à saisir la porcherie qu'elle a héritée de son père, elle tente de gagner un peu d'argent en vendant la récolte de marijuana que deux criminels de la ville cultivent sur ses terres. La sœur cadette de Stéphane, Bettie, est mère porteuse pour un couple de banlieue.

title: Les 3 Mousquetaires
description: D'Artagnan et les trois mousquetaires doivent affronter le sinistre Richelieu, le duc de Buckingham et la traîtresse Milady afin d'empêcher la France d'attaquer l'Angleterre.

title: So Weit Die Fuße Tragen
description: Clemens Forell, ein deutscher Soldat, muss mit mehreren Strapazen konfrontiert werden, bevor er nach der Flucht aus dem russischen Gefängnis nach Deutschland gelangt und zu seiner Familie zurückkehrt.

title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes
description: Many years after the reign of Caesar, a young ape goes on a journey that will lead him to question everything he's been taught about the past and make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.

title: Inside Out 2
description: Joy, Sadness, Anger, Fear and Disgust have been running a successful operation by all accounts. However, when Anxiety shows up, they aren't sure how to feel.

title: Hit Man
description: Professional killer Gary Johnson breaks protocol to help a desperate woman trying to flee an abusive husband and finds himself falling for her.

title: Furiosa: A Mad Max Saga
description: Snatched from the Green Place of Many Mothers, young Furiosa falls into the hands of a great biker horde led by the warlord Dementus. Sweeping through the Wasteland, they come across the Citadel, presided over by the Immortan Joe. As the two tyrants fight for dominance, Furiosa soon finds herself in a nonstop battle to make her way home.

title: Kali: Avenging Angel 2024
description: Lisa, alias Kali, n'a plus rien à perdre lorsqu'elle apprend que son mari a été exécuté à Rio pour dissimuler un scandale de corruption. Ancienne recrue des Forces Spéciales, elle part au Brésil à coups de poing, de sang et d'explosifs, pour connaître la vérité.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Mahi
description: मिस्टर एंड मिसेज माही 2024 की हिंदी भाषा की रोमांटिक स्पोर्ट्स ड्रामा फिल्म है, जो शरण शर्मा द्वारा निर्देशित और ज़ी स्टूडियो और धर्मा प्रोडक्शंस द्वारा निर्मित है। फिल्म में राजकुमार राव और जान्हवी कपूर हैं। इसकी घोषणा नवंबर 2021 में की गई थी, जबकि फिल्मांकन मई 2022 से मई 2023 तक हुआ था।

title: Srikanth
description: श्रीकांत 2024 की भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की जीवनी पर आधारित फिल्म है, जो दृष्टिबाधित उद्योगपति और बोलैंट इंडस्ट्रीज के संस्थापक श्रीकांत बोल्ला के जीवन पर आधारित है। शीर्षक भूमिका में राजकुमार राव अभिनीत, यह तुषार हीरानंदानी द्वारा निर्देशित है और सह-कलाकार ज्योतिका, अलाया एफ और शरद केलकर हैं।

title: L'Étrangère
description: Marie Fraser (Anne Caillon) es una treintañera que llega a una pequeña isla francesa donde comenzará una nueva vida contratada como periodista, aunque pronto empezará a verse afectada por la falta de confianza en sí misma que afecta las relaciones en su vida diaria.

title: Beate Uhse - Das Recht auf Liebe
description: Beate Uhse war eine deutsche Pilotin und Unternehmerin. In den 1930er Jahren war sie die einzige weibliche Stuntpilotin in Deutschland und eröffnete nach dem Zweiten Weltkrieg den ersten Sexshop der Welt. Das von ihr gegründete Unternehmen Beate Uhse AG ist an der Frankfurter Börse notiert und weltweit führend im Vertrieb von Sexualhilfsmitteln.

title: In den Tag hinein
description: Lynn (Sabine Timoteo) ist eine fröhliche 22-Jährige, die in einem Café arbeitet und mit ihrem Bruder zusammenlebt. Obwohl sie keine wirkliche Richtung im Leben hat, ist sie glücklich. Ihr Freund David (Florian Muller-Mohrungen) hingegen ist ein karriereorientierter Schwimmer, dem es offenbar nur um sein Training geht.

title: School's Out 2 und Insel der Angst
description: Nina und ihre Freunde werden während ihres Urlaubs auf einer Insel von einem maskierten Mörder verfolgt.

title: Engel & Joe
description: Eine Teenagerin (Jana Pallaske) rennt vor ihrer Mutter (Lena Sabine Berg) davon und verliebt sich in einen Straßenpunk (Robert Stadlober), der gerne Party macht.

title: Super Naani
description: सुपर नानी: मान की दादी भारती का उसके परिवार द्वारा तिरस्कार किया जाता है और उसके साथ दुर्व्यवहार किया जाता है। उन्हें उसकी कीमत का एहसास कराने के लिए, मान उसे पूरी तरह से मेकओवर देता है और उसे मॉडलिंग के अवसर लेने के लिए भी मनाता है।

title: Gurgaon
description: गुडगाँव: एक रियल एस्टेट कारोबारी की बेटी प्रीत का उसके ही भाई निक्की ने अपहरण कर लिया है। जैसे ही उसका परिवार उसके ठिकाने का पता लगाने की कोशिश करता है, कई रहस्य खुल जाते हैं और उन सभी के लिए चीजें एक बुरा मोड़ ले लेती हैं।

title: Yun Hota Toh Kya Hota
description: यूँ होता तोह क्या होता: भारत के विभिन्न हिस्सों से चार व्यक्ति अमेरिका जाने वाली उड़ान में सवार होते हैं। हालाँकि, वे एक दुर्भाग्यपूर्ण स्थिति में फंस गए हैं क्योंकि उड़ान भरने के तुरंत बाद विमान का अपहरण कर लिया गया है।

title: Don 2
description: डॉन 2: एशियाई अंडरवर्ल्ड पर प्रभुत्व जमाने के बाद, डॉन की नज़र यूरोपीय आपराधिक बाज़ार पर है। बर्लिन माफिया और कानून प्रवर्तन के बीच फंसा डॉन विश्वासघात और विश्वासघात से बचने की कोशिश करता है।

title: Los Ojos de Julia
description: Mientras Julia pierde lentamente la vista debido a una enfermedad ocular degenerativa, su hermana gemela ciega, Sara, es encontrada muerta. Julia corre contra la ceguera inminente para investigar la muerte de Sara.

title: Divertida Mente 2
description: Joy, Sadness, Anger, Fear and Disgust have been running a successful operation by all accounts. However, when Anxiety shows up, they aren't sure how to feel.

title: protetor 2
description: Robert McCall's close friend, Susan Plummer, is killed while investigating a murder-suicide. As a former marine and spy, he leverages his skills and resources to find the culprit and avenge her death.

title: Fights Break Sphere
description: Ma Boqian / Li Jiuxiao / Zhang Hanyu / Gao Shuguang / Jiang Wu / Hu Jing / Huang Wen / Jiang Zhuojun / Xia Ruoyan / Jin Yangyang / Xu Kerong / Zhang Xinyi

title: Shaitaan
description: A family outing takes a terrifying turn when an intruder takes over the body of the teenage daughter, putting her at the mercy of increasingly sinister orders.

title: سحر إل عيون
description: Sehr El Oyoun... يقرر ساسو استخدام السحر لإغراء كريم، مدير الإعلانات الذي فقد رأسه فيما بعد بسببها. تأخذ الأمور منعطفًا عندما يُعجب ساسو برجل آخر بسبب التأثيرات العكسية للسحر.

title: كليم ماما
description: Kallem mama... ترفض والدة إحدى الفتيات علاقتها بجارتها، مما يجعل صديقاتها الثلاثة يواجهن مشاكل ويتدخلن في حل المشكلة.

title: رشا جاريا
description: Rasha garea... يريد سلماوي وميما أن يصبحا مشهورين في عالم المسرح. لكن عليهم أن يمروا بالكثير من الصعوبات والعقبات لتحقيق أحلامهم.

title: 55 Esaaf
description: 55 سيارة إسعاف: وفاء طبيبة شابة تقوم بإعداد مشروع تطوير إجراءات الإسعافات الأولية في أحد المستشفيات لعرضه على وزير الصحة. تتورط وفاء مع تمرجي وسائق. تواجه سيارة الإسعاف العديد من المشاكل، وتلاحقهم عصابة بشكل مستمر. وتتفاقم الأزمة مع اختطاف وزير الصحة.

title: Yoyes
description: Yoyes es una película de drama político español de 2000 dirigida por Helena Taberna que consiste en una reconstrucción ficticia de la vida de María Dolores Katarain, una miembro de ETA, que fue atacada por esa organización a su regreso al País Vasco.

title: Sé quien eres
description: Un psiquiatra se enamora de un paciente que sufre de amnesia e intenta ayudarlo a explorar y recordar su pasado.

title: Lista de Espera
description: Cubanos frustrados (Vladimir Cruz, Thaimi Alvarino, Jorge Perugorría) intentan mejorar su situación mientras están varados en una estación de autobuses.

title: Krámpack
description: Nico y Dani, una pareja de adolescentes, tienen una gran casa de verano para pasar sus vacaciones. Disfrutan al máximo y en el proceso aprenden mucho sobre sí mismos, incluida su sexualidad.

title: Pantaleón y las visitadoras
description: Una severa capitana del ejército peruano (Angie Cepeda) recibe órdenes de montar un burdel improvisado para satisfacer las necesidades de sus tropas.

title: Km. 0
description: Un barman, una estudiante de cine, una prostituta, una bailaora de flamenco y otros lidian con los vaivenes del romance.

title: Plata quemada
description: Ambientada en la Argentina de 1965, la historia sigue la tumultuosa relación entre dos hombres que se convirtieron en amantes y, en última instancia, en despiadados ladrones de bancos en una nota a pie de página notoriamente famosa en los anales de la historia del crimen.

title: Plenilunio
description: Un detective cínico comienza un romance tentativo con la maestra de un niño cuyo asesinato está investigando.

title: A Mulher que Acreditava Ser Presidente Dos EUA
description: A Mulher que Acreditava ser Presidente dos Estados Unidos da América é um filme português, realizado por João Botelho, no ano de 2003. O papel principal é desempenhado por Alexandra Lencastre

title: Vai e Vem
description: João Vuvu, vive sozinho numa casa que necessita de regeneração mas por estar sozinho não consegue fazer a obra. A libertação do filho da prisão e o subsequente engano de João desencadeiam uma série de acontecimentos sombrios.

title: Um Filme Falado
description: No Mediterrâneo, uma professora (Leonor Silveira) mostra à sua filha (Filipa de Almeida) locais antigos, enquanto três mulheres debatem com o capitão do navio (John Malkovich).

title: Os Imortais
description: Cansados ​​de sua vida monótona, quatro ex-soldados decidem roubar um banco. No entanto, quando um inspetor local tenta solucionar o roubo, ele descobre mais informações do que esperava.

title: Complexo - Universo Paralelo
description: Complexo - Universo Paralelo is a 2011 Portuguese documentary film about life in the most dangerous favela in Rio de Janeiro, Complexo do Alemão, directed by Mário Patrocínio.

title: Apenas o Fim
description: Uma garota tenta encontrar equilíbrio em sua vida antes de fugir e terminar com o namorado.

title: Mauá - O Imperador e o Rei
description: Um filme sobre um empresário brasileiro que rivalizava com o homem mais rico da América em sua época, o conhecido Rockfeller. Irineu Evangelista de Souza em 1867 tinha $ 155.000 contos de réis, enquanto o orçamento anual do governo brasileiro era de 97.000 contos de réis.

title: Raul - O Início, o Fim e o Meio
description: O filme conta a história de Raul Seixas, uma lenda do rock brasileiro. O documentário desvenda por meio de raras imagens de arquivo, encontros com familiares, conversas com artistas, produtores e amigos, a trajetória do artista, falecido em 1989.

title: Orquestra dos Meninos
description: Quando um jovem músico é sequestrado em condições misteriosas, todas as suspeitas recaem sobre o maestro de meia-idade da orquestra, que está lidando com sua própria cota de problemas.

title: The Impact Factor
description: An ambitious Philadelphia political operative finds herself suddenly powerless to help when a rebellious girl on parole pleads for help.

title: The Lost World of Mr. Hardy
description: The story of the Hardy Brothers and the disappearing art of crafting fishing tackle is examined by featuring rediscovered archive movie footage from the 1920s.

title: Hey Diddle Diddle
description: A former popular high school student who squandered all his promise and currently battles a severe case of social anxiety disorder, faces the very people who once adored him at an upcoming high school reunion.

title: Dreams On Spec
description: A filmmaker follows three screenwriters as they make personal sacrifices and struggle against overwhelming odds to see their scripts turned into movies.

title: Gallery of Fear
description: Art critic Roberta Van Houten (Debbie Rochon) attends a private showing at the Lunatic Gallery and views a collection of murder, monsters and mayhem.

title: The Caretakers
description: An aging caretaker for a powerful vampire must help hunt down a rogue half-breed vampire at the same time that he trains his two new apprentices.

title: Vincent A Life In Color
description: Vincent is followed as he performs fashion shows on the bridges of Chicago for tour boats.

title: I Am Shakespeare: The Henry Green Story
description: Stephen Dest's documentary I Am Shakespeare: The Henry Green Story chronicles the true life story of 19 year old, Henry Green, living a dual life as a brilliant young actor and inner-city gang member, who was brutally shot and left for dead .

title: كامل الأوصاف
description: شاب ثري يعود إلى مصر من الخارج، يلتقي بامرأتين في وضعين مختلفين، ويواجه معضلة مثلث الحب. ينشأ التوتر عندما يكتشف أن الفتاتين شقيقتان.

title: Les Parrains
description: Trois anciens voleurs doivent découvrir où se trouve une fortune cachée.

title: À la conquête d'un cœur
description: Après le décès prématuré de son mari, Marty épouse Clark Davis, veuf, et élève sa fille Missie. Cependant, Missie refuse de l'accepter comme belle-mère, la laissant déprimée.

title: Jeanne d'Arc
description: Jeanne, une jeune religieuse qui grandit en France lors de l'invasion des forces anglaises, commence à avoir des visions qui l'amènent à prendre les armes contre les envahisseurs pour mettre fin à l'oppression.

title: Zeugin Der Toten
description: Judith Keplers mysteriöse Vergangenheit taucht wieder auf, als sie einen Tatort aufsucht, um einen Mordfall zu untersuchen, an dem eine Frau beteiligt ist, die sie zuvor während einer Recherche kontaktiert hatte.

title: Vergebung
description: Nachdem sie mehrere Schusswunden erlitten hat, wird Lisbeth auf die Intensivstation gebracht, wo sie auf ihren Prozess wegen dreier Morde wartet. Mikael versucht, ihre Unschuld zu beweisen, muss aber ihre düstere Vergangenheit enthüllen.

title: B-Side: For Taylor
description: A year after the sudden death of her mother, Taylor, a 14-year-old Korean-American adoptee becomes increasingly desperate to find her birth parents, especially as her relationship with her father grows more estranged. But when a Korean family unexpectedly immigrates to her all-white neighborhood, she befriends a new maternal figure who helps her discover her roots and the truth about her birth family's whereabouts

title: Dumb Money
description: Everyday people flip the script on Wall Street and get rich by turning GameStop into one of the world's hottest companies. In the middle of everything is Keith Gill, a regular guy who starts it all by sinking his life savings into the stock. When his social media posts start blowing up, so does his life and the lives of everyone following him. As a stock tip becomes a movement, everyone gets wealthy -- until the billionaires fight back and both sides find their worlds turned upside down.

title: Hacker
description: A young computer hacker and her father find themselves targeted by a powerful enemy when they uncover an assassination plot.

title: Daughter of the Wolf
description: Clair Hamilton is a military veteran whose son Charlie has been kidnapped. She brings a bag of money as ransom for Charlie but at the exchange the kidnappers is double-crossed, leading to a shootout. Clair shoots two of the kidnappers but one of the men, Larsen, escapes. Clair falls into a frozen lake while chasing him but Larsen pulls her out because he was not planning to kill anyone and did not know about the plans to double-cross her. Clair has a peaceful encounter with a black wolf while recovering, then catches up with Larsen and forces him at gunpoint to take her to the leader of the kidnappers, Father, a man who is angry at her deceased father for closing a mill and leaving money owed to him. As they near the hideout in the snowy forest they are fired upon, but the rifleman is attacked and killed by three wolves. Clair finds the hideout but the kidnappers have moved on to a lodge on the other side of the mountain to await a hand-off to sell off the boy and Larsen reveals that Father killed his father and abducted Larsen and his mother when he was a boy. At the lodge Clair attempts to exchange the money and Larsen for Charlie. Father pulls out a concealed gun and shoots at Charlie but Larsen jumps in front of the bullet and is shot in the back. Clair shoots Father and the other kidnappers, then flees on a snowmobile pursued by the uninjured kidnapper Hobbs whose metal knife stopped the bullet Clair shot at her. Clair crashes her snowmobile and gets into a knife fight with Hobbs but is pushed over the edge of a waterfall and Charlie is captured again. Clair climbs out of the river and is guided into the forest by three wolves. She returns to the lodge, kills the injured kidnapper with a hatchet, and confronts Father, who is inside torturing Larsen with a red hot fire poker while confessing that he killed Larsen's mother after she left him. Charlie returns with Hobbs and Clair throws a knife into her throat. Larsen attacks Father but Father shoots him then turns the gun on Charlie as Clair leaps at Father and pushes him out a window. Clair thanks Larsen before he dies, then she climbs on a snowmobile and exchanges glances with the black wolf as it approaches before she escapes with Charlie. Father rises out of the snow as a pack of wolves descends on him and tears him apart. Three months later, in the spring, Clair and Charlie are hiking a path on the mountain when she sees the black wolf again and smiles.

title: Sweet River: Hana's Search Unveils Dark Truths
description: Hana's search for her son's body leads her to the sleepy town of Billing, where her investigations uncover more than she expected and threaten to expose the town's secrets - secrets that both the living and the dead will fight to protect.

title: See for Me
description: A group of thieves break into the luxurious, secluded mansion Sophie is house-sitting. Sophie, a visually impaired former skier, must rely on Kelly, an army veteran living across the country, to help her fight back.

title: The Bodyguard
description: Ding, a retired bodyguard suffering from dementia, befriends a young girl who has been threatened by a local crime lord. However, Ding uses his skills to save the little girl from danger.

title: Monsters at Large
description: Alex assembles a task force when his brother complains of nightmares filled with monsters. The team is quite successful until they meet a real monster.

title: Survivor
description: A foreign service officer teams up with her colleague in order to prove her innocence while also trying to simultaneously thwart a terrorist attack.

title: Paltan
description: लेफ्टिनेंट कर्नल राज सिंह यादव अपने सैनिकों के समूह के साथ नाथू ला दर्रे को चीनियों से बचाने के लिए निकल पड़ते हैं, जबकि उन्हें अपने प्रियजनों से दूर रहने का दर्द भी सहना पड़ता है।

title: Post Mortem
description: A post mortem photographer and a little girl confront ghosts in a haunted village after the First World War.

title: Tiranga
description: Brigadier Suryadev Singh and Police Inspector Shivajirao Waghle are appointed to bring down Pralayanth, a terrorist who murdered officer Rudrapratap Chauhan and plans to evade India.

title: Hard Hit
description: On his way to work, a bank manager receives an anonymous call claiming there's a bomb under his car seat, and if anyone exits the car, it will explode unless he can pay a ransom.

title: Tod in der Eifel
description: In der Nähe des kleinen Eifeldorfes Eschbach gerät ein Geldtransporter in einen Hinterhalt. Die junge LKA-Hauptkommissarin Lona Schanz ermittelt anschließend im Ort und seiner Umgebung.

title: Yes Boss
description: येस बॉस: राहुल का बॉस सिद्धार्थ एक महिलावादी है जो राहुल को सीमा का दिल जीतने में मदद करने के लिए ब्लैकमेल करता है। लेकिन राहुल को सीमा से प्यार हो जाता है और वह अपने करियर की आकांक्षाओं और अपनी प्रेमिका के बीच फंस जाता है।

title: Behen Hogi Teri
description: बेहेन होगी तेरी: गट्टू बिन्नी से प्यार करता है लेकिन पड़ोस में हर कोई उसे और इलाके की सभी महिलाओं को अपनी बहनों की तरह मानने के लिए मजबूर करता है। वह उससे शादी करना चाहता है और इस पूर्वाग्रह के खिलाफ लड़ने का फैसला करता है।

title: Yamla Pagla Deewana 2
description: यमला पगला दीवाना 2: धरम और गजोधर, पिता-पुत्र की जोड़ी, एक बिजनेस टाइकून को ठगने के लिए एक बड़ी कंपनी के मालिक होने का दावा करते हैं। उनकी परेशानियों को और बढ़ाने के लिए, गजोधर का भाई बैंडबाजे पर कूद पड़ता है।

title: Badhaai Do
description: बधाई दो: शार्दुल, एक समलैंगिक लड़का और सुमन, एक समलैंगिक महिला, अपने परिवारों को खुश करने के लिए पवित्र विवाह में प्रवेश करते हैं। हालाँकि, जब सुमन की प्रेमिका उनके साथ रहने लगती है, तो उनका जीवन और अधिक जटिल हो जाता है।

title: Grand Masti
description: ग्रांड मस्ती: दोस्त अमर, मीत और प्रेम, जो अपने विवाहित जीवन से नाखुश हैं, मौज-मस्ती करने के लिए अपने कॉलेज के पुनर्मिलन में जाने का फैसला करते हैं। हालाँकि, उन्हें प्रिंसिपल और एक छात्र से परेशानी हो जाती है।

title: Extra Safe
description: نهى، 28 عامًا، تذهب إلى الصيدلية لشراء واقي ذكري، وتظهر والدتها فجأة لتقلب الوضع رأسًا على عقب، وتجد نفسها تعاني من سلسلة من الأحداث غير المرغوب فيها.

title: ليل خرجي
description: Leil Khargi : مو وتوتو ومصطفى، ثلاثة مصريين من مختلف مناحي الحياة، يلتقون ببعضهم البعض ويقضون ليلة صاخبة في بطن القاهرة.

title: Fußball ist unser Leben
description: Fußball ist unser Leben is a German football drama/comedy movie, centering on supporters of FC Schalke 04. It was directed by Tomy Wigand, with Uwe Ochsenknecht and Ralf Richter in the main roles.

title: الحارث
description: El-Hareth : يسمع زوجان في شهر العسل حكاية عن ليلة غياب القمر ويبحث الشيطان عن عروس.

title: أوقات فراغ
description: Awqat Faragh : تواجه مجموعة من الشباب عدة مشاكل تتعلق بمعتقداتهم. تأخذ حياتهم منعطفًا جذريًا عندما يحاولون تحقيق أحلامهم.

title: SPY: Una Espía Despistada
description: La analista de la CIA Susan Cooper se transforma en una agente de campo cuando se ofrece como voluntaria para infiltrarse en un negocio de armas y detener una catástrofe global con consecuencias hilarantes.

title: El camino de Santiago
description: Un padre emprende un viaje para recoger los restos de su hijo, fallecido durante una peregrinación. Encuentra nuevos amigos en el camino mientras descubre un nuevo significado en la vida.

title: Huérfanos
description: Zana y Dana son dos hermanos sin hogar que viven su vida al borde de la supervivencia.

title: Juan de los muertos
description: Después de que los muertos se levantan y comienzan a atacar a los vivos, Juan comienza un negocio de matar zombies, hasta que tiene que salvar a su pequeña banda de ser devorados.

title: Blackie & Kanuto
description: Blackie, una oveja negra agitadora, quiere desesperadamente ir a la luna. Kanuto, un perro pastor que la ama, decide acompañarla y juntos viven muchas aventuras en su búsqueda.

title: El callejón de los milagros
description: Los temperamentos acalorados, los deseos frustrados y las esperanzas frustradas plagan a un grupo diverso de personas cuyas vidas se cruzan en la Ciudad de México. Está el hijo del dueño del bar, Chava (Juan Manuel Bernal), que anhela emigrar a América.

title: La piel fría
description: Friend, un meteorólogo, viaja a una isla remota en el Atlántico Sur para trabajar como observador del tiempo. Sin embargo, se encuentra atrapado entre criaturas peligrosas que viven en la isla.

title: Siempre Habana
description: Ignacio (Pepe Sancho) y su sobrino Tomasín (Jordi Vilchez) son dos empresarios gallegos que comparten una herencia familiar con la prima Luz Divina, cubana de nacimiento, pero de ascendencia gallega. La partición de la herencia ante notario se hace en Santiago de Compostela, donde Luz Divina es recibida por sus desconocidos familiares.

title: Tesis sobre un homicidio
description: Roberto Bermúdez, profesor de derecho penal, se obsesiona con el asesinato de una mujer, que cree ha sido cometido por uno de sus brillantes alumnos.

title: Lusers
description: Tres hombres de diferentes zonas de Sudamérica emprenden un viaje salvaje por la jungla para llegar a la Copa Mundial de la FIFA en Brasil.

title: Alemão 2
description: A comunidade do Alemão no Rio de Janeiro é conhecida por seu alto índice de criminalidade. Mais uma vez, uma equipe enfrenta o tráfico de drogas para tentar concretizar as propostas dentro do complexo.

title: Aos Ventos que Virao
description: Zé Olímpio (Rui Ricardo Diaz) é um jovem cangaceiro que, após dizimar o bando de Lampião, precisa fugir para São Paulo. Algum tempo depois, decide voltar ao Nordeste e logo se torna político.

title: Uma Pitada de Sorte
description: Sonhando em ter seu próprio negócio de culinária, sua “sorte” surge quando ela é aprovada para ser assistente de um famoso chef em um programa de televisão.

title: O Candidato Honesto
description: oão Ernesto Ribamar é um político corrupto que concorre à presidência. Ele está no segundo turno, à frente nas pesquisas, quando recebe uma "mandinga" (maldição) da avó, que o impede de mentir. Agora começa o problema: como ganhar uma eleição dizendo apenas a verdade?

title: Causa e Efeito
description: Causa e Efeito é um drama brasileiro de 2014 dirigido por André Marouço e estrelado por Matheus Prestes, Naruna Costa, Luiz Serra, Rosi Campos e Henri Pagnoncelli. A trama do filme, inspirada nos ensinamentos de Allan Kardec, mostra a vida do policial Paulo, que perde a esposa e o filho em um acidente.

title: Confissões de Adolescente
description: Quatro irmãs adolescentes enfrentam os conflitos que antecedem a vida adulta enquanto ajudam o pai, que passa por dificuldades financeiras ao tentar sustentar as filhas.

title: Os Caras de Pau em O Misterioso Roubo do Anel
description: Os desajeitados seguranças Pedrão e Jorginho são contratados para proteger um valioso anel de herança. Mas quando o anel é roubado por um ninja, eles devem encontrá-lo para lutar e provar sua inocência.

title: Copa de Elite
description: Jorge é um capitão destemido e independente do BOPE (Polícia Militar Brasileira) que deve aprender a trabalhar com outras pessoas para salvar o Papa de um ataque na final da Copa do Mundo.

title: Lone Star Deception
description: Stuart Sagle is leading in the race for Governor of Texas, but a fling with a prostitute threatens to derail his campaign

title: Sky Monster
description: When a magnetic force pulls a small plane into the Bermuda triangle, a group of friends find themselves stalked by a beast in the clouds.

title: Election Night
description: Five friends hold an election night party in a politically-divided Britain, with a populist right-wing party and a radical left-wing party battling for the keys to 10 Downing Street.

title: Justice Is Mind
description: Henri is put on trial after a ground-breaking medical device reveals a memory of him shooting two men, but he remembers none of it; with Henri facing a guilty verdict, his wife goes on a mission to clear his name.

title: The Loch Ness Horror
description: A submarine vanishing prompts a rescue operation that comes face-to-face with the Loch Ness Monster. Having escaped the Loch, it is now unleashing decades of pent-up aggression on all those it encounters.

title: Skydog
description: A teenage boy working on achieving his pilot licence teams up with a new friend and a stray dog to rescue his mother, who works as a CIA agent, from a group of criminals.

title: Easter Replacements
description: A fighting married couple organise an Easter Sunday dinner for two other couples, but the invited couples back out of coming and send replacement couples to the dinner.

title: Popovich: Road to Hollywood
description: Popovich is kicked out of a travelling circus and gets stuck in a tiny desert town, where he sets his sights on making it big in Hollywood.

title: Anu
description: When her beloved grandfather passes away, a grieving teenager searches for ways to commune with the afterlife and discovers what truly connects them.

title: Les héritières
description: C'est la rentrée pour Sanou, 15 ans, au prestigieux lycée Henri-IV de Paris. L'adolescente de Seine-Saint-Denis a obtenu une place à l'école grâce à un programme d'égalité des chances, mais malgré tous ses efforts, elle peine à s'intégrer. En échange d'une bourse, elle encadre Khady, une élève de 10e.

title: Joyeuse retraite! 2
description: Marilou et Philippe déménagent au Portugal pour profiter de leur retraite, mais découvrent vite que la maison n'est pas terminée et que le promoteur immobilier est parti. Ils perdent alors leurs petits-enfants et n’ont que 24 heures pour les retrouver avant l’arrivée de leur fille.

title: Drôle de prof
description: Un élève-enseignant inexpérimenté inspire ses élèves avec ses méthodes non conventionnelles.

title: Treize a la Douzaine 2
description: Tom Baker, entraîneur à la retraite, emmène sa famille en vacances pour se détendre et passer du temps avec ses enfants, qui grandissent. Cependant, ils se retrouvent bientôt entraînés dans une bataille contre son ancien rival.

title: La traversée
description: Après que leur village ait été ravagé, deux frères et sœurs sont arrachés à leurs parents et poussés sur le chemin de l'exil. Ils se lancent dans une quête de refuge alors qu'ils parcourent une terre ravagée par la guerre à la recherche de sécurité.

title: Ice Storm
description: When a devastating blizzard freezes over the entirety of North Carolina, climatologists and disaster relief experts rush to save the inhabitants and halt the storm before it sends the entire East Coast to an icy doom.

title: Le Fiancé idéal
description: Français Tommy Fielding est une jeune star montante de Wall Street qui a tout pour lui : le charme, des amis et le début d'une histoire d'amour qui pourrait être très sérieuse. Mais, un jeune collègue qu'il prend sous son aile pourrait le mener à sa chute.

title: The Space Between the Lines
description: Aufgrund eines Tippfehlers schickt Emma versehentlich eine E-Mail an einen Fremden namens Leo Leike. Die Anonymität bringt sie näher zusammen und es entwickelt sich eine innige Freundschaft zwischen den beiden, obwohl sie sich nicht treffen.

title: Sixty Minutes
description: In der Verzweiflung, das Sorgerecht nicht zu verlieren, macht sich ein Mixed-Martial-Arts-Kämpfer gefährliche Feinde, als er ein Match abbricht, um zur Geburtstagsfeier seiner Tochter zu rennen.

title: Kriegerin
description: Svenja ist ein 14-jähriges Mädchen, das von der deutschen Kämpferin Marisa, einer Anführerin einer gewalttätigen Gruppe, als ihre Schützlingin ausgewählt wird. Doch Svenjas Leben verändert sich, als sie einen jungen afghanischen Flüchtling trifft.

title: Zila Ghaziabad
description: जिला गाज़ियाबाद : गैंगस्टर फौजी और सतबीर के बीच प्रतिद्वंद्विता बढ़ने के साथ गाजियाबाद जिले में एक पूर्ण गिरोह युद्ध शुरू हो गया है। एक भ्रष्ट पुलिसकर्मी, प्रीतम सिंह, को चीजों को ठीक करने के लिए भेजा जाता है।

title: Jajantaram Mamantaram
description: जजन्तरम् ममन्तरम्: जहाज डूबने के बाद आदित्य एक द्वीप पर जाने का रास्ता ढूंढता है। यहां, उसे एहसास होता है कि वह अन्य निवासियों के बीच एक विशालकाय व्यक्ति है, जो उसे एक राक्षस से अपना रक्षक मानते हैं।

title: Kahani Rubberband Ki
description: कहानी रबरबैंड की: आकाश और काव्या, एक नवविवाहित जोड़ा, तब हैरान रह जाते हैं जब वे सुरक्षा का उपयोग करने के बावजूद गर्भवती हो जाते हैं। इसलिए, आकाश गर्भनिरोधक के निर्माता पर मुकदमा करने के लिए तैयार हो जाता है।

title: Mr Joe B. Carvalho
description: एक व्यवसायी ने एक निजी जासूस को अपनी बेटी को ढूंढने का काम सौंपा है। हालाँकि, जाँच करते समय, वह अपनी पूर्व प्रेमिका, एक पुलिसकर्मी, जो एक अंतरराष्ट्रीय अपराधी का पीछा कर रही है, से जुड़ जाता है।

title: Ek Se Bure Do
description: एक से बुरे दो: जगत, एक गैंगस्टर, खजाने का नक्शा चुराने के लिए टोटी और टोनी को काम पर रखता है। लेकिन वे उसे नक्शे की नकली प्रतिलिपि प्रदान करते हैं और मूल को सुरक्षित रखते हैं। जब जगत को इसके बारे में पता चला, तो उसने उन्हें सबक सिखाने की योजना बनाई।

title: নায়ক
description: Nayak : নায়ক হৈছে ২০০১ চনত মুনীন বৰুৱাৰ পৰিচালিত আৰু পূজা মোচন পিকচাৰ্ছৰ বেনাৰত নিৰ্মিত ভাৰতীয় অসমীয়া ৰোমান্টিক নাট্য চিনেমা। সংগীত ৰচনা কৰিছিল জুবিন গাৰ্গে। ২০০১ চনৰ ৩০ নৱেম্বৰত মুক্তি লাভ কৰে ছবিখন।

title: বন্ধোই
description: Bandhoi: পৰিচালক ৰাজেশ ভূঞা। নিপ্পন গোস্বামী, অৰুণ হাজৰিকা, গায়ত্ৰী মহন্তৰ সৈতে।

title: জনমনি
description: Jaanmoni: অনাথ সন্তান জান এটা ধনী পৰিয়ালৰ মণিৰ প্ৰতি পৰে। দুয়োৰে সম্পৰ্কৰ মুকলি বিৰোধিতা হ’লে সামাজিক ভিত্তিত প্ৰত্যাহ্বানৰ সন্মুখীন হ’বলগীয়া হয় দুয়োৰে।

title: আবুজন মন
description: "Abujon Mon: ষ্টাৰকাষ্ট : ভাৰ্গব, সুনীতা দেৱী  পৰিচালক: ৰাজেশ ভূঞা গল্প, চিত্ৰনাট্য, সংলাপ : মুনীন বৰুৱা সহকাৰী সঞ্চালকঃ মনুজ শইকীয়া সম্পাদক: গগন ৰাজ প্ৰযোজক : দেবো বৰকটকি পটভূমি সংগীত : অনুৰাগ শইকীয়া"

title: জুণ্ডা ইমান গুণ্ডা
description: Junda Eman Gunda: বিভিন্ন জগতৰ পৰা অহা দুজন মেৰু বিপৰীত ব্যক্তি ইজনে সিজনৰ সন্মুখীন হয়। তদুপৰি চিন্তা আৰু মতামতত সংঘৰ্ষ হয় তথাপিও প্ৰেমত পৰে।

title: Hamare Baarah
description: हमारे बारह: एक महिला अपने पिता को अदालत में ले जाती है ताकि उसकी माँ, जो एक जोखिम भरी गर्भावस्था के बीच में है, को उसकी जान बचाने के लिए गर्भावस्था को समाप्त करने का अधिकार मिल सके।

title: ജനനം 1947 പ്രണയം തുടങ്ങുന്നു
description: Jananam 1947 Pranayam Thudarunnu: വൃദ്ധസദനത്തിൽ ഒറ്റപ്പെട്ട വൃദ്ധയായ ഗൗരി കെയർ ടേക്കർ ശിവനൊപ്പം പോകാൻ തീരുമാനിച്ചു, അതിനുശേഷം അവരുടെ ജീവിതം അനന്തമായ പ്രണയയാത്രയായി മാറുന്നു.

title: Ruslaan
description: रुस्लान: रुस्लान एक भारतीय हिंदी भाषा की एक्शन फिल्म है, जो करण ललित बुटानी द्वारा निर्देशित और के.के. राधामोहन द्वारा निर्मित है। इसमें सुश्री श्रेया मिश्रा, जगपति बाबू और विद्या मालवडे के साथ आयुष शर्मा मुख्य भूमिका में हैं। यह फिल्म 26 अप्रैल 2024 को रिलीज हुई थी और इसने बॉक्स ऑफिस पर धमाल मचा दिया था

title: ரத்னம்
description: Rathnam: ஒரு பெண் நேர்காணலுக்காக வேலூருக்குத் தனியாகச் செல்லும்போது, ​​ஒரு குண்டர் கும்பல் அவளுக்குத் தீங்கு செய்ய முயல்கிறது; ரத்னம் அவளை காப்பாற்றுகிறார், ஆனால் அவளை தொடர்ந்து பாதுகாக்க வேண்டும்.

title: ది ఫ్యామిలీ స్టార్
description: The Family Star: హైదరాబాద్‌కు చెందిన గోవర్ధన్, అంకితభావంతో కూడిన వాస్తుశిల్పి, తన కట్టుబాట్లను అర్థం చేసుకునే భాగస్వామిని వెతుకుతున్నప్పుడు తన పెద్ద కుటుంబానికి మద్దతుగా గారడీ చేస్తాడు. అతను తన కుటుంబంపై ఆది యొక్క థీసిస్‌ను కనుగొన్నప్పుడు, అతను ఆమెను సవాలు చేస్తాడు, ఇది ఊహించని మలుపులకు దారి తీస్తుంది.

title: Teri Baaton Mein Aisa Uljha Jiya
description: तेरी बातों में ऐसा उलझा जिया: Aryan cannot find his ideal partner. He meets Sifra on a trip to the USA and falls in love with her, only to discover later that it is an impossible love affair.

title: Lal Salaam
description: ஆர்வமுள்ள கிரிக்கெட் வீரர்கள் திறமை இருந்தும் அணியில் இருந்து அநியாயமாக வெளியேற்றப்படுகிறார்கள். அவர்கள் தங்கள் கனவுகளை அடைய இந்த பின்னடைவை சமாளித்து கடக்க வேண்டும்.

title: o protetor 2
description: Criminosos assassinam Susan Plummer, a melhor amiga de Robert McCall e sua ex-colega de trabalho. Obcecado, Robert pensa apenas em eliminar o bando de assassinos profissionais que destruiu sua vida.

title: Ocho apellidos marroquís
description: Un asunto marroquí es una película de comedia romántica española de 2023 dirigida por Álvaro Fernández Armero a partir de un guión de Daniel Castro y protagonizada por Julián López, Michelle Jenner, Elena Irureta y María Ramos.

title: Cruzando el río Yalu
description: En medio de las tropas chinas que cruzan hacia Corea del Norte en 1950, el comandante de una compañía se enfrenta a un heroico piloto de combate mientras luchaban unidos contra las fuerzas estadounidenses a lo largo del río Yalu.

title: Perdona Si Te Llamo Amor
description: Alex, un brillante ejecutivo de publicidad de 37 años, decide proponerle matrimonio a su novia. Sin embargo, cuando ella rechaza su propuesta, Niki, una estudiante de 17 años, entra en su vida y le da un giro.

title: Mr. Kaplan
description: Durante la Segunda Guerra Mundial, Jacob Kaplan abandona Europa y huye a Uruguay para llevar una vida tranquila. Unos años más tarde, cuestiona su existencia y se encuentra con un nazi que vive escondido.

title: El elefante desaparecido
description: Edo sigue obsesionado con lo que le pasó a su prometida Celia después de que ella desapareció durante un terremoto. Cuando una enigmática mujer le muestra fotografías que pueden ayudarlo a resolver el misterio, siente que lo están arrastrando a un juego peligroso.

title: Rec 4: Apocalypse
description: Ángela, una reportera, es salvada de un edificio y llevada a un área en cuarentena para ser examinada. Ella se despierta y no recuerda nada. Sin embargo, hay un virus demoníaco desconocido suelto.

title: Torrente 5: Operación Eurovegas
description: Torrente, un ex policía, regresa de la cárcel después de unos años, sólo para descubrir que el mundo exterior ha cambiado. Al no poder hacer frente a la presión de los cambios que lo rodean, decide convertirse en un forajido.

title: Torrente 3: El protector
description: José Luis Torrente, un detective español, vive un viaje de aventuras cuando decide convertirse en guardaespaldas.

title: Don De Dios
description: Dos jóvenes que solían ser mejores amigos están cegados por la codicia. Tienen la intención de destruirse unos a otros para conseguir lo que quieren.

title: Comboio de Sal e Açúcar
description: No meio da guerra civil, um comboio que transporta passageiros, soldados e mercadorias em Moçambique deve ser protegido ao atravessar o território controlado pela guerrilha, onde os rebeldes criam o caos.

title: O Gotejar da Luz
description: Um homem de meia-idade (Luís Sarmento) relembra a sua vida aos 14 anos (Filipe Carvalho) em Moçambique.

title: O Trapalhão E A Luz Azul
description: David, um cantor de rock, e Didi, sua assistente, são transportados para um mundo distante. Eles devem ajudar a princesa Allim a enfrentar o malvado Vizir, que quer se tornar rei casando-se com ela.

title: Tá Todo Mundo Louco!
description: Donald Sinclair, um magnata dos cassinos, coloca seis moedas de ouro em seu cassino. Seis competidores que estão trancados em um armário devem encontrar um caminho e competir entre si para ganhar dois milhões de dólares.

title: Rasganço
description: Um estuprador em série obcecado por filosofia persegue um campus universitário em plena luz do dia.

title: Eu Só Posso Imaginar
description: Arthur conserta seu relacionamento com seu filho, Bart Millard, depois de abusar dele fisicamente na infância. Como resultado de sua reconciliação, anos depois, Bart escreve um hit.

title: In Vanda's Room
description: Irmãs num bairro de lata de Lisboa chamado Fontainhas passam o tempo fumando heroína e conversando enquanto escavadoras destroem o seu bairro.

title: Palavra e Utopia
description: O padre jesuíta António Vieira usa sermões emocionantes para lutar pelos direitos humanos no século XVII.

title: O Que é Isso, Companheiro?
description: Baseado em uma história real, "Quatro Dias em Setembro" é um comovente relato do sequestro, em setembro de 1969, do Embaixador Americano no Brasil, interpretado por Alan Arkin. O drama desenrola-se à medida que um grupo de jovens idealistas, muitas vezes ingénuos, se junta para planear e executar um acto de terrorismo, o seu único meio de dar voz aos seus sonhos e visões progressistas num regime militar.

title: A Carta
description: Um popular cantor português (Pedro Abrunhosa) se apaixona por uma mulher (Chiara Mastroianni) casada com um médico de meia-idade (Antoine Chappey).

title: The Wrong House
description: After breaking into a remote house in the woods, five friends learn too late there are some people you just shouldn't mess with... and that they picked THE WRONG HOUSE.

title: Frank vs. God
description: David Frank, a former hotshot lawyer's life takes an ugly turn when a tornado destroys his house. He, however, does not give up hope and decides to file a lawsuit against God.

title: Siren
description: Leigh has lived a reclusive existence in a secluded old home on the outskirts of town for her entire adult life. You see, Leigh has excreted extremely potent pheromones.

title: Devil's Five
description: An anthology of four macabre horrors connected by a wraparound nail-biting mystery.

title: The Bride in the Box
description: Iris, the young daughter of Don and Heather, is returning to Maine with them for a much-needed vacation. They move into a rental house with an old trunk down the hall, and while Don and Heather aren't paying attention to Iris, something else does.

title: HACKERS Ningún Sistema Es Seguro
description: Benjamin (TOM SCHILLING) es un ser invisible. Esto cambiara repentinamente, cuando conozca al carismático Max (ELYAS M ' BAREK). Aunque ambos no pueden parecer más diferentes, los une el mismo interés: el hacking. Junto con los otros amigos de Max, el impulsivo Stephen (WOTAN WILKE MÖHRING) y el paranoico Paul (ANTOINE MONOT) establecen el subversivo grupo de hackers CLAY (Clown Laughing At You-Payasos Riendose de Ti). CLAY provoca golpes a grandes complejos corporativos e importantes conglomerados de empresas. Por primera vez en su vida, Benjamin se siente parte de algo y ni siquiera la atractiva Marie (HANNAH HERZSPRUNG) puede evitar sentirse atraida por él. Pero la diversión comenzara a tornarse en angustia, cuando una agente de Europol Hanne Lindberg (TRINE DYRHOLM) comience a considerar a Benjamin como uno de los hackers más buscados en el mundo.

title: Dumbo (1941)
description: Dumbo é um bebê elefante de um circo que nasceu com orelhas enormes. Após ser ridicularizado por seu grupo de amigos, ele se transforma na principal atração de seu circo quando descobre que, usando suas orelhas, é capaz de fazer o que nenhum outro elefante consegue: voar.

title: 13 Thirteen
description: STARRING, RABBANI SOYAM, BOIBHABI GOSWAMI, STORY & DIRECTION, RABBANI SOYAM, DOP / EDITING / COLOUR GRADDING, AMAL ROY, DIALOGUE, DHRITIMOY KALITA, RABBANI SOYAM, Film Music

title: Raghupati
description: Shri Raghupati Assamese movie

title: Upgraded
description: An aspiring art intern is invited on a last-minute work trip to London, where she meets a handsome stranger.

title: Call Me King
description: Two heavily armed brothers immigrate to the USA to correct the wrongdoings of their father. However, a dramatic turn of events changes their life forever.

title: The Mummy Resurrection
description: When an infamous "cursed" Egyptian sarcophagus falls into the hands of unscrupulous huckster Everett Randolph, he becomes obsessed with resurrecting the mummified princess held within it.

title: Snakehead Swamp
description: A group of teenagers set out to party in the middle of a swamp in a fishing trawler. Soon they fall prey to a swarm of deadly snakehead fish that have grown to gigantic proportions due to pollutants.

title: Premium Rush
description: Wilee is a bicycle messenger who rides a single-gear bike with no brakes. His routine delivery turns into a dangerous chase when his last package of the day is pursued by corrupt police officers.

title: The Water Horse
description: Young Angus MacMorrow discovers a mysterious egg that grows up to be the Loch Ness monster. As they form a strong relationship, the boy's family refuses to believe in the creature's existence.

title: Scoop
description: An insider account of how the women of "Newsnight" secured Prince Andrew's infamous 2019 interview about his friendship with convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein.

title: Trisha On The Rocks
description: त्रिशा ऑन द रॉक्स 2024 की गुजराती और हिंदी रोमांटिक कॉमेडी ड्रामा फिल्म है, जिसका निर्देशन और लेखन कृष्णदेव याग्निक ने किया है। इसमें जानकी बोदीवाला, रवि गोहिल और हितेन कुमार हैं। फिल्म का निर्माण कल्पेश के सोनी और क्रुणाल सोनी ने किया है और इसे पैनोरमा स्टूडियो द्वारा वितरित किया गया है।

title: 4N6
description: एक प्रतिष्ठित पुलिस अधिकारी से लगातार उत्पीड़न सहते हुए, नायशा और उसके सहयोगी मामलों को सुलझाने के लिए टीम बनाते हैं।

title: IF
description: After discovering she can see everyone's imaginary friends, a girl embarks on a magical adventure to reconnect forgotten IFs with their kids.

title: Dune Part Two
description: Paul Atreides unites with Chani and the Fremen while seeking revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the universe, he must prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.

title: Imaginary
description: When Jessica moves back into her childhood home with her family, her youngest stepdaughter, Alice, finds a stuffed bear named Chauncey. As Alice's behavior becomes more and more concerning, Jessica intervenes only to realize that Chauncey is much more than the stuffed toy bear she believed him to be.

title: No Way Up
description: Trapped underwater when their plane crashes into the ocean, survivors must find a way to escape as sharks start to circle the wreckage.

title: Devils
description: 수년 전 자신의 파트너를 살해한 연쇄살인범을 형사가 추적하면서 둘은 사고를 당하게 된다. 병원에서 깨어난 형사는 자신이 살인자와 몸이 바뀌었다는 사실을 깨닫는다.

title: A Writer's Odyssey
description: 管宁必须杀死作家卢孔文才能解救被绑架的女儿。他殊不知，卢孔文的最新小说走进了生活，影响了现实。

title: Anatomy of a Fall
description: Une femme est soupçonnée du meurtre de son mari et leur fils aveugle est confronté à un dilemme moral en tant que seul témoin.

title: The Boys in the Boat
description: During the height of the Great Depression, members of the rowing team at the University of Washington get thrust into the spotlight as they compete for gold at the 1936 Olympics in Berlin.

title: The Heartbreak Agency
description: When a skeptical journalist reluctantly enters heartbreak therapy for an article, he ends up opening his heart to his charming therapist.

title: Kill Me If You Dare
description: A winning lottery ticket has grave consequences for a married couple when they start hatching plans to kill each other for the prize money.

title: Final Summer
description: In the aftermath of a summer camp tragedy, camp counsellors find themselves fighting for their lives against a masked killer.

title: Five Blind Dates
description: Lia, a tea shop owner, is gifted a prophecy that says she will meet her soul mate in five dates and he will help her save her grandmother's tea shop.

title: Robert And The Toymaker
description: The Nazis set their eyes on a toymaker's mystical book, which can breathe life into inanimate objects. However, when they steal it from him, he gives life to his dolls to exact revenge against them.

title: ৰক্তবীজ
description: Raktabeez... ৰবিয়ে বছৰাক লগ পায় আৰু তাইৰ প্ৰেমত পৰে। কিন্তু তেওঁৰ জীৱনটো হঠাৎ অপৰাধ আৰু হিংসাৰ অন্ধকাৰ জগতখনৰ লগত জড়িত হৈ পৰে

title: ঘৰ সংসাৰ
description: Ghar Sansar... "তাৰকা অভিনেতা : যতীন বৰ, গীতাৱলী ৰাজকুমাৰী, সৌৰভ হাজৰিকা পৰিচালক: ৰাজেশ ভূঞা"

title: ৰত্নাকৰ
description: Ratnakar... জয়ন্ত আৰু তেওঁৰ কন্যা দুবড়ীয়ে শান্তিপূৰ্ণ জীৱন কটায় যেতিয়া তেওঁৰ অতীতৰ এজন ব্যক্তিয়ে তেওঁক অপহৰণ কৰে। পিছলৈ সি তাইক বিপদৰ পৰা বচাবলৈ এসময়ত যিজন মানুহ আছিল, সেইজন হৈ পৰে।

title: প্ৰেম কিছিম কিছিম
description: Prem Kisim Kisim... ষ্টাৰকাষ্ট : অৰুণ হাজৰিকা, গায়ত্ৰী মহন্ত, শ্যামন্টিকা শৰ্মা, চেতনা দাস, জ্যোতি ভূঞা, পবিত্ৰ বৰুৱা পৰিচালক : ৰাজেশ ভূঞা

title: কোঁৱৰপুৰাৰ কোঁৱৰ
description: Konwarpurar Konwar... ৰাজেশ ভূঞাই পৰিচালনা কৰা এই ছবিখনত নয়ন নিলিমৰ উপৰিও অভিষেক ঘটোৱা তাপসী, অমৃতা গগৈ, হিৰণ্য ডেকা, সৌৰভ হাজৰিকা, জুয়ান দত্ত, ৰিনা বৰা, সিদ্ধাৰ্থ শৰ্মা আদিয়ে অভিনয় কৰিব।

title: ৰাফ এণ্ড টাফ
description: Ruff & Tuff... নিৰ্দেশক। মণি সিনহা; লেখক। মণি সিনহা; তাৰকা। গুঞ্জন ভৰদ্বাজ · গাৰ্গ্য খৃষ্টি

title: দিছপুৰোট গাভৰু
description: Dispurot Gabhoru... দিছপুৰত গাভৰু হৈছে এখন অসমীয়া চিনেমা, য'ত পৰী প্ৰিয়া আহমেদ, জেফ্ৰি বাক্ষী, হিৰণ্য দাস, জোনালী দেৱী, ৰিমজিম শৰ্মা, আৰু সাজু আহমেদে বিশিষ্ট চৰিত্ৰত অভিনয় কৰিছে। ইয়াৰ পৰিচালনা কৰিছে এ.এম. ৰহমান।

title: ৰানংগন
description: Ranangan... অভয়ে, এজন যুৱকে সদায় অন্যায়ৰ বিৰুদ্ধে মাত মাতিছে। যেতিয়া তেওঁ এগৰাকী ছোৱালীৰ সন্মুখীন হয়, যিয়ে তাইৰ কুটিল ককাকৰ পৰিকল্পনাত মাক-দেউতাকক হেৰুৱাইছিল, তেতিয়া তেওঁ তাইক সহায় কৰাৰ সিদ্ধান্ত লয়।

title: Tô Ryca 2
description: Selminha is back. Now she is Ryca (Rich), paying top dollar for everything she needs and wants. The problem is that a poor person's happiness is brief. A namesake heir appears claiming that she is the legitimate inheritor. Selminha's assets are frozen and her only source of income is what the courts have stipulated until they resolve the case: a minimum wage salary of R$30 per day. However, Selminha has already forgotten how to live the hardship, bankruptcy and disgrace of poverty. And worst, she is the patron of the Quintino community, and with her financial difficulties the community also feels the squeeze. Selminha is a warrior, fighter, and a Brazilian that never gives up, who rises up not only to fix her life but that of all those she loves.

title: Masha e o Urso
description: Um urso de circo reformado decide viver uma vida tranquila na floresta. No entanto, quando Masha, uma jovem alegre, entra na floresta, a sua vida tranquila é interrompida.

title: Nueva York Bajo el Terror de los Zombies
description: ZOMBIES 2, A Nueva York llega un barco sin rumbo, cuando llega la policía descubren que en el interior del barco se alberga un zombie. A partir de ese momento la hija del dueño del barco, con la ayuda de un periodista, buscará a su padre que se encuentra en una isla plagada de zombies sedientos de carne

title: La Máscara
description: Stanley Ipkiss es un empleado de banca extremadamente amable, pero desgraciadamente es un pusilánime cuando tiene que enfrentarse a alguien. Tras uno de los peores días de su vida, Stanley encuentra una máscara que representa a Loki, un dios de la malicia y la travesura. Cuando se coloca la máscara se convierte en una persona completamente diferente.

title: Ya Veremos
description: Un niño hace una lista de lugares para visitar y cosas para ver después de enterarse de que podría perder la vista. Para cumplir sus sueños, sus padres separados acuerdan unirse y llevar a su hijo a un aventurero y alocado viaje de descubrimiento.

title: A Kid Like Jake
description: When Jake, a four-year-old boy, displays gender-nonconforming behaviour, a rift between his parents starts to form as they try hard to process things.

title: Romeo and Juliet
description: The rivalry between Verona's two well-established families, the Capulets and the Montagues, affects the relationship of their children Romeo and Juliet.

title: Senior Project
description: SENIOR PROJECT is an indie comedy written by Jeremy Lin, who was sixteen years old when he wrote the script. It is based on his school experiences, and is about five teenagers who cram a year-long senior project into one last crazy weekend.

title: Where is My Home
description: Wenya's parents separated when she was two, and after that she lived with her father and stepmother. Her stepmother couldn't stand her and was always arguing with her father. He had little choice—he had to send Wenya to her mother's house, but her mother was fully focused on running her business and didn't have any time to take care of Wenya, so she was often shuttled off to her relatives' and friends' homes to be fostered. After so many years of a life of foster care, young Wenya felt lonely and helpless, and longed for the warmth of a home. Only when her father and stepmother divorced did she return to her father's side, and from then on had a home, for better or for worse.

title: The Dutchman
description: In the 19th century, adventurers, treasure hunters, and soldiers risked their lives searching for a legendary gold mine hidden in the hostile Superstition Mountains of southern Arizona. Guarding the mythical mine are the fierce and bloodthirsty Apache. Among those seeking fortune is Clare Peralta, a descendant of the mine's original discoverers, armed with the infamous map.

title: Nosso Lar
description: No filme 'Nosso Lar', baseado na obra psicografada por Chico Xavier, acompanhamos a jornada espiritual de André Luiz após sua morte. Ele acorda em uma cidade espiritual chamada Nosso Lar, onde descobre a vida após a morte e aprende lições valiosas sobre amor, perdão e evolução espiritual. Enquanto se ajusta a essa nova realidade, André Luiz enfrenta desafios e encontra mentores que o ajudam em sua jornada de autoconhecimento e redenção. Uma história emocionante que nos faz refletir sobre o sentido da vida e o destino da alma.

title: Un Gran Dinosaurio
description: "Un Gran Dinosaurio" es una película de animación. La película está ambientada en un mundo donde el asteroide que causó la extinción de los dinosaurios nunca impactó la Tierra, lo que permitió a los dinosaurios prosperar y evolucionar hacia la era moderna.

title: Lucicreide Vai pra Marte
description: A casa de Lucidreide vira um inferno após a chegada da sogra, que, despejada, decide morar lá. Abandonada pelo marido Dermirréi e sem condições de conduzir a casa diante dos cinco filhos, ela só tem vontade de ir embora. Sem entender o tamanho de uma viagem espacial, Lucidreide aceita participar de uma missão que levará o primeiro homem ao Planeta Vermelho e é assinada pelo filho de seus chefes, Tavinho.

title: Capitães da Areia
description: Uma gangue de crianças abandonadas vive aventuras em Salvador, na Bahia, na década de 1950.

title: Mãos talentosas
description: Dr. Ben Carson, um neurocirurgião criado por mãe solteira e que enfrentou muitas dificuldades na infância, enfrenta o desafio de operar dois gêmeos siameses ligados pelo crânio.

title: Bairro
description: A polícia tenta deter um bando de criminosos responsáveis ​​por vários assaltos em Lisboa.

title: 7 Pecados Rurais
description: Quim, Zé e os seus dois primos encontram-se subitamente no céu durante uma viagem a Lisboa. Eles então encontram Deus, que lhes oferece uma segunda chance somente se resistirem aos sete pecados capitais.

title: Virgem Margarida
description: Virgem Margarida é um filme de drama português de 2012 dirigido pelo realizador moçambicano Licínio Azevedo e co-produzido por Jacques Bidou, Pandora da Cunha Telles, Marianne Dumoulin, Pablo Iraola e Pedro Pimenta. O filme é estrelado por Sumeia Maculuva com Hermelinda Cimela, Iva Mugalela e Rosa Mario em papéis coadjuvantes.

title: Besos de Azúcar
description: Nacho, un chico de 13 años, intenta encontrar su lugar en la vida en los lugares equivocados.

title: Sweet Home
description: Alicia, una joven agente inmobiliaria, planea una noche de fiesta con su novio Simón, en un edificio antiguo. Sin embargo, su velada se ve amenazada cuando un grupo de asesinos viene a atacarlos.

title: Rey Gitano
description: Gipsy King es una road movie de comedia española de 2015 escrita y dirigida por Juanma Bajo Ulloa. El reparto está formado por Manuel Manquina, Carra Elejalde, Arthur Valls, María León, Rosa María Sardá, Charo López, Pilar Bardem y Albert Pla.

title: Sólo química
description: Cuando se enamora de su ídolo televisivo, una joven inicia un viaje de romance, lujo, fama, éxito y dinero. Cree haber encontrado un final de cuento de hadas, hasta que descubre que la buena química y el amor verdadero no son lo mismo.

title: Los exiliados románticos
description: Tres amigos españoles viajan a París para encontrar uniones románticas.

title: Regresión
description: Cuando una adolescente cae presa de un ritual satánico, un detective y un psicoanalista se unen para descubrir pruebas y exponer la secta.

title: Texas Twister
description: A small town worker believes he's seeing visions from God in the form of a violent tornado.

title: The Detonator
description: Sonni Griffith, a US secret agent, is tasked with shielding Nadia, the widow of an accountant of the Romanian mafia. But quislings and double agents within the CIA place obstacles in his path.

title: The Gods 2
description: Following the gods, Mikey James comes back from hiding to pay old debts, only to be fighting for survival against his old enemy Anthony Fasano, who is awaiting his return.

title: Goal!
description: Santiago dreams of playing professional soccer but his father wants him to support the family and earn his livelihood. Santiago must make a choice between the needs of his family and his passion.

title: Immanence
description: Radio astronomers discover a mysterious signal in the deep sea that could be contact with extraterrestrials. After several terrifying manifestations threaten their beliefs, the team must fight to survive the ultimate evil.

title: The Attic Door
description: Left alone on the family farm in the Old West, a young brother and sister struggle to survive -- until something in the attic awakens.

title: FIGHTS BREAK SPHERE
description: 蕭炎是個天才兒童，突然失去了所有的力量。在強權統治的世界裡，蕭炎的天賦不足，是他家族的恥辱。

title: I CAN DO BAD ALL BY MYSELF - TYLER PERRY
description: When Madea, Americas favorite pistol-packing grandma, catches sixteen-year-old Jennifer and her two younger brothers looting her home, she decides to take matters into her own hands and delivers the young delinquents to the only relative they have: their aunt April. A heavy-drinking nightclub singer who lives off of Raymond, her married boyfriend, April wants nothing to do with the kids. But her attitude begins to change when Sandino, a handsome Mexican immigrant looking for work, moves into Aprils basement room. Making amends for his own troubled past, Sandino challenges April to open her heart. And April soon realizes she must make the biggest choice of her life: between her old ways with Raymond and the new possibilities of family, faithand even true love. Coming to theaters September 11th, 2009!

title: Monsieur Batignole
description: Le futur gendre d'Edmond Batignole arrête une famille juive dont le plus jeune fils parvient à s'enfuir et est ensuite rejoint par ses cousins. Batignole les plaint et décide de les faire passer clandestinement en Suisse.

title: Quelque Chose A Change
description: Le conseil d'administration a mis Louis-Régis, PDG d'une grande entreprise, dans une situation difficile. Son chauffeur l'emmène à la campagne pour changer lorsqu'il croise son ex-femme dans une auberge.

title: Paris, Je T'aime
description: Un film d'anthologie qui dépeint le concept de l'amour dans le quartier de Paris, où les gens vivent l'amour, le chagrin et le désespoir.

title: 1000 Mexikaner
description: Lukas und Adam sind beste Freunde und Mitbewohner im Hamburger Rotlichtviertel; Luke, klug und kreativ, ist auf dem besten Weg, in einer Werbeagentur Karriere zu machen; Adam, ein charmanter Hitzkopf, versucht vergeblich, die Filmindustrie in den Griff zu bekommen.

title: Happy Few
description: Afin de s'amuser, deux couples échangent leurs partenaires. Au début, tout fonctionne bien, mais peu à peu, leur relation se détériore.

title: Edelweisspiraten
description: Eine Gruppe junger deutscher Arbeiter, die sich Edelweißpiraten nennen, plant Sabotageakte gegen das Nazi-Regime im Deutschland des Zweiten Weltkriegs. Während die Gestapo die Gruppe verfolgt, müssen sie sich zwischen Loyalität und Überleben entscheiden.

title: Kästner und der kleine Dienstag
description: Der Schriftsteller Erich Kästner findet Inspiration, als er sich mit seinem siebenjährigen Fan Hans anfreundet, doch angesichts des Aufstiegs des Nationalsozialismus muss er den Kontakt zu dem Jungen abbrechen. Als sich die beiden jedoch Jahre später wiedersehen, wird ihre Freundschaft auf eine harte Probe gestellt.

title: Fritz Lang
description: Fritz Lang wuchs mit einem misshandelnden Vater auf und diente im Ersten Weltkrieg. Er nutzt seine gewalttätige Vergangenheit als Inspirationsquelle für die Regie von „M“, einem Tonfilm über einen Serienmörder.

title: Pataakha
description: पटाखा: बड़की और छुटकी दो बहनें हैं जो हमेशा एक दूसरे से झगड़ती रहती हैं। हालाँकि, जब वे शादी करते हैं, तो वे एक-दूसरे के महत्व को समझते हैं और एक मजबूत बंधन बनाते हैं।

title: MISSION 118
description: Kalyan Ram, Nivetha Thomas, Shalini Pandey, Nassar, Gagan Vihari

title: ماكس وعنتر
description: Max w Antar... بناء على المراجعة. ماكس (إيلي متري)، رجل لبناني ثري يعمل في الولايات المتحدة الأمريكية وحقق إنجازات كبيرة في سوق الأوراق المالية في وول ستريت، وجد نفسه مفلسًا ومتشردًا مع كلبه المدلل (عنتر). لقد عاد الآن إلى بيروت بعد أن أصبح فقيراً وعاطلاً عن العمل.

title: يوم إيه يوم لا
description: Yom Eh Yom La2... مع اقتراب يوم زفافها، يتزايد خوف سحر من الزواج بسبب ارتفاع معدلات الطلاق التي تشهدها. وللهروب من هذه النهاية المدمرة، تتفق مع خطيبها المحافظ شفيق على التناوب بين الزواج وفك رباطهما.

title: Kalki 2898 AD
description: कहा जाता है कि हिंदू भगवान विष्णु का एक आधुनिक अवतार दुनिया को बुरी ताकतों से बचाने के लिए पृथ्वी पर अवतरित हुआ था।

title: Ishq Vishk Rebound
description: इश्क विश्क रिबाउंड: यह चार युवाओं के जीवन पर आधारित है जो दोस्ती, प्यार और आत्म-खोज के जाल में फंस जाते हैं।

title: Chandu Champion
description: चंदू चैंपियन: यह फिल्म एक ऐसे एथलीट की असाधारण कहानी पर आधारित है जिसने कभी हार नहीं मानी।

title: Unwoman
description: अनवूमन एक हिंदी भाषा की ड्रामा फिल्म है, जो हैशटैग फिल्म्स एलएलपी के बैनर तले गुंजन गोयल द्वारा निर्मित है। फिल्म को प्रेम, सामाजिक मुद्दे, LGBTQ+ और नाटक की शैली के अंतर्गत वर्गीकृत किया गया है। फिल्म का पहले नाम सांवरी था।

title: Praise This
description: A young woman with dreams of being a superstar joins an underdog Atlanta praise-team choir in the lead up to the national competition.

title: Honk for Jesus. Save Your Soul.
description: Proud first lady of a Southern Baptist megachurch, Trinitie Childs carries immense responsibility on her shoulders. After a scandal involving her husband, the church is forced to temporarily close, leaving Trinitie struggling to manage the aftermath. Now, she and her spouse must rebuild their congregation and reconcile their faith by all means necessary to make the biggest comeback that commodified religion has ever seen.

title: La Soga 3: Vengeance
description: Un asesino a sueldo regresa a su tierra natal en busca de venganza, sólo para descubrir una red de caos, corrupción y un prodigio inesperado.

title: Do Aur Do Pyaar
description: दो और दो प्यार: अलगाव के कगार पर, एक अंतरंग रात ने अनी और काव्या के लंबे समय से खोए हुए रोमांस को फिर से जगा दिया, अब वे अपने गुप्त प्रेम संबंधों को सुलझाने के लिए मजबूर हैं।

title: Hatya
description: Starring: Vijay Antony, Ritika Singh, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Radikaa Sarathkumar, Murli Sharma, Siddhartha Shankar, Kishore Kumar, John Vijay, Arjun Chidambaram & Samkit Bohra.  Written & Directed by: Balaji K Kumar

title: Tadeo Jones 3: La Tabla Esmeralda
description: Tad descubre un sarcófago poco común, pero accidentalmente desata un antiguo hechizo que pone en peligro las vidas de sus amigos. En su intento de hacer las paces, emprende una aventura que lo llevará a los rincones más lejanos del mundo.

title: Beverly Hills Cop: Axel F
description: After his daughter's life is threatened, wisecracking Detective Axel Foley teams up with a new partner and some old pals to turn up the heat on a conspiracy.

title: Down the Rabbit Hole
description: Raised in opulence and culture, 10-year-old Tochtli's lavish life contrasts with the darkness that seeps from his father's criminal activities.

title: Pared con pared
description: Valentina es una pianista que se prepara para una audición. David es un inventor de juegos que sólo puede concentrarse en completo silencio. Separados por una pared delgada como el papel, se esfuerzan por vivir en armonía unos con otros.

title: The Lego Movie
description: In a world made entirely of Lego bricks and pieces, an ordinary construction worker is chosen by a resistance movement to overthrow an evil, micromanaging businessman.

title: Real Steel
description: Charlie, a prize fighter, loses his chance to win the title when humans are replaced by heavy, towering robots in the boxing ring. After failing badly, he teams up with his estranged son Max to win.

title: Cold Meat
description: David Petersen is passing through the Colorado Rockies during a blizzard. One false move behind the wheel has him waking up inside a ravine, in the eye of the storm. But the cold is the least of his worries when a beast starts prowling outside.

title: Getúlio
description: Depois de ser reeleito por voto direto, o presidente brasileiro Getulio Vargas cometeu suicídio em meio a graves crises envolvendo corrupção e traição, gerando protestos.

title: Os Gatos Não Têm Vertigens
description: Rosa vive na solidão após a morte do marido, até encontrar Jo, um jovem de 18 anos, dormindo em seu telhado. Ela descobre que Jo foi expulso de casa por seu pai alcoólatra e decide colocá-lo sob sua proteção.

title: Mau Mau Maria
description: Três irmãos tentam desesperadamente encontrar as mulheres de suas vidas para realizar o desejo do pai e proteger o futuro como herdeiros da família.

title: Virados do Avesso
description: John, um escritor famoso que está passando por um bloqueio criativo, desenvolve amnésia. Enquanto luta com suas memórias e identidade, ele se afasta e faz experiências com sua carreira.

title: Carlos do Carmo: Um Homem no Mundo
description: Sobre o maior fadista masculino de todos os tempos, Carlos do Carmo. Uma homenagem a Lisboa e a Portugal mas também ao mundo para onde Do Carmo leva a sua arte depois de 50 anos.

title: Raquel 1:1
description: Raquel é uma adolescente que se muda com o pai para uma pequena cidade em busca de uma nova vida. Durante seus primeiros dias lá, ela acredita que recebeu uma missão importante e controversa relacionada à Bíblia.

title: A Simple Favor
description: Stephanie, a single mother, along with Sean, Emily's husband, set out to unravel the mystery behind Emily's disappearance. However, they counter secrets much more than what they bargained for.

title: Security
description: Eddie, a former marine captain who works as a security guard in a mall, must protect Jamie, an eleven-year-old girl, from a gang that wants to kill her.

title: Ice Age: Collision Course
description: Scrat accidentally sets off an asteroid to Earth while trying to get his acorn. However, Manny, Sid and Diego must join forces with Buck to prevent the asteroid from wiping out their existence.

title: Arthur the King
description: Desperate for one last chance to win, Michael Light convinces a sponsor to back him and a team of athletes for the Adventure Racing World Championship in the Dominican Republic. As the team gets pushed to the outer limits of endurance, a dog named Arthur comes along for the ride, redefining what victory, loyalty and friendship truly means.

title: Eu Sou o Número Quatro
description: John, um alienígena, se refugia na Terra junto com seu guardião Henri. Tudo muda quando ele descobre suas poderosas habilidades, desenvolve uma conexão com outros de sua espécie e encontra o amor.

title: Civil War
description: In a dystopian future America, a team of military-embedded journalists races against time to reach Washington, D.C., before rebel factions descend upon the White House.

title: Ghostbusters: Frozen Empire
description: The Spengler family returns to the iconic New York City firehouse where the original Ghostbusters have taken ghost-busting to the next level. When the discovery of an ancient artifact unleashes an evil force, Ghostbusters new and old must unite to protect their home and save the world from a second ice age.

title: Vulcania
description: Vulcania is a 2015 dystopian drama film directed by José Skaf from a screenplay by Diego Soto which stars Miquel Fernández and Aura Garrido alongside Ginés García Millán, José Sacristán, Ana Wagener, Silvia Abril, Jaime Olías, and Rubén Ochandiano.

title: ¡Ni te me acerques!
description: Juan decide trabajar como guardia en un hotel balneario con el fin de inspirarse para escribir una novela histórica. Lo que parecía un simple trabajo temporal se complica debido al confinamiento provocado por el coronavirus.

title: Atraidas por la Noche
description: Mientras investiga la desaparición de varias chicas de secundaria, una policía encubierta que se hace pasar por una estudiante se encuentra luchando por su vida.

title: Las Caras del Diablo
description: Pedro Ramírez, un subinspector, persigue implacablemente un caso sin resolver de tres años de un menor cuando le informan sobre el secuestro de su hija, Sarah, en circunstancias similares.

title: Tueurs
description: Frank Valken, un criminel à la retraite, doit se battre pour son intégrité et prouver son innocence après avoir été arrêté et accusé à tort du meurtre d'un magistrat qui enquêtait sur une affaire importante.

title: Kirikou et les hommes et les femmes
description: En souvenir de son grand-père qui aidait les nécessiteux, Kirikou entreprend un voyage pour résister à la générosité de son grand-père.

title: Kavacha
description: Jayarama, who is visually challenged

title: Ronal the Barbarian
description: A group of brawny barbarian warrior

title: Remo
description: SK, an aspiring actor, falls in love with Kavya

title: Yamadonga
description: Directed by S.S. Rajamouli

title: Stalingrad (1993)
description: "Stalingrad" ist ein epischer Rückblick auf die Schlacht, die den Verlauf des Zweiten Weltkriegs entscheidend beeinflusste. Eine Gruppe entschlossener russischer Soldaten kämpft gegen eine gnadenlose deutsche Armee um die Verteidigung eines strategischen Gebäudes in ihrer zerstörten Stadt und knüpft dabei eine tiefe Verbindung zu zwei russischen Frauen, die dort gelebt haben. In IMAX 3D präsentiert, steht das Ausmaß der Schlacht in dramatischem Kontrast zum menschlichen Drama der russischen Soldaten, der wenigen verbliebenen Zivilisten und ihrer Invasoren in Stalingrad.

title: Kaithi
description: दिल्ली, एक पूर्व अपराधी, जेल से छूटने के बाद पहली बार अपनी बेटी से मिलने का प्रयास करता है। हालाँकि, इंस्पेक्टर बेजॉय द्वारा नियोजित ड्रग छापे के कारण उसके प्रयास बाधित हो जाते हैं।

title: Fighter
description: शमशेर पठानिया ने अपने आजीवन सपने को पूरा किया और भारतीय वायु सेना के सदस्य बने। कड़ी चुनौतियों का सामना करते हुए, पैटी को एक सच्चा हीरो बनने के लिए अपनी सीमाओं से ऊपर उठना होगा।

title: Varkey
description: Directed & written by Adarsh Venugopalan

title: The Icebreaker
description: Film directed by Nikolay Khomeriki.

title: Jurassic Expedition
description: A group of scientists travel to a distant planet to examine its characteristics, only to fight for survival when they meet its native inhabitants.

title: Ghajini
description: Ghajini is a 2008 Indian Hindi-language action thriller film written and directed by A. R. Murugadoss, jointly produced by Allu Aravind, Tagore Madhu and Madhu Mantena.

title: Singh Is Bliing
description: Singh Is Bliing is a 2015 Indian Hindi-language action comedy film directed by Prabhu Deva and produced by Ashvini Yardi under Grazing Goat Pictures

title: Student Of The Year 2
description: Student of the Year 2 is a 2019 Indian Hindi-language teen romantic action comedy film directed by Punit Malhotra and produced by Karan Johar's Dharma Productions.

title: Archana 31 Not Out
description: Directed by Akhil Anilkumar

title: Raanjhanaa
description: Raanjhanaa (transl. Beloved one) is a 2013 Indian Hindi-language romantic drama film directed by Aanand L. Rai and written by Himanshu Sharma.

title: Banjo
description: Directed by Ravi Jadhav and produced by Krishika Lulla

title: BANG BANG!
description: Directed by Siddharth Anand and written by Abbas Tyrewala, Sujoy Ghosh

title: Eine Prinzessin zum Verlieben
description: Eine Prinzessin, die ein normales Leben führen möchte, nimmt einen Job in der Botschaft an. Dort lernt sie einen charmanten Gärtner kennen, der sich in sie verliebt, ohne etwas über ihre königliche Herkunft zu wissen.

title: Reveille
description: Im November 1943 werden eine Gruppe amerikanischer Soldaten und ihre verwundeten deutschen Gefangenen gezwungen, sich mit ihrer gegenseitigen Menschlichkeit auseinanderzusetzen, als sie nach einem Gefecht in Mittelitalien gemeinsam in Deckung gehen.

title: Die Trapp Familie
description: Maria, eine Nonne, wird zum Haus von Baron von Trapp geschickt, um sich um seine widerspenstigen Kinder zu kümmern. Die beiden heiraten bald und führen ein glückliches Leben, bis Baron zum Militärdienst einberufen wird.

title: Young and Wild
description: „Young And Wild“ ist eine überraschende und melancholische Coming-of-Age-Komödie über drei Teenager-Freunde, die ihr letztes gemeinsames Partywochenende in ihrer Heimatstadt verbringen, bevor sie sich trennen, um zu studieren und ins Ausland zu gehen. Sie treffen alte Freunde und Fremde, und so wird aus dem Party-Marathon ein verrückter Roadtrip.

title: Caveman
description: Robert Müller wollte schon als Kind Komiker werden, doch bisher hat er es nur als Autoverkäufer geschafft. Das soll sich ändern, als er an einer Open-Mic-Show teilnimmt. Er stellt das Programm mit seinem imaginären Freund, dem Steinzeit-Höhlenmenschen, zusammen. Dann trennt sich seine Freundin Claudia von ihm...

title: Asphaltgorillas
description: Der Kleinkriminelle Atris hat es satt, für den Berliner Verbrecherboss El Keitar zu arbeiten. Doch um sein eigenes Syndikat aufzubauen, braucht er Geld. Als sein Freund Frank ihm einen lukrativen Deal anbietet, glaubt Atris, dass seine Chance endlich gekommen ist, ohne zu ahnen, dass er dabei ist, eine schicksalhafte Kette von Ereignissen in Gang zu setzen.

title: Das Lehrerzimmer
description: Als einer ihrer Schüler unter Diebstahlsverdacht gerät, beschließt die Lehrerin Carla Nowak einzugreifen. Gefangen zwischen ihren Idealen und dem Schulsystem drohen die Konsequenzen ihres Handelns sie zu zerbrechen.

title: Freier Fall
description: Ein junger Polizist, der bald Vater wird, verliebt sich in einen Polizistenkollegen, was dazu führt, dass er sein Eheleben aufs Spiel setzt.

title: Schächten
description: Victor Dessauer, Sohn eines jungen jüdischen Geschäftsmannes, beschließt Ende der 1960er Jahre, das Gesetz selbst in die Hand zu nehmen, nachdem es ihm nicht gelungen ist, eine gerechte Strafe für den Nazi-Konzentrationslagerkommandanten zu erreichen, der seine Eltern gefoltert hat.

title: Ein ganzes Leben
description: Um die Wende des 20. Jahrhunderts wird ein junger Waise namens Andreas Egger in ein Tal geschickt, wo er den größten Teil seines Lebens verbringen wird. Acht Jahrzehnte lang wird sein Leben geprägt sein von Armut, Krieg und Gewalt, aber auch von Momenten des Glücks und der Liebe.

title: Wanted Man
description: Hoping to save his job, an aging detective travels to Mexico to extradite a woman who witnessed the murders of two DEA agents. Once there, he realizes that bad hombres on both sides of the border are now gunning for him.

title: Gold
description: Eine Frau schließt sich einer Gruppe Deutscher auf der Suche nach Gold in der schrecklichen und feindseligen Wildnis von British Columbia an.

title: Höhenfeuer
description: Ein gehörloser Bauernjunge (Thomas Nock) baut Felsmauern und Türme und wird in der Schweiz der Liebhaber seiner älteren Schwester (Johanna Lier).

title: Das perfekte Geheimnis
description: Sieben Freunde treffen sich zum Abendessen. Jeder soll sein Handy auf den Tisch legen. Egal welche Nachricht eingeht, jeder darf sie lesen und den Telefonaten zuhören.

title: Das finstere Tal
description: Greider, ein Fotograf, kommt in einer abgelegenen Bergstadt in Österreich an und beginnt bei einer alten Witwe zu leben. Als es in der Stadt zu zwei Morden kommt, vermuten die Menschen, dass Greider der Mörder ist.

title: Knowing
description: Als John von der Zeitkapsel erfährt, die kryptische Botschaften über die bevorstehende Apokalypse enthält und die Daten von Katastrophen nennt, macht er sich daran, die Entwicklung der schrecklichen Ereignisse zu verhindern.

title: Nichts, was uns passiert
description: Die 27-jährige Anna und der ein Jahr ältere Jonas lernen sich über ihre Uni-Clique kennen. Die erste Attraktion führt zu einem unspektakulären One-Night-Stand, der wie der Beginn einer lockeren Sommeraffäre wirkt. Auch die Begegnungen der beiden sind von viel Reibung und Provokation geprägt.

title: Der Nebelmann
description: Detective Vogel untersucht das plötzliche Verschwinden der 15-jährigen Anna Lou in einem dunstigen Bergdorf.

title: Ich Will Dich
description: Marie ist eine erfolgreiche Designerin, Ehefrau und Mutter von zwei Kindern im Teenageralter. Ihr scheinbar glückseliges Leben gerät jedoch aus den Fugen, als sie die Verlobte ihres Freundes Dom, Ayla, trifft und sich in sie verliebt.

title: Schlaf
description: Das idyllische Dorf Stainbach wird von einem mysteriösen Dämon heimgesucht. Es stellt sich heraus, dass die Albträume von Marlene für die dunklen Ereignisse verantwortlich sind.

title: The Princess and the Frog
description: A young waitress, Tiana, embarks on a hilarious adventure after her fateful kiss with a frog prince who cannot wait to be human again.
genres: Action, Comedy, Adventure, Romance, Family, Animation

title: Lehrer kann jeder
description: Richard lebt getrennt von seiner Frau. Er ist arbeitslos. Sein Leben läuft derzeit wirklich nicht rund. Eher durch Zufall kommt er mit dem Direktor der Schule seiner Tochter ins Gespräch, die händeringend nach Lehrern sucht – was Richard auf eine Idee bringt. Er ist Mathematiker. Und schließlich kann jeder Lehrer werden!

title: Neid ist auch keine Lösung
description: Als Marie und Markus, ein Paar Anfang Vierzig, Maries Freundin zu ihrem Geburtstag besuchen, sind sie neidisch auf ihren rasanten Erfolg und versuchen, über ihre Mängel nachzudenken

title: Die Hände meiner Mutter
description: Ein Familientreffen an Bord eines Schiffes wird zum Wendepunkt im Leben des 39-jährigen Ingenieurs Markus. Als sein Sohn Adam (4) nach dem Toilettengang mit seiner Großmutter Renate eine kleine Schnittwunde bekommt, erinnert sich Markus zum ersten Mal daran, was seine Mutter ihm angetan hat, als er noch ein kleiner Junge war.

title: Die Hölle
description: Eine junge Dame aus der Türkei zieht nach Wien, um sich ein besseres Leben zu ermöglichen. Leider wird sie Zeugin der Ermordung einer Prostituierten durch einen Serienmörder und muss fliehen, da sie zu seinem nächsten Ziel wird.

title: Familienfest
description: Zum siebzigsten Geburtstag von Hannes Westhoff kommt seine ganze Familie zusammen, um zu feiern. Doch die friedliche Feier wird bald chaotisch, als unterdrückte Gefühle der Vergangenheit wieder aufleben.

title: Ein starker Abgang
description: Verfolgt zwei Jahre im Leben von Greg Sommer, auch bekannt als Skull Man, während er die kanadische Sektion von Box Wars aufbaut, einer internationalen Untergrundbewegung für Pappkämpfe.

title: Weniger Ist Mehr
