description: An 'urban explorer' is blackmailed into infiltrating a derelict building on the eve of its demolition in the hope he can recover a forgotten treasure.  Starring: Jonny Cruz, Nathalie Kelley, Hallee Hirsh, Gregory Jbara, Rocco Nugent, with Robert Picardo and Steve Railsback

title: Ballerina
description: Using the dance skills she learned as a child, Tara (Amanda Nutting) has become an enforcer for a crime family under the guidance of her brother.

title: Wyatt Earp Shoots First
description: Wyatt Earp is one of the best lawman in the West and a first-rate gunfighter. But he is a conflicted individual who is haunted by what he was taught early in his career. Never, ever shoot first. But even a good man learns that sometimes, rules have to be broken to survive.

title: Lake Fear
description: Tina, Jordan, Kathy and Stephanie decide to stay at a remote cabin for their weekend getaway. Things begin to get out of hand when they find themselves fighting their way out of an evil game.

title: Lake Fear 3
description: A demonic evil is unleashed and follows a man who recently escaped its clutches. Trying to evade the demon, the man hides in a bar with two women. It becomes a battle for survival as the evil spirit tries to collect the souls of three new victims.

title: Tooth Fairy
description: Nana starts to tell the legend of the evil tooth fairy who rips out teeth. Carla is sick of her crazy alcoholic stories and tries to leave, however a power outage suggests something is amiss, something much more sinister than Carla could imagine.

title: Turf Wars
description: Turf War - A detective chases down rogue cops. In order to figure out who they are, the detective proves that his Sergeant is framing murders on two motorcycle riders.

title: Mandy the Doll
description: Three burglars will soon realise they are not alone in a manor house when they discover a doll mysteriously appearing.

title: No Letting Go
description: Timothy, a teenager, battles anxiety, depression and mood disorder as his family struggles to cope with decisions that will change their lives forever.

title: Tie the Knot
description: The hysterical cross cultural journey of hearts.

title: Stuck
description: On his anniversary, a man decides to present his wife with a gift. But while wrapping the gift, he struggles to find the end of an adhesive tape leading to amusing consequences.

title: Randy's Canvas
description: Randy, a talented young man with autism, aspires to be an artist. Having been abandoned by his parents early on, his life changes drastically after he experiences love for the first time.

title: The Rack Pack
description: A group of military brats play out their adventures in the woods. They find a map to a buried treasure that thieves are after. But when one of their fathers is kidnapped, they must embark on a rescue mission as "The Rack Pack".

title: Ju-Rei: The Uncanny
description: Japanese school girls are killed by a man wearing a hood.

title: Lake Effects
description: Sara, a successful lawyer, learns of her father's death and returns to her lakeside hometown. Things take a turn when his spirit visits her in order to help her reconnect with her estranged family.

title: A Gift Horse
description: Amanda, a girl who has just lost her mother, works at a ranch to erase her sadness and raises a neglected small horse wholeheartedly.

title: Worth: The Testimony of Johnny St. James
description: Worth: The Testimony of Johnny St. James - Johnny St. James was a young seminary student who lost his wife to a drunk driver. With his reason for living gone, John lost his faith and turned to alcohol. Ten years later, John is finally ready to get his life back on track. With his best friend Hickey ('Eric Roberts') in tow John attends his first AA meeting. He soon finds that his road to recovery tested when he runs into the man who ran down his wife.

title: Jason's Letter
description: Grieving from the loss of his best friend who was killed in a shooting and fed up with the ineffectiveness of protesting, a 12-year-old boy decides to take matters into his own hands.

title: The L.A. Riot Spectacular
description: A depiction of Los Angeles and its inhabitants as the city explodes in the wake of violent clashes and police brutality against Rodney King.

title: Coisa Ruim
description: Uma família descobre que a casa de campo que acabaram de herdar vem com uma maldição.

title: Hard Times
description: The town of Kilcoulin's Leap will never be the same after a down-on-his-luck mailman botches a get-rich-quick scheme.

title: Lisboetas
description: Este documentário mostra-nos de uma forma muito completa e realista a vida destas pessoas em Lisboa.

title: Diário de Um Mundo Novo
description: Em 1752, um navio chega ao Brasil trazendo o médico e escritor Gaspar de Fróes. Mantém um diário sobre a perigosa viagem, as doenças e a fome a bordo, as suas impressões sobre o novo país e a luta política entre as coroas de Castela e Portugal. No Brasil, ele vai se apaixonar pela esposa de um oficial português.

title: Spirit Riders
description: When 17-year-old Kacie Lewis is arrested and sentenced to an equine therapy camp, she finds solace in a horse named Blaze. She decides to train Blaze, and in the process, learns to let go of her past.

title: Guillaume, la jeunesse du conquérant
description: En 1752, un navire arrive au Brésil, transportant le médecin et écrivain Gaspar de Fróes. Il tient un journal sur le voyage dangereux, les maladies et la faim à bord, ses impressions sur le nouveau pays et la lutte politique entre les couronnes de Castela et du Portugal. Au Brésil, il va tomber amoureux de la femme d'un officier portugais.

title: Hemingway
description: When a wealthy publisher dies, his son and heir are shocked to discover that the wealth will be equally divided among the family members under the condition that they resolve life-long family issues.

title: Alatriste
description: En el siglo XVII, Diego Alatriste, un soldado del ejército del rey Felipe IV de España, regresa de la guerra para cuidar del hijo de su amigo. Posteriormente, es contratado para asesinar al Príncipe de Gales.

title: All Between Us
description: Clara and Ray, a newly engaged couple, invite their friends to dinner to announce the happy news. However, their evening soon turns into a disaster where deep secrets are brought to the surface.

title: ClownDoll
description: After purchasing a doll, Lane's life takes a turn for the worse when close friends and family begin vanishing.

title: Light of Mine
description: Owen is a photographer with an incurable and debilitating eye disease that will soon leave him blind. Before his sight is completely gone, he and his wife Laura take a once-in-a-lifetime road trip to Yellowstone National Park.

title: Black Ghost
description: An ex-commando living in a city controlled by criminals, Black Ghost makes his living carrying out contracts for the highest bidder, though he has made a promise to stop killing.

title: Without Warrant
description: A young by-the-book detective gets partnered with a seasoned, renegade undercover cop to solve a brutal gangland murder.

title: Vanished
description: A woman searches for many years to exact revenge on a kidnapper. A psychological thriller that examines how far a person would go if pushed to the extreme.

title: Colourful & Impossible
description: A competitive puzzle tester working in Japan discovers a code he is unable to decipher which may be the cause to a global economic disaster.

title: Das Sommerhaus
description: Das Doppelleben eines Architekten als verschlossener Bisexueller führt zu Spannungen in seinem Zuhause und mit seiner Familie; Schließlich gipfelt es darin, dass er sich zu einem jüngeren Jungen hingezogen fühlt.

title: Am Hang
description: Zwei Männer sind in dieselbe Frau verliebt. Einer von ihnen ist sich dieser Dreiecksbeziehung bewusst, ist aber nicht bereit, sich damit auseinanderzusetzen. Was passiert, wenn sie sich persönlich treffen?

title: Jonathan
description: Jonathan kehrt auf die Farm seiner Familie zurück, um sich um seinen kranken Vater zu kümmern. Ein streng gehütetes Geheimnis scheint jedoch für Spannungen in einer ohnehin angespannten Beziehung zu sorgen.

title: Marécages
description: Alors qu'une sécheresse dessèche la terre, les membres d'une famille sont confrontés à une crise interne.

title: The Remake
description: Actors and former lovers Sheridan and Ricardo reunite after years apart when they are cast in the remake of a film that they had worked on together.

title: Less Adolescent
description: A youth learns about family secrets after his mother's death.

title: Alien Abduction
description: Una familia de vacaciones se encuentra con una amenaza alienígena en este thriller basado en el fenómeno real ocurrido en Brown Mountain Lights, en Carolina del Norte.

title: Exorcismo Documentado
description: En observación del material, Saura descubre hechos sobrenaturales, inexplicables por la ciencia. Convencida que una energía maligna se ha apoderado de Ana, su madre decide recurrir a la iglesia.

title: Escapee
description: Abby, a psychology student, visits a mental asylum on a class trip. She comes across a highly unstable patient, Harmon, who is fascinated by her. After a storm moves in, he escapes to look for her.

title: Jack Goes Home
description: After his father dies in a car crash, a man (Rory Culkin) returns home to care for his injured mother and slowly begins to question his own childhood memories.

title: Host
description: Seis amigos contratan a una médium para hacer una sesión de espiritismo a través de Zoom durante el confinamiento, pero las cosas se estropean rápidamente.

title: Real Beleza
description: João, fotógrafo, tenta reiniciar a carreira e convence os pais de Maria a permitirem que ela seja modelo para ele. No processo, ele se apega romanticamente à mãe de Maria.

title: Los Novios de mi Madre
description: Luisa tiene la costumbre de traer sus dátiles a casa, lo que irrita a su hijo César. Cuando César invita a su mejor amigo Pablo a una fiesta de pijamas, los coqueteos de Luisa se vuelven demasiado difíciles de soportar, especialmente porque César tiene sus propios sentimientos hacia Pablo.

title: White Chicks
description: Two disgraced FBI agents, Kevin Copeland and Marcus Copeland, are assigned a new case where they must protect Tiffany and Brittany Wilson, two cruise line heiresses, from getting abducted.

title: Bearry
description: In order to cheer up recently divorced Chloe, her friend, Sam gives her a giant teddy bear, Bearry. As Chloe confides her wishes to Bearry, people close to her go missing or die. Is Chloe a murderer, is it her stalker? or is it Bearry?

title: The Shifting
description: No matter who you are or who you become, your past always catches up to you.

title: Billa 2
description: டேவிட் பில்லா கோவாவில் பிரபல கும்பல் அப்பாஸியிடம் பணிபுரிகிறார். கருத்து வேறுபாடு காரணமாக, அப்பாசி டேவிட்டிற்கு எதிராக மாறி, இறுதியில் அவனால் கொல்லப்படுகிறான். டேவிட் கவனமாக சூழ்நிலையை கையாள வேண்டும்.

title: Anaïs in Love
description: Une jeune femme pleine d'entrain tombe amoureuse du conjoint de l'homme avec qui elle entretient une liaison.

title: Stiller Sommer
description: von Nana Neul. Kristine, eine Kunsthistorikerin, verliert nach einer erfolgreichen Auktion plötzlich ihre Stimme. Sie zieht sich in das Haus ihrer Familie in Südfrankreich zurück. Sowohl die Dorfbewohner als auch die dort lebenden Deutschen sind überrascht, sie nach so langer Zeit wiederzusehen.

title: ARQ
description: Renton y Hannah quedan atrapados en un bucle temporal y deben sobrevivir a unos ladrones armados que vienen a por una misteriosa máquina, ARQ. Sin embargo, Renton, quien la construye, tiene sus razones para no entregársela.

title: Deshora
description: El matrimonio de Helena y Ernesto entra en crisis cuando el primo de Helena llega para completar su rehabilitación en su aislada casa en la montaña. Su llegada desata emociones y deseos reprimidos y los pone en contacto entre sí.

title: Fala Comigo
description: Um estudante do ensino médio de 17 anos que gosta de fazer ligações anônimas para os pacientes de sua mãe psicanalista conhece uma divorciada de 43 anos.

title: La Passagère
description: La vie paisible d'un couple de pêcheurs sur une île au large de la côte atlantique française est mise en doute par l'arrivée d'un nouveau stagiaire.

title: Les Grandes Chaleurs
description: Lorsque Gisle, 50 ans, perd son fidèle mari, elle se laisse séduire par son client Yannick, 20 ans, mais elle ne cède toujours pas aux pulsions. Que se passera-t-il lorsqu'il sera révélé que son mari avait une maîtresse ?

title: La cantera
description: Un joven queda conmocionado al encontrar a su padre muerto. Sospecha que el hermano de su padre lo hizo, pero no puede probarlo. Cuando descubre que su madre tiene una relación con el tío, decide tomar la justicia por su propia mano.

title: La Chance de Ma Vie
description: Julien porte malheur à toutes les femmes avec qui il sort. Cependant, sa vie prend un tournant positif après avoir rencontré une belle jeune femme, Joanna.

title: 1 1/2 Ritter - Auf der Suche nach der hinreißenden
description: Ein in Ungnade gefallener Ritter sucht Erlösung, indem er die Prinzessin rettet, die unter seiner Obhut entführt wurde.

title: Adam resucitado
description: Adam, un artista de circo, se salva del campo de concentración y se ve obligado a entretener a un comandante nazi. Cuando es paciente en un asilo, se identifica con un joven criado en un sótano.

title: In jeder Sekunde
description: Zwischen einem verheirateten Arzt (Sebastian Koch) und einer selbstbewussten Frau (Mina Tander) entwickelt sich eine gegenseitige Anziehung.

title: Rebel Ridge
description: A former Marine confronts corruption in a small town when local law enforcement unjustly seizes the bag of cash he needs to post his cousin's bail.

title: 6 Nonsmokers
description: Dr. Henry Caldwell, the world's foremost mediator, faces the biggest challenge of his career when he takes on six roommates whose only thing in common is that none of them smoke.

title: Lethal Eviction
description: Apartment dwellers meet violent ends soon after a new landlord takes over their building.

title: Bad Nun
description: Catherine and her family recently moved into a converted church. Upon moving in, they have been harassed by an unknown religious stalker, claiming them to be sinners. Pamela, Catherine's grandmother soon begins to reveal she has secrets hidden to the local church, and not all is as it seems. Each night the Nun returns, and this time, she is looking to claim more than one soul.

title: The Accountant
description: The O'Dell farm is on the rocks. A non-traditional accountant comes with a variety of ways to save the farm.

title: Jeepers Creepers
description: Trish Jenner (Gina Philips) y su hermano menor Derry (Justin Long) cruzan los Estados Unidos en coche, en un viaje largo y aburrido cuya monotonía sólo se rompe por sus continuas discusiones. De pronto, en mitad de ninguna parte, descubren una iglesia abandonada cuyo tejado está cubierto por una espesa bandada de cuervos y ven como un misterioso personaje arroja un bulto al interior de una gran boca del alcantarillado. A partir de ese momento comienzan una huída aterradora, perseguidos por una de las criaturas más letales que se pueda imaginar.

title: Cria Siniestra ( Pahanhautoja )
description: Tinja es una joven gimnasta que intenta desesperadamente complacer a su madre. Esta es una mujer obsesionada con mostrar ante el mundo, a través de sus redes sociales, la imagen de una vida familiar perfecta. Una noche, Tinja encontrará un extraño huevo. En lugar de deshacerse de él, lo esconde y mantiene caliente, porque percibe vida dentro de él. Pero ni ella misma podría haber imaginado nunca lo que saldría del cascarón.

title: V/H/S 2
description: Una aterradora antología de cinco historias que incluyen la desaparición de un estudiante universitario, un implante ocular, zombis, una secta indonesia y una abducción extraterrestre.

title: Jeepers creepers 2
description: Un autobús lleno de un equipo de baloncesto de secundaria, entrenadores y animadoras se queda varado en una carretera solitaria. Pronto son atacados por The Creeper, un monstruo alado y devorador de carne que se levanta cada 23 años.

title: Kalki 2898 AD
description: A modern avatar of the Hindu god Vishnu, is said to have descended on Earth to protect the world from evil forces.

title: Vai que Dá Certo 2
description: Rodrigo, Tonico e Amaral se deparam com um vídeo e decidem chantagear Eloi para ganhar dinheiro fácil. Eles logo descobrem que seu plano pode não funcionar, pois não são os únicos atrás de Eloi.

title: Totalmente Inocentes
description: Da Fe é um bom homem que embarca em uma divertida missão para se tornar o líder do trânsito do morro onde mora a garota dos seus sonhos.

title: Entre Idas e Vindas
description: Quatro operadores de telemarketing em uma viagem pelo Litoral Sul de São Paulo se cruzam com pai e filho pedindo carona na estrada.

title: Assalto ao Banco Central do Brasil em Fortaleza
description: Depois de obter informações vitais de segurança de um banco e montar uma empresa falsa, Barão e sua gangue se preparam para roubar o cofre do banco.

title: Uma Quase Dupla
description: Um policial e um detetive que não poderiam ser mais diferentes um do outro precisam deixar suas diferenças de lado para solucionar uma série de assassinatos que acontecem em uma cidade.

title: Um Suburbano Sortudo
description: Denilson, um brasileiro trabalhador, percebe que herdou uma grande quantia em dinheiro de seu pai biológico, que nunca conheceu. Mas ele deve aguentar as travessuras da família de seu pai.

title: Minha Fama de Mau
description: Na Tijuca, durante a década de setenta o jovem Erasmo Carlos alimenta uma paixão: o Rock and Roll. Fã de Elvis, Bill Haley e Chuck Berry, ele aprende a tocar violão enquanto vive seus sonhos, shows e pequenos delitos.

title: Rock Brasília: Era de Ouro
description: O cineasta Vladimir Carvalho usa imagens de arquivo da década de 1980 para mostrar como bandas brasilienses realizaram seus sonhos.

title: Los Hermanos: Esse é só o começo do fim da nossa vida
description: Documentário sobre a banda brasileira Los Hermanos que acompanha o retorno da banda em 2012 após cinco anos afastada dos palcos.

title: Eduardo e Mônica
description: Num dia inusitado, uma série de coincidências leva Eduardo a conhecer Mônica em uma festa. A curiosidade é despertada entre os dois e, apesar de não serem parecidos, eles se apaixonam perdidamente. Esse amor precisa amadurecer e aprender a superar as diferenças.

title: Pai em Dobro
description: Enquanto sua mãe está no exterior, uma mulher de 18 anos que viveu toda a sua vida em uma comunidade hippie foge para o mundo real para encontrar seu pai biológico.

title: Elis
description: Um olhar sobre a vida de Elis Regina, uma célebre cantora brasileira, desde o início de sua carreira até seu sucesso internacional e sua conturbada vida pessoal.

title: Entre Abelhas
description: Após romper o casamento com Regina, Bruno volta com a mãe. Mas quando as pessoas ao seu redor começam a desaparecer lentamente, ele é forçado a descobrir o que está acontecendo.

title: Desenrola
description: Quando a mãe de Priscila, de 16 anos, faz uma longa viagem de trabalho, ela aproveita para viajar com as amigas, enquanto tenta decidir se está pronta para abrir mão da virgindade.

title: Last Seen at Angkor
description: In the lost streets of Cambodia, an American girl disappears without a trace. After four years of searching, her fiancé Jeremy Oden returns one last time to find her. Singaporean private detective Khai Lo Jin takes him outside the law and into the grip of a human trafficking syndicate. But when the trust between them breaks down, the unraveling of the truth is about to begin...

title: Lost River: Lincoln's Secret Weapon
description: True story of Anna Ella Carroll, unrecognized heroine of the American Civil War who assisted Lincoln as an unofficial cabinet member; she later devised the Tennessee River Plan that brought an early end to the war.

title: The Child Remains
description: An expectant couple's intimate weekend turns to terror when they discover their secluded country inn is a haunted maternity home where unwanted infants and mothers were murdered.

title: The Buddy Cop
description: Veteran LAPD officers Bontrager and Gast take down a violent criminal and his sister, who runs an organ trafficking ring, vows revenge against the pair. Once unstoppable, Gast has suffered a brain injury that leaves him a happy-go-lucky man-child. When Bontrager's sole kidney is stolen, Gast must rise to the occasion to become the hard-boiled, bad-ass cop he once was.

title: Shin Ultraman
description: After the accidental death of a human during battle, Ultraman takes on the man's appearance and his place at the S-Class Species Suppression Protocol to protect Earth from further threats.

title: Dead Sound
description: Four best friends from boarding school decide to attend a massive blow-out High School graduation party on Block Island. After missing the last ferry they decide to hire a fishing boat to take them on what should be a simple journey. What they get is the trip from hell, with a captain and his first mate that have no intention of taking the kids to Block Island, putting them into a fight to survive and to simply make it back to land... any land.

title: Shadow Fighter
description: A homeless ex-boxer and an inner-city kid's unlikely bond helps them face their future, while fighting the tragedy from their past.

title: A Rose on Ninth Street
description: Bob O'Connor is sent my his crime boss to kill his boss's enemy and falls in love with the man's daughter. Things take a dramatic turn when his boss sends others to complete the job Bob was supposed to do.

title: Sweet Bird of Youth
description: A drifter and gigolo from Florida enters the life of a once-famous movie actress who is devastated by a failed comeback, as the two begin a drug-fuelled affair.

title: Zeit der Kannibalen
description: Drei internationale Berater erfahren, dass die Organisation, für die sie arbeiten, von einem mächtigen Unternehmen übernommen wurde. Sie versuchen einen Weg zu finden, in die Gunst ihres neuen Arbeitgebers zu gelangen.

title: Der Auftrag
description: Die 16-jährige Miki Witt war zufällig zur falschen Zeit am falschen Ort: Der libanesische Gangsterboss Ahmed Sayed erschoss vor den Augen der Schülerin einen V-Mann des LKA. Nur knapp entkommt der Teenager dem Mörder, der ihn fortan mit allen Mitteln zum Schweigen bringen will.

title: Im Zweifel
description: Für Pfarrerin Judith Ehrmann ist ihr Job als Notfallseelsorgerin mehr als nur ein Teil ihres Jobs: Menschen zu helfen ist für sie eine Berufung. Doch wenn eine Klassenkameradin ihres Sohnes bei einem Autounfall ums Leben kommt, ist das ungewöhnlich. Judith beginnt zu zweifeln: an sich selbst, an ihrem Job – aber auch an ihrer Familie.

title: Collar
description: Timothy James 'TJ' Williams (David Wilson) is a streetwise detective whose checkered career, family life and long standing friendship with the would-be mayor, police chief Hamilton Markham (Tom Sizemore), spins out of control and teeters on the brink of catastrophe as a result of a bust gone bad. While his life begins to crumble, his fast fading future is bartered for political gain by his former best friend and boss, a mayor with her eye on a Senate seat (Rebecca De Mornay) and an ambitious, activist 'man-of-the-cloth,' the Rev. Alonso Sparks (Richard Roundtree). The political machinery, geared to grind up Williams as a bad cop, has a wrench tossed into the works by the detective, who with the help of his partner, Angel Santangelo (Jaime Santana), gets back on the job to reclaim his reputation and his dignity in spite of their worst efforts.

title: Fou d'amour
description: En 1959, après avoir été déclaré coupable d'un double meurtre, un homme est décapité. Au fond du panier qui vient de l'accueillir, la tête du mort raconte son histoire.

title: Zwei verlorene Schafe
description: Um die Finanzkrise zu überwinden, muss Rebecca, eine talentierte, aber erfolglose Schauspielerin, Thaddeus die Kunst des Schauspielens beibringen. Sie stellt jedoch bald fest, dass ihm das nötige Talent fehlt.

title: The Scandalous Lady W
description: When a young heiress, Lady Worsley, elopes with her lover, her husband along with his lawyers comes up with vicious schemes to unravel her infidelity.

title: Schwesterlein
description: Lisa, einst eine brillante Dramatikerin, schreibt nicht mehr. Sie lebt mit ihrer Familie in der Schweiz, doch ihr Herz bleibt in Berlin und schlägt im Takt mit dem ihres Bruders Sven, dem berühmten Theaterschauspieler. Als bei Sven eine aggressive Leukämie diagnostiziert wird, wird die Beziehung zwischen den Zwillingen noch enger.

title: Mi Amigo Mr. Morgan
description: Matthew, un anciano viudo que vive en París y habla poco francés, se acerca a Pauline, una bella profesora de baile que tiene la mitad de su edad. Sin embargo, sus hijos mayores se oponen a su relación.

title: Exit Through the Gift Shop
description: Tells the tale of Thierry Guetta, a French immigrant in Los Angeles, and his undying love for street art.

title: Die Bestatterin – Der Tod zahlt alle Schulden
description: Hinter vermeintlich natürlichen Todesfällen entdeckt die junge Bestatterin Lisa Taubenbaum Morde und bringt damit den ganzen Ort gegen sich auf. Als ein Stuttgarter Kommissar anrückt, beginnen die Ermittlungen und Lisa mischt kräftig mit.

title: The Last Compartment
description: Nachdem ihr Zug in den Alpen von einer Lawine erfasst wurde, finden sich Greta und fünf Fremde im letzten Waggon eines Zuges wieder, begraben unter dem Schnee.

title: Kabale und Liebe
description: Ferdinands Vater, der Präsident der Residenz, kann eine ernsthafte Beziehung zwischen seinem Sohn und einem Bürgerlichen nicht dulden; er beabsichtigt, ihn mit Lady Milfod, der Geliebten des Prinzen, zu verheiraten, um seinen eigenen Einfluss am Hofe zu vergrößern.

title: Kick-Ass
description: Comic book geek Dave sets out to become Kick-Ass, a real-life superhero. Big Daddy and Hit-Girl attempt to dismantle the underworld empire of mob boss Frank D'Amico, when Kick-Ass gets involved.

title: Superhero Movie
description: A regular guy finds out that he possesses super powers after being bitten by a radioactive dragonfly. However, he soon realises that even though he is bitten by a dragonfly, he cannot fly.

title: Wonka
description: Armed with nothing but a hatful of dreams, young chocolatier Willy Wonka manages to change the world, one delectable bite at a time.

title: The Blackcoat's Daughter
description: During the winter, two students are stranded in a prestigious Catholic boarding school. However, they soon realise that in order to survive they will have to fight a sinister unseen evil force.

title: The House of the Devil
description: Desperate to make some money so she can move into a new apartment, college student Samantha Hughes (Jocelin Donahue) takes a mysterious babysitting job. When she arrives at the house, Mr. Ulman (Tom Noonan) mentions a full lunar eclipse and explains there is no child, but that Samantha will be watching his mother instead.

title: Lovely, Dark, and Deep
description: A new back-country ranger travels alone through the dangerous wilderness, hoping to uncover the origins of a tragedy that has haunted her since she was a child.

title: Lake Mungo
description: Alice drowns while swimming and her family begins experiencing inexplicable events in their home. The family hires a parapsychologist whose investigation unveils Alice's secret double life and leads them all to Lake Mungo.

title: V/H/S
description: A group of burglars who have the habit of filming their crimes on tape get hired by an unknown accomplice to break into a house and steal a V/H/S tape with some valuable footage

title: The Woods Are Real
description: Wealthy Brooklyn couple Joba and Quincy value charity above all else, but when a friend returns from a country pilgrimage to challenge their bleeding hearts, they accept an invitation that changes their lives forever.

title: BPM (Beats per Minute)
description: ACT UP Paris proteste activement contre le gouvernement en raison de son indifférence face à l'épidémie de sida. Pendant ce temps, Nathan, un homme gay séronégatif, tombe amoureux de Sean, qui est séropositif.

title: Facing the Giants
description: A coach strives to inspire his disheartened football team to win despite the prospect of losing his job and facing a myriad of other problems.

title: Eastern Boys
description: Lorsqu'un Français âgé de Paris, Muller, demande à un jeune prostitué d'Europe de l'Est de visiter sa maison, ce dernier accepte. Lorsque la visite a lieu, le vieil homme subit le choc de sa vie.

title: Beach Rats
description: An aimless teenager on the outer edges of Brooklyn is having a miserable summer. With his father on his deathbed and his mother wanting him to find a girlfriend, Frankie escapes the bleakness of his life by causing trouble with his delinquent friends and flirting with older men online. When his chatting and webcamming intensifies, he finally starts hooking up with guys at a nearby cruising beach while simultaneously entering into a cautious relationship with a young woman.

title: God's Own Country
description: A young farmer's life changes after he meets a migrant worker from Romania, giving him a new and interesting way to look at various things in life.

title: Un coup de maître
description: Un peintre en crise existentielle s'appuie sur son ami de longue date, propriétaire d'une galerie d'art, pour le soutenir.

title: Ils sont partout
description: Un juif discute de la condition juive et des stéréotypes courants avec son psychologue.

title: C'est la vie
description: Cinq femmes sont sur le point d'accoucher. Ils ne se connaissent pas, ne se ressemblent pas, mais vont se retrouver dans la même maternité pour vivre le plus beau jour de leur vie. Des premières contractions à la naissance, le film retrace leur parcours, entre rires et larmes.

title: Till Death Do Us Part
description: Michael and Madison Roland had planned to spend the rest of their lives together, until one day Michael's controlling ways turned their perfect marriage. With the help of her best friend, Madison decides to get away. After adopting a new identity, she meets Alex Stone and learns to love again. All is well, until Michael discovers Madison's whereabouts, and recreate the nightmare she once lived all over again.

title: Bella's Story
description: Young Bella lives in a bad situation and wants to go to college to become a journalist. From tragic beginnings this young girl finds a way to realize her dreams but not with out facing some very hard truths.

title: Legend of Hell
description: An archaeologist finds an amulet and a scroll that will unlock the gates of Hell. She is murdered for them, transported to a past life, and thrust into a perilous adventure to prevent the future artefacts from falling into the wrong hands.

title: Baphomet
description: A violent battle between good and evil ensues when a satanic cult tries to force a family off its ancestral land.

title: The Honor Farm
description: After several students wander into the woods on prom night, they are forever changed.

title: Beast: A Monster Among Men
description: Friends on vacation in a remote cabin are killed one by one until only two remain. They have to figure out if the monster hunting them is one of their own group.

title: Tooth Fairy: Queen of Pain
description: An escaped lunatic who was once known for murdering and collecting teeth has escaped from a mental asylum. Now, a group of teachers on a trip find themselves in grave danger as they are stalked one-by-one in the middle of the mountains.

title: The Leprechaun's Game
description: Tilly has inherited a Manor House. Soon, she will learn just how she has managed to inherit it when an evil Leprechaun begins to stalk her down, taking out anyone in its way - for his gold.

title: House Red
description: When a couple travels to a remote vineyard in the south of Italy to spend the summer grape-picking, they soon discover that there is more to the terroir than meets the eye.

title: Abaddon's Pit
description: Blaming himself for the death of his wife Samara, Dave moves to the abandoned family farm to recover. There, he connects with his cousin Gareth.

title: Santi Marti
description: A couple of friends on their way to a rock festival pick up two hitchhiking girls going to the same event, but their trip is ruined due to an unexpected car breakdown. Now, this group of travelers find themselves in the creepy and dilapidated shanty town of Sant Marti, and all hell is about to break loose.

title: Del Playa
description: Claire must confront her demons and put an end to the menace of her stalker who returns after having murdered her boyfriend years ago.

title: Legion of the Dead
description: William (Michael Carr) and Luke (Russell Friedenberg) take a trip through the desert and are kidnapped by Psycho Mike, a notorious killer. They escape from his clutches and arrive in a town run by a sadistic gang who are creating an army of the dead.

title: Amityville Scarecrow
description: A summer camp is about to open to unwitting guests. However, there is something evil that lurks on the land.

title: Tooth Fairy: Drill to Kill
description: After the events of a horrifying school trip where students and teachers were brutally slain, Sammy, a surviving teacher, rejoins her colleagues back at work. When she hears the familiar knocking at the door, she realizes her nightmare has not ended.

title: Mark of the Witch
description: A professor (Robert Elston) and a student (Anitra Walsh) of superstition are taken by a 17th-century witch (Marie Santell).

title: Obstacles
description: A turf war looms when a college student (D-Shot) intrudes on a drug dealer's (E-40) territory to raise some much-needed cash.

title: Dark by Noon
description: A man with a perfect photographic memory is used by a shady organization with the ability to view events eight hours into the future. When he sees a nuclear explosion instead of the stock numbers, he races to prevent catastrophe.

title: Ethel e Ernest
description: Ethel, a maid, gets married to Ernest, a milkman. The couple dreams of a middle-class lifestyle and strives to fulfil their dreams.

title: Bride of Scarecrow
description: A woman inherits a farmhouse in rural Wales. She soon learns the property's dark secret: every 20 years, an evil scarecrow visits the home to claim a new bride.

title: Paternoster
description: Tito, de cincuenta años, está encantado con la perspectiva de convertirse en padre por primera vez cuando su esposa queda embarazada. Su vida da un giro cuando recibe una herencia inesperada de un familiar.

title: Animal Among Us
description: Merrymaker Campgrounds was shut down after two girls were killed by an alleged animal attack. However, things take an ugly turn after the camp is reopened 15 years later.

title: Witch in the Woods
description: An insurance broker, Doug Richards loses his job and decides to follow his passions of becoming a nature photographer. His journey to start his new life begins at beautiful and historic house deep in the New England woods. However, over the coming days, random and unexplained acts seem to haunt him and the home. Eventually, Doug realizes he is not alone, but sharing his home with an entity that is trying to capture his soul before he figures it out.

title: Girl with a Straight Razor
description: Driven by an instinct she doesn't understand and haunted by memories of another life, Valerie prowls the night, guided by visions of a ghostly woman.

title: A Haunting in Ravenwood
description: A newlywed couple arrives at the house of the husband's late wife, where eerie events start to lead his new bride to believe she's losing her mind.

title: Trace
description: When a group of musicians experiment with electronic voice phenomena at a party, they accidentally open the gate to hell and find themselves terrorised by a force from another realm. They don't have much time to correct their mistake.

title: Zebra Girl
description: Catherine lives a perfect life with her husband in a rural city. Her life takes a turn for the worse when she uncovers her husband's secret and tries to cover up his murder.

title: Jack & Jill: The Hills of Hell
description: Following a quest for her missing daughter, a woman and her team uncover the myth surrounding the murderous duo of Jack and Jill.

title: Skinford
description: James Skinford plans to steal and flip a mystery truck to make some money and save his sick father, but his plans are thrown into chaos when he meets a woman with an immortal touch.

title: Die in One Day
description: After the failure of his marriage, Richard is in search of his daughter. He meets an aspiring actress who promises to help him, but the promise of some quick cash by performing in a 24-hour play soon turns into a bloody game.

title: Pterodactyl
description: After her sister goes missing, a young lady will discover what lurks on a deadly island.

title: Camp Massacre
description: Ten overweight men compete against each other in a reality show which revolves around weight-loss. However, when they begin to disappear, everyone suspects a serial killer prowling around.

title: House of Purgatory
description: A group of teenagers set out in search of a haunted house in a bid to earn money. Once inside the house, they are forced to face their darkest secrets.

title: Lost Lake
description: A young woman (Katie Keene) and her fiance (John Shartzer) encounter a terrifying evil after they arrive in a desolate desert town to find her mysterious uncle (Ezra Buzzington).

title: The Castle
description: On their wedding day, Michael and Catherine break down in the middle of nowhere. They walk for several kilometres when they discover an old castle. Against her better judgement, Catherine is convinced by Michael to spend the night.

title: A Stranger in the Woods
description: A young film student is about to make a documentary about an elderly man who has been hiding from the world for many years. But as secrets from his past come to light, their strange relationship takes a fateful turn.

title: Knucklebones
description: A group of friends decides to unleash a demon through an ancient board game. A terrifying outcome awaits them as the demon enters their world.

title: Quiet, Pretty Things
description: A small-town detective is following a string of puzzling local murders when a mistake inadvertently directs the killer's focus to him.

title: The Dark Room
description: As murders grip a small town, a photographer uncovers something sinister while developing pictures for a local religious leader. While the body count rises around him, the photographer is pursued by a mysterious woman and also finds his sanity.

title: House of Shadows
description: A woman visits the mysterious house she has inherited, hoping to learn more about the deaths of her mother and late sister. Haunted by ghosts, she must uncover the truth behind the curse of the house, or become the next victim.

title: The Gates
description: A serial killer has been sentenced to death by electric chair in London in the 1890s, but in his final hours, he puts a curse on the prison he is in, and all of those in it.

title: The Last Seven
description: A cataclysmic event leaves only 7 people remaining on earth. They are desperate and struggle to understand the events, as they are hunted one by one by a demonic power.

title: A Vida De Jesus Cristo
description: Filmagem da encenação teatral ao ar livre da vida de Jesus Cristo na pequena cidade de São Roque, Espírito Santo, Brasil. Os únicos profissionais do elenco são Fernanda Montenegro e Angelito Mello.

title: Todas as Canções de Amor
description: Chico e Ana se mudam para um novo apartamento em São Paulo. Enquanto arrumam as coisas, ela acha uma fita K7 e decide escutar. Trata-se de uma seleção que Clarisse fez 20 anos antes para seu marido, Daniel. Os dois casais, apesar de distanciados pelo tempo, têm muito em comum.

title: Dead County
description: Even though the world has been taken over by the Living Dead, Wendell still finds a way to encounter the tribulations of mankind.

title: Killer BBQ
description: A small-town landmark BBQ stand becomes the focus of a tenacious new deputy's dogged investigation, as people go missing and bloody mayhem ensues.

title: Killing Ariel
description: Rick wants to escape his boring married life and invites his beautiful new acquaintance Ariel to a secluded house. However, strange things suddenly happen that begin to weaken the veil between the world of the dead and the living.

title: Witches' Well
description: While traveling in Edinburgh to research her book on the Scottish Witch trials, a best-selling Horror writer is hounded by a stalker and a potentially paranormal threat, which challenges her skepticism of the otherworldly.

title: Aware of the Wolf
description: Terry is a life coach and motivational speaker for the meek and afraid, and his methods are very effective. But when his students start to become aware of the wolf inside of them, their transformations take a dangerous turn.

title: The Night of the Chupacabras
description: Morte e sangue estão no meio de uma rivalidade entre duas famílias. Algo assustador ronda a fazenda Silva e faz deles suas vítimas. A família Carvalho, presa ao passado e ao ódio, não consegue ver o mal que se aproxima vindo da mata.

title: Death on Scenic Drive
description: A young woman's job as a house sitter takes a sinister turn after she encounters a supernatural entity that transforms her into death itself.

title: Nightmare Radio: The Night Stalker
description: Late-night radio DJ Candy hosts a show where people share real horror stories. One night a listener calls repeatedly, and Candy soon discovers a strange connection between them

title: Mangue Negro
description: Em um mangue poluído, cadáveres levantam-se durante a noite, atacando e mordendo os moradores e transformando-os em zumbis agressivos. O pescador local Luís luta contra os monstros para sobreviver e salvar a vida das pessoas ao seu redor.

title: Ghostline
description: Tyler and Chelsea begin to receive threatening phone calls from an unstable woman claiming Tyler is her ex-boyfriend.

title: Knifecorp
description: High school senior Wally Banks sells knives door to door and gets trapped in a man's house.

title: Bad Candy
description: On Halloween night in New Salem, Mass., disc jockeys Chilly Billy and Paul tell a twisted anthology of terrifying local myths that lead to a grim end for small-town residents.

title: Lillith
description: After catching her boyfriend cheating, Jenna turns to impractical means of getting revenge; her vengeance comes in the form of Lillith, who is bloodthirsty.

title: Noise In The Middle
description: After the death of his wife, a grieving father with a severely non-verbal autistic daughter seeks experimental therapy. He unknowingly rents a home with a haunted history.

title: Katernica
description: An ambitious drama student; her actor sister and a washed up television director are sent on a surreal and nightmarish journey when they happen upon the manuscript of a cursed play that wants to be seen again and again and again at any cost.

title: Entombed
description: Civilization has collapsed, and Seamus is on a desperate run. He finds a subterranean shelter and decides to entrench himself there. However, he is not alone, and things are not what they appear to be.

title: Waking Nightmare
description: Jordan suffers manic episodes after the loss of her friend and is prescribed Ambien. Her nightmares and sleepwalking continue, but she has issues remembering what happened.

title: Deep Murder
description: The set of a soft-core porn film turns deadly when a masked killer begins picking off the stars and filmmakers one by one.

title: Red Eye
description: In the backwoods of West Virginia, a group of friends set out to document a local legend, blurring the lines between stories and reality.

title: Mar Negro
description: Uma pequena vila de pescadores no Brasil é atingida por uma misteriosa contaminação que transforma os animais marinhos em perigosos assassinos. Albino então decide colocar sua vida em risco e salvar seus entes queridos.

title: Johnny Z
description: Johnny is a half-human, half-zombie, who, under the guidance of a martial arts master, seeks vengeance on the evil corporation that created him.

title: Blood Redd
description: A forensic pathologist is determined to solve the mystery of a rash of killings that look to be the handiwork of a large canine.

title: Resonance
description: In need of a break, Max and Elena venture off into a remote area and discover strange noises originating from deep within the woods. When Elena is in desperate need of a doctor, Max realises there's no way out but to go straight through the woods.

title: Corazón Muerto
description: Claudia Villegas, una exitosa empresaria, se encuentra en una grave crisis cuando dos hombres misteriosos secuestran a su hija.

title: Werewolf Rising
description: Emma travels to her family's cabin in the Arkansas hills to get away from the city. After she settles in, she has to fight for her life when a werewolf begins slaughtering everything in its path.

title: Anytown
description: A teenage boy who is affected by September 11th and the war in Iraq becomes involved in an altercation after school that escalates into a hate crime.

title: Brides of Satan
description: When a happy young couple in the dawn of love are kidnapped by a gang of thrill-seeking strippers, a brutal and terrifying evening unfolds.

title: Door in the Woods
description: Things take a turn for the worse when a small-town family finds a mysterious door in the woods.

title: Mrs. Doubtfire
description: Nach einer bitteren Scheidung verkleidet sich der Schauspieler Daniel als Mrs. Doubtfire, eine ältere Haushälterin, um Zeit mit seinen Kindern zu verbringen, die sich in der Obhut seiner ehemaligen Frau befinden.

title: Kottan ermittelt - Rien ne va plus
description: Nach einer 27-jährigen Suspendierung kehrt Maj. Kottan in den aktiven Dienst zurück, um bei der Aufklärung einer Mordserie mitzuhelfen.

title: Cabrini
description: Al llegar a la ciudad de Nueva York en 1889, la inmigrante italiana Francesca Cabrini es recibida por enfermedades, delitos y niños empobrecidos. Pronto emprende una audaz misión para convencer al alcalde de que garantice vivienda y atención médica para los más vulnerables de la sociedad. Con un inglés deficiente y mala salud, Cabrini utiliza su mente emprendedora para construir un imperio de esperanza como nunca antes había visto el mundo.

title: Racheengel - Ein eiskalter Plan
description: Lübeck im Winter: Der Zimmerservice eines Luxushotels findet einen toten Gast in der Badewanne. Kommissarin Tina Campenhausen, verheiratet und Mutter einer Tochter, beginnt mit den Ermittlungen. Sie kennt den Toten: Es ist der ehemalige Direktor einer Besserungsanstalt, Kurt von Brederstein. Campenhausen wuchs als Kind in dieser Anstalt auf und von Brederstein hatte die ihm anvertrauten Kinder vergewaltigt und sexuell missbraucht. Tina verschweigt, dass sie von Brederstein von ihren Kollegen kennt.

title: El bar
description: Un grupo de personas en un bar de Madrid queda aterrorizada cuando uno de ellos muere tras recibir un disparo. Sin estar seguros de quién es el asesino, empiezan a dudar de las intenciones del otro.

title: A Mentira
description: Quando Olive mente para sua melhor amiga sobre ter perdido a virgindade com um dos universitários, uma garota ouve a conversa. Logo, sua história se espalha por toda a escola como um incêndio.

title: Decay
description: A group of PhD students who work at CERN find themselves in an emergency situation as a result of a problem with the accelerator. The maintenance crew have been transformed into zombies after the particle accelerator malfunctions.

title: Decline
description: Ian lives a life full of hate. Alone and lost he takes it out on the vulnerable people he sees around him. Stalking the seedy streets of Portsmouth, he looks for his next kill.

title: Creature
description: When a spaceship crashes during an expedition in outer space, a team is sent to investigate the matter. However, they are unaware of the danger that lies ahead.

title: Paramedics
description: Two killers pose as paramedics and sell their victims' organs on the black market. They kidnap a woman who proves impossible to kill.

title: Breakdown Lane
description: When Kirby's jeep breaks down in the middle of the desert, she must fight against dehydration, wolves and zombies in order to survive. She cannot contact anyone except Max, her only lifeline, who tries to guide her right via the car's direct line.

title: The Winter Hunger
description: Un grupo de cinco personas en fuga intenta ir un paso por delante de una mutación del virus de la rabia que se ha transmitido a los humanos, pero el invierno se acerca y no hay electricidad, comunicaciones, ejército ni gobierno.

title: Punch
description: A night out on the town turns into a terrifying fight for survival when a masked killer named Mr. Punch stalks a college student and her friends.

title: All I Need
description: A woman (Caitlin Stasey) wakes up bound and gagged inside a dirty hotel room and must use all of her wits if she is to escape the den of a mysterious killer.

title: The Good Things Devils Do
description: On Halloween night, a small-time crook and a museum curator form a motley alliance to save their families from a centuries-old vampire.

title: Heartland of Darkness
description: In the small town of Copperton, Ohio, Paul Henson, a former big-city journalist, buys a small local newspaper. He quickly falls into a wide-reaching conspiracy of ritualistic murder and cult mind control when he discovers that the entire town may be under the spell of a Satanic reverend and his flock, as he is thrust into a life-or-death struggle to stop the demonic cabal's reign of evil.

title: Death of Me
description: A hungover couple makes a horrific discovery about the events of the previous night. They try to deconstruct the night to the best of their memories while waiting for a typhoon to pass.

title: The Wild Man: Skunk Ape
description: The skunk ape, also known as the Florida Bigfoot has been rumoured to be responsible for several murders in South Florida. A documentary crew sets out to uncover the truth.

title: 12 Deaths of Christmas
description: Based on the myth of Frau Perchta, a witch comes on the twelve days of Christmas to steal children away by night.

title: The Blackout Experiments
description: This documentary follows a group of friends whose experience with Blackout becomes deeply personal, developing into an obsession that hijacks their lives and blurs the line between reality and paranoid fantasy.

title: Atelophobia
description: After constantly being bullied by a group of girls, Meredith decides to exact revenge by trapping them in a dangerous game of life and death.

title: Fox Trap
description: Five years after a terrible accident leaves a girl disabled, those responsible are invited to a remote manor in the countryside for a class reunion; little do they know, they are being targeted by a masked maniac who is hell-bent on revenge.

title: Maharaja
description: एक नाई अपने घर में चोरी होने के बाद बदला लेना चाहता है, रहस्यमय तरीके से पुलिस को बताता है कि उसकी "लक्ष्मी" चोरी हो गई है, जिससे पुलिस को यह समझ में नहीं आता कि यह कोई व्यक्ति है या कोई वस्तु। मायावी "लक्ष्मी" को वापस पाने की उसकी खोज शुरू होती है।

title: SAVIING DADDY
description: A daughter looks to help her dad find his way back.

title: Blindsided : The Game
description: Walter, a blind man, goes to the grocery store to buy some apples to make his favorite desert, an apple pie. But while at the store, the shopkeeper is shaken down by a trio of thugs, and Walter steps to defend his friend.

title: HIERARCHY OF EVIL
description: When science and magic accidentally start a zombie outbreak in Nigeria, it's up to Captain Drew (Steve Andrew Skyrell) to lead his troops against the zombies while scientists race to develop a cure.

title: VIDA DE INSETOS
description: Flik, ​​​​um inventor, lidera um exército de formigas contra um grupo de gafanhotos que lhe roubam a comida todos os anos. Também convoca uma tropa de insetos de circo para o ajudar.

title: The Black String
description: After a date with a mysterious woman, Jonathan becomes severely ill and experiences hallucinations and blackouts. Convinced that he is the victim of a nefarious cult, he sets out to find the truth.

title: Island of the Dolls
description: After drowning on an island many years before, the evil spirit of a deceased young girl is looking for some new friends to play with, dead or alive.

title: The Black Fables
description: Um grupo de crianças embarca em uma aventura macabra, cheia de lobisomens, bruxas, fantasmas e monstros.

title: Days of Darkness
description: In a kingdom ruled by an aristocratic ruler, the people of the onowu community have to tolerate the atrocities because the king thinks that the Almighty approves his actions.

title: Hell's Belle
description: While on an archeological expedition, a group of young people stumbles upon a piece of jewellery that once belonged to the famous outlaw Belle Starr.

title: Most Horrible Things
description: Six strangers are invited to a dinner party by an enigmatic host, lured by the promise of substantial financial reward if they last the whole evening. However, all is not what it seems as the host reveals the dangerous secrets of his guests.

title: A Bailarina
description: Na França do século XIX, Felicie, uma aspirante a bailarina, foge do orfanato junto com seu melhor amigo, Victor, um jovem inventor. Ela logo se torna aluna de uma prestigiada casa de ópera.

title: O Dom da Premonição
description: Annabelle Wilson, uma mulher com habilidades psíquicas, tenta encontrar Jessica King, uma jovem socialite que desapareceu misteriosamente. Enquanto a busca continua, ela começa a suspeitar dos moradores da cidade.

title: Super-Herói
description: Um cara normal descobre que possui superpoderes após ser picado por uma libélula radioativa. No entanto, ele logo percebe que mesmo sendo mordido por uma libélula, ele não pode voar.

title: Aves de Rapina
description: Depois de ser jogada nas ruas pelo Coringa, Harley luta para se recompor. No entanto, Harley se une à Caçadora, Canário Negro e Renee Montoya para derrotar um gangster e proteger uma garota.

title: Pacarrete
description: Russas, uma pequena cidade no nordeste do Brasil, é a casa de Pacarrete, um professor de dança aposentado e mal-humorado que sonha em se tornar um figurão e estrelar um espetáculo de dança para toda a cidade ver.

title: I Travel Because I Have to, I Come Back Because I Love You
description: Um geólogo (Irandhir Santos) pondera o efeito que um canal tem sobre uma comunidade.

title: No coração do mundo
description: Selma, moradora da cidade brasileira de Contagem, sonha em morar em um lugar que seja o coração do mundo, onde todos sejam felizes e levem uma vida tranquila.

title: Hablame
description: Cuando un grupo de amigos descubre cómo invocar espíritus utilizando una mano embalsamada, se enganchan a esta nueva sensación hasta que uno de ellos va demasiado lejos y abre la puerta al mundo de los espíritus, obligándoles a elegir en quién confiar: en los muertos o en los vivos.

title: Land Shark : le requin mutant
description: Un groupe scientifique tentant de modifier génétiquement un requin crée une machine à tuer destructrice, que même lui ne peut contrôler. Après s'être libéré de captivité, ce nouveau prédateur se déchaîne à la recherche de son repas préféré : les humains.

title: Mr. & Mrs. Smith
description: Un mari et sa femme luttent pour maintenir leur mariage en vie jusqu'à ce qu'ils réalisent qu'ils travaillent tous deux secrètement comme assassins. Désormais, leurs missions respectives les obligent à s'entre-tuer.

title: Diamond Dogs
description: Ronson se retrouve dans une situation où soit il va en prison, soit il rembourse ses dettes. Il rencontre un homme riche qui promet d'effacer ses dettes à condition que Ronson l'aide à trouver un artefact bouddhiste.

title: Jamais entre amis
description: Des années après leur première relation sexuelle, un playboy phobique de l'engagement et un accro au sexe se rencontrent et tentent de nouer une amitié platonique malgré leur attirance l'un pour l'autre.

title: Romeo und Jutta
description: Jürgen Stoll ist nicht nur Filou und Lebenskünstler, sondern der Liebling vieler Frauen. Als der Ehebetrüger vor die Wahl gestellt wird, Gefängnis in der DDR oder eine Karriere als „Romeo“ in der BRD, beschließt er, in den Westen zu gehen. Stoll spielt nun das große Spiel der Geheimagenten mit, bis ihm klar wird, dass die Stasi noch ganz andere Pläne mit ihm hat.

title: Die drei ??? – Das verfluchte Schloss
description: Die drei Ermittler Pete, Bob und Jupiter begeben sich auf eine Reise, um eine Nachricht zu entschlüsseln, die Jupiters verstorbene Eltern hinterlassen haben. Ihr einziger Hinweis führt sie zu Terror Castle, einem Anwesen in North Carolina.

title: Männer ticken, Frauen anders
description: Alice Tanner arbeitet für eine Frankfurter Ratingagentur und ist äußerst erfolgreich. Die Tatsache, dass sie eine Nacht mit einem verheirateten Kunden verbrachte, könnte ihre Karriere gefährden. Das Unternehmen Solarisopt bittet daraufhin um eine Zweitmeinung und Chef Brugger holt mit Michael von Marck einen vierten Analysten an Bord.

title: Zimmer Mit Tante
description: Marie-Luise wird wegen Ladendiebstahls zu gemeinnütziger Arbeit – Altenpflege – verurteilt. Dies ist ihre letzte Chance, dem Sorgerecht zu entgehen. Ihr völlig überforderter Vater schickt sie zur Verbüßung ihrer Strafe aufs Land zu ihrer „verrückten“ Tante Johanna.

title: Und Dann Kam Wanda
description: Karl Heinz Kluss, verwitweter Vater zweier frühreifer Kinder, kämpft gegen Bankrott und Arbeitslosigkeit. Im Laufe der Zeit lernt er die Kellnerin Wanda kennen und verliebt sich in sie.

title: The Missing Piece: Mona Lisa, Her Thief, the True Story
description: On August 21, 1911, the portrait of Mona Lisa disappeared from the Salon Carré in the Louvre; the famous work of art will remain untraceable for almost two and a half years; it is one of the most successful art thefts of the time.

title: Pancho, el perro millonario
description: Después de ganar la lotería, un perro mimado se convierte en el objetivo de los secuestradores.

title: Primos
description: Un rapero en apuros se apresura a recuperar el dinero necesario para participar en el concurso de rap que podría ser su billete a la fama.

title: Combustion
description: El día de su compromiso con Julia, Mikel se siente atraído por una seductora camarera, Ari. Lo que no sabe es que la camarera y su peligroso novio le robarán el negocio a Mikel.

title: La mula
description: Un soldado que lucha durante la Guerra Civil Española salva la vida de un burro en medio del campo de batalla y luego decide quedárselo. Juntos, los dos emprenden una aventura para ganarse el corazón del amor del soldado.

title: Salvador
description: Salvador Puig Antich, atracador de bancos y anarquista, es ejecutado por Francisco Franco. A partir de entonces, España sufre un cambio en materia de democracia.

title: Rumbos Paralelos
description: Gaby y Silvia llevan una vida tranquila y pacífica junto a sus hijos Fer y Diego. Sin embargo, las cosas cambian cuando descubren que sus hijos fueron cambiados al nacer.

title: 15 años y un día
description: Una madre está cansada de su rebelde hijo adolescente. Ella lo envía a vivir con su abuelo, un militar retirado. Ambos aprenden una lección cuando el niño se ve involucrado en un crimen.

title: Lasa eta Zabala
description: En 1983, un escuadrón de la muerte patrocinado por el Estado captura, tortura y mata a dos presuntos militantes de ETA. Cuando los cuerpos de Lasa y Zabala son descubiertos después de más de una década, sus familias exigen justicia.

title: Al Final Todos Mueren
description: Una antología de cuatro cuentos que representan diferentes percepciones de las personas que enfrentan sus vidas a medida que se acerca el día del apocalipsis.

title: Guerra do Paraguay
description: Um soldado voltando para casa após a Guerra do Paraguai conhece um grupo de teatro. Um choque entre a guerra e a arte.

title: Galeria F
description: Filiado ao Partido Comunista Revolucionário Brasileiro (PCBR), Theodomiro Romeiro dos Santos foi o primeiro preso brasileiro condenado à morte no período republicano – pelo assassinato de um sargento em 1971. A pena foi posteriormente alterada para prisão perpétua .

title: Memória em Verde e Rosa
description: A favela da Mangueira é o cenário onde Tantinho e os antigos sambistas relembram histórias sobre a favela e o samba.

title: Martírio
description: Uma análise sobre a violência e a luta sofrida pelo grupo Guarani Kaiowá, uma das maiores populações indígenas do Brasil.

title: Joaquim
description: No Brasil do século XVIII, o país é governado por oficiais coloniais corruptos. Joaquim, um soldado eficiente e famoso por capturar contrabandistas de ouro, parte para uma missão arriscada. Porém, a injustiça que vê o galvaniza a se tornar Tiradentes.

title: Gostosas, Lindas & Sexies
description: Quatro grandes e inseparáveis ​​amigas moram no Rio de Janeiro: Beatriz, Tânia, Ivone e Marilu. Elas usam roupas plus size e enfrentam todas as aventuras e contratempos românticos e profissionais que quatro jovens podem enfrentar na capital carioca, quase sempre de bom humor.

title: Elon Não Acredita Na Morte
description: Como faz todos os dias, Elon vai encontrar sua esposa no local de trabalho, mas ela não está lá. Ele também não a encontra em casa e começa a refazer o caminho que Madalena faz diariamente. Na manhã seguinte, Elon vai à delegacia e faz um boletim de ocorrência, corre para hospitais, necrotérios. Sozinho, ele perambula por uma metrópole em busca de notícias sobre o súbito e misterioso desaparecimento de sua esposa.

title: Ninguém Entra, Ninguém Sai
description: Um acontecimento inesperado surpreende casais durante seus casos amorosos em um motel. De repente cercado pela polícia, imprensa e curiosos agora ninguém pode entrar, e pior, ninguém pode sair do motel.

title: O Rastro
description: Um jovem médico que coordena a transferência de pacientes entre hospitais públicos da cidade do Rio de Janeiro enfrenta um mistério: um paciente desaparece uma noite e desaparece completamente do sistema. À medida que o médico tenta descobrir a verdade, ele lentamente perde o senso de realidade.

title: Real: O Plano por Trás da História
description: Economistas elaboram um plano de emergência para salvar a economia do Brasil após anos de hiperinflação.

title: Amor.com
description: Quando uma blogueira de moda se apaixona por um vlogger de videogame, o romance deles se torna viral, mas separar a vida virtual da realidade fica complicado.

title: Animal Político
description: Ela tem tudo que seu coração deseja. Ela é popular, adora fazer compras, vem de uma família amorosa. Ela joga vôlei e depois fuma com as amigas. Clube esportivo, churrascaria, cabeleireira: a vida dela é perfeita. Só há uma coisa que a destaca: ela é uma vaca.

title: Um Tio Quase Perfeito 2
description: Uncle Tony (Marcus Majella) reigns sovereignly over the hearts of his nephews, Patricia (Julia Svacinna), Valentina (Sofia Barros) and João (João Barreto). He no longer appears to be a swindler and lives in perfect harmony with his family until Beto's (Danton Mello) arrival. Beto steals the heart of Tony's sister, Ângela (Letícia Isnard), and enchants the kids. Feeling jealous and unresigned, Tony gets into a dispute with Beto and will make fantastic plans involving the children to try to prove that the future brother-in-law is worthless.

title: Gaz Bar Blues
description: François Brochu est "The Boss" - le gérant d'une station-service de Montréal qui tente de renforcer ses liens avec ses fils tout en maintenant son entreprise. Il fait face à une multitude de problèmes, notamment des vols, des braquages ​​et des clients peu fiables. Sa vie de famille a été compliquée : après le décès de sa femme, il a élevé ses trois fils, qui hésitent désormais à reprendre son entreprise malgré l'apparition de sa maladie de Parkinson.

title: Bunker
description: Deux soldats canadiens isolés reçoivent l'ordre de lancer une frappe nucléaire contre la Russie.

title: Kick-Ass
description: Après un congé, le patron de Sandra refuse de la laisser reprendre le travail à moins qu'elle ne convainque ses collègues de renoncer à leur prime annuelle. Durant le week-end, elle tente de convaincre ses collègues de l'aider.

title: La Cité de Dieu
description: Deux garçons sont élevés dans un quartier sadique de Rio de Janeiro. Plus tard, ils adoptent des parcours professionnels divers, l'un d'eux devenant photographe et l'autre garçon devenant trafiquant de drogue.

title: The Jogger
description: A man's evening jog turns into a race for survival when a psychotic killer starts stalking him.

title: Run, Hide, Die
description: Five girls head out to a cabin to help their friend find balance on the anniversary of her husband's death. As the weekend continues a secret begins to emerge and may boil over into revenge.

title: Werewolf Island
description: Detective Michael James races to solve mysterious tragedies that have occurred on Dog Lady Island throughout the years.

title: Slasher.com
description: Jack and Kristy travel to rural Missouri for a weekend getaway, to get to know each other. After they arrive, they learn there are hidden terrors in the forest.

title: The Devil's Work
description: Two friends' weekend getaway at a serene countryside home takes a terrifying turn when a blood-spattered woman suddenly appears and stalks them.

title: The Devil Complex
description: Rachel Kusza and her team of film makers go missing while in a Transylvanian forest; after searching for the film crew for two years, Rachel's teacher finds a camera buried in the snow.

title: The Inhabitants
description: A young couple buy an old bed and breakfast in New England and quickly learn the old house is hiding a dark secret within its walls.

title: Teeth and Blood
description: Detectives Mike Hung and Sasha Colfax uncover an age-old war between rival vampire covens is about to consume humanity.

title: Mummy Dearest
description: A mother recently confined to a wheelchair moves into her daughter's home, but suggestions that the house is haunted and strange behavior byher daughter's boyfriend send her on a journey into madness.

title: Don't Come Back Alive
description: A police detective, prosecutor and beat cop must stop a serial killer before they strike again.

title: Poltergeist Activity
description: A father and daughter experience strange occurrences and frightening visions coming into their new home.

title: Ravenstein
description: Best buddies David and Marky stumble upon an abandoned worksite. Tempted by urban exploration, they find themselves hunted by a killer bird man.

title: White Coffin
description: Después de que su hija es secuestrada por un camionero en una carretera aislada, una joven madre la persigue y se convierte involuntariamente en un peón de un juego demoníaco mortal.

title: Happy Hell Night
description: The devil's henchman escapes from an asylum and stops at a fraternity house he visited 25 years before.

title: The Final Scream
description: Aspiring actress Kia Anderson gets a callback for a horror movie she auditioned for previously. However, things take a deadly turn for her when she discovers something sinister at play.

title: The Last House on Cemetery Lane
description: A writer living in an old manor house in West Wales discovers the property is haunted by angry spirits.

title: Necrofobia
description: Un sastre adquiere fobia a la muerte, lo que le impide estar en contacto con la muerte. Sin embargo, deberá vencer su miedo para poder sobrevivir a un asesino.

title: Lake Effect
description: Some friends head into a storm to locate one member's terminally ill father. Once they brave the elements, they realize there's more than just weather to worry about: a creature with telekinetic abilities has entered the city to wreak havoc.

title: Scream Bloody Murder
description: A deranged murderer with a gory past develops an unhealthy obsession with a sex worker and decides to imprison her until she reciprocates his feelings.

title: The Stake Killer
description: The legend says Count Falkenstein sought eternal life by taking souls. He's known as the first serial killer, predating Jack the Ripper.

title: Washerwoman
description: A pregnant woman who is alone in the wilderness must get through a forest inhabited by a banshee.

title: Sex Game
description: Rachel and Ryan are two popular influencers who will do anything to get a few more likes and win the next virtual challenge.

title: House of Rooms
description: A desperate TV director creates a chilling reality show where contestants are trapped in a haunted location. Unbeknownst to them, a deadly mole and killer lurk among the group, leading to a fight for survival and a shocking twist that defies.

title: Devil's Witness
description: Two college girls' Italian vacation clashes with an ancient ritual and the prey become hunters.

title: The Zombinator
description: After college students discover a corporation has developed a virus that turns people into zombies, they enlist a former soldier to battle the undead.

title: The Night Eats the World
description: Sam, a musician in Paris, wakes up after a party at his ex-girlfriend's place and finds himself the lone survivor in a city invaded by zombies.

title: Hexing
description: A woman returns home to piece together the circumstances of her mother's death. She uncovers a deadly curse that may be connected to an ancient device.

title: 1962 Halloween Massacre
description: In 1969, the FBI finds the mask of the serial killer who killed seven people during a costume party on Halloween night in 1962. The killer is never found, but, along with the mask, the FBI finds a video that tells the true story of that massacre.

title: The Long Dark Trail
description: Two teenage brothers finally fight back against their abusive father and run away, hoping to reunite with their estranged mother. They embark on a dangerous journey to rural Pennsylvania, not knowing that she's become a disciple of a sadistic cult.

title: Pounce
description: A group of conspiracy theorists watches a top-secret military base in the desolate Welsh mountains.

title: 666: Devilish Charm
description: A cursed bracelet arrives at a sorority house, and as each coed makes a wish, unintended consequences cause tragedies.

title: All the Wrong Friends
description: A reunion among friends ends up turning into a night of terror when one gets murdered and accusations start flying.

title: Apocalypse Road
description: Two sisters are separated in a post-apocalyptic world, chased by a ruthless gang. In the hope of reuniting, the sisters must fight to survive the dangerous new world order.

title: Black Water
description: Grace, her husband, Adam, and her sister, Lee, go on a fishing trip to the mangrove swamps of Northern Australia. When their tour guide is killed by a crocodile, they are left to fend for themselves.

title: Devil's Whisper
description: Alejandro, a fifteen-year-old who aspires to be a Catholic priest, comes across a strange box and unleashes an ancient demon that preys on children.

title: The 7th Hunt
description: A group of friends must run for their lives when they end up in an abandoned military training school where they come face-to-face with sociopathic killers, each with their own unique killing style.

title: Strangers at the Door
description: A family's peaceful evening takes a horrifying turn when three men in masks and hoods break into their house and take them hostage.

title: Stinger
description: The USS Newark has been lost at sea, carrying top-secret cargo from experimental military project. Finally, the submarine is discovered sixty miles off the coast of California.

title: The Night of the Wererooster
description: Something's killing people in the woods, and it's covered in feathers. Reluctant heroes battle to keep their community safe from a deadly wererooster.

title: Th'dread Rattlin'
description: A group of university students investigate a strange noise phenomenon known as the 'th'rattlin' coming from a sinister-looking forest.

title: Fields of the Dead
description: A group of seven friends try to survive on an isolated farm, where they unwittingly summon demons from the woods using an ancient book.

title: Compound Fracture
description: Michael returns home to live with his father who suffers from dementia. Afraid of his father's condition, he learns that there is more to the situation than what meets the eye.

title: The Dead Don't Scream
description: When a group of vacationing students stumble into a small crime-ridden Texas town they realise its entire economy is based on car theft, but unfortunately for them, the locals are more dangerous than they realise.

title: Sisters of the Plague
description: Sensing evil, a haunted house tour guide seeks a medium's help only to be warned that she is facing a vengeful power beyond her control.

title: Inbred
description: Four offenders along with their caretakers visit a remote village. However, everything turns upside down owing to an incident.

title: Shadow Puppets
description: Eight strangers awaken in an unknown prison with no memory of how they got there.

title: Splatter University
description: A young sociology teacher is sent to a private college as a replacement for a teacher who was recently murdered by an escaped mental hospital patient. The new teacher must protect herself and her students from this deranged serial killer.

title: Dark Parasite
description: After a robbery at a jewellery store, a group of robbers take refuge with the owner of a dingy suburban apartment building. However, little do they know that a dark alien creature with telepathic powers is hiding in the basement.

title: Skanda
description: A young man renowned for his martial arts skills sees his life take a dramatic turn when a secret government agency recruits him for a dangerous mission to thwart the plans of a group of terrorists.

title: Fear, Inc.
description: A stranger hands Joe, a horror movie buff, the details of a company, asking him to call them. Despite warnings from his friends, Joe calls up the office and this unravels a series of strange events.

title: Reap
description: A stranger shows up at a house party to inform guests they're all doomed to die before the end of the night unless they find others to take their place.

title: Silhouette
description: A married couple's past comes back to haunt them when they try to start life over following the death of their daughter.

title: Theatre of Fear
description: After a young girl disappears during a magic show, her boyfriend's search for her leads to the unveiling of disturbing facts about the performers.

title: El club de los incomprendidos
description: Valeria se muda a Madrid con su madre soltera y se ve obligada a asistir a sesiones de asesoramiento después de la escuela cuando se pelea. Pronto, los estudiantes del grupo de asesoramiento forman una estrecha amistad.

title: Pa ¡Por mis hijos lo que sea!
description: Un padre hace locuras para mantener a su familia segura económicamente.

title: Mamá se fue de viaje
description: Un ama de casa cansada se toma unas vacaciones muy necesarias lejos de su familia. En su ausencia, su marido adicto al trabajo y sus cuatro hijos se dan cuenta de cuánto la necesitan.

title: Pagafantas
description: Tras romper con su novia, Chema conoce a Claudia, quien cree que está interesada en él. Pero cuando aparece su novio, Sebastián, Chema se da cuenta de que sólo lo ve como un amigo.

title: El fin de ETA
description: Trazando el proceso de una década que condujo al fin de ETA, un grupo separatista vasco que operó durante más de 50 años.

title: La educación de las hadas
description: Aunque su matrimonio es inestable, Nicolás es cercano a su hijastro Raúl. Consuela la angustia de Raúl por la muerte de su padre hablándole de las hadas. Pronto, Raúl conoce a una mujer que cree que es un hada.

title: La flaqueza del bolchevique
description: Pablo choca contra el coche de Sonsoles y ella presenta una demanda por lesiones en su contra. La acosa y la observa con su hermana María, de 15 años. Empieza a acosar a María y se obsesiona con ella.

title: La vida que te espera
description: Gildo, un granjero, vive con su familia. Sus hijas no están contentas con su profesión y su estilo de vida rural. Cuando uno de sus asociados muere, Gildo se convierte en el principal sospechoso.

title: Te doy mis ojos
description: Una noche de invierno, una mujer llamada Pilar (Laia Marull) no puede tolerar más a su marido abusivo, Antonio (Luis Tosar), y abandona su casa llevándose sólo unas pocas pertenencias y a su hijo, Juan (Nicolás Fernández Luna). Pilar busca consuelo y se muda al apartamento de su hermana. Sin embargo, Juan anhela volver a la vida con su padre.

title: La Última Fiesta
description: Tres amigos tienen que recuperar un cuadro de valor incalculable que fue robado de una casa donde solían organizar una gran fiesta.

title: Em Nome da Lei
description: A jornada do idealista Vitor, um jovem juiz federal que decide desmantelar a máfia que domina a fronteira entre o Brasil e o Paraguai. Inspirado em fatos reais.

title: Polícia Federal: A Lei É para Todos
description: A verdadeira história de como a Polícia Federal no Brasil revelou uma onda de lavagem de dinheiro, roubo, corrupção e suborno, que envolveu executivos da petrolífera Petrobras e políticos de alto escalão.

title: 400 contra 1 - Uma História do Crime Organizado
description: A verdadeira história por trás da criação do Comando Vermelho, poderosa organização criminosa que aterrorizou o Rio de Janeiro por várias décadas.

title: Pacificado
description: Uma adolescente introvertida luta para se conectar com o pai depois que ele é libertado da prisão.

title: Bróder
description: Às vésperas de completar 23 anos, um jovem realiza uma reunião com a ajuda de sua mãe.

title: Na Quebrada
description: Nos guetos da maior metrópole do Brasil, em meio a balas voadoras, amores e inúmeras barreiras, as histórias de jovens se misturam e se chocam na busca por sonhos e escolhas.

title: Segurança Nacional
description: O governo brasileiro lidera todos os países latino-americanos numa guerra contra os cartéis de drogas. As coisas mudam quando os cartéis começam a atacar locais do Brasil, começando pela Amazônia.

title: Reza a Lenda
description: Numa sociedade anárquica, Ara e o seu bando de motociclistas ousam restaurar a justiça e a liberdade ao povo. Suas ações provocam a ira do poderoso Tenório, que jura destruí-los.

title: Meu Tio Matou um Cara
