description: Após o tio confessar um crime, Duca decide investigar ele mesmo o assunto. Para aumentar sua situação, sua amante também está associada ao crime.

title: The Man Who Copied
description: André, de dezenove anos, quer ganhar dinheiro para cortejar sua vizinha Silvia. Ele começa a falsificar notas, participa de uma loteria e finalmente planeja um assalto a banco com seu amigo.

title: Saneamento Básico, o Filme
description: Depois de os moradores da Linha Cristal terem sido negados dinheiro para melhorar as instalações sanitárias e serem solicitados a usar os fundos para fazer um filme, eles decidem fazer um filme para destacar seus problemas.

title: O Homem do Ano
description: Maiquel, um homem comum e inseguro, pinta o cabelo de loiro após perder uma aposta com os amigos. Este evento de repente o transforma em uma pessoa totalmente diferente.

title: Madame Satã
description: Nas favelas do Rio de Janeiro da década de 1930, João Francisco dos Santos (Lázaro Ramos) é muitas coisas - filho de escravos negros, ex-presidiário que passou mais de duas décadas na prisão, gangster, homossexual e patriarca para uma família substituta de párias sociais.

title: O Cheiro do Ralo
description: O dono de uma loja de penhores joga jogos de poder com moradores pobres, até que um traseiro e um banheiro o fazem perder o controle.

title: Houve Uma Vez Dois Verões
description: Uma jovem (Ana Maria Mainieri) seduz um jovem (André Arteche) e depois desaparece, apenas para reaparecer alegando que está grávida.

title: O Coronel e o Lobisomem
description: Ponciano de Azeredo Furtado herda a fazenda e outros bens do avô. Ao se apaixonar por Esmeraldina, descobre que ela se casou com Pernambuco Nogueira, amigo íntimo de Ponciano.

title: A Febre do Rato
description: Zizo passa o tempo vomitando poesia subversiva para seus amigos de fora, até que a bela Eneida injeta uma história de amor em sua vida mundana.

title: O Som ao Redor
description: A vida em um bairro do Recife, Brasil, revela-se uma experiência enervante para seus moradores. Felizmente, as coisas melhoram quando uma empresa de segurança se muda para as proximidades.

title: A Jaula
description: Em A Jaula, Djalma (Chay Suede) é um ladrão que se envolve em um jogo psicológico de gato e rato com um rico médico (Alexandre Nero). Para ele, era só mais um dia de roubo em São Paulo, o alvo, um carro de luxo que já estava nos planos de Djalma há um bom tempo.

title: Tempos de Barbárie - Ato I: Terapia da Vingança
description: Uma bem-sucedida advogada de 38 anos leva uma vida normal até que sua filha é baleada por criminosos. Desesperada e impotente porque o agressor de sua filha não foi preso, Carla decide fazer justiça com as próprias mãos.

title: O Doutrinador
description: Miguel é agente federal da Divisão Armada Especial e, após vivenciar um trauma, parte para uma jornada pessoal de vingança e assume a identidade de vigilante mascarado.

title: Meu Pé de Laranja Lima
description: José tem talento para contar histórias, apesar de ser intimidado por seu pai alcoólatra e seus colegas de classe. Mas tudo muda quando ele encontra uma laranjeira e faz amizade com um homem mais velho e gentil.

title: Que Horas Ela Volta?
description: Val, uma diligente governanta de uma família rica, sente-se culpada por deixar a filha ser criada por parentes. Sua vida muda quando sua filha pede abruptamente para morar com ela por um tempo.

title: Boca do Lixo
description: Boca é um filme brasileiro de drama policial de 2010 dirigido por Flavio Frederico. O filme foi exibido no Festival do Rio 2010. Inspirado na autobiografia de Hiroto de Moraes Joanide, o filme se passa na Boca do Lixo, zona de prostituição de São Paulo nas décadas de 1950 e 1960

title: A Concepção
description: Alex, Lino e Liz conhecem uma doutrina que defende o uso de drogas e o sexo sem restrições.

title: Narradores de Javé
description: Narradores de Javé (The Storytellers) is a 2003 Brazilian film by Eliane Caffé. Narradores de Javé

title: Observer
description: A troupe of demons stake their claim on a troubled youth, while a benevolent spirit battles to protect them.

title: Forgiveness
description: Three women mysteriously wake up in a hospital with no recollection of how they got there. To their horror, they each discover they've been forever altered: one is blind, one is deaf, one is mute.

title: Faye
description: Still grieving the loss of her husband, a self-help author retreats to a cabin in Louisiana to gather her thoughts and work on her book. However, her trip soon turns into a nightmare when she is haunted by something far more sinister than her past.

title: Conjuring the Dead
description: After her divorce, Kristen moves from London to a small Welsh village for a new beginning. When she learns a coven has awakened inert spirits to get revenge, she is the only one who can stop them before they kill everyone in town.

title: Werewolf Santa
description: After Santa is bitten on Christmas Eve, amateur monster hunter Lucy witnesses his transformation into a werewolf. Armed with only a rusty ice skate and a vague understanding of how werewolves operate, Lucy and her family set out to save Christmas.

title: Sever
description: A violent patient escapes an asylum to exact revenge on an unsuspecting young couple.

title: Clown Motel: Spirits Arise
description: Ghost hunters encounter a group of Las Vegas partygoers at an old motel where the ghosts of clowns who once dwelled there put the unwitting visitors through a violent nightmare.

title: Naturaleza muerta
description: En un pequeño pueblo ganadero de Argentina, personas vinculadas a la industria comienzan a desaparecer y un periodista hace un descubrimiento impactante.

title: Damned by Dawn
description: Claire and her family fight a bloody battle for survival against the Banshee and her gang of summoned spirits who seek the family's damnation.

title: The Barn Part II
description: With the ban on Halloween lifted in her hometown, Michelle and her best friend Heather in charge of the annual haunted house. Unfortunately for Michelle, some uninvited trick-or-treaters from her past come knocking.

title: The Hitchhiker
description: A demented hitchhiker (James C. Morris) terrorizes four women traveling to Las Vegas.

title: Conjuring the Beyond
description: Participants in a sleep study start to go missing.

title: Into the Abyss
description: The world falls into decay in the wake of a mysterious deluge. A survivor is trapped in an isolated city covered by darkness.

title: Nobody
description: Strange events plague an assassin when he tries to kill his next intended victim.

title: Parasite
description: The Merchants, an evil organisation which runs America, forces Dr Paul to create a parasite. However, when the parasite attaches itself to him, he must do everything he can to destroy it.

title: The Exorcism of Anna Ecklund
description: Once a mild mannered churchgoer, Anna Ecklund is now prone to bouts of violent rage with a particular anger toward religious imagery. Desperate to find a cure for her behaviour, her family call on doctors and psychiatrists to provide a diagnosis.

title: A Crack in the Floor
description: A group of friends on a hiking trip find themselves in a perilous situation when they interrupt the self-imposed exile of a deranged hermit.

title: Centipede
description: Cave explorers (Trevor Murphy, Larry Casey, Margaret Cash) fight for their lives after becoming trapped with a horde of giant voracious insects.

title: Hotel Infierno
description: Hotel Infierno es una película argentina de drama y terror de 2015, producida por Mavelo Films Argentina, Milonga Entertainment y Ninja Films.

title: Life of Belle
description: Eight-year-old Annabelle Starnes is missing and there are no leads as to where she might be.

title: Dead Men Walking
description: Inmates and guards try to survive while zombies run amok inside a maximum-security prison.

title: Ashcan Copies
description: An oversexed woman's plot to snuff out her psychotic husband forces her to rely on a lover.

title: Anna 2
description: Paranormal hunters discover pure evil while investigating an abandoned amusement park.

title: Zombie Hood
description: Several survivors of a global zombie outbreak escape the city and raid formerly populated areas searching for food.

title: Rosa Leigh
description: Four paranormal investigators seek to debunk the claims surrounding an abandoned school where a little girl, her teacher and the school's janitor were killed 60 years earlier.

title: Shed
description: A group of friends party in a cabin in the woods, unaware that skin-stealing monsters are about to prey on them.

title: Hell's Half Acre
description: A group of young urban explorers who film their paranormal experiences discover dangerous demonic entities inside an abandoned prison.

title: Evil at the Door
description: Liz shows up at her sister Jessica's house unexpectedly as the house is surrounded by the Locusts, who perform violent home invasions once a year.

title: Albino Farm
description: Four college students investigate the real-life legend of Albino Farm; a place where sadistic, grotesque freaks await their prey.

title: The Echo Game
description: When her adopted daughter's psychic powers attract the wrong kind of attention, April must save both herself and her child from a crazed scientist.

title: The Pack
description: When a vicious pack of wild dogs sneak into a deserted farm house, the lives of the family residing there are gravely endangered. They must now fight for survival and make it through the night.

title: Forêt Noire
description: Em uma floresta do interior do Brasil, a jovem Clara vê sua vida mudar para sempre ao encontrar o Livro Perdido de Cipriano, cuja magia, além de conceder poder e riqueza a quem a possui, é capaz de lançar uma maldição sobre a Terra.

title: Bone Breaker
description: A group of friends plan a weekend of extreme exercise in the woods. But when one of their party breaks her leg while jogging, they find themselves on the run from a sadistic killer known only as the Bone Breaker.

title: The Mangler Reborn
description: A decade after the original massacre, a repair man goes on a murderous rampage to feed a bloodthirsty machine.

title: Easter Bunny Massacre
description: A killer wearing a bunny mask hunts down a group of friends, one by one, who are hiding a deadly secret.

title: Kiss the Abyss
description: A young woman's husband and father bring her back from the dead after she is killed by an intruder. Soon after her resurrection, she realizes that something is horribly wrong.

title: Cram
description: Marc is out of time. Desperate to finish his final paper, he crams all night in the library. He can't even pull that off. After dozing off, Marc awakens to discover that his paper has vanished. Desperate to end this nightmare, Marc seeks answers in the mysterious and enchanting stacks.

title: Mummy's Kiss
description: An Egyptian sorceress (Ava Niche) awakens from the dead and searches for her reincarnated lover (Sasha Peralta).

title: Scare Zone
description: A crazed killer unleashes bloody terror at a haunted-house attraction.

title: Inner Demon
description: A drug dealer hires a scientist to create a monster that will guard his stash of cocaine hidden in an abandoned resort. Many years later, people start appearing mysteriously.

title: Furry Nights
description: What begins as a carefree weekend for a group of camping teens soon takes a tragic turn when one of the campers shoots a grizzly bear. When the other furries realize what has happened, they will stop at nothing to make the teens pay.

title: The Bone Garden
description: Alice, an attractive middle-aged wife, suspects her husband is having affairs with coeds, and does not know what to do when students start disappearing.

title: Invicta
description: After swarms of a deadly breed of fire ants are discovered in Texas, residents find a solution to get rid of the flesh-eating insects.

title: Deadly Weekend
description: Jealousy and exposed secrets turn two young couples' weekend getaway into a nightmare that catches an airboat captain and his daughters in the middle of a deadly situation.

title: Scarecrow County
description: When the residents in a small town start to mysteriously die in strange accidents, a librarian realises a killer scarecrow has awakened for revenge, forcing her to stop its rampage.

title: Hotel Death
description: A paranormal investigator shares three tales of terror as he explores an abandoned hotel that has been seeing its fair share of supernatural activity and a spate of panic driven by local murderous maniacs.

title: Tardy Terror
description: An unlikely group of teenagers band together to battle a mysterious monster that preys on tardy students.

title: Southern Chillers
description: Two serial killers create havoc and panic in the southern part of the United States.

title: Playing with Dolls
description: A serial killer is released from an asylum so he can continue his horrifying killing rampage. The killers targets are a group of unsuspecting actors who have been chosen to participate on a new reality television show.

title: The Perfect House
description: An anthology that pays homage to the history and sub-genres of horror. Each of three short stories are inspired by the genre's most famous time periods.

title: Patient Seven
description: When a psychiatrist at a mental hospital interviews his patients, he suspects their horrific stories are all connected to someone known as Patient Seven.

title: Conjuring the Plastic Surgeon
description: A group of ladies seeking the perfect faces soon realise when they conjure a demonic plastic surgeon, that no surgery comes without a price.

title: Fang
description: Chloe and Joe, two local junkies, become criminals and take a road trip to escape their faith.

title: Sand Sharks
description: A group of teenagers on spring break gathered on the island of White Sands, for a festival. Chaos ensues when one of them falls prey to a prehistoric predator.

title: Coffin 2
description: Trick is among five hostages who are trapped together and paralyzed from the neck down. An FBI agent and a former detective race against the clock to find them before their promised execution is carried out.

title: Between The Darkness
description: A girl grows convinced that a monster is haunting the nearby woods. On a mission to vanquish it, she uncovers horrifying secrets.

title: Big Bad Wolf
description: Derek (Trevor Duke) and a group of his college friends go to a cabin owned by his stepfather in the woods. They are attacked by a strange beast that takes great pleasure in killing them one by one, unless Derek and his friend Samantha (Kimberly J. Brown) can stop it.

title: The Barn
description: Two best friends and their group wander off on their way to a concert, and they end up in an abandoned barn filled with evil spirits. Now, it is up to the duo to save the gang and escape harm.

title: Ditch Day Massacre
description: When their parents go out of town, high school seniors decide to ditch school; but with a mysterious stranger ready to crash the party, cutting class may be the last mistake they ever make.

title: ReVisitant
description: A victim plagued with paranormal attacks inadvertently passes on an evil entity to a single mother and her two teenage daughters.

title: Close Your Eyes
description: Strangers take refuge in a cabin in the woods to escape a bird attack and end up cut off from the world and reality.

title: Butchers
description: Anyone who crosses their path is dead meat for a family of sadistic butchers in the backcountry.

title: End Trip
description: A ride-share driver has a fateful night after picking up a passenger going through a breakup.

title: The Bad Nun
description: A woman takes a break and stays at an isolated bed and breakfast in the Kent countryside, but finds herself being harassed by the mysterious and unsettling figure of a nun who persistently visits her doorstep throughout the night.

title: The Chosen
description: A family battles against time in order to save their daughter after a child stealing demon takes her.

title: God's Acre
description: A destitute man needs to renovate and sell his house to pay off his debts, but a dreadful secret lies entombed within its walls.

title: This Land
description: A traumatised mother agrees to a rustic getaway on the 4th of July with her husband and son in hopes of putting back the pieces of their lives after a violent home invasion cost her a child exactly one year to the date. However, after arriving.

title: Teenage Wasteland
description: Teenage Wasteland is a 2006 drama film written and directed by Welsh director Andrew Jones. It was funded through the independent film company Steel & Glass Films Ltd. The film is a cinéma vérité style look into the lives of several disenchanted teens and their dysfunctional home lives in Swansea, south Wales.

title: So was wie Liebe
description: Obwohl sie sich zunächst zueinander hingezogen fühlen, entscheiden Oliver und Emily, dass sie nicht füreinander bestimmt sind. Doch das Schicksal vereint sie in der Zukunft, in der ihre Beziehung viele Veränderungen erfährt.

title: Dunkle Wasser
description: Dunkle Wasser beginnt mit der Entdeckung der Leiche einer jungen Frau im Mattsee. Es ist Elena, ein siebzehnjähriges Mädchen. Detektiv Dorner (gespielt von Christoph Luser) wird mit der Aufklärung des Falles beauftragt und erhält bei dieser Gelegenheit Unterstützung von der jungen Kommissarin Alex Fink (Salka Weber).

title: Im Netz der Camorra
description: Bevor Matteo DeCanin als Kronzeuge gegen die Mafia aussagen kann, wird seine Frau ermordet. Daraufhin erhöht die Polizei die Sicherheitsstufe und versteckt den ehemaligen Winzer und seine Tochter Laura auf einer kleinen Insel vor der italienischen Küste.

title: Unsichtbarer Angreifer
description: Fortschritt oder Freiheitsberaubung: Wie gefährlich ist Künstliche Intelligenz? Psychothriller zu einem sehr aktuellen Thema.

title: Besser als Schule
description: Steven ist schüchtern und unerfahren und verliebt sich in seine Klassenkameradin Dana

title: Nuvvu Leka Nenu Lenu
description: ఇద్దరు చిన్ననాటి స్నేహితులు ఎప్పుడూ చేదు-తీపి క్షణాలను పంచుకుంటారు. మీరు ఒకరినొకరు ప్రేమిస్తున్నారా అని వారి తల్లిదండ్రులు వారిని అడిగితే, వారు తిరస్కరించారు. అబ్బాయి పెళ్లి వేరే అమ్మాయితో ఫిక్స్ అయినప్పుడు అసూయ పొంగుతుంది.

title: Falling Star
description: Relato ficticio del breve reinado de Amadeo de Saboya de España y sus esfuerzos por modernizar un país ingobernable. Amadeo escapó a un mundo de fantasía en la corte, mientras el país se derrumbaba afuera.

title: La mujer dormida
description: Una enfermera auxiliar se siente atraída por el marido de una paciente en estado vegetativo y se siente perturbada por acontecimientos sobrenaturales a su alrededor.

title: Boy Missing
description: Eine Anwältin nimmt die Gerechtigkeit selbst in die Hand, nachdem ihr entführter Sohn traumatisiert aufgefunden wird und die Polizei offenbar nicht in der Lage ist, den Mann zu verhaften, den ihr Sohn als Entführer identifiziert.

title: Mar Inquieto
description: Na esperança de deixar seu passado tóxico para trás, uma ex-viciada se muda para uma cidade costeira isolada.

title: Banlieusards
description: Le sort de trois frères originaires d'une banlieue sensible de la région parisienne. Soulaymaan, étudiant en droit à Paris, a brillamment mené ses études. Demba, l'aîné, marche au rythme de son propre tambour. Le petit frère Noumouke cherche encore sa voie.

title: Mes frères et moi
description: La vie de Nour, 14 ans, un garçon issu d'un quartier bourgeois, change lorsqu'il rencontre Sarah, chanteuse d'opéra.

title: Das Glaszimmer
description: Kurz vor Ende des Zweiten Weltkriegs suchen Anna und ihr elfjähriger Sohn Felix Zuflucht auf dem Land, wo ebenfalls ein strenges Nazi-Regiment herrscht. Im Gegensatz zu seiner Mutter erliegt Felix langsam der rechten Propaganda.

title: Ein gutes Jahr
description: Max, ein Investmentmakler, erbt das Weingut seines Onkels in Frankreich. Als er sich auf den Verkauf vorbereitet, ruft ihn sein Vorgesetzter dringend nach London zurück, doch er fällt in eine Pfütze und verpasst seinen Flug.

title: Emil und die Detektive
description: Ein 12-Jähriger (Tobias Retzlaff) engagiert eine Gruppe Straßenjunge, die ihm dabei helfen sollen, einen Dieb aufzuspüren.

title: Bibi Blocksberg
description: Als Bibi zwei Kinder aus einem Feuer rettet, wird sie für ihre Heldentat geehrt und erregt damit den Neid der bösen Hexe Rabia. Die beiden beginnen einen amüsanten Kampf zwischen Gut und Böse, komplett mit Zaubersprüchen und Verwirrung.

title: Nichts als Gespenster
description: In fünf Ländern erleben fünf Paare auf der ganzen Welt verschiedene Feinheiten des Lebens wie Kameradschaft, Sehnsüchte und verwirrte Gefühle.

title: 666 – Traue keinem, mit dem du schläfst!
description: 666 – Traue keinem, mit dem du schläfst! ist ein deutscher Film von Rainer Matsutani aus dem Jahr 2002. Es basiert sehr lose auf einigen Elementen des Theaterstücks Faust von Johann Wolfgang von Goethe aus dem Jahr 1808

title: Als der Weihnachtsmann vom Himmel fiel
description: Noch sind es zwei Wochen, aber Ben fällt es schwer, in Weihnachtsstimmung zu kommen. Der Umzug in eine neue Stadt und Schule war schwierig. Doch alles ändert sich, als der Weihnachtsmann und seine Helfer auf seiner Spur landen.

title: Lo mejor de Eva
description: Eva, una jueza inteligente, que tiene control sobre todos los aspectos de su vida, comienza a ver su vida desmoronarse después de que decide descifrar el caso del asesinato de una stripper.

title: Tengo ganas de ti
description: Un hombre regresa a su ciudad natal después de dos años para superar su relación pasada y pasar tiempo con amigos y familiares. Sin embargo, volver a sus raíces trae consigo nuevas luchas en su vida.

title: La noche que mi madre mató a mi padre
description: Una reunión entre un grupo de profesionales de la industria cinematográfica sale terrible y peligrosamente mal cuando empiezan a discutir el guión de un nuevo proyecto.

title: Sangre
description: Fernando chega à cidade de Rosário para trabalhar em um petroleiro que liga a cidade a Buenos Aires. Lá ele se envolve em um triângulo amoroso com duas mulheres, o que logo traz violência e obsessão para sua vida.

title: Mince Alors 2!
description: Des mésaventures hilarantes s'ensuivent alors que Nina ouvre un centre de bien-être et de désintoxication quelque part dans le sud de la France, assistée par un groupe diversifié de personnages excentriques et intéressants.

title: Die Vergesslichkeit der Eichhörnchen
description: Die 27-jährige Ukrainerin Marija (Emilia Schüle) kommt nach Deutschland in der Hoffnung, mit dem hier verdienten Geld ihre Familie in der Heimat ernähren zu können. Schließlich findet sie einen Job als Altenpflegerin und kümmert sich 24 Stunden am Tag um Curt (Günther Maria Halmer).

title: Project Solitude: Buried Alive
description: A researcher brings a group of people into the woods for a terrifying experiment on human survival instincts.

title: La Fracture
description: Raf et Julie, un couple au bord de la rupture, se retrouvent aux urgences au bord de l'effondrement le soir d'une manifestation parisienne des Gilets jaunes.

title: Baby Doll
description: Four foreign exchange students are forced to take shelter in an abandoned home after discovering the villa they were supposed to be staying in is no longer available. Before long, one of the students hears whispers and sees creepy things everywhere.

title: De rouille et d'os
description: Alain, combattant d'arts martiaux mixtes, entame une relation stable avec Stéphanie après l'avoir sauvée d'un accident. Mais une responsabilité envers son fils, Sam, met leur relation à rude épreuve.

title: Cult Girls
description: Looking for meaning between death and reincarnation, three young sisters' relationship with a cult drags them to a dark future.

title: Sea Horse
description: After being forced into the unforgiving elements during a mysterious event, three women struggle to survive in the Alaskan wilderness.

title: The Cult of Humpty Dumpty 2
description: A group of troubled teen girls and their teacher must fight for survival after discovering a cult has brought Humpty Dumpty, a killer doll, back to life and set loose on the camp where they are staying.

title: Season of the Witch
description: When Mary and her two children Alice and Sam return to their hometown Maiden Hollow after the death of Mary's father, they discover a small, isolated village. Upon their arrival, the locals seem hostile to them. In addition, the local pastor Michael shows a worrying interest for Alice. Because of the consequences of a car accident in which his wife died, Michael suffers from surreal fantasies.

title: The Entity Within
description: A renowned celebrity medium is forced to confront the paranormal that lurks in her past while helping to banish unwanted spirits in the present.

title: Lake Artifact
description: Time and space begin to function without reason for five friends staying in a cabin.

title: Death Rink
description: A mysterious hooded figure slashes his way through the night staff at a roller-skating rink.

title: Party Bus
description: Friends are reunited in a sordid bachelor party kidnapping that involves a secret from everyone's past.

title: Without a Body
description: After moving into a run-down farmhouse with his two daughters, a sceptical author seeks to uncover a sinister past that haunts the house and terrorises his family.

title: Bloody Mary
description: A reunion for a group of old friends at a spa getaway in the mountains takes a terrifying turn after a seemingly innocent game unleashes a deadly curse.

title: The Amityville Playhouse
description: Following the tragic death of her parents Fawn Harriman discovers she has inherited a theatre in the town of Amityville.

title: Poseidon Rex
description: While searching for lost treasure, a group of deep-sea divers awaken a prehistoric monster. Eventually, the divers join hands with a marine biologist to quell the monster's carnage.

title: Witch Trials
description: Two filmmakers and an ex-cop investigate the disappearance of a young girl rumoured to have been abducted by a witch in Connecticut's haunted woods.

title: Escape to the Cove
description: In the near future, a pandemic has ravaged the earth. Fear, greed and destruction have made way for such terrors as famine, pirates, and zombies.

title: Reel Nightmare
description: Three beautiful, vengeful witches awakened by an ancient book, the Necronomicon, bring production of a film in their old family home to a deadly halt.

title: Devil’s Path
description: Two men encounter each other on a dangerous hiking trail and quickly find themselves caught up in a deadly game of cat and mouse.

title: Ghost Month
description: Alyssa begins having nightmarish visions during the Chinese calendar's seventh month when the dead return to the mortal world to raise hell.

title: Yesterday
description: Six strangers come together and flee the city to survive a zombie outbreak, only to realise that it's each other they should be scared off.

title: Seclusion
description: Grant and Sarah want to celebrate their wedding with their closest friends in a small country house; however, the romantic dream soon turns into a nightmare when one wedding guest after another disappears without a trace.

title: Drainiac
description: While working on a old mansion, an ancient water demon that inhabits the drain pipes manifests itself in the flesh.

title: ChromeSkull: Laid to Rest 2
description: The associates of Jesse 'ChromeSkull' Cromeans bring him back from death. They help him to get back on his feet and start from where he had left.

title: Garden of Love
description: Rebecca's entire family is murdered, and the attack leaves her in a coma for two years. She awakes with no memory of the incident, but as she slowly regains it, she learns the spirits of her family have unfinished business.

title: Rattlers
description: A zoology professor (Sam Chew) and a photographer (Elisabeth Chauvet) hunt Mojave Desert snakes riled by nerve gas.

title: The Hunting
description: When a mysterious animal attack leaves a mutilated body in the forest, a conservative small town detective must enlist the help of an eager wildlife specialist to uncover the dark and disturbing truth that threatens the town.

title: La forma del bosque
description: Andrés y Silvia, dos hermanos que viven con su abuelo en una casa en medio del bosque, desatarán la ira de un ente oscuro que los perseguirá sin descanso hasta atraparlos, durante el transcurso de una noche.

title: Land Shark
description: A research scientist becomes the target of a dangerous killer after she uncovers a sinister plot to inject sharks with human DNA.
genres: Action, Comedy, Horror, Adventure, Thriller, Sci-fi

title: Scarecrow's Revenge
description: When Henrik is banished by his own Viking tribe for his misbehaviour, he exchanges his soul to become an indestructible demonic scarecrow and seek revenge on those who did him wrong.

title: Like Dogs
description: A man and a woman find themselves unwilling participants in an experiment in which their captors treat them like dogs.

title: Aftermath
description: Nine strangers are holed up in a makeshift shelter in Texas and fight hunger, radiation sickness and internal conflict as the US is embroiled in the Third World War.

title: Red River
description: In the backwoods of Kentucky a family man named Roland (Dave Haney) does not like strangers, and when a group of city kids sets up a camp on his property, it sparks a chain of deadly events that ends with bloodshed, dismemberment and mass murder.

title: Doppelsauger: El Misterio de Sara
description: El agente especial Ramírez debe resolver la desaparición de una joven. Las pistas lo llevan al negocio de la esclavitud de blancas como principal sospechoso, un hombre con una doble vida. Cuando el caso parecía resuelto, con el peor desenlace, Ramírez decidió iniciar su propia búsqueda.

title: Grave of the Vampire
description: Kroft, a legendary vampire, returns from sleep. Kroft attacks a couple in a graveyard. A child is born and feeds only on blood from his mother's breast.

title: The Burning Dead
description: A sheriff rescuing an estranged family from a mountain during a sudden volcano eruption finds himself having to fight off a horde of lava-filled zombies brought to life by a curse.

title: Slayed
description: A crazed killer returns to a condemned water treatment plant to continue his reign of terror five years after a Christmas Eve massacre, but the lone survivor is waiting to exact his own revenge.

title: When a Killer Calls
description: A serial killer calls a baby sitter and threatens her life after murdering an entire family.

title: Bleed - Eat or Be Eaten
description: Dana is failing Biology. To pass she must attend an extra credit assignment with several classmates that will lead them into a remote region of the Great Dismal Swamp, a place teeming with life... and death. While the group keeps one eye out for hungry bear, deadly snakes and lurking gators, they are unaware of the real danger.

title: Live or Let Die
description: With the outbreak of a deadly virus, mankind is on the verge of extinction and zombies roam the earth. Two men are in possession of a map showing the way to what appears to be the only remaining refuge.

title: Death's Door
description: Twelve teenagers get invited to an impromptu party in an eerie mansion. All goes well until they find themselves trapped in a house full of their worst nightmares.

title: Sendero
description: Ana es una joven a la que le acaban de conceder una beca para estudiar en un país extranjero. Decide celebrar con sus amigos fuera de la ciudad. En el camino, tras ayudar a una mujer herida, son secuestrados por una extraña familia.

title: Vile
description: Four friends are kidnapped by a madman and locked in a house with six other people. Each of the captives has to endure life-threatening torture to fill a device attached to their heads or they will be trapped inside forever.

title: Hell House LLC III: Lake of Fire
description: A host takes his show into an abandoned hotel that is rumoured to be haunted.

title: The Devil's Woods
description: Friends trying to repair their strained relationships go on a road trip in rural Ireland; they stay in a town plagued by a dark history, and they have to survive an evil before it tears them apart.

title: Don't Suck
description: A veteran comedian's last chance at stardom takes him on the road with a young comic who reveals an unexpected past

title: The Follower
description: After an unsuccessful attack on an online sensation, an enraged follower stalks a group of millennials on vacation.

title: Lurking Woods
description: In rural Western Australia six young ex-university students have all agreed to spend a weekend away together. A game that starts out as a bit of fun, quickly takes an horrific turn as an unknown masked person begins attacking the group one by one.

title: Jack Frost
description: A family is terrorised by the Christmas demon Jack Frost and must learn their family's dark secrets. This Christmas, Jack will stop at nothing to exact his vengeance on those left in the bloodline.

title: Red Summer
description: Four youngsters embark on a hellish journey after they delve into an inhospitable place.

title: Blood Mania
description: Dr Craig Cooper and the nymphomaniac Victoria conspire to kill her sick father for the inheritance; when it is revealed, that Victoria's estranged sister Gail is the primary beneficiary of the deceased's will, Cooper begins seducing her.

title: No moriré sola
description: Cuatro mujeres jóvenes viajan juntas en el remoto campo de La Plata. En el camino, son testigos de un crimen. Una pandilla de basura local disparó a una niña y la dio por muerta. Los amigos arrastran a la víctima a su coche y corren a la comisaría más cercana.

title: Lo siniestro
description: Clara se enfrenta a un pasado horrible cuando regresa al pueblo donde creció mientras atraviesa una crisis matrimonial. Sólo un policía podría ayudarla a resolver lo que les está pasando a sus abuelos y al resto de la gente del lugar.

title: Howard's Mill
description: An abandoned piece of farmland in rural Tennessee may hold the key to multiple missing person cases spanning over 40 years.

title: Sniper: Reloaded
description: Brandon Beckett and his men are attacked by a sniper while on a mission to rescue a farmer. Brandon seeks his father's protege's help to avenge the deaths of his men.

title: Room For Rent
description: When a lonely widow rents out a room in her home, she becomes dangerously obsessed with her young tenant.

title: While We Sleep
description: A radiologist tries to uncover the source of a 13-year-old girl's sleeping disorder and discovers something far darker than she could have imagined.

title: Minotaur
description: Theo cannot bear the loss of his love, a girl who was sacrificed to the beast, and believes she is alive and held as a slave in the palace. Against the wishes of his father, he goes to search for her.

title: The Rise of the Beast
description: A group of activists break into a government facility in hope to expose what they're doing, only to realise they are in more danger than they could have ever imagined, when a wild beast breaks free.

title: Break
description: Four young girls head out into the Canadian woods for some outdoors fun. They end up running into two brutal and sadistically inhuman rednecks. A blood-soaked fight for survival ensues.

title: Witch House: The Legend of Petronel Haxley
description: Petronel Haxley, a witch also known as the Hag of Black Howe Moor, rises after centuries and unleashes her wrath upon a group of unmindful youngsters who have invaded her home.

title: Serena Waits
description: When an alcohol-fueled hookup takes a violent and horrifying turn, three college athletes find themselves haunted by the very girl they left for dead.

title: Return of the Slasher Nurse
description: After a teen prank goes wrong, one person dies and another gets institutionalized. Twenty years later, a group of friends are partying at a cabin in the woods unaware that a deranged psychiatric patient escaped and is hell bent on revenge.

title: House of Good and Evil
description: Chris, a firefighter, buys a new house in the deepest woods in an attempt to save his breaking marriage. Everything turns upside down when they encounter weird things happening around.

title: Close Calls
description: A drug-addicted teenager has to deal with her crazy grandmother and a psychotic phone caller when her father leaves her home alone. She is forced to face some of her worst fears and inner demons when she believes everyone is plotting against her.

title: Aquaslash
description: A killer targets a group of recent high school graduates who are in competition for a cash prize for the fastest team to slide down the park's water slides. A combination of tiny bikinis and gory dismemberment in this murder mystery.

title: The Drifter
description: A troubled man finds himself on a downward spiral induced by the painful memories of his dark and distant past.

title: Dead Body
description: Nine friends celebrate graduation together and decide to play a game called "dead body." One of them takes the game too far, and players begin to die for real.

title: American Hunt
description: In a sadistic game, two hunters set out in pursuit of a group of friends.

title: Blood Hunt
description: To improve their relationship, a couple embark on a road-trip through Tasmania. During their travels, they come across a suspicious stranger who asks for their help, but he soon proves to be more than he appears.

title: Blood Deep
description: Katie and her friends become trapped in her deceased grandmother's house, and fight to survive the night.

title: The Beast of Bray Road
description: The Beast of Bray Road is a 2005 American horror film written and directed by Leigh Scott. A direct-to-video release produced and distributed by The Asylum, it is based on the Beast of Bray Road, a purported wolf-like cryptid that was allegedly first sighted in Elkhorn, Walworth County, Wisconsin, in 1936.

title: Darkheart Manor
description: Following the sudden death of their last surviving parent, two brothers and two sisters return to the family home after many years to face each other, face facts and face the future.

title: Blood Prism
description: A serial killer preys on the hopeless as she attempts to find meaning behind the voices she hears.

title: Fist Full Of Dollars
description: A stranger rides into a town known for the deadly rivalry between two of its factions-the Baxter's and the Rojo's. Instead of fearing for his life, the man plays the two sides to his own advantage.

title: For a Few Dollars More
description: While chasing El Indio, a most-wanted criminal, Monco meets Colonel Douglas Mortimer, who incidentally is also looking for El Indio. They enter into a partnership and decide to split the reward.

title: The Good, the Bad and the Ugly
description:
final entry in the Dollars Trilogy 
Starring Clint Eastwood and Lee Van Cliff

title: The Book of Zombie
description: All hell breaks loose in a sleepy town in Utah when the Mormon community become flesh-eating zombies. Non-believers seem unaffected by the mysterious virus, and they group together to try and smash some zombie brains.

title: The Great and Terrible Day of the Lord
description: On their first getaway as a couple, a woman's boyfriend becomes a conduit for god and warns her that she will die and go to hell unless she repents and worships him.

title: I'm Haunted 2
description: A woman who watched the Genesis Brady videos from the first I'm Haunted movie attempts to summon the same entity herself to determine whether or not it was a hoax.

title: Mary Tyler, Millennial
description: New to Los Angeles, Mary Tyler takes a job at a mysterious startup called DaJaVue, which begins to warp her reality in strange and unsettling ways as she learns more about herself.

title: Slaughter Daughter
description: An autistic man finds himself trying to balance his witchcraft-obsessed mother, a best friend, and an unexpected love interest.

title: Remy's Demons
description: An autistic man finds himself trying to balance his witchcraft-obsessed mother, a best friend, and an unexpected love interest.

title: The Whispering Man
description: After inheriting an ominous painting, a family becomes disturbed by a demonic presence known as The Whispering Man.

title: The Carver House
description: Evelyn, Tommy, Willow, Josie and Wesley, a group of friends from Youngstown Ohio called the Youngstown Ghost Hunters, are looking to create more content for their YouTube channel.

title: Hank Boyd Is Dead
description: A struggling actress moonlighting as a caterer is left alone to tend to the post-funeral gathering for accused killer Hank Boyd, and she learns that his crimes and death may not be what they seem.

title: Swamp Zombies 2
description: A TV contestant threatens to bring down the world's most popular TV show, `Lucky Stiffs', because of the immoral treatment of the zombies on the show.

title: Fables For the Witching Hour: Vol. 1
description: Late-night lab tech Tina warns viewers to be cautious of five tantalizing tales of terror.

title: Three Blind Mice
description: Abi is going cold turkey; her family has taken her to a cabin in the woods so she can be away from all her troubles. However, little do they know, "The Three Blind Mice" is more than just a fairy tale, and they may be next up on the menu.

title: Cold Eyes of Fear
description: In 60s London, a young playboy picks up a beautiful Italian girl and suggests she comes back to his place. Unfortunately, some criminals kidnap the couple as a way of exacting revenge upon the playboy's father, the judge who sent them to jail.

title: The Dark Sisters
description: Two sisters attempt to reconnect in the woods, but a hidden power in the forest looks to collect against the dark crime from their past.

title: The Dead Follows
description: Two ghost-hunting detectives venture into the heart of a highly haunted complex of horrors. As the night develops, they uncover disturbing revelations about the hauntings at the location and must fight for their lives to escape.

title: Witch of the Woods
description: An insurance broker, Doug Richards loses his job and decides to follow his passions of becoming a nature photographer. His journey to start his new life begins at beautiful and historic house deep in the New England woods. However, over the coming days, random and unexplained acts seem to haunt him and the home. Eventually, Doug realizes he is not alone, but sharing his home with an entity that is trying to capture his soul before he figures it out.

title: The Nothing
description: Clayton Thompson, a recent college graduate, believes that the best art in the world is created in the darkest hours of those artists' lives. Fueled by this thought, he decides to self document the process of writing his first story.

title: 4 Dead Girls: The Soul Taker
description: Four nubile collegians learn that the owner (Mike Campbell) of their low-cost rental has a sinister secret.

title: Dolls
description: A struggling children's book author and his rebellious teenage daughter move into a house they've inherited and find a cache of sinister dolls in the attic.

title: Aegri Somnia
description: Aegri Somnia is a 2008 Canadian existential horror film, written and directed by James Rewucki. Shot in a mixture of black and white and colour, Aegri Somnia tells the story of Edgar, a simple man who is haunted by the death of his wife Muriel and plagued by shadows and terrifying visions.

title: Investigation 13
description: A group of college students investigate the urban legend of the Mole Man, an ex-patient of the Black Grove Psychiatric Asylum who is thought to live within its walls.

title: Mommy's Dollhouse
description: Emma, now dead, takes on an evil presence that coerces her son from the afterlife to commit crimes that put dolls and little girls together in graves.

title: The Sacred
description: A group of students go to a patch of Native American land where the dead come back to life to punish the guilty.

title: Exorcist Vengeance
description: When a prominent family is terrorized by a demonic force, a tough but troubled priest is called upon by the Vatican to root out the murderous demon. He must find the killer and stop the devil's hold before it's too late.

title: The Demon's Waltz
description: A private investigator comes to learn the origin of a viral challenge that has caused the deaths of many people. As she discovers more about the challenge, she learns the true evil that is hiding behind.it.

title: Fear House
description: People suffer horrible deaths when they try to escape from a supernatural force at an isolated house.

title: Mary Had a Little Lamb
description: A radio host and her crew set out to learn the truth behind some disappearances for a true-crime show. They soon discover they have far more to learn when they meet Mary and her lamb.

title: Nicotine Stains
description: While trying to quit smoking, a mentally ill man (Matt Fowler) suffers a psychotic break and believes that cigarettes are telling him to kill his roommates.

title: Deliverance from Evil
description: A married couple lose their son in a tragic accident and move into a new house. After some time, they realise, the house is inhabited by an evil presence that does not want them there.

title: 8 Days to Hell
description: Twisted tales provide proof that evil knows no bounds as the lives and crimes of several serial killers cross paths.

title: American Terror
description: The ghost of a young girl who committed suicide a century ago is summoned by a group of college students.

title: Dogman2: The Wrath of the Litter
description: A litter of enormous dogman pups has been hiding in the Midwestern woodlands. When the pups stray from their territory, they begin terrorizing a small community.

title: Forsaken
description: A priest has no idea he will release the vengeful souls of people he was unable to save when he uses his knowledge of exorcisms to possess his wife to save her life.

title: The Devil Comes at Night
description: Ben, a washed-up boxer, goes searching for his inheritance and must fight for his life when he is trapped in his deceased father's farmhouse by a local cannibal cult.

title: Phantasmagoria 2: Labyrinths of blood
description: The vampire countess is trying to bring her master Dracula back to life and create a new kind of immortal creature - the doppelganger. But for this, she needs innocent blood obtained voluntarily, and this is a very difficult task.

title: Vampyrz on a Boat
description: A man boards a boat crawling with bloodthirsty vampires that can disappear at will. As he fights to save the life of the woman he loves, he finds himself stuck in a bizarre cosmic time loop.

title: Ghosts of Darkness
description: Two paranormal investigators are unexpectedly thrown together in the hope of solving a 100-year-old mystery. Locked for three nights in a house with a dark and unsettling past, the two investigators must put their differences aside and work together.

title: 13th Friday, The
description: A woman discovers an ancient demonic device capable of opening a gateway to another realm. A dark entity crosses through the gateway and begins posing as the woman's daughter.

title: Dark Within, The
description: A disturbed man with unknown psychic abilities and a troubled past tries to unravel the mystery of his parent's disappearance.

title: Bethany
description: Claire and her husband move into her childhood home, and traumatic memories of her abusive mother come back to haunt her. When her husband begins to work longer hours, a mysterious figure begins haunting Claire's memories. During the encounters, she finds herself living in the past as well as the present while trying to figure out what the figure wants from her.

title: Virgin Cheerleaders in Chains
description: A film crew shoots a low-budget horror movie in an abandoned orphanage.

title: Body Farm
description: An independent film company sends a videographer ahead of a story to investigate a body farm where human decomposition is researched. The footage she sends back leads the rest of her team to follow her footsteps to uncover a grisly medical abyss.

title: Terror Trips
description: Six young friends start a business providing tours to the shooting locations of famous horror movies. Things change when they find a spot where the horror is real.

title: Haunted 5: Phantoms
description: A private investigator returns to London. The investigator and his team investigate a London pub that has poltergeist activity. They encounter paranormal events, ghosts and phantoms who will make their investigation go all the way to hell.

title: The Nights Before Christmas
description: Special Agent Natalie Parker sets out to capture a pair of serial killers who have adapted the personas of Santa Claus and his wife.

title: Haunted 4: Demons
description: In a housing estate in London, a house is haunted by an evil ghost child. A team investigates the haunting and looks for evidence of poltergeist activity.

title: Haunted 3: Spirits
description: Andrew Robinson returns to the Halloween horror nights phenomenon. On a rural farm in deepest, England he encounters a series of paranormal events that lead to a mystery being solved with frightening consequences and ultimate finale.

title: The Z Effect
description: Through six parts, following Scott and Mike as they try to survive the beginning of a zombie apocalypse.

title: Haunted 2: Apparitions
description: A private investigator encounters paranormal events on a rural farm in England.

title: Horror In The Forest
description: The curse of Rudwick Forest awaits three fearless paranormal investigators, delving into the long history of its unexplained missing persons cases, said to be the work of a vengeful witch.

title: Doctor Prim
description: A group of individuals come together during the virus lock down. They tell their stories of love, hate, greed and death.

title: My Deadly Playmate
description: Shortly after a young couple reopen a hotel, a string of cult-like murders begins to unfold around them. Meanwhile, their daughter, Chloe, finds what appears to be a harmless doll named Tommy.

title: Dark, Deadly & Dreadful
description: Fun Size Horror Presents "Dark, Deadly & Dreadful", an anthology of short films from Fun Size Horror's community of filmmakers. Each film explores different themes in the horror genre all from the unique perspective of its creator. Featuring work from a diverse group of filmmakers, shorts include submissions to Fun Size Horror, world premiers, and festival winners.

title: An Idle Mind Is the Devil's Playground
description: A reclusive man with an intense fear of human contact unexpectedly finds himself playing host to a group of ghosts.

title: The Slaughter Tapes
description: A documentary film crew from Dallas follows a young woman as she begins a porn career. Then within a month, she disappears without a trace.

title: Seeing Evil
description: A homeless man is struck by lightning and finds himself with the blessing of increased intelligence and the curse of seeing evil entities everywhere he goes.

title: Tales of the Supernatural
description: Lucifer banishes a demon from hell to Earth and requires him to harvest 666 souls before he can return to the underworld.

title: Blood of the Mummy
description: Louise's life has been haunted by her parents' deaths and the ancient Egyptian curse that followed. Now near the brink of insanity she must unlock the secret of the mummy's curse and stop its bloody trail of carnage or risk losing her mind forever.

title: A Place Among the Dead
description: The team explores the repercussions of growing up under the sway of narcissism and evil. Juliet Landau tries to make a documentary around the alleged reappearance of Darcel, a vampire that existed in local legends.

title: Cause of my Death
description: Two friends are unwittingly trapped inside a haunted apartment complex with strange neighbours and no hope of escaping.

title: Attack of the Radioactive Zombies
description: In the wake of an apocalypse, an organization known as the Undead Manor offers a way to contain radioactive zombies. But all does not go as planned.

title: Wolfwood
description: Ferrall is haunted by a childhood trauma related to a terrifying Wolfwood night and her father's death; she discovers a pattern of evil stalking Wolfwood, and wants to take revenge.

title: Deadly Revisions
description: Possible memories blend with characters from his own horror films when an amnesiac uses hypnotherapy and medication to try to restore his memory.

title: Fatal Influence: Like. Follow. Survive.
description: A social-media ambassador assembles a class of rising influencers. In an attempt to gain followers, they enter a dangerous game of chance with a mysterious shadowy power, until all that remains is the content they were willing to die for.

title: The Rideshare Killer
description: A ridesharing app's CEO must stop a serial killer, who uses the app to lure victims into his car, before he kills her whole team and destroys the company.

title: Clowns in the Woods
description: Marcus, a young man with a disability, is bullied and killed after a prank goes wrong. In the afterlife, he meets a group of ghostly clowns who help him exact revenge on those who have wronged him.

title: Happy Hour Slasher
description: Sonny Garrison (Ray Martin) owns the last true corner bar in Havertown a small town in Delco. The neighborhood has been bombarded with Hipster bars and breweries. Suddenly the Hipsters along with other Neighborhood bar patrons start getting picked off during Happy Hours.

title: Grave Images
description: A creepy cemetery caretaker introduces some of its occupants and tells how each met their untimely death.

title: Jacquilynn the Ripper
description: Jacquilynn the Ripper creates her own brand of horror and mayhem.

title: Vacuum Killer
description: After a laboratory assistant loses his arm in a freak explosion while trying to revive his dead boss, a momentary madness inspires him to graft a vacuum cleaner to the stump and transform himself into a vigilante determined to clean up society.

title: Take Back the Knife
description: After surviving separate gruesome incidents, three girls help each other adapt and cope with the scars that were left behind by the slashers, psychopaths, and monsters from their pasts. When a relaxing weekend getaway is interrupted by a crazed stalker, tensions rise as the three fall back into the hell they tried to forget. This time, they would rather spill blood than run from their demons.

title: Pourquoi Nous!
description: Cinq amis sont invités chez le père de l'un d'eux. Ils décident de filmer leur week-end pour se faire un petit souvenir. Rien ne se passe comme prévu et leur film deviendra la preuve que des choses étranges, violentes, mystérieuses et effrayantes existent.

title: The Field Guide to Evil
description: An anthology of the dreadful parables, myths and folklores giving out significant reasoning to the darkest fears and inhibitions of mankind.

title: The Lady Starfighter
description: Alex Rogan, an expert video game player, lives in a trailer park and has no promising future. One day he meets Centauri, an alien ranger, who wants to recruit him as a starfighter pilot.

title: Millennial Killer
description: When Naomi and Daniel search for their first shared home together, they expect to live together forever. However, their real estate agent has other plans as he takes out a personal vendetta against Generation Y.

title: Tainted Love
description: A young woman elopes with her boyfriend on the night of her arranged marriage to another man. Her brothers give chase, planning to drag her back to the wedding one way or another.

title: Frights and Fears Vol 1
description: 6 horror shorts curated from the Film Village "Frights and Fears Horror Festival" are featured in this feature length horror anthology. Featuring international horror shorts from Ty Jones, Jude Bertrand, Kenneth Lawrence, Priscila Carvalho Vailones, Tito Fernandes, and David A. Roncone.

title: Severed
description: Loggers and activists band together after tree sap turns local denizens into bloodthirsty zombies.

title: Big Freaking Rat
description: Ranger Brody, along with his niece and nephew, works on opening a campsite for the season. All seems to be going well until a gigantic rat, mutated by hazardous waste, starts killing people.

title: Evil Souls
description: A young atheist is recruited by a secret organization formed by the Catholic Church that combats the growing number of cases of demonic possessions across the country.

title: The Devil's Familiar
description: Two student filmmakers make a documentary about the Ribbersford woods murders. A mist of controversy surrounds the case, with conspiracy theories about a mythical creature living in the woods.

title: The Truth Will Out
description: Thomas Laboss interviews families from differing cultures across the U.K., uncovering truths. There's something a bit more sinister about one family, and he may not get out of this one alive.

title: Desolation
description: A young mother goes into a remote wilderness area with her son and her best friend to scatter her late husband's ashes. On their trek home, they begin to realize that a lone hiker has been following them. After a series of disturbing encounters, they are forced to confront their deepest fears when the stranger's true motives are revealed.

title: Dead Awake
description: A woman investigates peculiar cases about people who died in their sleep. As she delves deeper into the mystery, she encounters a sinister force that threatens her life.

title: Rebirth
description: What starts as a visit to their family grave site turns into a night of terror for two brothers forced to fight a sudden onslaught of zombies.

title: The Call
description: Four teenagers torture an elderly woman, but their prank goes terribly wrong when she commits suicide. Their worst nightmares come alive when her husband invites them to his house.

title: Purvos
description: His mind terminally warped due to years of abuse, a disturbed young man adopts the persona of his father's circus act, Purvos the Clown, and sets out to satiate his deceased mother's bloodlust, murdering unsuspecting prostitutes and escorts.

title: Hacksaw
description: Terror strikes when a young couple investigate the urban legend of notorious killer Ed "Hacksaw" Crow.

title: Doomed to Consume
description: A small town is overrun by zombies and a small group of survivors heads out to find salvation.

title: Reanimator Academy
description: A brainy outcast develops a serum that allows him to bring a severed head back to life.

title: Sick
description: Doctor Leigh Rozetta, who has been trying to find a vaccine for plague, along with Seph and Mckay, must survive a night at Leigh's house after a group of plague-infected victims try to harm them.

title: Karma
description: When recent college graduate Manny has trouble making ends meet, his father-in-law offers him a job evicting delinquent tenants. Manny soon finds himself unleashing a karma demon which stalks him at every turn.

title: The Amityville Murders
description: When he sees his family fast asleep on their beds, Ronald DeFeo Jr takes a gun and murders them. He then states that inner voices compelled him to commit the crimes.

title: Elder Island
description: Five families live with a curse that started with the murder of a reverend in 1856.

title: Drive-In Horrorshow
description: People meet gruesome and gory deaths at an old outdoor theatre.

title: Psycho Santa 2
description: A killer in a Santa Claus suit returns to the quiet town that burned him. Along the way, he finds his son and makes the Christmas killing a family affair.

title: The Devil's Heist
description: Three thieves effortlessly pull off a bank heist in a small town due to the absence of security. Little do they realize that they messed with the devil himself.

title: Leda
description: Haunted by memories and divine visions, a young woman must deal with trauma, rape and pregnancy.

title: Attack of the Giant Leeches
description: Join Comedian Killer Beaz for a Roger Corman movie about people disappearing in the swamps of Florida. Could it be the result of over-sized blood sucking leeches? Of course it is! Kick back and enjoy this riff on a creature leecher feature classic!

title: Vampire Conspiracy
description: A vampire kidnaps five strangers and makes them players in a bizarre game.

title: Killer Rack
description: A woman getting a breast enhancement is unaware her surgeon is using her in a diabolical plot to take over the world.

title: Tucker & Dale vs. Evil
description: Tucker and Dale decide to go on a vacation to their cabin in the mountains. Their vacation takes a nasty turn when they are mistaken for chainsaw killers by a group of college students.

title: Blood Empires
description: Blood Empires is about pride, family, redemption, and above all love; struggling people on either side of the law, rise out of pain and misery.

title: She's the Eldest
description: Three eccentric siblings return to their childhood home to reconnect but end up digging up the past of their parents' mysterious disappearances.

title: Final Heat
description: The married owners of a struggling functional fitness gym recruit the best athletes to compete in the Games for the huge cash prize. But a figure from the past with a secret threatens to destroy their team, their gym, and their lives.

title: Gift Of Fear
description: Mili watched her mother's murder 11 years ago. Mili now has a family with the Jiu Jitsu team, but the gang she once ran with decides to teach her a lesson. Now Mili must risk everything to save her friend from a life of sex trafficking.

title: Murder and Cocktails
description: When their next-door neighbour is murdered, a couple invite other residents over to search for clues over cocktails. However, when another body is found, things get even more complicated as no one can be trusted.

title: The Full Moon Fathers
description: The year is 1979. Hiding in the woods to escape the law, a fearless biker gang must come face to face with a terror from their past.

title: City Of Gold
description: एक मिल मालिक ने अपना व्यवसाय बंद करने और उसके स्थान पर एक शॉपिंग कॉम्प्लेक्स बनाने का निर्णय लिया। इसके बाद, जब बेरोजगार मिल मजदूर अपनी आवाज उठाने की कोशिश करते हैं तो उन्हें दुखद रूप से चुप करा दिया जाता है।

title: The Nursery
description: When Ranae agrees to babysit for a family with a tragic past, a run-of-the-mill Saturday night quickly turns into a confrontation with unspeakable horror.

title: Behave
description: After the death of their friend, a group of eccentric young adults are whisked away to a villa on the outskirts of London, but a mysterious entity seems to have followed them to their luxurious getaway.

title: The Elevator
description: A disturbing psychological thriller, that engages the audience to the point that it is always caught off guard, thus changing the point of view of the two main performers.

title: Devara: Part 1
description: A village chief's son secretly continues his father's mission to end smuggling, while pretending to be weak and maintaining the illusion that his father is still alive.

title: Black Web
description: After receiving his future obituary via a cryptic Internet file, Easton Denning is forced to confront his troubled past in order to prevent his predicted demise.

title: The Lockpicker
description: A teenage thief tries to leave town to escape the violence that threatens him and he people he loves.

title: Restoration, Inc.
description: During home renovations a young couple release a fiery spirit and if they're to save themselves and set the spirit free they must discover the dire truth.

title: To Your Last Death
description: Following the death of her siblings, caused by her devious father, a young woman is granted the opportunity by a powerful entity to go back in time and change the course of events.

title: Grave Caller
description: A novelist retrieves his uncle's diary from a family cabin. Within its pages, he discovers a macabre tale of violence and demonic possession.

title: Bundy Manor
description: When a family moves to a small town, they discover a haunted house run by a retired surgeon.

title: Prosper
description: An immortal witch (April Hollingsworth) prepares to sacrifice a group of teenagers to maintain her youth and power.

title: Insight of Evil 2: Vengeance
description: Tanya returns to the scene of the crime to rid herself of nightmares of the horror that occurred three years earlier.

title: If I Tell You I Have to Kill You
description: An alarmed professor undertakes the investigation of his students' murders that reveals a disturbing truth behind the reason for the killings.

title: Horror House on Highway 6
description: College students have a grisly encounter with a demented doctor (William D. Caldwell) who's awaiting the second coming of Elvis Presley.

title: Last American Horror Show Vol. 2
description: This is the sequel to Last American Horror Show.

title: The Hounds
description: A group of old friends goes camping, while a detective investigates a criminal gang who are linked to the group in a macabre way.

title: The Pit
description: While hiking in an isolated forest, survivalist Danny Coile (Les Stroud) and old Army buddy Arron James (Stacy Brown Jr.) become hopelessly trapped when they fall into a deep dark cenote with steep walls and no way out.

title: Don't Let the Devil In
description: A couple become wrapped up in a nightmarish tapestry of evil after they move to a small Appalachian town.

title: Apparition
description: A group of young people discover an application which connects the living to the dead. Soon, they find themselves at an abandoned castle which has a horrific connection to each.

title: Kill Teaser
description: Based on True Events: An Asian American Hacker investigates a website that creates torture videos. He becomes the unwilling sidekick for the sinister mastermind behind it, who changes his life in horrible ways.Based on True Events: An Asian American Hacker investigates a website that creates torture videos. He becomes the unwilling sidekick for the sinister mastermind behind it, who changes his life in horrible ways.

title: Curse of the Witch
description: Ron returns to his childhood home in Louisiana after his estranged father dies. Haunted by feelings of anger, remorse, and guilt, Ron decides to stay and uncover the truth behind his father's death and the involvement of a witch named Lily Grace.

title: Cabin Fever Patient Zero
description: A highly infectious and deadly virus breaks out on a remote island. When a group of four friends party on a bachelor boat, they land on the infected island.

title: Cruel Peter
description: Peter, a man who is cruel to children, animals and servants all his life, finds himself in a dangerous situation when he is ambushed and trapped in a coffin.

title: The Stragglers
description: A team of researchers investigates the disappearance of people and fights a psychological battle for survival.

title: A Haunting at Silver Falls 2
description: A young woman struggles to escape her troubled history until her aunt's demented spectre surfaces seeking revenge.

title: Vampegeddon
description: A gorgeous lesbian college student named Melissa (Katherine Von Forelle) is obsessed with summoning vampires, and after buying a mysterious book, she and her three friends finally are successful in doing so.

title: I Am an Addict
description: A self-help guru's show on a public access channel is for one purpose only: to scare viewers out of whatever addiction may be plaguing them.

title: The Night Watchman
description: Jack an ex police agent is now a rookie watchman who is tasked with taking his first night shift at a School of Music. Strange events lead him to believe that it may be haunted but his dark past as a police agent rises during the night.

title: The Shattering
description: Donovan lures several friends into the woods to meet a healer with his cancer-stricken girlfriend. Lucy. As they are hunted by creatures and commandos, the friends realize they were set up to pay for Lucy's cure.

title: A Haunting at Silver Falls
description: An orphaned teen moves in with relatives in Silver Falls, where she finds a mysterious ring and becomes haunted by twin sisters supposedly murdered by their father.

title: Survival of the Dead
description: Zombies have taken over the world, and a ragtag band of soldiers led by Sarge Crockett (Alan Van Sprang) roams the countryside trying to scavenge what they can. Constantly on guard against flesh-eaters, the group is intrigued when they hear of a safe haven on Plum Island. But when they arrive, they find the supposed paradise torn apart by a family feud between the O'Flynns, who want to exterminate all zombies, and the Muldoons, who coexist peacefully with their undead relatives.

title: The Thing on the Doorstep
description: Edward Derby becomes romantically involved with a hypnotist. Later, Daniel, his friend, notices a change in his behaviour and begins to investigate.

title: Lady Belladonna Tales From the Inferno
description: Lady Belladonna offers up another round of suspenseful tales from Pandora's Box, including a vengeful vampire, a misplaced curse, an alien invasion and more tantalizing trips beyond the veil.

title: Bad Kitties
description: The Marcomb County Police Department releases footage of several troubled teenage girls committing violent and disturbing behaviors.

title: Exorcism Of Fleete Marish
description: Many years ago in the Acadian forest, a local sheriff and his oldest friend are forced to perform an exorcism in a remote cabin.

title: Bone Eater
description: A company decides to build a casino on an ancient Indian burial ground and accidentally awakens a demon. Soon, the demon goes on a killing spree, terrorising the small desert community.

title: Cerberus
description: When Jack, an avid gambler, is kidnapped, his sister suspects that his massive debt could be the reason. She travels to Romania to save him but gets involved in a supernatural adventure along the way.

title: The Laughing Mask
description: After his wife and child are murdered by a psychotic killer named the Laughing Mask, Jake Johnson sets out to exact revenge.

title: The Horror Crowd
description: Conversations with the Hollywood horror community that show how creators chose to be involved with the making of horror films and how they support each other with different projects.

title: Ghostfinders
description: A reality show crew has a spooky experience during their stint in a haunted house known to have been abandoned by everyone who ever inhabited it.

title: I Scream on the Beach!
description: In a small seaside town, Emily attempts to discover what happened to her father as her friends start getting picked off one-by-one by an unknown killer.

title: The Mount
description: Bohemian senior Philomena prepares for her favourite night of the year, Halloween, but her solitude is disrupted when four fiendish kids unleash gory chaos on her ageing, run-down mansion.

title: Apparition of Evil
description: A researcher stumbles upon disturbing evidence of supernatural incidents.

title: Intervention
description: An amnesiac suspects that the friends trying to help her recall her memories are hiding the truth about her near fatal accident

title: 3 Hours Till Dead
description: An AWOL soldier (Vladimir Zaric) and his buddies stop at an abandoned farmhouse and encounter the living dead.

title: Atrocity
description: Zach catches his girlfriend cheating on him and faces devastating surprises that escalate into horror. Seven years later a detective reveals that the truth is much worse than anyone feared, because of the most disturbing video ever seen.

title: Dimension Z
description: During a zombie apocalypse, survivors band together to fight for one last chance to survive against evolved zombies.

title: Fresh Hell
description: In the dog days of 2020, a year in which every hour brought a new horror, a group of old friends stumbles across a very different flavour of terror: blood.

title: Dances with Werewolves
description: A paranormal investigator gets caught in a love triangle with a werewolf while trying to help her escape from her master.

title: Matched
description: People expose their deepest desires, obsessions, fears, vulnerabilities, and betrayals through online dating.

title: A Dark Place Inside
description: A man (Chris Dalbey) is driven to commit terrible acts of violence and desecration.

title: La Ciénaga
description: Mecha y Tali son primas que viven con sus maridos e hijos. Cuando sus familias se reúnen en su destartalada casa de campo para pasar los veranos, se descubren varios misterios familiares.

title: 100 años de perdón
description: Cuatro amigos de la infancia de mediana edad deciden robar un banco para poner fin a su desesperada crisis financiera, sólo para descubrir que el banco ya ha quebrado.

title: Dois mais dois
description: Diogo e Emília estão juntos há 16 anos. Eles têm uma filha adolescente e passam por uma fase tediosa. Porém, tudo vira de cabeça para baixo quando descobrem que seus melhores amigos, Ricardo e Bettina, têm um casamento aberto.

title: 2 Mais 2
description: Richard e Bettina convidam Diego e Emilia para aderirem ao seu estilo de vida swinger. O convite desperta desejos adormecidos em Emília, que insiste que devem aceitar o convite.

title: La Celestina
description: Dos sirvientes celosos incriminan a su amo (Penélope Cruz) por el asesinato de una mujer mayor que lo ayudó a ganarse el corazón de su amada (Ángel de Andrés López).

title: Ozzy
description: When Ozzy's family decides to take a vacation, they leave him at a dog's resort that happens to be a front for a pet prison. Realising this, Ozzy and his new friends hatch a daring plan to escape.

title: 100 metros
description: Un español que padece esclerosis múltiple hace todo lo posible para competir en la competición Iron-Man. A pesar de que le dicen que no puede terminar los 100 metros en la carrera, se esfuerza hasta el final.

title: Garota Dourada
description: Um surfista se apaixona por uma garota da praia no paraíso.

title: Dona Helena
description: O filme conta a história da compositora e violeira autodidata Helena Meirelles, natural de Mato Grosso do Sul. Apesar do seu inegável talento, Helena actuou pela primeira vez num palco de teatro aos 67 anos, desafiando a sociedade com o seu estilo de vida.

title: Dalua Downhill
description: O skatista brasileiro Douglas Rodrigues da Silva tenta ser campeão mundial.

title: American Violence
description: A psychologist, Dr Amanda Tyler, studies the mental behaviour of prisoners who are sentenced to death and interacts with Jackson Shea, an inmate. She must decide whether he deserves to live or not.

title: Killer Nightshift
description: Amy begins her first night shift in a hotel with a murderous past. Witnessing terrifying events and trapped within a loop, Amy must find a way to escape the flesh obsessed murderer and save residents of the hotel.

title: Bruiser
description: Henry Creedlow awakens to a nightmare world in which he has no face, features or identity. Stripped of everything he's ever known, he sets out on a bloody rampage to destroy the people who've betrayed him, including his philandering wife, his belittling boss and his evil best friend.

title: Halloween Hell
description: Reality television show contestants vying to win a cash prize must spend Halloween stuck on a set with a demonically possessed doll and a presenter who believes he is Dracula with every second of their ordeal recorded for a pay-per-view audience.

title: A Nova Onda do Apocalipse
description: O mundo sofre uma nova pandemia, uma doença maldita que pode estar em qualquer lugar, com qualquer pessoa. Muito pior que a COVID anos atrás. Para ficar imune do vírus, é necessário ir para um local seguro, o único jeito é ir através de um trem.

title: The Ideal
description: An evil presence at a nearly empty school captures students and teachers in its clutches, blurring the lines between sanity and madness, as well as past and present.

title: Hoodman
description: As a troubled young woman looks for her missing child, an urban legend haunts the small town she resides in. A relentless detective pieces together evidence that leads them both to a suspected killer.

title: Circo Esperança
description: No início da pandemia do coronavírus, o palhaço Nanaca e sua equipe de circenses se veem presos dentro do circo sem poderem fazer o que mais amam, que é levar alegria às pessoas.

title: Amityville Cult
description: After unexpectedly and mysteriously inheriting his estranged grandmother's mansion, Stanley DeFeo finds himself in the small town of Amityville and is surrounded by buried family secrets and a sinister plot against him.

title: The Farm
description: A couple decide to stay at a remote cabin when they run out of fuel during a road trip. When they wake up in the morning, they find themselves locked up in cages by people wearing animal masks.

title: A Paixão de Jacobina
description: Na década de 1870, Jacobina, filha de imigrantes alemães no sul do Brasil, começa a romper com as igrejas católica e luterana para pregar a cura física por meio da limpeza da alma.

title: Hangman
description: The Millers return to their home after a vacation and find out that someone had broken into their house. They continue with their normal lives, unaware of the fact that their lives are in danger.

title: Untitled Horror Movie
description: A comedy about making a horror movie. When six co-stars learn their hit TV show is about to be cancelled, they decide to shoot their own film, unintentionally summoning a spirit with an affinity for violence.

title: Amor Bandido
description: Uma menina abandonada pelo pai vira prostituta e se apaixona por um ladrão que mata suas vítimas.

title: Cannibals and Carpet Fitters
description: Dean and Colin, two working-class carpet fitters, are called on a job in the middle of nowhere by a sweet elderly lady Mrs Hanning. However, the house has its own secrets and the two quickly realise that this maybe the last job they ever go to.

title: Kicking Zombie Ass for Jesus
description: A miracle pill intended to cure disease has unforeseen side effects, turning people into zombies in a small town in Texas.

title: Tim Lopes - Histórias de Arcanjo
description: A trajetória de Arcanjo Antonino Lopes do Nascimento, Tim Lopes. Considerado um dos maiores repórteres investigativos do Brasil, que fez um jornalismo singular e venerado.

title: Ouija Warehouse
description: As some friends prepare a birthday party in a warehouse, Kay and best friend Noah find a Ouija board in a storage room. They try to contact the spirits of the dead, and strange things begin to happen.

title: Luzia Homem
description: Uma cowgirl sul-americana fica presa no meio de uma guerra entre dois irmãos.

title: The Solemn Vow
