description: Dora is a young journalist searching for her missing twin sister. Her investigation leads her to Carol, a mother in need of a caregiver for her son. Pretending to be a nurse, Dora takes the job and begins to search for clues.

title: El Gringo
description: En un intento de escapar de los ataques de los agentes encubiertos, un hombre cruza México con dos millones de dólares. Se encuentra en una situación complicada cuando un cartel de la droga local le pisa los talones.

title: Angela
description: Depois de um rompimento tumultuado e de ser obrigada a abrir mão da guarda dos três filhos, a socialite Angela Diniz conhece Raul e acredita ter encontrado alguém que ama seu espírito livre tanto quanto ela. No entanto, o relacionamento termina em tragédia.

title: Acantilado
description: Después de que algunos miembros de una secta se suicidan en masa en las Islas Canarias, un hermano visita el lugar para buscar a su hermana separada, que era seguidora de la secta.

title: Orca La ballena asesina
description: La muerte de su compañero y su hijo a manos del Capitán Nolan hace que Orca, la orca, se vuelva vengativa y se vuelva loca en el puerto de pescadores para poner en peligro a la comunidad pesquera.

title: 1898, Our Last Men in the Philippines
description: Un batallón español de 50 soldados queda atrapado en una iglesia luchando contra los rebeldes. Aunque algunos de sus hombres mueren y sufren escasez de alimentos, se niegan a rendirse y siguen luchando.

title: La corona partida
description: Juana I de Castilla, hija de Fernando de Aragón, intenta lograr la paz entre dos reinos en guerra para evitar la caída del imperio español a principios del siglo XVI.

title: María (y los demás)
description: Tras la muerte de su madre, María, una mujer de 35 años, se hace cargo de su padre enfermo y de sus hermanos. Sin embargo, la vida de María se derrumba cuando su padre decide casarse con su enfermera.

title: Cien años de perdón
description: El Uruguayo contrata un equipo para realizar un atraco a un banco y robar cajas de seguridad. Mientras las fuertes lluvias amenazan con sabotear su plan, el equipo pronto descubre el motivo oculto del atraco.

title: Dos más dos
description: Dos más dos es una película de comedia sexual mexicana de 2022 dirigida por Alfonso Pineda Ulloa y escrita por Héctor Octavio Valdés Barrientos, Armando Gracia Medina y Patricio Saiz. Protagonizada por Arath de la Torre, Adriana Louvier, Luis Ernesto Franco y Tessa Ía. Es un remake de la película argentina de 2012 2+2

title: Donde caben dos
description: Cinco historias intercaladas brindan un recorrido divertido a través de una noche de sexo y posibilidades en la que nada sale según lo planeado pero todos obtienen lo que necesitan.

title: A Menina do Lado
description: Jornalista casado de meia-idade vai ao balneário de Búzios, no Brasil, para escrever um livro. Aos poucos, ele se apaixona pela filha do vizinho, uma bela adolescente bem mais nova que ele, ignorando as implicações sociais.

title: Divertida Mente 2
description: Alegria, Tristeza, Raiva, Medo e Nojo têm executado uma operação bem-sucedida em todos os sentidos. No entanto, quando a Ansiedade aparece, não têm a certeza de como se sentir.

title: Aprendiz de Espiã: Na Cidade Eterna
description: JJ, um veterano agente da CIA, reúne-se com a sua protegida Sophie, a fim de evitar um esquema nuclear catastrófico dirigido ao Vaticano, que perturba uma viagem do coro de uma escola secundária a Itália.

title: Toy Boy
description: Nikki, ein Obdachloser in den Dreißigern, nutzt sein Aussehen und seine Taktiken, um wohlhabende Frauen zu umwerben. Während er mit Samantha zusammen ist, hat er eine Affäre mit Heather, einer Kellnerin. Samantha erfährt bald von seinem Verrat.

title: Primos
description: Um jovem desenvolve uma atração inesperada por um primo distante que acabou de sair da prisão.

title: O Amor Não Tem Regras
description: A incrível história verídica de um estranho casal judeu que lutou contra as normas sociais do final dos anos 1960 para encontrar a verdadeira felicidade.

title: Esposa de Aluguel
description: Para cumprir o último desejo de sua mãe e evitar ser afastado de seu testamento, um solteirão inflexível contrata uma atriz para interpretar sua noiva e convencer o resto de sua família de que eles estão em um relacionamento.

title: Das Glück an meiner Seite
description: Bec, eine selbstbewusste Studentin, arbeitet als Begleiterin von Kate, bei der eine degenerative Krankheit diagnostiziert wird. Die beiden Frauen entwickeln eine enge Bindung, während sie in der Gesellschaft der anderen wachsen und reifen.

title: Brezeln für den Pott
description: Roland Reuter, ein schwäbischer Geschäftsführer der Bäckereikette Weckle, wird als Filialleiter nach Meiderich bei Duisburg im verlassenen Ruhrgebiet befördert. Seine Frau Sibil, eine Lehrerin, und seine lästige Teenagertochter Lea wollen zumindest vorerst nicht mit ihm umziehen.

title: Gabriela
description: No Brasil da década de 1920, um rico dono de bar turco toma uma mulher como cozinheira e amante. Baseado no romance de Jorge Amado.

title: Tieta of Agreste
description: O regresso de uma mulher exilada (Sónia Braga) à sua aldeia provinciana 26 anos depois provoca especulações e convulsões.

title: Dona Flor and Her Two Husbands
description: Flor, viúva, casa-se com o Dr. Teodoro, um cavalheiro respeitável, após a morte de seu belo mas imprestável marido Vadinho. A hilaridade acontece quando o espírito de Vadinho retorna à sua vida.

title: Orfeu Negro
description: O romance de Orfeu e Eurídice, lenda mítica popular que foi recontada na bela história de amor de um taxista que termina em tragédia, durante o carnaval no Brasil.

title: Beira-Mar
description: Martin e Tomaz viajam ao Brasil para acertar uma herança. Quando estão sozinhos em uma casa à beira-mar, os sentimentos se desenvolvem à medida que exploram a fronteira entre a amizade e o amor.

title: Do Começo ao Fim
description: Ambientado no Brasil, Francisco e seu meio-irmão mais novo, Thomas, são melhores amigos e estranhamente próximos um do outro, para consternação da família. Vários anos depois, a intensidade da infância evoluiu para um relacionamento sexual intenso.

title: Casa Grande
description: Vindo de uma família de elite, um adolescente luta para escapar de seus pais superprotetores. Ao mesmo tempo, sua família também está à beira da falência.

title: Garabandal, solo Dios lo sabe
description: Cuatro niñas que viven en San Sebastián de Garabandal, un pequeño pueblo español, afirman haber visto a María y San Miguel. Cuando la gente de otros pueblos se entera, empiezan a visitar a las niñas.

title: Ein Pferd für Lizzy
description: Lizzy, eine rücksichtslose Teenagerin, wird zu Weihnachten auf die Pferderanch ihrer Großmutter geschickt, wo sie eine starke Bindung zu einem Pony aufbaut und entschlossen ist, das Gehöft vor der Zwangsvollstreckung zu retten.

title: Die Spätzünder
description: Als Rochus „Rocco“ Siwak herausfindet, dass einige Senioren in einem Altersheim schlecht behandelt werden, hilft er ihnen und motiviert sie, ihre Würde wiederzuerlangen und eine Rockband zu gründen.

title: Zu weit weg
description: Ben (11) und Tariq (12) haben mehr gemeinsam, als ihnen bewusst ist. Beide sind neu in der Schule und im Fußball und haben ihre Heimat verloren. Bens Dorf wird bald zu einem offenen Braunkohlebergwerk. Er und seine Familie ziehen in eine nahegelegene Stadt, aber Ben passt sich in seiner neuen Schule nicht ein. Geschikaniert kehrt er heimlich in sein altes, verlassenes Zuhause zurück.

title: Detektiv Wider Willen
description: Nach dem Tod seiner Frau wendet sich Rechtsanwalt Mark Degen vom Bösen zum Guten und beginnt, überwiegend armen Menschen zu helfen. Als seine Tochter, Bezirksstaatsanwältin, ihren ersten Fall verliert, leitet er eine Untersuchung ein.

title: My Tree
description: Filmmaker Jason Sherman embarks on a journey to find the tree that was planted in his name in Israel years earlier. When he discovers that it stands on the remains of a Palestinian village that was destroyed in 1967, he embarks on another journey.

title: L'arbalète
description: Asphalt Warriors alias The Syringe est un film d'action français réalisé par Sergio Gobbi en 1984. Il met en vedette Daniel Auteuil comme personnage principal. L'intrigue raconte des bagarres entre gangs ethniques à Paris.

title: Take This Waltz
description: Margot, a freelance writer, meets an artist named Daniel and is instantly attracted to him despite being married. She then finds herself at crossroads when she starts dreaming of living with him.

title: Aquaman 2 O Reino Perdido
description: Depois de não conseguir derrotar Aquaman pela primeira vez, Arraia Negra exerce o poder do mítico Tridente Negro para libertar uma força antiga e malévola. Na esperança de acabar com o seu reinado de terror, Aquaman forja uma aliança improvável com o seu irmão, Orm, o antigo rei da Atlântida. Deixando de lado as suas diferenças, unem forças para proteger o seu reino e salvar o mundo da destruição irreversível.

title: Gente Grande 2
description: Lenny (Adam Sandler), Eric (Kevin James), Kurt (Chris Rock) e Marcus (David Spade) voltam a morar na mesma cidade. Lá, suas vidas seguem o curso natural dos adultos, seja pela existência dos problemas com as esposas para uns, com os filhos para outros, ou tudo junto e misturado. A coisa dá uma complicada quando os marmanjos pretendiam matar a saudade num dia de folga e acabam encarando os jovens da região, que agora dominam o lugar. É quando eles acabam tendo que enfrentar alguns fantasmas do passado, entre eles a covardia diante de valentões e o famigerado bullyng na escola. Mas algumas surpresas estão para acontecer, como a chegada de um filho rebelde para Marcus domar, uma possível gravidez e uma festa de arromba, que não vai deixar pedra sobre pedra.

title: Gamines
description: Les sœurs Sibylle, Corinne et Georgette vivent avec leur mère célibataire. Sibylle, blonde, se sent souvent isolée et rêve de retrouver son père, qui les a abandonnés.

title: Wolves
description: Wolves 2014... A popular high school student finds himself turned into a dangerous monster after the murder of his parents. When he sets out in search of his true identity, he comes across a shocking revelation.

title: Tráfico humano
description: Depois de matar uma mulher inocente e incapaz de lidar com a culpa, um assassino perambula pela cidade de Ghetto em busca de redenção. As coisas mudam quando ele encontra uma mulher que precisa de sua ajuda.

title: Cinderela Baiana
description: Cinderela Baiana é um filme brasileiro de comédia romântica biográfica semificcionalizada de 1998, dirigido por Conrado Sanchez e produzido por Antônio Polo Galante. É uma biografia fortemente ficcional da dançarina Carla Perez, famosa por ser ex-integrante do grupo de axé É o Tchan!.

title: Hoje Eu Quero Voltar Sozinho
description: Leonardo, um adolescente com deficiência visual, anseia pela independência enquanto lida com uma mãe superprotetora. Mas quando ele conhece Gabriel, sua vida vira de cabeça para baixo à medida que ele se descobre.

title: Being Light
description: After LOVERS and TOO MUCH FLESH, the third part of the trilogy on freedom. The friendship between two men who are separated by everything and who decide to let go of everything. They try to free themselves from their social, professional and cultural constraints.

title: Federal
description: Vital (Carlos Alberto Riccelli), um deputado da Polícia Federal brasileira, lidera uma equipe especial de policiais em busca do traficante internacional Carlos Batista. Vital tem que liderar a equipe de policiais e lidar com suas diferenças para mantê-los concentrados.

title: Meu Amigãozão - O Filme
description: Meu Grande Amigo - O Filme é um filme brasileiro de animação, aventura e fantasia de 2022, dirigido por Andrés Lieban e escrito por Claudia Koogan Breitman e Clive Endersby. A música do filme foi composta por Christiaan Oyens, que gravou a trilha sonora com a Orquestra Filarmônica da Cidade de Praga.

title: O Beijo da Mulher-Aranha
description: Numa cela de prisão em algum lugar da América Latina, dois homens muito diferentes se confrontam com cautela. Molina é visto pela primeira vez enrolando a cabeça em uma toalha, em forma de turbante, enquanto Valentin, barbudo e de aparência classicamente machista, observa com um misto de fascínio e repulsa. Durante o tempo que passam juntos, os dois homens passam a se compreender e respeitar.

title: O Auto da Compadecida
description: João Grilo, um mentiroso patológico, e seu amigo Chico, um covarde, lutam para ganhar a vida, e é quando bolam um plano astuto para resolver seus problemas.

title: Os Trapalhões no Auto da Compadecida
description: Na pequena cidade de Taperoá João Grilo e a confusão de Chicó vivem o cenário, dirigindo-se a um sacristão e a um humilde padeiro. Todos vivem sob os excessos do bispo, do padre e do major. Até um ataque à cidade, todos morrem nas mãos do bandido Severino e devem ser julgados no céu, o que coloca todos diante de Deus e da Virgem Maria.

title: Aquarius
description: Uma incorporadora imobiliária adquire todos os apartamentos da cidade de Recife, Brasil. No entanto, Clara, uma crítica musical aposentada, mantém sua posição e promete morar em sua casa até sua morte.

title: Ovid and the Art of Love
description: The young Ovid finds his life in danger when he clashes with the emperor by writing a guide to love and seduction.

title: Out of Print
description: An exploration of the importance of 35mm exhibitions and revival cinema at places like the New Beverly Cinema, an independent revival cinema in Los Angeles.

title: Imperfections
description: A struggling actress desperate to save money to move to Hollywood, takes a job working as a runner for her mother's boyfriend.

title: Manhattan Romance
description: While filming a documentary about relationships, a man (Tom O'Brien) must decide if he wants to find love with a free-spirited dancer (Caitlin FitzGerald) or his best friend (Katherine Waterston).

title: Eu Te Amo
description: A misteriosa Maria (Sonia Braga) tira o fabricante de sutiãs Paulo (Paulo César Pereio) de seu estilo de vida decadente no Brasil.

title: J'aurais voulu être un danseur
description: Déterminé à devenir danseur de claquettes après avoir regardé « Singin' in the Rain », François quitte sa famille. Cependant, le destin le met face à face avec son père, que l'on croyait mort il y a plusieurs années.

title: The Brass Teapot
description: John and Alice, a couple in their mid-twenties, who are facing grave economic issues at home, find a magical brass teapot. The teapot gives out money every time John and Alice injure themselves.

title: Cash
description: Après que son frère ait été tué par des criminels rivaux, un voleur, Cash, décide de se venger d'eux en rassemblant une équipe de criminels professionnels à cet effet. Mais l’un d’eux est un policier infiltré.

title: Repas de famille
description: Bernard et sa femme décident d'appeler Bruno, son frère et sa femme pour déjeuner. Une folle tournure des événements se produit lorsqu’ils décident d’inviter leur grand-mère pour Noël.

title: Screwed
description: After returning home from the Middle East, a former soldier (James D'Arcy) takes a job as a prison guard and soon realizes that the only thing that separates the guards from their dangerous charges is who holds the keys to the cells.

title: Killshot
description: Carmen Colson et son mari sont placés dans le programme de protection fédérale après avoir été témoins d'un incident choquant.

title: Almighty Zeus
description: When an old Asian man is attacked, a young boxer knocks out the aggressor. This turns him into a viral star and gains the attention of the Middleweight champion, who challenges the young boxer to an unorthodox match during the COVID-19 pandemic.

title: May
description: Una adolescente que sufre un trastorno del desarrollo de la visión se vuelve violenta después de quedar desconsolada por dos relaciones fallidas.

title: Rize
description: El célebre fotógrafo de moda David LaChapelle hace su debut en el cine documental con una película visualmente deslumbrante filmada en las calles del arenoso vecindario South Central de Los Ángeles. Después de que su comunidad fuera casi destruida en los días de violentos disturbios raciales posteriores al veredicto de Rodney King en 1992, el bailarín Tommy "The Clown" Johnson crea una forma cinética y atlética de baile competitivo de hip-hop que él llama payaso, que luego irrumpe en la corriente principal como krumping.

title: Haunted Trail
description: Some college friends receive the surprise of their lives when they discover there is an actual killer on the scene of a local haunted trail.

title: Ginger Snaps 2: Unleashed
description: Bereaved Brigitte relies on a drug to keep her lycanthropy at bay. Mistaken for an addict, she is forced into a rehab clinic for teen girls. Once there she must go to extremes to guarantee her supply continues. Making the situation even more grave is the fact another werewolf is on her trail.

title: Skipped Parts
description: Sam es un adolescente y un aspirante a novelista que está obsesionado con descubrir el único tema que sus autores favoritos se saltan.

title: Rage at Dawn
description: James Barlow, a former secret agent for the Confederacy, joins the infamous Reno brothers by posing as a training robber to investigate and provide information about their crimes.

title: Gods of the Deep
description: A daring mission leads a deep-sea submarine team into a mysterious opening on the ocean floor. They soon uncover a lost underwater world and awaken its ancient race of otherworldly beings.

title: New York, I Love You
description: The lives of a few New York residents have different stories to tell. Mansukhbhai befriends a Hasidic woman, Rifka. Ben meets his match, Molly, but she already has a boyfriend, Garry.

title: The Mysteries of Pittsburgh
description: After graduation, Art Bechstein has to follow a career path according to his gangster father's plan. However, Art decides to enjoy a summer exploring his sexuality before committing to his father.

title: Catchfire
description: Mientras arregla un neumático pinchado, la artista Anne Benton  ve una mafia matando. Ella denuncia el asesinato a la policía local, pero no pueden protegerla de la mafia don Lino Avoca, quien ordena al asesino a sueldo Milo que la localice y la mate. Anne cambia de identidad, se muda a Seattle y construye una nueva vida, mientras Milo, preparándose para su misión, se obsesiona cada vez más con ella. Cuando finalmente encuentra a Anne, Milo necesita decidir cuál será su próximo paso.

title: Dream a Little Dream
description: Un accidente cambia las mentes de un hombre mayor casado (Jason Robards) y un adolescente (Corey Feldman) que persigue a la chica de sus sueños (Meredith Salenger).

title: Turbulence
description: Una azafata debe burlar a un asesino en serie y garantizar el aterrizaje seguro de un avión después de hacerse cargo del avión que transporta a un grupo de prisioneros.

title: Dark Streets
description: The owner of an exclusive nightclub lands in trouble when he runs into debts. At the same time, he is caught up in a love triangle between the club's star singer and the newly recruited chanteuse.

title: Little Monsters
description: Un niño conoce al monstruo que vive debajo de su cama. Incluso se convierte en uno de sus mejores amigos. Pronto el niño descubre un mundo completamente nuevo de diversión y juegos.

title: Children of the Night
description: During the final days of the WWII, British private Jim McLeod is the only survivor of a German ambush. After seeking refuge with a French family, he has more than his personal demons to battle as he finds himself in a web of horror.

title: Wishmaster
description: Alexandra, una gemóloga, encuentra un antiguo ópalo escondido. Sin saberlo, libera a un genio malvado desde dentro, que desea apoderarse del mundo, pero está restringido hasta que su dueño pide tres deseos.

title: The Substitute
description: Jane, una maestra de escuela, es atacada por Juan, líder de una pandilla escolar. Shale, un ex mercenario y prometido de Jane, visita su escuela como maestro sustituto para arreglar las cosas a su manera.

title: Leprechaun 2
description: Un duende malvado reclama como esposa a la descendiente de uno de sus esclavos en su cumpleaños número dos mil. Mata a todos para llegar hasta su novia, pero su novio está a la altura del desafío.

title: Macunaíma
description: Nascido como um homem negro adulto em uma vila na selva brasileira, Macunaíma (Grande Otelo) mais tarde se transforma magicamente em um homem branco (Paulo José) antes de fazer uma viagem cheia de aventuras à cidade de São Paulo. Uma vez lá, ele se torna uma espécie de dândi, apaixonando-se por Ci (Dina Sfat), uma revolucionária que morre em um atentado acidental.

title: Lixo Extraordinário
description: Localizado nos arredores do Rio de Janeiro, o Jardim Gramacho, no Brasil, é o maior aterro de lixo do mundo. O artista moderno Vik Muniz trabalha com os chamados catadores, homens e mulheres que catam o lixo, para criar arte a partir de materiais reciclados.

title: 7 Prisioneiros
description: Para proporcionar uma vida melhor para sua família no país, Mateus, de 18 anos, aceita um emprego em um ferro-velho em São Paulo para seu novo chefe, Luca, mas fica preso no perigoso mundo do tráfico de pessoas.

title: Fala Comigo
description: Um estudante do ensino médio de 17 anos que gosta de fazer ligações anônimas para os pacientes de sua mãe psicanalista conhece uma divorciada de 43 anos.

title: Nosso Lar 2 : Os Mensageiros
description: Nosso Lar 2 : Os Mensageiros, comumente conhecido como Nosso Lar 2, é um drama brasileiro de 2024, escrito e dirigido por Wagner de Assis, lançado em 25 de janeiro de 2024.

title: Eu Não Faço a Menor Ideia do Que Eu Tô Fazendo Com a Minha Vida
description: Eu Não Faço a Menor Ideia do que eu Tô Fazendo Com a Minha Vida is a 2012 Brazilian comedy-drama film directed by Matheus Souza. The film opened the competitive exhibition at the 40th Gramado Film Festival.

title: Copper Bill
description: Two thieves attempt to steal $80 million of hidden drug money from the ranch belonging to a dead member of the Cowboy Mafia.

title: The Martyr Maker
description: Zahid is a Muslim, born and living in the United States. After struggling with his Islamic roots, he begins to take advantage of all the aspects of his religion, but getting to know his ancestry is not as easy as he thinks.

title: Bug
description: A 12-year-old discovers that her grandfather, the town sheriff, may have once committed a racially motivated murder.

title: Os Famosos e os Duendes da Morte
description: Numa cidade rural do sul do Brasil, um adolescente chamado Sr. Tambourine passa o tempo navegando na internet e fumando maconha com seu melhor amigo, Diego, enquanto sonha em fugir de casa e assistir a um show de Bob Dylan.

title: O Maior Amor do Mundo
description: Um astrofísico em estado terminal (José Wilker) retorna ao Brasil em busca de sua mãe biológica.

title: Chega de Saudade
description: Os clientes (Tônia Carrero, Leonardo Villar, Stepan Nercessian) de um salão de dança em São Paulo, Brasil, buscam companheirismo e amor.

title: Eu Não Quero Voltar Sozinho
description: Não Quero Voltar Sozinho é um curta-metragem brasileiro de 2010 dirigido por Daniel Ribeiro. O curta ganhou o Prêmio Iris 2011. Posteriormente, foi expandido para o longa-metragem de Ribeiro de 2014, The Way He Looks.

title: Bellini e o Dêmonio
description: Um detetive (Fábio Assunção) em São Paulo investiga uma série de assassinatos que estão ligados a um livro específico.

title: O Xangô de Baker Street
description: Sarah Bernhardt pede ao Imperador Pedro II que ligue para Sherlock Holmes e o Doutor Watson para encontrar seu violino desaparecido. No entanto, eles descobrem que um assassinato está ligado ao violino desaparecido.

title: Pobre Familia Rica
description: Después de ganarse la lotería hace 15 años, Tino y su familia empiezan a tener problemas económicos. Tino le pide ayuda a su vecino, pero este también tiene sus propios problemas.

title: El secreto de la calabaza mágica
description: Un niño aprende el significado del trabajo después de que una calabaza mágica le concede todo lo que quiere.

title: Mi pobre angelito 2
description: Kevin aborda accidentalmente un vuelo a la ciudad de Nueva York y se separa de su familia que se dirige a Miami. Luego se topa con dos de sus viejos enemigos, que planean robar una juguetería.

title: Un gallo con muchos huevos
description: Cuando el joven Toto, el enano de la camada, se entera de que su casa está siendo vendida porque su familia se enfrenta a la quiebra, decide luchar contra el gallo campeón de boxeo Bankivoide para salvar su casa.

title: Estación Zombie
description: Seok-woo y su hija van en tren a Busan el día del cumpleaños de este último para ver a su esposa. Sin embargo, el viaje se convierte en una pesadilla cuando quedan atrapados en medio de un brote zombi en Corea del Sur.

title: Aves de Presa
description: Después de ser arrojada a la calle por Joker, Harley lucha por levantarse. Sin embargo, Harley se une a Huntress, Black Canary y Renee Montoya para derrotar a un gángster y proteger a una niña.

title: Baile urbano
description: El hermano de DJ Williams, Duron, es asesinado por el líder de su equipo de baile rival. Como resultado, se muda a Georgia y se une al esfuerzo de su fraternidad para ganar una competencia de baile.

title: Cómo matar a un esposo muerto
description: Una mujer se ve obligada a afrontar todas las dificultades que implica poner fin a su relación con un hombre poderoso y arrogante. Exasperada, decide arruinar la vida de su marido y padre de sus hijos, incluso después de su muerte.

title: Hansel y Gretel: cazadores de brujas
description: Hansel y Gretel son cazarrecompensas que se ganan la vida persiguiendo brujas. Tienen la tarea de rescatar a los niños que han sido secuestrados por brujas para ser sacrificados en la noche de Luna de Sangre.

title: Casper Meets Wendy
description: After drawing the ire of a nefarious warlock named Desmond (George Hamilton), Wendy the Good Little Witch (Hilary Duff) and her aunts seek sanctuary in a special resort that caters to the supernatural. There, Wendy meets Casper the Friendly Ghost (Jeremy Foley), who is vacationing with his quarrelsome uncles. Despite their families' prejudiced warnings, Wendy and Casper become fast friends.

title: Passport to Love
description: Travel blogger Nicole meets Kade, a competing magazine rep while travelling abroad. When Kade's boss tasks him with buying her out, he struggles between doing his job and his growing feelings for Nicole.

title: Mythica: Stormbound
description: Years after Szorlok's devastation and the Red Thorns' victory, a new evil will threaten the world and new heroes will rise to fight it

title: The Way Back Home
description: New York attorney Spencer Krane pays a visit to his grandmother, after she suffers from a heart attack. But what starts as a simple visit becomes more about learning the importance of faith.

title: Fitful: The Lost Director's Cut
description: Paula, an inspector of the Historic Trust, visits an abandoned ship on a desolate waterfront and meets the unusual, self-appointed caretaker of the vessel, Vigs. From the outset, Paula's world is transformed into a fitful nightmare.

title: The Deliverance of Amy Stronghold
description: Amy Stronghold, a homeless hustler, must get off the streets, hold a job, move to the strange land of suburbia and find God before her daughter is lost to her forever.

title: In A Silent World
description: Musician Marshall Lawrence and his wife Terry, a communication professor, were excited to welcome newborn Rachel into their world. But because of Rachel's deafness, they had to enter hers instead.

title: The Printing
description: Prior to the fall of communism in the Soviet Union, a group of people defies edicts by illegally printing Bibles.

title: The Insanity of God
description: Based on the best selling book by Nik Ripken, The Insanity of God is the personal and lifelong journey of an ordinary couple from rural Kentucky who thought they were going on just your ordinary missionary pilgrimage, but discovered it would be anything but. After spending over six hard years doing relief work in Somalia, and experiencing life where it looked like God had turned away completely and He was clueless about the tragedies of life.

title: The Dirty 30
description: The Dirty 30 follows 29 year-old Ricky Simmons (Sean Riggs) whose ex, Lisa, walked out on him with no explanation and broke his heart. Reeling from this crushing blow with no closure, Ricky's best friend Jessy (Giovanni Watson) pressure him to enter the dating world again.

title: Act of Faith
description: Mr. Brady and the staff at his diner become a tight-knit family after his wife dies. When life challenges the small family, they come together and persevere with help from a higher power

title: Pastor's Daughters
description: A pastor brings up his daughter with good family values. However, he is taken by surprise when he learns that his daughter has been corrupted by her friends.

title: The Red Effect
description: Tensions rise in a Washington D.C. community after police shoot an unarmed black teenager.

title: Sugar!
description: A middle-aged housewife and piano teacher (Alice Ripley) decides to finally pursue her dream of becoming a rock 'n' roll singer much to the embarrassment of her politician husband (Robert Clohessy) and her teenage daughter (Leah Barker).

title: Free Birds
description: Two turkeys, who despise each other, leave their differences aside and team up to travel to the past in an attempt to withdraw turkeys from the Thanksgiving menu.

title: Hero of the Underworld
description: Dylan, the overnight manager of a chic hotel, is also hiding a dark drug problem. One night, when a woman is beaten nearly to death in his hotel, Dylan takes it upon himself to become a saviour.

title: Murder in A College Town
description: Bobby Earl, a young collegian, loses his way after being influenced by his ambitious roommate Tom Stahl. His criminal choices lead him to a tragic end.

title: Silent Witness
description: A hotshot attorney is dragged back to his hometown to defend an old friend from a murder charge, but soon begins to distrust his innocence.

title: Pirates Parody
description: This electrifying, swashbuckling sex-adventure takes you on a humorous and mystical journey through haunted seas and deep into the abyss of our most lustful desires. The biggest epic in the history of adult films.

title: Christmas in the Highlands
description: When Blair, a sales manager from New York, is sent to a remote area in the Scottish Highlands to get hold of a special perfume, she ends up falling in love with a nobleman.

title: Once Upon a Wedding
description: The engaged daughter of a dictator falls for a poor fisherman she struck with her car while nursing him back to health.

title: The Golden Voices
description: The Golden Voices Competition will be at Terrell Christian College this year, but they don't have a choir. The Assistant Dean forces the head of the music department to put together a choir or lose her job.

title: A Nashville Wish
description: A country music singer dreams of dating a popular cheerleader and going to Nashville, Tenn., to become a star. As fate would have it, his career takes off at the same time as their relationship, but she doesn't share his love of music.

title: The Last Passport
description: The Last Passport is an uplifting, inspiring drama about a mysterious old man who enters a magical passport office. George meets characters from all walks of life, dispensing his homespun wisdom as they slip in and out of the lines.

title: Cranberry Christmas
description: A separated couple feign marital bliss on national television to help their town's Christmas festival and their business, but rekindled love is complicated by new opportunities.

title: Férias Trocadas
description: José Eduardo, conocido como Zé, es dueño de una pequeña escuela de fútbol y gana un viaje con su esposa y su hija bloguera a Cartagena en un sorteo. José Eduardo, conocido como Edu, es un empresario exitoso que se va de vacaciones con su esposa y su hijo. La confusión comienza cuando, por error, Zé se aloja en el lujoso hotel de Edu, que, a su vez, termina en la sencilla posada de Zé. Este intercambio proporciona experiencias a las que las dos familias no estaban acostumbradas, pero que termina uniéndolos aún más.

title: Killer Bean Forever
description: Top-notch assassin Killer Bean is called upon to clean-up the mess when things go bad. With Detective Cromwell stuck between him and the head of a mob, Killer Bean learns that he is the next target.

title: RAMABANAM
description: Vicky runs away from home after having a disagreement with his brother Rajaram and goes on to become a known gangster. Years later when he returns, the two polar opposite brothers reunite.

title: The Elf
description: Nick is haunted by night terrors stemming from a tragic murder he saw when he was young. After inheriting an old toy shop, he discovers a cursed elf doll sealed inside an ancient chest with a naughty list of his family's names written on it. He soon discovers that the elf was an evil conduit meant to unleash a supernatural killing spree during the Christmas Holidays by whomever set it free.

title: Seize the Night
description: Over the course of one night, a whirlwind romance between a drug dealer and a mysterious singer takes them on a collision course with a dangerous mind-control drug through the Los Angeles underground scene.

title: The Other Side
description: Which side will you choose when evil takes over...

title: Hearts & Vines
description: A builder and decorator on a home renovation show end up quarantined during the holidays in the home they are renovating.

title: ElemenTory
description: Following the disappearance of their son, a couple joins other parents whose children have gone missing from school. Frustrated by the lack of progress they take control of the school looking for answers.

title: The Nothing Man
description: A unstable war veteran with a troubled past reconnects with an old army buddy with tragic results.

title: Enchanting Christmas
description: A father's ice sculpture of a princess magically comes to life, causing unexpected disruptions in the lives of those she meets.

title: Elfette Saves Christmas
description: Elfette has to save the day when Santa Claus is kidnapped by the mafia, who try to take over Christmas.

title: Spirit of Friendship
description: A touching family tale that follows little Billy as he sets out on a mission to speak with his mother in the afterlife while he is still coming to terms with her passing.

title: For Prophet
description: A struggling entrepreneur encounters the Archangel Raphael, who reveals that he is chosen by 'The Most High God' to be a part-time prophet, tasking him to save his crumbling and corrupt hometown.

title: A culpa é das estrelas
description: A vida da adolescente Hazel Grace muda quando conhece Augustus Waters num grupo de apoio ao cancro. Os dois embarcam então numa viagem de mudança de vida que os aproxima ainda mais.

title: A Holiday Homecoming
description: The residents of Hope, NY come to the aid of displaced foster children after St. Jerome's Home for Children has a fire right before Christmas, and many families find the foster children complete their homes.

title: Displacement
description: A young woman who suffers from short-term memory loss must find a way to reverse quantum time anomaly and get to the bottom of her boyfriend's murder.

title: Little Women
description: Time, ambition and the pursuit of happiness define and mould the March sisters as they face various challenges at the cusp of womanhood.

title: Demise
description: One lie destroys the lives of many, while one's obsession leads to the demise of a rising star in the fashion world.

title: Café
description: A tragedy strikes a community surrounding a cafe in West Philadelphia, forcing the cafe's regulars to realize how intertwined their lives have become.

title: Death Valley
description: Two hired guns who are commissioned to rescue an imprisoned scientist from a secret facility are hunted down by a terrifying creature of unknown origin.

title: Arctic Blast
description: A US research vessel gets shipwrecked in Australia, leaving its entire crew of 15 dead. Soon, a cold wind sweeps across the planet due to a solar eclipse and wreaks havoc everywhere.

title: Kaw
description: A throng of bloodthirsty ravens invade a little town and start attacking the locals. Meanwhile, Sheriff Wayne and his wife try to save the townspeople from the clutches of the ferocious scavengers.

title: Parents for Christmas
description: Two orphan girls are left rejected and without a family. Their only wish is for parents and now they are the only two remaining at the children's home. They are joined by a new troubled child for the holidays that will bring more naughty than nice to the home. The director of the children's home decides to cheer them up with a visit to a farm. The visit will not just be for the children but for his secret crush.

title: Small Town Santa
description: Rockford Sheriff Rick Langston arrests an elderly intruder who claims to be Santa Claus. His life takes many pleasant turns and makes him believe in the holiday spirit.

title: Who Will Move the Stone
description: Detroit attorney David Keller is no stranger to high-stakes cases, defending some of the most dangerous people with unmatched precision and grit. But when he decides to take the case of a born-again Christian he represented years prior, who is accused of murdering a Catholic priest, the trial becomes more about faith in God than it does about Keller getting his Marquee acquittal.

title: The Christmas Room
description: Grace shares a special bond with her granddad during the holidays. When she returns home for Christmas, she discovers it's not what she expected. As she readjusts to her family's routines, she notices her granddad's declining health is being overlooked. After witnessing symptoms of memory loss, Grace becomes determined to get him the help he needs.

title: Something Good Coming
description: Two grocery store workers from different districts meet and end up spending time with each other over a weekend after the store they are assigned to open in another town shuts down unexpectedly.

title: Merry Birthday, Happy Christmas
description: Best friends Sarah and Kevin are reunited when Kevin returns to their hometown after finishing veterinary school. With Sarah's marketing help, the grand opening of Kevin's new practice is a success, and they fall back into the easy friendship they have always shared. But when Sarah's boss shows a romantic interest in Kevin, Sarah realizes that she may have deeper feelings for him and wonders if Kevin shares those feelings.

title: This Train
description: Fading rock star Ricky "Hellcat" Heller returns home after disappearing for three years following the death of his teenage son. Shunned by the town and his estranged wife, he believes he's better off dead until he's reintroduced to his son's troubled best friend. Ricky desperately seeks to right his wrongs and provide support.

title: A Fireman For Christmas
description: Sparks fly between a woman and a firefighter when she returns home to Holly, Michigan, to plan her best friend's wedding

title: Civil Christmas
description: During the Civil War, a wounded Union soldier falls in love with a Southern woman while taking refuge in her cabin on Christmas Eve.

title: December Horses
description: A young woman who is struggling with her failing vision receives a blind horse for Christmas; her mother hires a trainer, who will not only teach the girl how to take care of her new horse, but how to move forward in life with a disability.

title: Grace of the Father
description: A man remains steadfast in his faith, although his family is tested with trials that would tear most families apart. His eldest son, Jacob sets out on his own only to find his Father waiting with open arms on his return.

title: Bumbling Ballerina
description: Adults struggle with their abusive past lives as foster children at the hands of a monster. Amidst this, a girl dreams of being a ballerina and strives to clear her friend of wrongful charges for murdering their foster mother.

title: Core
description: Abby knows the world is not fair enough to let her good fortune fall on her lap, so she works hard and takes pride in her success...until it all comes crashing down one Monday morning. Abby tries to build herself back up in an unforgiving world and rediscovers a relationship she has neglected for far too long.

title: Southern Gospel
description: Given a second chance, a rebellious rock star follows in his father's footsteps and becomes a preacher. However, his desire to share a message of forgiveness gets tested at every turn.

title: Never Give Up
description: Twenty-year-old Brad Minns does the impossible in the 1985 Deaf World Games, winning the gold medal in the men's singles tennis finals after a five-hour match.

title: Luminous
description: The story of the first astronomer to publicly predict the near-future explosion of a star.

title: Fear Falls
description: After her grandmother is mysteriously murdered, a young girl uncovers a secret about her family's farm.

title: Church of Darkness
description: A devout Christian teen boy moves to a new town and discovers a sinister underground society flourishing under the protection of the mayor. When he learns of their evil plans and sacrificing rituals, he tries to save them all, but it may be too late.

title: Vincent's Vow
description: After the tragic loss of a love, Vincent Lovell buries his pain through multiple relationships. When he meets Lena Carlyle, he begins to discover the emotions he was protecting himself against are the very things keeping him from finding happiness.

title: Mary 4 Mayor
description: Eighteen-year-old Mary Parson contests for the mayor's role to retaliate against her estranged father, the current mayor. But her motive changes when she detects the town's common woes.

title: A Birder's Guide to Everything
description: Fifteen-year-old David Portnoy is a birder who is convinced he has discovered a rare duck species. He and his friends go on a road trip on the eve of his father's wedding to search for this duck.

title: To Joey With Love
description: Telling the story of singers Joey and Rory Feek as they document the birth of their daughter and Joey's battle with cancer.

title: Critical Assignment
description: While journalist Michael Power is writing an article on the African water shortage, he uncovers links with government corruption and the international arms trade and will stop at nothing to unmask the perpetrators. Soon he's in danger as the links go right to the very top.

title: Miracle Maker
description: It all starts with one little seed of love."The Miracle Maker is coming!" Everyone in the tiny hamlet is excited when they hear the news that the renowned man of wonders is coming to their village. But the humble traveler who appears isn't what anyone expected.

title: By Appointment Only
description: Recently widowed, Val Spencer is struggling to raise her 14-year-old son and embarking on a career in real estate. When she gets the listing for a multi-million dollar home, her hopes for a quick sale are interrupted when the owner disappears and someone claiming to be his nephew appears at the house. Little does she realise that this man has dangerous plans of his own. Will Val be able to find the evidence that will expose him?

title: Our Wild Hearts
description: Willow, an independent young woman from Malibu, determined to meet her biological father, encounters him in the Sierra Nevada mountain range. As she bonds with him, she is fascinated by a mustang.

title: Egg
description: When Tina, a conceptual artist, introduces her heavily-pregnant friend, Karen, to the quirky and odd woman who is her surrogate, many patriarchal attitudes and truths stumble out of the closet.

title: Miss Arizona
description: Bored with her life, Rose, a former beauty queen, decides to teach a life skills class to a group of uninterested women which changes her life.

title: From Time to Time
description: A thirteen-year-old boy realizes that he can travel through time and begins an adventure that unlocks family secrets laid buried for generations.

title: The Ron Clark Story
description: A restless but gifted young teacher leaves his home in North Carolina to seek adventure and a job in the bright lights and tough schools of New York City. Will he make the difference he dreams of ?

title: The Pharmacist
description: When a drug-dealing pharmacist quits dealing when he falls in love with a woman who wants nothing to do with drugs. But when a psychotic killer informs the pharmacist that they are now business partners, quitting is no longer an option.

title: One Week : The Connection
description: One Week The Connection”, starring Andrea Spruill takes viewers on a thrilling journey into the heart of a small town gripped by an unsettling mystery. The story revolves around a military veteran suffering from PTSD.

title: un extraño en sugarcreek
description: Micah, un jugador de béisbol, y su hijo pequeño huyen a una comunidad Amish para evitar el ataque de los medios después del asesinato de su esposa. Como viven y trabajan allí bajo alias, una mujer policía sospecha de ellos.

title: Rec
description: Una reportera de televisión y su camarógrafo registran el horrible brote de una enfermedad que convierte a los humanos en feroces caníbales.

title: Los lunes al sol
description: Vigo, una ciudad portuaria de España, atraviesa tiempos difíciles. La industria de la construcción naval, que era una fuente primaria de empleo, ha despedido a muchos trabajadores. Varios de estos antiguos constructores navales pasan su nuevo tiempo libre en un bar local propiedad de su amigo Rico (Joaquín Climent).

title: Camino
description: Camino sufre una enfermedad mortal y se ve obligado a someterse a tratamientos insoportables. Desafortunadamente, su madre sigue una organización católica que cree que su sufrimiento es el plan de Dios.

title: The Secret Life of Words
description: Durante unas vacaciones forzadas, Hanna, una trabajadora de una fábrica con problemas de audición y una persona solitaria, acepta un trabajo temporal de enfermería para un hombre que resultó gravemente herido en un accidente en una plataforma petrolera.

title: Celda 211
description: "Un nuevo funcionario de prisiones se encuentra en el centro de un motín carcelario debido a acontecimientos desafortunados. Se hace pasar por un prisionero y se asocia con el líder del motín para tomar el control de la situación. "

title: El orfanato
description: Laura y su familia se mudan a lo que solía ser su antiguo orfanato. Pronto, su hijo adoptivo, Simon, le dice que tiene cinco amigos invisibles. Pero sus juegos aparentemente inocentes dan un giro desagradable.

title: Jaime
description: Desesperado para reunir seus pais, um menino tenta procurar a motocicleta roubada de seu pai, presumindo que tudo ficará bem. Então ele decide ganhar dinheiro suficiente para comprar uma motocicleta nova.

title: Aparelho Voador a Baixa Altitude
description: É o futuro e a humanidade está morrendo. As mulheres dão à luz mutantes que o governo totalitário as obriga a abortar. Com a população a diminuir por toda a Europa, Laura (Margarida Marinho) está grávida pela sétima vez, mas está determinada a não fazer o sétimo aborto.

title: A Comédia de Deus
description: Um vendedor de sorvetes (João César Monteiro) cobiça as funcionárias de sua loja.

title: Um Tiro no Escuro
description: Verônica (Vanessa Machado) nem sempre foi uma stripper amarga e irritada. Há apenas dois anos, ela era uma jovem mãe esperançosa e com uma linda menina. Mas depois que sua filha foi arrancada dela em um aeroporto no Rio de Janeiro, ela recorreu ao pole dancing para se sustentar. É uma vida cansativa e Veronica quer sair.

title: Uma Patricinha de Outro Mundo
description: Amber, uma colegial má, mas popular, morre acidentalmente. Ela tem uma semana para ajudar a aluna menos impopular de sua escola a se tornar Rainha do Baile, ou então ela será enviada para o Inferno.
في ليلة دامية في مكان من المفترض أن نشعر فيه بالأمان، يكافح شاب وحبيبته ليس للوصول إلى المستشفى، بل للهروب منه. يحاولان البقاء على قيد الحياة طوال الليل.

title: Das Leben der Anderen
description: 1984 überwacht ein Agent der Geheimpolizei in Ostdeutschland einen Schriftsteller und seine Geliebte. Anschließend stellt der Agent fest, dass er sich zunehmend für ihr Leben interessiert.

title: 500 días con ella
description: Tom revive el año que compartió con Summer, la chica con la que pensó que podría pasar el resto de su vida. Ella, en cambio, no cree en las relaciones ni en los novios.

title: For Love Or Money
description: When a single girl falls for a handsome real estate mogul, she must determine if he's in it for love or if she is his latest investment project.

title: Tripla Ameaça
description: Um grupo de assassinos profissionais planeja matar a filha de um bilionário que está mirando um sindicato do crime. Outro grupo de homens tenta protegê-la.

title: Rush Hour 2
description: While Detective James Carter and Chief Inspector Lee are vacationing in Hong Kong, a bomb explosion at the US Consulate kills two undercover customs agents. Soon, Lee is assigned to solve the case.

title: All Girls Weekend
description: High school friends reunite after many years to spend a weekend in the mountains, but when everything goes wrong, there is no time for girl bonding.

title: Man vs. Bigfoot
description: After his brother goes missing on a hiking trail, Jack Rollins goes in search of him but in doing so, Jack soon finds himself in a game of cat and mouse with a creature thought only to be legend.

title: Robot
description: A brilliant scientist creates a humanoid robot to protect mankind, but things go awry when human emotions are programmed and inner turmoil causes the robot to switch sides.

title: Magic in Mount Holly
description: A new gallery owner discovers that she can paint the future using a paintbrush left by Santa. As she discovers the true magic within herself, she also learns to love and be more confident.

title: Quicksand
description: Follows a married couple almost divorcing who become trapped in quicksand while hiking through a rainforest in Colombia. They will battle the elements of the jungle and must work together in order to survive.

title: Finding Christmas
description: On Christmas Eve, a rebellious teen takes a treacherous journey to learn the meaning of Christmas, sacrifice and true love.

title: Christmas at Xander Point
description: Pastor Ian Sullivan and his wife Dr. Colleen Sullivan find out the Xander Lighthouse will be torn down. Colleen tries to keep Jacob (a war veteran believed to be KIA and her patient) secret.

title: My Private Line to God
description: Joy believes her birthday gift from Auntie Kay holds a divine power, a direct line to God, activated when two or more gather in his name.

title: The Day You Found Me
description: The passing of time does not diminish the childhood connection of two friends, a young boy and a girl, who were bound by a promise. Life has been challenging yet successful and full for both, yet neither gave up the search for the other.

title: Joy of Horses
description: After suffering a loss of someone close to her, Joy moves to a new state and must encounter new people, new experiences, and a love triangle. When she reunites with someone from her past, things get complicated.

title: Summer Rain
description: The alluring sounds of violin music bring back memories that reunite a father and daughter separated at birth. Though neither realized what had happened in the past, they were drawn to each other unmistakably when they do meet.

title: Hero
description: Hoping to reconnect with his son, a man forms a baseball team which helps the town transform into a connected community.

title: Stray
description: A dangerous serial killer decides to settle down and start a family in a small town. When she finally finds the right man, he will help her out whether he wants to or not.

title: The Afterglow
description: Oliver, a writer, hides a sinister childhood encounter. When he meets Olivia, an enigmatic girl trying to recover her memories after trying to kill herself, their secrets threaten to destroy them both.

title: Dog Park
description: Nick isn't lucky in love until he takes his self-centred ex-girlfriend's dog to a dog park, where he attracts the attention of a spirited young woman who soon becomes the envy of his jealous ex.

title: Draupadi Unleashed
description: A young woman seeks an identity of her own while battling an arranged marriage and the manipulations of a powerful guru in 1930s India.

title: A Devil's Game
description: When a gang's drug supply runs dry and the collectors make threats, the men start dealing in girls. The plan quickly goes to hell when they unknowingly kidnap the daughter of a retired black-ops agent.

title: Out Past Dark
description: Gregory and Matilda embark on a weekend getaway to the quaint village of Chama, New Mexico, intending to determining whether they will return home together as a couple; as their toxicity intermixes with the folklore of the town, they soon find themselves entangled in the enigmatic events unfolding in the town.

title: Christmas Dreams
description: A poor but talented little drummer boy seeks to win the friendship of the pretty girl he knows from the playground.

title: Einstein's God Model
description: A man embarks on a quest to do the impossible and contact the afterlife with help from a physicist, a blind medium and Thomas Edison's final experiment. If he is to be successful, he must defy the laws of quantum physics and nature.

title: Heroes Don't Come Home
description: A promise made after September 11th is broken, forcing two Maine friends to confront who they once were and who they've become.

title: How to Beat a Bully
description: Cory falls prey to the school bullies when he moves to a new city. He tackles them by spreading a rumour that his father is a hitman for the mafia, which later backfires.

title: Miles To Go
description: A rock bottom junkie trades a needle for a gun and sparks an explosive conflict with the local cartel, when you've lost the will to live, you ain't afraid to die.

title: Sinatra Club
description: In 1972 an ambitious young mobster named John Gotti (Danny Nucci) plans to steal silver bullion using people of warring crime families.

title: Confused by Love
description: A reclusive author and his socialite wife invite their rich friend and a former girlfriend to stay with them, to save their home from foreclosure.

title: Blur Circle
description: A single mother (Cora Vander Broek), still grieving the loss of her young son who disappeared two years earlier, meets a man (Matthew Brumlow) with a shrouded past while following up on a lead.

title: Aquarians
description: A young man enrolled in a seminary tries to reconnect with his estranged, drug-peddling brother, forcing both of them to face their inner demons.

title: Broken Ceiling
description: When Angela Walker is passed over for yet another promotion, she decides she's going to have to break through the invisible corporate barriers once and for all.

title: Druid Peak
description: A troubled teen is sent to live with his estranged father, where he develops a bond with a pack of wolves in a park.

title: The Storyteller
description: Abby, a young girl, is accompanied by an invisible fairy as she tries to run away from her past. Soon, her magic sparks a series of events that brings joy to her broken family.

title: Idled
description: Val relives his memories with Mickey as he travels to see his brother.

title: Live Fast Live Free
description: A singer in a rock 'n' roll band tells his new girlfriend that he has cancer.

title: Fray
description: Recently returned from combat, a young Marine tries to find meaning in his civilian life. Baring the physical and emotional scars of war, he struggles to make it in a time of national economic strife.

title: The Ghost of Winifred Meeks
description: A successful writer rents a remote farmhouse in England to begin work on the latest of a series of teen crime novels, when her idyll becomes unsettled by the spirit of Winifred Meeks.

title: Kecksburg
description: Inspired by the real life events of Dec. 9, 1965, a reporter investigates a mysterious crash and uncovers a massive government conspiracy.

title: BOONE: The Vengeance Trail
description: Boone: The Vengeance Trail is a modern-day retelling of the true Daniel Boone story and was shot entirely on location in Boone's home state of Kentucky.

title: Vatos Locos 2
description: Mickey, born near El Piño, a veteran of the streets, finds that his past finally caught up to him when his family is literally slaughtered in front of his eyes. Mickey enlists a beautiful, mysterious nun (Paz De La Huerta) who secretly is a mercenary for hire. She obtains info after personally placing a hit on the Chinese mob who gunned down Mickey's Chicano family on the streets of East L.A. Mickey gets busted for the crime with no way out until a brilliant attorney (Angus Mcafayden) finds a way to make a deal that the prosecutors cannot refuse. Death to their own family.

title: Welcome to the Men's Group
description: As a men's support group descends into chaos when one member appears to be headed for a breakdown, some long-standing resentments and secrets threaten the trust between the men.

title: My Saviour
description: A lonely housewife becomes the victim of a gang attack, after which she feels she has nothing left in life and desperately wishes for someone to come save her.

title: Northern Shade
description: Army veteran Justin McLaughlin comes out of isolation when his younger brother Charlie goes missing. Teaming up with private investigator Frankie, Justin discovers his brother's been recruited by an extremist militia.

title: A Bennett Song Holiday
description: The Bennett-Song clan faces a crisis when the community school is on the brink of closure. To raise funds for the centre, everyone comes together and understands the true spirit of the holidays.

title: Pemukiman Setan
description: "Pemukiman Setan" (Demon Settlement) is a horror film that attempts to blend supernatural horror with psychological tension. The story follows a group of people who move into a seemingly abandoned village, only to discover that it's haunted by dark forces.

title: The Toybox
description: Jennifer, her husband and their relatives go on a trip in an RV. When it stops working in the middle of a desert, they realise that the car is haunted by a supernatural entity.

title: Deck The Heart
description: When an EVP inherits a manor, he's expected to host his family for Christmas. Since he doesn't have time or Christmas spirit, he hires an event planner. As Merry decorates and plans, she wins him over and helps him love Christmas again.

title: The Lady of the Lake
description: A grief-stricken Native American woman investigates the legend of the Lady of the Lake, determined to unravel its mysteries after her brother's tragic demise.

title: The Etruscan Smile
description: Rory MacNeil, a rugged old Scotsman, reluctantly leaves the comforts of his home to seek medical treatment in San Francisco. His life changes unexpectedly after he moves in with his estranged son.

title: Estación Zombie
description: Seok-woo e sua filha estão em um trem para Busan no aniversário deste último para ver sua esposa. No entanto, a viagem se transforma em um pesadelo quando eles ficam presos em meio a um surto de zumbis na Coreia do Sul.

title: A Bailarina
description: Na França do século XIX, Felicie, uma aspirante a bailarina, escapa do orfanato junto com seu melhor amigo, Victor, um jovem inventor. Ela logo se torna aluna de uma prestigiosa casa de ópera.

title: Pretty Crazy
description: A successful, handsome, eligible bachelor is ready to find the one to settle down and build a future with. He meets and falls for the perfect girl, but will his past come back to ruin his chances of them building their lives together?

title: Santa's Squad
description: An unemployed art teacher must accept a job with the Santa Squad in an effort to help a widower and his two precious daughters rediscover the magic of Christmas.

title: It's Christmas, Eve
description: A woman is given the hard task of shutting down a school's music department. However, she uses her friend's husband's help to open a website for donations for the music teacher and his students.

title: Fuel
description: Fuel is the story of a young man's struggle to save his girl from an abusive environment. Emilio discovers that he has the ability to run incredibly fast. With the hope of a scholarship, he sees an opportunity to be able to leave his hometown, along with all his troubles, and take Sandy with him. But a tragic flaw, a violent streak he possesses, induced by exposure to gasoline vapors, will all but destroy his best-laid plans. Emilio's hopes race through his heart, not like blood, but like fuel.

title: El Coyote
description: The Italian mob descends on the Mexican border to take on the most powerful cartel in America. Spencer, an ex-mobster in witness protection, battles the cartel who captured his son in Arizona, with his mob buddies coming to help.

title: Tails of Christmas
description: A military veteran searches for purpose in his life after an injury cut his career short. He finds it in a kind woman who runs an animal shelter. As they work together to find animals homes during the Christmas adoption season, they develop feelings for each other, and help each other with the challenges each faces.

title: A Sweet Christmas Romance
description: When a food stylist returns home for Christmas, she learns that the elderly owner of her favourite childhood bakery is retiring and has started a contest to give the bakery away to whoever can re-create her famous 12 Days of Christmas recipes.

title: Santa's Boots
description: Holly returns home for Christmas and is put to work as Santa's elf at her family's store, where she meets Nick, and falls in love. When Nick disappears days before Christmas, Holly searches for him with her only clue: his misplaced black boot.

title: Christmas with a Prince
description: Tasha, a pediatric specialist, must reluctantly tend to Prince Alexander, who is admitted in the children's ward. She, however, has a change of heart when she sees him connect with the children.

title: The Key to Christmas
description: When a disgruntled elf seeks to turn back time and ruin Christmas, it is up to a teenaged Santa and his little helper to save the holidays.

title: O POÇO
description: Numa prisão onde os reclusos são alimentados numa plataforma descendente, os que estão nos níveis superiores recebem mais do que deveriam, enquanto os que estão abaixo são deixados a morrer de fome, e um homem decide mudar o sistema.

title: Authors Anonymous
description: When a dysfunctional group of unpublished writers accept Hannah into their fold, the last thing they expect is her overnight success. Can these lovable misfits achieve their artistic dreams and avoid killing one another in the process?

title: Pippi Longstocking
description: As Pippi Longstocking awaits the return from the South Seas of her father Ephraim Longstocking, captain of the sailing ship Hoptoad, she gets involved in adventures with her monkey and horse.

title: Love Switch
description: Married couple James and Michelle, on the verge of divorce, magically switch bodies on their anniversary. Forced to experience life from each other's perspectives, they gain newfound respect and understanding, rekindling their love.

title: Once Upon A Christmas Miracle
description: This holiday romance is based on the incredible story about organ donor Chris Dempsey and recipient Heather Krueger, who were brought into one another's lives by a transplant surgery that led to a miraculous romance.

title: Love Alaska
description: It may not be the happiest of circumstances but two childhood friends, Maggie and Finn, have come home and are reunited in Love, Alaska. While starting their lives again and dealing with their pasts, will these two get a second chance at love?

title: 14 Love Letters
description: After historic love letters start anonymously appearing in Kallie Sharp's mailbox, the hobby farmer searches for her secret admirer and opens herself up to love.

title: Angel Dog
description: Jake loses his wife and children in a car accident, in which their dog Cooper survives. Jake starts hating Cooper after the accident, but eventually grows fond of the dog.

title: Dance Rivals
description: An unexpected turn of events introduces her to the intense LA dance scene and in no time she is teaching dance and competing against the pros - but can she juggle both while falling in love?

title: Guardian of the Ancient Shadow Crown
description: Nine-year-old Matthew finds a key to a magical world at the bottom of his grandmother's garden where he encounters the mystical Shadow people.

title: Turkles
description: Featuring a young Noah Centineo, this family adventure film follows a group of curious kids from Camp Loggerhead as they embark on an adventure to solve the mystery of the missing sea turtle eggs.

title: My Dog the Champion
description: When 16-year-old Maddy's mother had to go work overseas for three months, she had to move in with her hardcore grandfather. There she becomes friends with someone who trains dogs.

title: Hank's Christmas Wish
description: Through unwavering kindness and infectious joy, cheerful townspeople help a retired elf rediscover the true meaning of Christmas.

title: The Hybrids Family
description: A movie about a dysfunctional family of vampires and witches, it is mostly focused on the two children who are hybrids.

title: Adventure Harbor
description: Four tweens develop a life-long friendship when they discover an injured mystical sea creature. They bravely go to extreme lengths to protect her from selfish scoundrels set on capturing her and even harming her for their own profit.

title: Evil Little Things
description: A young boy finds a mystical toymaker with dark stories to tell.

title: A Christmas Exchange
description: This holiday season, Molly Cooper swaps her snow covered farmhouse for Patrick Kensington's posh London apartment. While enjoying Christmas time in the UK, Molly begins to look forward to every communication with Patrick. Likewise, Patrick finds Molly's warm emails and texts charming and compelling. Sparks fly between them as they get to know each other and fall in love as they live in each other's spaces. Coming home for Christmas Day, Molly is greeted to a new life and a new love.

title: Christmas With a Prince: The Royal Baby
description: Things get complicated for the expecting Prince Alexander and Dr. Tasha when a Royal State Visit is planned abroad, passing through her hometown. The couple must struggle with defying tradition and delivering, literally, on expectations.

title: An Evergreen Christmas
description: After her father's unexpected death, a singer becomes torn between pursuing her career and saving her family's Christmas-tree business in small-town Tennessee.

title: Best Friend From Heaven
description: When a tragic accident takes the life of her dog, Tara is forced to cancel her wedding. With a little help from above, their small town rallies together to make sure these two are able to have the wedding of their dreams.

title: Dimming Lights
description: Three sisters head to their childhood home for Christmas, after they have learned that their estranged mother, is in the late stages of Alzheimer's.

title: In the Sea of Grace
description: Apostle John is imprisoned on the island of Patmos, He struggles to understand why he's the last living apostle of Jesus Christ. He is visited by angels and the Apostle Paul. He receives visions which inspire him to write "Revelations."

title: Chicken Coop
description: On the brink of Christmas Eve, a young lawyer, Isaac, and his wife embark on a journey to reconcile with Isaac's estranged father. As they delve into home repairs, buried secrets emerge, revealing the heartbreaking reason Isaac missed his mother's funeral.

title: Grace Wins
description: Overcoming addiction against all odds movie. Counselor intervened on behalf of burglar of his home.

title: Echoes of Glory
description: Nine heroes from the American Revolution tell stories of danger, bravery and overcoming. Viewers meet John Featherstone, African American Naval mariner who fought in the first sea battle in Charleston Harbor in South Carolina, Daniel Morgan, wild, brilliant leader of revolutionary forces at the Battle of Cowpens, Rebecca Motte, clever spy who was willing to burn her home to force a company of British soldiers to surrender, Francis Marion, The Swamp Fox, shares how he became fearless in battle, Peter Harris, a Catawba warrior, fought German mercenaries with the patriots, Mary Oliver, a Christian slave woman who performed a unique act of mercy and Captain Henry Felder, who led a patriot militia and paid the ultimate price. Two Scholars, Professor Damon L. Fordham and Alexia Jones Helsley, trade off introducing the courageous, historic freedom fighters..

title: Operation Overreach Universe Part 1: Hidden
description: Bryan Rakell,a well known podcaster and documentary filmmaker, stumbles upon information that shows that there is something big going on in the world. Before he can get the word out, he finds himself in the middle of a nightmare.

title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
description: La estudiante de secundaria Bella es perseguida por la vampiresa vengativa Victoria. En medio de la amenaza inminente, se ve obligada a lidiar con su graduación y una elección crucial entre el amor y la amistad.

title: Ghost Town
description: In the untamed West of Victorian-era America, a drifter takes a job as a barman in a small Arizona town. After a series of bizarre deaths, he soon finds himself the target of suspicion.

title: When Everything's Gone
description: Post-apocalyptic survivor Rory, grieving lost brother, journeys through wasteland. Meets Casper and daughter Rosie. Group searches for other survivors after devastating plague, finding hope to begin anew.

title: But I'm a Cheerleader
description: Megan (Natasha Lyonne) considers herself a typical American girl. She excels in school and cheerleading, and she has a handsome football-playing boyfriend, even though she isn't that crazy about him. So she's stunned when her parents decide she's gay and send her to True Directions, a boot camp meant to alter her sexual orientation. While there, Megan meets a rebellious and unashamed teen lesbian, Graham (Clea DuVall). Though Megan still feels confused, she starts to have feelings for Graham.

title: Santa's Second Wife
description: After Mrs. Claus divorces Santa, he returns to his 40 year old self in search of love.

title: 5 passos de você
description: Stella e Will, ambos pacientes com fibrose cística, desenvolvem um relacionamento improvável, apesar da ameaça de infecção cruzada. No entanto, eles eliminam suas restrições para experimentar a união.

title: Max and Sadie
description: Max and Sadie have been best friends since childhood. In the aftermath of the pandemic, they impulsively take a road trip for a college classmate's birthday party in an attempt to escape deeper problems they're each facing.

title: Christmas Tears
description: Three best friends hit rock bottom on Christmas Eve and have a magical day that they will never forget.

title: No Time Like Christmas
description: Emma bumps into Fletcher, her ex-boyfriend from college, at a guest house before Christmas. Soon, they begin to fall for each other while planning a Christmas Eve show to save the local theatre.

title: AXE Giant
description: A young woman takes grisly revenge on the three sadists who terrorised her and her paralysed grandfather.

title: Dangerous Waters
description: A young woman, her new boyfriend and her single mother embark on a sailing adventure to Bermuda. However, when criminals suddenly attack their boat, the pleasure trip turns into a desperate fight for survival and a quest for vengeance.

title: The Christmas Bunny
description: When Julia, a lonely foster child, discovers an injured rabbit on Christmas Eve, she forms an unlikely friendship with an eccentric farm woman (Florence Henderson) who vows to help Julia nurse the bunny back to health.

title: Frenzy Shark
description: A group of friends run a popular travel vlog that helps fund their adventures. Paige (Gina Vitori), the leader of the group, includes her younger sister, Lindsey (Aubrey Reynolds), for the next scuba diving trip to an isolated cove. But when their plane crashes, the two sisters must use their strength, resourcefulness and immense courage to survive a pack of great white sharks.

title: The Spirit of Christmas
description: " Just before Christmas Kate is supposed to broker the sale of the Hollygrove Inn, but finds that her appraiser has left because of the ghost. Determined, Kate stays and soon meets Daniel, a man claims to have died 95 years ago. The two strike a deal - if she can help him discover the truth of his death, he will leave so Kate can finish her job. But as they work together, Kate begins falling for this dashing Christmas spirit, and a romance develops that will alter the course of both their lives."

title: Megalodon: The Frenzy
description: When a frenzy of five Megalodons torment the open ocean, the stakes have never been higher. Stars: Caroline Williams, Eric Roberts, Jessica Chancellor

title: Christmas Matchmakers
description: Maggie's boss needs a date for the publishing company's Christmas party, and she finds her eleven. Maggie is a successful matchmaker, but what about herself when her ex Jaxson reenters her life?

title: CROCODILE SWARM
description: After Sam's sister goes missing in a caving system, she recruits a team to assist her in the search. However, when the team begins the rescue mission, they soon learn the caves are infested by deadly crocodiles waiting for them. Sam and the team must fight for their lives if they hope to save her sister and get out of there in one piece.

title: THE DIVE
description: A deep-sea diving trip at one of the world's most remote spots becomes a fight for survival for sisters Drew and May when a catastrophic landslide sends rocks tumbling into the sea. After being struck by the rockfall, May now lies 28 meters below the surface, trapped by debris and unable to move. With dangerously low levels of oxygen, it is up to Drew to fight for her sister’s life. She must put her own life in jeopardy and risk paying the ultimate sacrifice. But with no help in sight, time is quickly running out…

title: Age Of Tomorrow
description: Mankind must fight to survive as Earth is invaded by hostile UFOs bent on destroying the planet. As the epic battle wages on, astronauts sneak aboard the mothership where they discover a portal to the aliens' home world.

title: Adventures of Aladdin
description: Aladdin is recruited to steal a magic lamp. But when he uses its powers to help him win the heart of the newly appointed Sultana, it opens up a whole new world of excitement and danger.

title: Space
description: In the year 2050, Dr. Ada Gray and her fellow astronauts aboard The Udo fight for survival after an accident leaves them stranded in deep space.

title: Bad President
description: The devil encourages media personality Donald Trump to run for president of the United States, so he can have a political puppet. But throughout Trump's many gaffes, the devil wonders if he even has a chance of winning.

title: Tranquility: Ghost Stories
description: Now a sophomore agent, Danny Malloy realizes a new threat is emerging when he's tasked with transferring two mysterious Twins.

title: Dog Jack
description: In the midst of the Civil War, a boy and his dog escape a plantation and embark on a life-changing journey. Inspired by true events, "Dog Jack" chronicles a turbulent moment in American history, and a tale that's never been forgotten.

title: Reed's Point
description: A vehicle crash in the Pine Barrens leads to a missing teen which raises conspiracy theories about the infamous Jersey Devil legend. On the anniversary of the crash, Sarah Franklin, convinced her cousin Kelsey is alive, goes out to the crash site with Alex, Kelsey's boyfriend, to investigate. Things go downhill quickly as Sarah and Alex uncover what really lurks in the woods.

title: Joy & Hope
description: Joy and Hope McGregor run Two Sisters Ranch upstate New York with their dad and longtime friend. When a handsome stranger comes to town to find inspiration to get over writer's block, he learns how special Christmas on the ranch really is.

title: Insane Like Me?
description: Combat veteran returns home after duty, wrongly convicted for girlfriend's disappearance. After 9 years in asylum, he's released, seeking truth and vengeance regarding her fate.

title: Blood of My Blood - Expansion Ain't Easy
description: Prepare for a cinematic rollercoaster as "Blood of My Blood" immerses you in the tumultuous life of Levi Harper, a young real estate agent and aspiring record label owner. In a world where dreams collide with harsh realities, Levi finds himself at a crossroads as the pandemic cripples home sales and interest rates soar.  With his father, Sam, a former kingpin in the drug trade serving time, Levi faces an unprecedented dilemma - be a law-abiding citizen or follow in his father's criminal footsteps. The gripping narrative unfolds against the backdrop of a world grappling with economic turmoil, forcing Levi to make choices that will define his destiny.  Fueled by the allure of fast cars, fast money, and fast living, Levi plunges into a realm where the line between citizen and criminal blurs. As he navigates the complexities of his father's legacy, Levi discovers that expansion ain't easy. The movie explores themes of loyalty, ambition, and the high price one pays when dreams clash with the unforgiving realities of life.  "Blood of My Blood" is a pulse-pounding drama that delves into the choices we make, the paths we walk, and the consequences that follow. Will Levi rise above his father's shadows, or will he succumb to the allure of a life on the edge? Buckle up for a riveting ride that will leave you questioning the fine line between ambition and the cost of the choices we make. Don't miss the chance to witness Levi's journey unfold in this intense crime drama. #BloodOfMyBloodMovie #Brickbybrickfilm #ExpansionAintEasy

title: Red Line
description: Commuters on an LA subway train receive the shock of their lives when a bomb goes off and they are stuck underground with one of the perpetrators among them and another explosive yet to detonate.

title: 13 Miles
description: Two triathletes battle their personal demons while they train for the biggest event of their lives.
