title: House of Screaming Glass
description: Elizabeth, a troubled young woman who has lived an isolated life, troubled by memories of her tumultuous relationship with her deceased mother, inherits her grandmother's schoolhouse. There she begins to experience strange visions and terrifying dreams. As she delves into her family history, she discovers that her grandmother was a witch and soon Elizabeth begins practicing the same black magic rituals. As Elizabeth's powers grow, she struggles to reconcile her newfound identity with the ghosts of her past. Ultimately, Elizabeth becomes the ghost that will haunt the schoolhouse after her death, forever tied to the dark magic that consumed her.

title: The Covenant
description: Lumo Project Films presents The Covenant, a captivating film rooted in the Torah, bringing to life the stories of Adam and Eve, Noah, Abraham, Moses, and more. A Word-for word narration of the first five books of the Bible.

title: Pilgrim's Progress: Journey To Heaven
description: From Director Danny Carrales comes this modern adaptation of the beloved Christian classic, John Bunyan's Pilgrim's Progress. This movie is a powerful allegory of the life of a believer on a journey from the City of Destruction to the Celestial City.  Follow Christian and his companions on a great Journey to the gates of Heaven as they face obstacles large and small, man-made and demon-spawned. This allegory has very good truth presented and has the right message for anyone who wants to understand more about the real Christian life journey.

title: The Life of Jesus
description: 'The Life of Jesus' is a story told by his closest friends. Adapted from the book of John in the Bible. Discover now how Jesus changed the course of history in this movie about his life! ​​Jesus Christ was born about 2,000 years ago. His life and death changed the world forever. He still makes an everlasting impact on the lives of many with his radical teachings and miracles.

title: The Transporter Refueled
description: Frank Martin, a former mercenary, is hired by a woman and her accomplices to fulfil a contract. Soon, however, he must join forces with them to bring down a Russian crime lord.

title: Vampyre Nation
description: As mankind accepts the existence of vampires, Bucharest, Romania, becomes a city where vampires live openly. An already fragile peace crumbles when a murder triggers a bloody vampire hunt.

title: Tsunami Sharks
description: A tsunami hits the city and soon, sharks begin infesting the waters..

title: The Divergent Series: Allegiant
description: After the fall of the oppressive faction system, Tris ventures out into the city outside her walled homeland and discovers the existence of an organisation that has been controlling her life.

title: The Death and Life of Nancy Eaton
description: A wealthy young Canadian department store heiress tries her best to help out a deeply troubled and jealous childhood friend, with disastrous results that shock the whole country.

title: Been There All Along
description: After her public break-up, Charley, the determined founder of a dating app, is near bankruptcy. She teams up with Liam, a self-assured and innovative marketing expert, to save her company.

title: Big Stan
description: Stan Minton, a con man, is sentenced to imprisonment for fraud. Filled with fear of dealing with the dangerous inmates, he hires a martial arts trainer to toughen him up.

title: Love's Fast Lane
description: After accidentally ruining a wedding, mechanic and all-round bad ass Nikki Turner finds herself falling for bookish ivy league professor Jeremy Mitchell as she helps him try to win back his fiancée.

title: The Perfect Day
description: Retired Navy S.E.A.L. Christopher 'Soup' Campbell is a tactical specialist for a private security firm at a counter terrorism training facility hidden in the Blue Ridge Mountains. The military and intelligence community call him 'Soup', not only because of the familiarity of his last name, but his ability to combine and assess a variety of threats into a strategic tactical response. A specific skill that came useful on many of his combat tours into Iraq and Afghanistan.

title: Monkey Puzzle
description: Dylan takes his best friend and three others on a trek to find the world's rarest tree; as the forest closes in on them, they all come face-to-face with their haunted pasts.

title: Lightning Strikes
description: Sheriff Bradley must devise a plan to save the people of his town from the deadly clutches of a monster who literally rides the thunder and strikes lightning.

title: The Andy Baker Tape
description: The last known footage of food blogger Jeff Blake and his half-brother Andy Baker.

title: Dead Before Dawn
description: A group of college kids accidentally create, and then unleash, a curse that makes anyone they come into contact with kill themselves and then turn into zombie demons.

title: Escape Through Africa
description: In 1914, a British nurse escapes an attack on her outpost in Africa. Hunted by a German-led war party, and with help from local warriors, she embarks on an epic journey to save a neighboring outpost from a massacre.

title: The 5th Execution
description: A group of scientists working on the regenerative abilities of salamander make a breakthrough in their research. However, they also discover a new disease which could potentially wipe them out.

title: Burial Ground Massacre
description: A group of college students spend a night at an old, eerie manor, only to realize that a terrifying stalker is watching their every move as he begins plans to repossess an ancient Native American artifact located inside.

title: Falcon Down
description: U.S. Air force officer Hank Thomas attempts to expose a military cover-up after a civiian airliner crashes.

title: As Night Falls
description: Holly and Elizabeth's friends are losing their heads at their party when an evil couple returns from the dead.

title: SALVAGE: CONTAINED FEAR
description: When a container washes ashore the residents of a sleepy cul-de-sac are plunged into violence, terror and paranoia. Ring fenced by the military a single mother must overcome all the odds to save her daughter.

title: THE NIGHT THEY KNOCKED
description: During their last weekend together, a group of friends staying at a reclusive mountain house have their fun suddenly interrupted by a knock at the door

title: Skinwalker
description: After looting a Native American burial site, a hunter unleashes the legendary Skinwalker, a shape shifting demon, onto an unsuspecting world.

title: Supercollider
description: When the largest particle collider ever built suffers a catastrophic malfunction, it opens an alternate dimension and causes a series of cataclysmic events that threaten the entire human species.

title: VooDoo
description: When Dani, an innocent southern girl, vacations to Los Angeles to evade her increasingly complicated life, she learns that escaping her past isn't as easy as she hoped.

title: Christmas Wreaths & Ribbons
description: After a wreath maker hurts her arm, she gets help from a kind neighbor to keep her wreath-making business running during the busy holiday season. As they work together, the pair form an unexpected bond and holiday connection.

title: A Christmas of Wonders
description: After years of globetrotting, a travel writer returns to her small hometown for the holidays, where she rediscovers the magic of family traditions and reconnects with an old flame.

title: Monster Grizzly
description: A terrifying monster grizzly bear comes out of a blinding blizzard to feed on the trapped residents of an isolated town.

title: Liebe auf Aruba
description: A single father hires a woman to take care of his daughter while they're in Aruba.

title: The Secrets of Jonathan Sperry
description: A group of children are tired of being bullied at school. However, things change after an old man named Jonathan Sperry begins to mentor them by imparting Biblical truths.

title: Play the Flute
description: Faced with an indifferent youth group, a new youth pastor (Brett Varvel) tries to motivate his students to read God's Word and get serious about their faith.

title: Mountain Top
description: A lawyer-turned-preacher must embrace his former profession as he chooses to represent an eccentric man in a court to solve a case that is linked to his sober life in a small town.

title: A Matter of Faith
description: Rachel Whitaker, a college freshman, questions her Christian roots after learning about evolution from her teacher, Dr Kaman. Her father, Stephen, decides to refute the professor's claims in a debate.

title: The Santa Squad
description: An unemployed art teacher must accept a job with the Santa Squad in an effort to help a widower and his two precious daughters rediscover the magic of Christmas.

title: Rabata
description: Gulshan Kumar and Prem Vijan present the official Trailer of the upcoming Indian film "Raabta" a film by Dinesh Vijan and Produced by  Dinesh Vijan Homi Adajania Bhushan Kumar Krishan Kumar.The Film stars Sushant Singh Rajput and Kriti Sanon in lead roles with Music by Pritam.

title: Padmavati
description: Presenting the Official Trailer of Padmavati starring Deepika Padukone, Ranveer Singh, Shahid Kapoor, Aditi Rao Hydari and Jim Sarbh.

title: Simran
description: Gulshan Kumar presents in association with Karma Features Pvt. Ltd official movie trailer of the upcoming Bollywood movie in 2017  "Simran". The film is directed by   Hansal Mehta, produced by  Bhushan Kumar, Shailesh R Singh, Krishan Kumar & Amit Agarwal, Featuring Kangana Ranaut in the lead role.

title: Do Patti
description: Two sisters' carefully constructed lives are shattered when a police inspector uncovers a web of deceit that threatens them.

title: Shaadi Mein Zarror aana
description: "Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana" is a heartfelt romantic drama directed by Ratnaa Sinha. It tells the tale of love, betrayal, and second chances as Satyendra and Aarti's lives take an unexpected turn on their wedding day. Rajkummar Rao and Kriti Kharbanda deliver powerful performances in this emotional rollercoaster. With its engaging storyline, memorable moments, and soulful music, "Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana" is a must-watch for all romantics at heart.

title: Sanam Teri Kasam
description: Sanam Teri Kasam | Superhit Hindi Full Romantic Movie | Harshvardhan Rane | Mawra Hocane

title: Fanney Khan
description: "A Film by Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra Pictures. In Association with Anil Kapoor Film & Communication Network.  Produced by Bhushan Kumar, Rakeysh Omprakash Mehra, Anil Kapoor, P.S. Bharathi, Rajiv Tandon, Krishan Kumar, Kussum Arora & Nishant Pitti"

title: Unstable
description: A divorced mother takes in a former footballer as a lodger and child-minder, but her decision has dangerous consequences.

title: Not on This Night
description: The story centers on a chance encounter between enemy combatants in a small farmhouse, the home of a young French woman, Jacqueline Broulet, in the Ardennes Forest on Christmas Eve 1944. As the Battle of the Bulge has been raging around her for weeks, Jacqueline unexpectedly finds herself sheltering and tending to two young, wounded soldiers, one American, Eddie Miller, and one German, Reinhold Shultz, who have been lost in the woods after being separated from their units. As the night passes, enemies see themselves as human beings. Humanity prevails, even in the bloody, wretched depths of war.

title: A culpa é das estrelas
description: A vida da adolescente Hazel Grace muda quando ela conhece Augustus Waters em um grupo de apoio ao câncer. Os dois então embarcam em uma jornada transformadora que os aproxima ainda mais.

title: Island of Lost Girls
description: When a riptide sweeps three young sisters away, they wash up on an island where they must escape a sea cave filled with crashing waves, discover abandoned artifacts from the island’s previous residents, and encounter hundreds of sea lions and giant elephant seals. As they make their way to a distant lighthouse, they learn the importance of never giving up and sticking together along the way.

title: Island of Lost Girls
description: When a riptide sweeps three young sisters away, they wash up on an island where they must escape a sea cave filled with crashing waves, discover abandoned artifacts from the island’s previous residents, and encounter hundreds of sea lions and giant elephant seals. As they make their way to a distant lighthouse, they learn the importance of never giving up and sticking together along the way.

title: O Homem que Desafio o Diabo
description: Após ser forçado a se casar e suportar uma rotina de trabalho humilhante nas mãos de seu sogro, Zé Araújo se torna o mítico Ojuara, um herói não convencional dedicado à libertação.

title: Blackmail
description: Dev discovers that his wife, Reena, has been cheating on him with Ranjit. To teach them a lesson, he decides to blackmail the cheating duo as part of his revenge.

title: The Exorcism of God
description: Peter Williams is an American priest in Mexico who's considered a saint by many local parishioners. However, due to a botched exorcism, he carries a dark secret that's eating him alive until he gets an opportunity to face his own demon one last time.

title: One Shot
description: Kyle Matthews, a sniper, gets trapped in the territory that belongs to an enemy. He bravely fights against the enemy soldiers. But a beautiful woman catches his attention and he is unable to kill her.

title: Heaven's Door
description: After the sudden demise of her grandfather, Riley, a young girl discovers a portal that helps her access heaven. She receives miraculous healing powers but with a heavy price.

title: Bookworm And The Beast
description: Izzy, a PR professional, gets embroiled in a public scandal when a celebrity hits her father. She has to work with the celebrity to manage the crisis, unexpectedly falling for him while navigating personal and professional challenges.

title: Walking Thunder
description: In the 1850s, a young boy and his family on their way west become stranded in the Rockies. With the help of a local mountain man, a Sioux medicine man, and a legendary bear known as "Walking Thunder," the boy learns to become a man, and his family's survival is secured.

title: Love, Lost And Found
description: Joey plans to propose to Claire at a picnic in the wilderness. Accidents separate them and Joey ends up with amorous ranger Natalie, while Claire ends up with rescue volunteer Colt, her ex.

title: The Beautiful Beast
description: Isabelle, a spoilt rich girl, goes on a trip with her friend but they have an argument and he leaves her wandering alone in the cold. She later encounters a reclusive man and gets intrigued by him.

title: A Hundred Lies
description: Following the journey of Ricky, a 25 year-old musician from Toronto, while he navigates the volatile terrain, and overcomes personal adversity.

title: Counting Bullets
description: One of 12 westerns in 12 months, Counting Bullets tells the story of a small group of cavalry soldiers who are pinned down in a canyon by the enemy. Over the course of a few days, they are forced to face their differences and rely on each of their instincts to survive.

title: A Leading Man
description: When a young and talented Chinese American actor is fired from a starring role on a television show, he attempts to salvage his career by entering into a romantic relationship with a successful casting director.

title: Shaking Dream Land
description: When Robert marries the beautiful Alice they are the 'perfect couple'. But the moment he learns his wife is pregnant, dark secrets from the past fly unbidden into the present and threaten to destroy their future.

title: MINI MINI MINI
description: Titli is tasked with taking care of her teenage niece, Mini, when her sister is hospitalised. With time, the two of them become inseparable. What happens when Mini's mother returns?

title: Los Muertos Desperados
description: Inhaling a hallucinogenic drug, our anti-hero Paul becomes obsessed with a woman who appears to be an exact double of his ex-wife. But he soon finds himself embroiled in a criminal conspiracy.

title: Obsidian
description: Haunted by his tragic past, Jack Carre, a heavily-scarred introvert, volunteers for a Phase I clinical trial of a miraculous new tissue regeneration medication, dubbed "Obsidian." Soon, under the watchful surveillance of respected pharmacologist, Dr. James Walsh, Jack and the group of hopeful volunteers start to experience hellish side effects from the drug and soon find that the quest for vanity can be deadly.

title: After the World Ended
description: An astronaut crashes in the middle of nowhere. A young woman searches for her family in an abandoned urban wasteland. A prisoner prepares for a space program that will make him the first human being on Mars.

title: Handshake
description: After a chance encounter, two strangers devise a bizarre plan to solve their financial problems.

title: Fun Mom Dinner
description: Four mothers, who know each other because their kids go to the same preschool, decide to go out for dinner. However, the seemingly harmless night out soon takes a wild turn.

title: The Next 24 Hours
description: The Next 24 Tells a story about the harsh truth of human trafficking, right here in the United States. The Next 24 takes a deep look at how young girls are targeted and lured into this modern-day slavery, and how they are bought and sold for profit around the globe. "It only takes 24 hours for a young girl to be lost for good, in the world of Human Trafficking".

title: Hope
description: When a vlogger suffers a severe injury on her latest adventure, her optimism and positive outlook on life get pushed to their limits as she fights to survive.

title: The Stratum
description: In the year 2057, a greedy CEO takes control of the Earth, and it's up to his rebellious daughter and a cyberpunk hacker to save mankind.

title: Please Kill Mr. Know It All
description: Sally ghostwrites an advice column under the pseudonym Mr. Know It All and submits a sketch of a handsome stranger as the image, but she doesn't realize that the face is that of a hit man, who plans to kill the columnist to protect his identity.

title: Henri
description: Henri was raised in a monastery in the Far East and now he lives in America in the deep south where his story begins. As peaceful as he was trained to be, trouble always seems to finds him. Henri's story is filled with love, action, suspense and adventure.

title: Night Explorers: The Asylum
description: When a group of Urban Explorers get the chance of a lifetime to explore one of the world's most haunted asylums, they encounter something truly evil, that will not let them leave and will push them to the edge of sanity.

title: Witchville
description: Malachy returns to his father's medieval kingdom and becomes the new king. A magician/witch hunter tells him and his brother that the kingdom is under attack by witches, ruining the crops etc.

title: The Big Trip
description: A goofy stork mistakenly delivers a baby panda to the wrong door. A bear, a moose, a tiger and a rabbit set on an arduous but fun filled adventure through wilderness to return the panda to its rightful home.

title: Beauty and the Billionaire: Bali
description: A reluctant billionaire goes to Bali as a donor and meets a beautiful female doctor working there. Both leave their prejudices behind and fall in love.

title: Operation Overreach Universe Part 2: Sheltered
description: Darren Culling may be losing his mind. After years of manipulation by what he sees, hears, and reads in the media, he decides to leave society and live off the grid. He seems to have lost hope despite the ember of Faith that still burns inside him. While secluded in the middle of nowhere, Darren encounters an unconscious woman in the woods.

title: New Hope
description: Michael, a high school senior, moves to New Hope, a small town, but is still reeling from the death of Chase, a high school basketball star.

title: Night Walk
description: In this modern-day Romeo and Juliet, star-crossed lovers are torn apart by cultural tensions between the East and the West. Sarah takes her American boyfriend Frank to her home country in the Arab world. After an incident during a night stroll, Frank is imprisoned by corrupt police for Sarah's murder. His quest for justice turns into a spiritual journey led by Muslim inmates, from the moderate convert to terror-linked fundamentalists.

title: Ordinary Magic
description: When his father dies, Jeffrey is sent to live with his aunt Charlotte in Canada; once there he leads his aunt and his friends in staging a non-violent hunger strike to try to save his aunt's house from being demolished to make room for a ski resort.

title: Hot Mess
description: Loz is an aspiring playwright who finally thinks she's found the answer to all her existential angst, and his name is Dave.

title: Life & Me
description: Franklin has lost his faith and contemplates suicide, but some divine intervention from an offbeat psychologist will try to convince him through a series of flashbacks that God has never left his side - even in his darkest moments.

title: Horrid
description: Take a trip to the north woods, but don't plan on going home.

title: American Backwoods: Slew Hampshire
description: In June of 1994, one of the most brutal mass slaughters in history occurred in the backwoods of northern New England. Four months later, history is about to repeat itself. The end of summer signals the brink of manhood for a group of lifelong friends who proudly call New Hampshire their home. But when they embark upon a local rite of passage - traveling north for one final weekend of debauchery together - it just might prove to be their final weekend PERIOD, as this rite is doomed to go frightfully wrong. When they find themselves ensnared in a struggle for survival amongst a sinister hunting party, a bloodthirsty tribe AND a mythical beast, what began as a comedy of errors devolves into an all-out Darwinian duel to the death, and less than 24 hours will pass before a slew of lives have been claimed and the last of the living remains.

title: The Chair to Everywhere
description: A father and daughter invent a teleportation device designed to ultimately replace all other forms of transport on Earth. During one of the tests, the daughter disappears and fails to arrive at the receiving device. The father desperately tries to recover her with devastating consequences. A shocking mind-boggling twist in the tale of a story with many layers to excite, horrify, and explore the power of human love.

title: A Bride's Revenge
description: Owning a successful hair salon and about to be married to the man of her dreams, MIYA doesn’t think things can get any better. Things quickly begin to fall apart when she receives a wedding invitation – to the wedding of her fiancé Ian and his ex-fiancée Lily. Soon Miya is being stalked by an eerie bride dressed in a wedding gown and veil and Ian begins to suspect Miya might be making it all up! When a series of horrifying events start to occur, Miya is convinced that Lily is carrying out a twisted and deadly plan of revenge.

title: Nanny Cam
description: Linda has a seemingly happy home life with her handsome husband Mark and adorable daughter Chloe. The new babysitter, Heather, seems like the ideal addition to this practically perfect family. But as Heather ingratiates herself with Mark and Chloe, Linda grows suspicious and begins to obsessively watch the nanny cam footage to see what happens while she's at work. Caught on camera, Heather's actions evolve from sweet to mischievous to very dangerous.

title: The Book of Genesis
description: A woman in hiding tells the story of humanity in this inspiring Biblical drama exploring the beginning of man's relationship with God.

title: Wyrmwood : Road of the Dead
description: A survivor of a zombie outbreak tries to rescue his kidnapped sister from a psychotic doctor and his henchmen.

title: A Housekeeper's Revenge
description: A college student fears for her life after a number of disturbing occurrences, leaving her desperately searching for the culprit. Her suspicions lead to her family housemaid, unaware that their connection is much deeper than meets the eye.

title: Miracle in the Valley
description: Thirteen-year-old Melinda is determined to find out what happened to her real Daddy, and no one in Boonville will help her.

title: Namorada de aluguel
description: Ronald, um nerd marginalizado, está lutando para fazer sua presença ser sentida na faculdade. Ele aborda a garota mais popular e a paga para ser sua namorada.

title: Ghosts of Mars
description: Officer Melanie and Sergeant Jericho travel to a mining outpost to transport a prisoner. On arriving, they realise that demons of an ancient Martian civilisation have possessed the entire colony.

title: Deadly Obsession
description: Brielle & Robert are a newlywed couple, with their share of issues that have risen over their first 3 years of courtship, but when an aggressive argument between the two, forces Robert to reconsider his commitment, Brielle finds herself going through a whirlwind of emotions, only to run into an old schoolmate buddy, "Quincy Wright", that turns her world as she knows it, upside down."Deadly Obsession" is a suspense thriller about a wife on the verge of divorce, who has a one night stand that has deadly consequences for all involved.

title: Killer In Law
description: Inspired by true events. Melissa, a happily married woman with an eight-year-old daughter invites her husband’s mother to live with them. However, Melissa comes to realize that Grandma is unhinged and wants to kidnap Melissa’s daughter to replace her own dead child.

title: The Daughter Stalker
description: After the death of her estranged sister Nikki, with whom she’d hadn’t seen since they were separated in foster care, Carly is surprised to learn that she is named in Nikki’s will as guardian of her adopted daughter Mallie. Upon moving across the country to honor her sister’s wishes, Carly quickly realizes that not only was Mallie left a substantial inheritance, but that not everyone is happy about the existence of a long lost sister. Someone else wants custody of rich Mallie, and they aren’t going to let Carly stand in their way for much longer.

title: An Unlikely Angel
description: Janie is a power player in the boardroom but is falling apart at the thought of becoming a mom. A silent prayer is answered when an Angel intervenes and fast forwards her life. Can Janie learn to trust God and find her new purpose?

title: THE GIRLFRIEND KILLER
description: A businesswoman, creating perfect marriage proposals for wealthy men, becomes the object of a client's mad obsession when she shows him compassion following his girlfriend's public rejection.

title: Mary White
description: Mary White (1977) - The true story of the relationship between famed author William Allen White and his teenaged daughter Mary, who died in a horseback-riding accident at age 16, and the powerful effect the tragedy had on the life of her father.

title: My Super Ex-Girlfriend
description: Matt Saunders, a mild-mannered project manager at a design firm in New York, finds himself entangled in a whirlwind romance after meeting the mysterious and enchanting Jenny Johnson on the subway. Intrigued by her enigmatic allure, Matt invites Jenny out for dinner, which quickly spirals into a passionate relationship. Jenny soon reveals her true identity as the powerful superhero G-Girl, taking Matt's world by storm. However, as their relationship deepens, Matt's connection with his co-worker and friend Hannah Lewis awakens Jenny's jealousy, turning her possessive and manipulative. Faced with a heartbroken G-Girl who begins wreaking havoc on his life, Matt must navigate the treacherous path of romance, all while grappling with the dangerous proposition from Jenny's archenemy, Professor Bedlam, to strip her of her powers.

title: LA Apocalypse
description: For 5 billion years the Earth's core has operated like a giant, nuclear reactor. Now it's overheated, melting down like a bomb that's about to explode. The earth is being ripped apart at the seams and beneath LA, pressure is building. After a mass evacuation, Calvin Crawford is one of few left, desperately searching for his fiancée, Ashley Pace, who unbeknownst to him, has been kidnapped and is being held hostage. With LA becoming more unstable by the minute, Calvin, must find a way to save Ashley and get them both to safety before the city is completely annihilated.

title: American Prom
description: "Experience the heartfelt journey of American Prom, a modern coming-of-age story that brings spirituality into focus amidst the trials of high school life.  Trinity, a bright and spirited teenager, navigates the complex world of high school, balancing popularity, peer pressure, and the allure of the ""in-crowd."" As prom season approaches, she faces a life-changing decision: follow the crowd or stay true to her faith and values."

title: A Love Inspired Bestseller
description: It sounds like Konstantin Makheyev is living quite an unusual and somewhat chaotic life! His creative process is directly tied to the intensity of his romantic relationships, which sparks his inspiration for his detective novels. This setup creates a fascinating dynamic, where love fuels his work but also becomes an expendable element—once the passion dies, so does his inspiration for that particular story.

title: Killer Under The Bed
description: After her husband dies, Sarah moves her daughters Chrissy and Kilee to a new city. Kilee hates the move, feeling that they’re running away from her dad’s memory. When she’s bullied at school and is endlessly fighting with her sister, it feels like the world is against her, until she discovers a doll, riddled with pins, in her backyard shed. She soon comes to believe that the doll holds supernatural powers but when it starts acting on its own, Kilee becomes concerned about what she might have unleashed on the people in her life.

title: Who Killed My Sister
description: "It follows Drea, a college freshman, who decides to rush the same sorority as her sister to find the truth behind her death. Drea, a freshman at college, decides to rush the same sorority her sister Gabi died rushing two years earlier in hopes of finding out the truth about her death. Who Killed My Sister Lifetime trailer is after the news report.  Directed By: Michelle Mower"

title: UMA COMÉDIA NADA ROMÂNTICA
description: Julia, uma mulher obesa, está convencida de que nunca encontrará o amor de sua vida e decide perder peso. Mais tarde, ela conhece Grant e se apaixona por ele, mas eles têm que enfrentar muitos desafios para se unirem.

title: 101 Dálmatas
description: A herdeira má Cruella de Vil decide fazer um casaco de pele para si mesma com as peles de filhotes de dálmata. Quando ela rouba uma ninhada de 15 filhotes, cabe aos pais resgatar os filhotes inocentes.

title: MURDER IN THE VINEYARD
description: Grace, a woman suffering from a histrionic personality disorder, murders her husband and obsesses over her new neighbour after she moves her residence to Philadelphia.

title: Nick
description: Margret is a police officer in a small town where nothing ever happens. But her happiness is shattered when she receives a call from Social Services. Nick, her fifteen-year-old stepbrother, has just been expelled from boarding school.

title: Porches and Private Eyes
description: "PORCHES AND PRIVATE EYES tells the story of three women in the small town of Brookhaven, Mississippi whose gossip circle turns to amateur detective work when an eccentric man in town disappears.   "

title: Cut Color Murder
description: When a beauty pageant creator is found dead, a savvy hairdresser works with a detective and risks everything to clear the names of those she loves.

title: Below The Fold
description: Without a trace, Susie Potter vanished from her home in the quiet town of Skidmore, Missouri. Ten years later two reporters uncover a harrowing new detail, which leads them on an obsessive hunt for the truth through the dark labyrinth of rural northwest Missouri.

title: A Vida Depois
description: Depois da trágica perda da filha, Irina e Alexander não conseguiram lidar com a dor e se divorciaram. Irina se casou com Igor, um amigo de Alexander e empresário de sucesso. Alexander também encontrou outra mulher, buscando recomeçar sua vida.

title: Eu Acredito
description: " Somos o melhor destino para quem busca trailers assim que eles são lançados.  Se você é fã de cinema como a gente, INSCREVA-SE e receba todas as novidades dos seus filmes favoritos! "

title: Jesus
description: Jesus de Nazaré narra sua história de vida e lança luz sobre os eventos desde seu nascimento até sua crucificação e eventual ressurreição.

title: Uma Chance para Viver
description: Dr Dennis Slamon, um oncologista americano, descobre um tratamento que poderia possivelmente curar o câncer de mama sem radiação ou quimioterapia. Ele tenta procurar maneiras de financiar a medicação.

title: Chá Forte Com Limão
description: No verão de 1870, Raquel, dona de uma fazenda e que vive isolada em sua mansão com um velho mordomo e um punhado de criados, sente-se orgulhosa quando um estranho conhecido aparece. Adriana e sua nora, Ermesinda, uma menina muito jovem, por acaso estão visitando - a segunda vez em 15 anos para Adriana, e a primeira vez para a adolescente Ermesinda.

title: À flor do mar
description: Laura Rossellini, uma viúva de Roma, está de férias na costa do Algarve em um verão quente. Um dia, enquanto tomava sol, ela encontra um homem ferido chamado Robert à deriva nas ondas em um bote de borracha. Ela o leva para casa e, depois que ele é reanimado, descobre sua história. Enquanto conversam, sua atração mútua cresce, até que um grupo de homens armados chega de repente procurando por Robert.

title: Gebo e l'ombra
description: Ambientado no final do século XIX, sobre um patriarca honrado, mas pobre, que se sacrifica para proteger seu filho fugitivo.

title: Mistérios de Lisboa
description: A trágica história das muitas vidas do Padre Dinis, das suas origens obscuras e das suas obras piedosas, e dos diferentes destinos de todos aqueles que, presos numa sinistra teia de amor, ódio e crime, cruzam o seu caminho ao longo de anos de aventura.

title: Veredas
description: Para sua estreia no cinema, Monteiro tomou emprestado criativamente lendas tradicionais portuguesas para criar uma série de contos paralelos e ecoantes de jovens casais escapando desesperadamente de pais falsos e cruéis, cada casal fugindo por diferentes regiões do país e durante períodos de tempo cada vez mais contemporâneos.

title: José e Pilar
description: Um documentário sobre o ganhador do Prêmio Nobel José Saramago e seus sentimentos em relação à esposa, ao país e à vida como um todo.

title: Dona Flor e Seus Dois Maridos
description: Flor, uma viúva, casa-se com Dr. Teodoro, um cavalheiro respeitável, após a morte de seu belo, mas imprestável marido Vadinho. A hilaridade acontece quando o espírito de Vadinho retorna à sua vida.

title: Memórias Póstumas de Brás Cubas
description: Adaptação livre do clássico de Machado de Assis. O narrador é um morto rico, que nos conta sobre sua vida e época, fazendo piada de ambos.

title: Tentação
description: Padre Antonio é um padre por vocação, comprometido e generoso, querido povo de Vila Daires, uma pacata vila do norte. Mas Padre Anthony também é um homem, e Vila Daires não é tão pacífica quanto parece. As boas intenções do Padre não serão suficientes para deter o agravamento do conflito. E quando seu destino cruza com Lena, a "ovelha negra" da vila, Padre também será forçado a confrontar seus próprios demônios. Principalmente com aqueles que nunca sequer pensaram que poderiam existir

title: Zona J
description: Tó é um garoto negro da Zona J, um bairro difícil de Lisboa, e se apaixona por uma garota branca, Carla. Tó sonha em viver em Angola, onde seus pais nasceram, porém a realidade em que os dois adolescentes se encontram torna tudo complicado.

title: Living On
description: O filme documenta o início e o difícil progresso de uma cooperativa de casas na vila de pescadores de Meia Praia, durante o processo revolucionário em Portugal, de 25 de abril de 1974 até meados de 1976.

title: As Bodas de Deus
description: Após receber a visita de um mensageiro de Deus, um homem (João César Monteiro) conquista a namorada do seu amigo (Joana Azevedo) através de um lance de dados.

title: Goodbye, Father
description: Para um garoto de 13 anos como Filipe, a perspectiva de umas férias de verão nos Açores com seu pai é como um sonho que se torna realidade. Mas os sonhos às vezes são apenas uma maneira de evitar encarar a realidade.

title: La Pat'Patrouille
description: Les chiots de la Pat'Patrouille acquièrent des super pouvoirs par magie après qu'une météorite a frappé Adventure City. Cependant, les choses tournent mal lorsque Humdinger et un savant fou volent leurs pouvoirs et se transforment en super-vilains. Alors que l'équipe passe à l'action pour sauver la ville, Skye apprend bientôt que même le plus petit chiot peut faire la plus grande différence.

title: Sapatos Pretos
description: No Alentejo de hoje, uma história de amor e morte baseada num caso criminal real.

title: Bleach 4 | Verso En El Infierno
description: Cuando la hermana de Ichigo, Yuzu, es secuestrada por pecadores y se le pide que haga algo por ellos para liberar a su hermana, Ichigo debe encontrar una manera de sacar a su hermana del infierno con la ayuda de Rukia, Renji y Uryu.

title: A menina que acredita em milagres
description: Quando a jovem Sara ouve um pregador dizer que a fé pode mover montanhas, ela começa a orar. De repente, as pessoas em sua cidade são misteriosamente curadas, mas a fama logo cobra seu preço.

title: A Princesa e o Sapo
description: A bela, mas arrogante, Princesa Iria, a única filha do Rei, se esforça para encontrar pretendentes que correspondam à sua alta autoimagem. Preocupado com sua atitude excessivamente perspicaz, o Rei se preocupa com sua felicidade futura e com a perspectiva de que ela possa perder sua herança se não encontrar um par no tempo prescrito para a coroação.

title: الرسالة
description: The Message : لوحة جدارية تاريخية تحكي حياة وعصر النبي محمد، آخر أتباع الديانات الإبراهيمية، بمعنى أنه، وفقًا للإسلام، أكمل وختم الوحي التوحيدي الذي نزل على إبراهيم.

title: A Hora da Sua Morte
description: Countdown (A Hora da Sua Morte) : A nurse downloads an application that predicts the time of a person's death accurately. However, things turn ugly when she discovers that she has only three days to live.

title: Desespero Profundo
description: Presos debaixo d'água quando seu avião cai no oceano, os sobreviventes precisam encontrar uma maneira de escapar enquanto tubarões começam a cercar os destroços.

title: Pajarico
description: Manu, que acaba de completar dez anos, faz sua primeira viagem a Múrcia para passar um tempo com a família de seu pai. Cercado por pomares, mar, natureza e uma família alegre e acolhedora, ele encontrará seu primeiro amor e os primeiros sinais de sua vida adulta.

title: Berenice Procura
description: A taxista Berenice vive uma crise familiar com seu marido machista e seu filho, que está descobrindo sua identidade sexual. O assassinato de um transgênero na praia de Copacabana a faz começar uma investigação por conta própria, o que vira seu mundo de cabeça para baixo

title: Little Lips
description: Um escritor retorna para casa da Primeira Guerra Mundial. Ele desenvolveu um caso muito grave de transtorno de estresse pós-traumático. Ele pensa em suicídio, mas se interessa pela sobrinha de 12 anos do estalajadeiro do lugar onde ele está se recuperando.

title: Silvestre
description: As filhas de um nobre dão abrigo a um estranho. Depois que a visita termina com uma mão decepada, o peregrino assume diferentes identidades para buscar vingança. O nobre desaparece e seu filho mais novo tem que se passar por um cavaleiro para salvá-lo.

title: Maladolescenza
description: Um adolescente deixa de brincar e brigar com seu cão pastor alemão e passa a brincar de brincadeiras de criança — e depois de adulto — com duas meninas igualmente jovens em uma floresta onírica que, com o tempo, se torna assustadora e sombria.

title: A Lagoa Azul O despertar
description: Emmaline e Dean, dois adolescentes de grupos opostos, precisam aprender a sobreviver sem tecnologia ou comodidades modernas depois que acidentalmente vão para uma ilha remota no Caribe.

title: A Hora da Estrela
description: Uma brasileira pobre (Marcélia Cartaxo) trabalha como digitadora na cidade, onde encontra um namorado (José Dumont) e sonha com a felicidade.

title: O Principio da Incerteza
description: The Uncertainty Principle :- Tendo perdido seu lugar entre a elite social, uma viúva se casa novamente e começa uma família

title: Recordações da Casa Amarela
description: Lisboa, 1989. Um pobre idiota de meia-idade, atormentado por uma doença, vive num quarto barato numa pensão familiar, na zona antiga da zona ribeirinha da cidade.

title: Simplesmente Acontece
description: Rosie e Alex são amigos desde a infância e não conseguem se imaginar como um casal. No entanto, quando seguem em direções diferentes, percebem que foram feitos um para o outro.

title: A Prova De Fogo
description: À beira do divórcio, Catherine não quer nada com Caleb. No entanto, o pai de Caleb o desafia a um experimento de 40 dias para amar Catherine incondicionalmente, apesar da rejeição total.

title: Divã
description: In Therapy : Mercedes é uma mulher de 40 anos que vive às voltas com as alegrias e desafios da sociedade contemporânea. Casada e mãe de dois filhos, Mercedes decide, mesmo sem saber bem o porquê, procurar um psicanalista. E, assim, o que antes era apenas uma curiosidade, se transforma em uma experiência devastadora, que provoca uma série de mudanças em sua vida cotidiana.

title: Entre Irmas
description: Duas irmãs, uma morando no campo e a outra na cidade, contam uma com a outra para realizar seus sonhos, quando a sociedade joga sexismo e misoginia contra elas a cada passo do caminho.

title: East West
description: Leste Oeste : Ezequiel, um ex-piloto profissional de corrida, retorna à sua cidade natal após 15 anos para competir em sua última corrida. Ele encontra Stela, um antigo caso; Angelo, o patriarca da família, assim como Pedro, um garoto de 16 anos que sonha em ser piloto.

title: Krampus 2: O Retorno do Demônio
description: Krampus: The Devil Returns : Cinco anos após seu primeiro encontro com a fera que pune crianças desobedientes, o ex-policial Jeremy Duffin é chamado para deter o monstro natalino de uma vez por todas.

title: Gótica Americana
description: Após o acidente com o ônibus da prisão, dois condenados escapam e invadem uma casa de fazenda isolada. O casal tranquilo que mora lá prova ser tudo, menos vítimas.

title: Neighboring Sounds
description: O Som ao Redor : A vida dos moradores de um prédio de apartamentos brasileiro e dos seguranças que ficam encarregados de vigiar as ruas do entorno.

title: Valentine's Town
description: Jude works for a well-known dating service that will develop a cheesy, romantic resort in his hometown of Arrowheart. Local businesswoman Melissa has organized the town against the resort. Melissa is Jude's former high school sweetheart.

title: Peaks and Valleys
description: A reclusive man nurses a traumatized woman back to health after she's thrown from a plane into an Alaskan lake.

title: THE TRAIL
description: A young housewife is stranded alone in the woods after a tragic accident along The Oregon Trail. Far from home, she is tested mentally, physically, and spiritually in a battle for her life.

title: Lost Wilderness
description: During a camping trip, four soon-to-be siblings are encouraged to bond with each other. But their plans to search for a family heirloom turns into a disaster when they all get stuck in the woods.

title: Never Cry Wolf
description: Tyler, a Canadian biologist, embarks on a governmental mission to find out the reason behind the declining population of caribou in the Canadian arctic wilderness.

title: Ferdinando
description: Ferdinand :- A soft-hearted bull, Ferdinand, escapes from Casa del Toro after his father does not return from the bullfight. However, due to a turn of events, he is taken back to the place he escaped from.

title: Branca de Neve e os Sete Anões
description: Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs :- Deixada numa floresta perigosa por sua madrasta malvada, uma princesa é resgatada por sete mineiros anões que a fazem parte de sua casa.

title: A Missed Connection
description: After finding a spark with a woman on a train platform, a photographer posts a missed connection in the newspaper but never hears from her. Five years later, they meet again while on the way to the same wedding - hers.

title: Bunker Project 12
description: Soviet officials pull the plug on a dangerous experiment and seal the evidence in a remote bunker. Years later, a reckless scientist hires some mercenaries to infiltrate the bunker and recover whatever they can.

title: A Country Called Home
description: After her estranged father's death, Ellie travels to Texas, where he spent the last years of his life. Her life changes when she meets a group of intriguing people there.

title: Mr. Morgan's Last Love
description: Matthew, an elderly widower who lives in Paris and speaks little French, gets close to Pauline, a beautiful dance instructor half his age. However, his grown-up children object to their relationship.

title: The Hessen Affair
description: In Frankfurt, Colonel Jack Durant and Lieutenant Kathleen Nash discover a bag full of precious German jewels, and try to smuggle it into New York City.

title: Lethal Seduction
description: Mark, a college freshman, moves out of the protective shadow of his overbearing mother Tanya. Soon he meets Carissa, a seductive older woman, whom Mark's mother and friends suspect to be insane.

title: Not My Life
description: After a car accident, a woman with a seemingly perfect life begins to have visions of her past that suggest she is not who she thinks she is.

title: To Survive
description: When Jonathan finds himself all alone in a post-apocalyptic world, he must fight the forces that seek to destroy him, and survive.

title: Cadia: The World Within
description: Devastated by the loss of their mother, three teenagers discover a mystical realm where they learn about the nature of good versus evil.

title: Double Daddy
description: A teen's life turns upside-down when her boyfriend impregnates both her and a new student at school.

title: Love You Like That
description: A sleepy coastal town springs to life with romance with the sudden appearance of a mysterious woman who washes ashore one day in the nude.

title: Becky
description: A pretty, twisted and dangerous woman becomes obsessed with a happily married man who recently moves into the neighbourhood and wreaks havoc in every aspect of the couple's life.

title: Few Options
description: After a prolonged period of unemployment, an ex-con is forced to take a job with his former crime partners to make ends meet.

title: Once There Was a Winter
description: The Canadian north's unforgiving nature is amplified to chilling effect in this claustrophobic, white-knuckle thriller from Ana Valine (Sitting on the Edge of Marlene). What is supposed to be a quick stop at a remote trailer turns into a standoff between embittered brothers, with an innocent woman (Kate Corbett) caught in the crossfire. As old wounds are reopened and fresh blood is spilled, the wolves at the door pose little threat in comparison to the personal demons being unleashed inside.

title: Invasion Earth
description: We follow a group of addicts who attend therapy together to avoid being sent to prison as a TV journalist tries to expose the group as a scam. However, all of their lives are thrown into chaos with the beginning of an alien invasion.

title: Children of the Corn
description: Two lovers stumble across a small American town where local children have killed the adult population in a bizarre ritual.

title: Carjacked
description: Lorraine Burton, a single mom, is carjacked along with her son, Chad, by a desperate bank robber. They try hard to save themselves from the thief.

title: Pursued
description: A fast rising hi tech executive must protect his career and family from the ruthless tactics of a homicidal corporate headhunter.

title: Looking for Dr. Love
description: Recently divorced hairstylist, Jenny, is on a mission to reconnect with Liam, her college sweetheart. She is shocked to learn that he is Dr. Love, the DJ she listens to on the radio.

title: For the Love of Puppies
description: Animal-lover Amber desperately wants a dog to love. When she falls for Shadow, she takes on her family and city hall to fight for her new best friend in a race against the clock.

title: Hope Springs
description: After being dumped by his fiancee, Colin is stuck in a rundown hotel in a small town where he meets an enchanting girl and romances her. Things change when his ex decides to re-unite with him.

title: Truly Everlasting
description: As the holidays settle in around Houston, Texas, young Austin has but one wish- for a Christmas Daddy. When his mother, Felicia Madaris, learns of his wish, she turns to childhood rival turned family friend, Trask Maxwell, to help fulfill her young son's wish. But soon, Felicia realizes that its not just Austin's Christmas wish that is coming true....

title: What If It Works?
description: Adrian, an irrepressibly chirpy tech nerd, has OCD. Grace, a beautiful street artist, has multiple personality disorder. Although it's a love story that seems impossible, it might just work.

title: Throwback Holiday
description: Jacqueline awakens to find she's become eighteen again, with the chance to go back and relive her senior year of high school, and meet the boy who will grow up to become the man of her dreams.

title: Crossword Mysteries: A Puzzle to Die For
description: When a crossword is found on the murdered body of an art gallery owner, a crossword editor, Tess, discovers clues. She works hand-in-hand with detective Logan to investigate the case.

title: Blind Trust
description: Cassie is accused of killing her boyfriend and best friend. Despite being defended by the best criminal lawyer in town, she loses the case. She sets out to find the person who framed her.

title: Morning Show Mystery: Mortal Mishaps
description: Billie Blessings has gone from beloved chef, restaurant owner, and morning show segment host to the prime suspect in a murder case when one of the executives at the network dies from poisoning.

title: Operation Overreach Universe Part 3: Found
description: Again, Brian Rakell finds himself fighting for his life, just trying to survive. He takes shelter in a place he knows well and then proceeds to find more and more clues to the conspiracies surrounding him.

title: Valentine in the Vineyard
description: Frankie and Nate, two winemakers, strive to plan for a secret wedding on Valentine's Day amidst the challenges that come at work and in their relationship.

title: What We Don'T Say
description: Ben, an aspiring cartoonist is closed off from a recent breakup. While lost in self doubt he meets vivacious and free spirited Juliette. They have an instant connection but she also has plans to move away soon. Regardless, the two decide to spend time together while they can. As their love for each other grows, their time together dwindles and they have to face that love may not be enough for her to stay.

title: Tô de Graça – O Filme
description: Depois de ganhar uma indenização inesperada, Graça decide levar metade dos 14 filhos e filhas para um resort. Mas o plano vai por água abaixo e a família acaba tendo que se acomodar em um camping onde Graça reencontra um antigo crush.

title: Tudo Por Um Popstar
description: Três melhores amigos tentam convencer seus pais a deixá-los assistir a um show de sua banda pop favorita em uma cidade próxima.

title: Asylum of Fear
description: A team of paranormal investigators are hired to inspect a mental institution after two police officers are mysteriously murdered, they discover horrifying clues that reveal the cause of a violent massacre by an insane doctor in the 1960's.

title: Alex & Eve
description: Trouble brews when Alex, a Greek Orthodox schoolteacher, falls in love with Eve, a Lebanese Muslim lawyer, as their families do not accept their relationship.

title: Hell Fire
description: Meet the Antichrist. He's been kidnapped by a group of women who've mistaken him for someone else, and now they're about to find out exactly who they're messing with. One by one the women become possessed by demonic forces and turn on each other. As the bodies begin to pile up, the girls fight for their lives and to save mankind against the Prince of Evil.

title: Cryptic
description: Eight guys from a crime organization in London are sent to guard a coffin.

title: The Trip
description: Four friends in their 30s visit a Pennsylvania farmhouse for a weekend getaway. What began as a relaxing retreat takes a sinister turn when the house reveals its ominous intentions. Their fun quickly spirals into a chilling ordeal.

title: Bloody New Year
description: A group of friends take refuge in an island hotel that is decorated for New Years. The problem is, it's early summer, and soon enough, even the walls themselves are striking out against them.

title: Better Criminal
description: A police officer is forced to work for two warring crime syndicates while under an internal investigation.

title: The Other Side of the Tracks
description: After the death of his girlfriend in a tragic train accident, Josh struggles to deal with the real world. Everything changes for him when he meets a seductive waitress at his high school reunion.

title: Mr & Mrs Smith
description: Un mari et sa femme luttent pour préserver leur mariage jusqu'à ce qu'ils réalisent qu'ils travaillent tous les deux en secret comme assassins. Désormais, leurs missions respectives les obligent à s'entretuer.

title: A Haunted House
description: Malcom and Kisha's lives are turned upside down when Kisha gets possessed by the demon inside their newly-purchased house. Malcolm seeks the help of experts to get his sex life back.

title: The Trial
description: After losing his family in a car accident, attorney McClain is on the verge of committing suicide. His life alters when McClain is assigned with the murder case of the daughter of a business tycoon.

title: Heidi
description: Una huérfana llamada Heidi se muda a los Alpes suizos para vivir con su anciano abuelo, Alpohi. A pesar de tener fama de recluso, Alpohi acaba queriéndola y cuidándola.

title: Let Go And Let God
description: Two people from vastly different worlds question the existence of God after sudden death in their families.

title: The Lady of Heaven
description: After losing his mother in the midst of a war-torn country, an Iraqi child learns the importance and power of patience by discovering the historical story of Lady Fatima and her suffering.

title: The Flood
description: The city of London faces doom when a mega storm coincides with high seas, resulting in a disastrous tidal surge. Rob, a marine engineer, his ex-wife Sam and his father try to save the city.

title: Day Off
description: After his brother's murder, John Gordon, a wrongly imprisoned ex-marine, takes 24-hour leave to avenge the crime.

title: The Cold Father
description: A 55-year-old man desperate for truth uses a lie-detection machine to interrogate all the suspects involve in the daughter's disappearance, all while battling his inner demons and uncovering hidden secrets.

title: Sunfall
description: Trevor and his scientist colleague Nick discover that the sun has been pushed towards Earth, causing all sorts of fire-related disasters as the planet begins heating up rapidly.

title: Tornado Warning
description: Alien Tornado : Extraterrestrials appear as destructive "electrical tornadoes" on Earth.

title: Nola
description: Tired of her stepfather's abusive nature, Nola runs away to New York, hoping to find her real father. Her life changes when she meets Margaret, who makes her an assistant in her escort service.

title: 20.0 Megaquake
description: As a megaquake threatens San Francisco, a series of foreshocks wreaks havoc across the city. Now an elite team of emergency service and disaster experts converge on the anticipated epicentre, working tirelessly to save as many lives as possible before the city is crushed into oblivion.

title: Horror Story
description: दोस्तों का एक समूह एक दूसरे दोस्त को विदाई देने के लिए मिलता है, जो विदेश जा रहा है। वे एक भूतिया होटल में रात बिताने का फैसला करते हैं, जो उनकी ज़िंदगी को एक ऐसे तरीके से बदल देता है जिसकी उन्होंने कम से कम उम्मीद की थी।

title: Permafrost
description: In a collapsed frozen world, factions fight for power. A lone bounty hunter at the center of it all saves a little girl who helps him find redemption from his past.

title: The Tomorrow War
description: The world is stunned when a group of time travellers arrive from the year 2051 to deliver an urgent message: thirty years in the future, mankind is losing a global war against a deadly alien species.

title: Warhorse One
description: A Navy SEAL master chief must guide a child to safety through a gauntlet of Taliban insurgents.

title: The Huntress: Rune of the Dead
description: After her father embarks on a Viking journey indefinitely, young Runa takes over his responsibilities back home. Soon, Runa begins to experience nightmares and receives some disturbing news.

title: The Deputy's Wife
description: When an outlaw is captured and scheduled to hang, the local deputy's wife makes a fateful decision that will forever change her life.

title: The Veil
description: Redemption gives way to a reckoning when a reclusive retired priest shelters a young Amish runaway in crisis, only to reveal a mystery that ties her to a terrifying encounter from his youth- and the aurora that rages overhead.

title: Wake Up
description: A suburban community is shaken when a pair of teenagers mysteriously disappear, uncovering a darkness hiding in plain sight. Tension builds, lives intersect as the community races against time to save their youth in this crime thriller inspired by true events.

title: Never Leave Alive
description: Two people on a deserted island find themselves hunted by a sociopathic ex-KGB agent and his brutally violent partner.

title: Titanic II
description: Honouring the 100th anniversary of its namesake, a modern luxury liner called 'Titanic 2' sets sail along the same path. When a looming iceberg spells doom, the crew struggles to avoid a similar fate.

title: Hyena Road
description: During the war in Afghanistan, an intelligence officer who has never killed anyone on duty, employs an expert but merciless sniper to locate a famous Afghan warrior who shunned warfare long ago.

title: Beyond Your Consciousness
description: Amanda, a psychiatrist, believes her home is haunted by a murdered woman's spirit. She and her husband George search for the woman's missing daughter, unveiling shocking truths about Amanda's perceptions and the situation's complexity.

title: Tourist
description: December 2020. Former police officer Grisha Dmitriev arrives in the Central African Republic with a small group of Russian instructors. Grisha's assignment does not seem complicated, because the instructors' tasks are only to teach the local army soldiers the basics of tactics and methods of fighting. However, everything goes wrong from the start. Several bandit groups march on the capital to stage a coup d'Start in the country. Russian instructors together with their charges fight back against the bandits. But for Grisha, who has never taken part in military operations, this business trip turns into a living hell.

title: The Seeds
description: Tobias' quest for the one takes a chilling turn when a woman's ominous past triggers a series of accidents that threaten to unravel his life.

title: London Gangsters
description: Ryan and his brother James stumble upon a conspiracy after James is falsely accused of a grave offence.

title: The Legend of the Five
description: A group of teenage misfits find an ancient relic that turns their world upside down, and discover they have the responsibility of stopping an age-old evil from destroying the world.

title: Far from Home
description: A teenage girl and her father driving cross-country become stranded when their car runs out of gas in a remote Nevada desert town and they're forced to stay in a dilapidated trailer park where a serial killer lurks.

title: Over the Red River
description: A tenacious young widow braves the perilous desert to free her kidnapped sister and wreak vengeance on the outlaws who murdered her husband. She crosses paths with an ex-member of the same gang that ruined her life.

title: Un-Resolved
description: Upon his release from prison, an ex-convict tries to make up for lost time with his youngest daughter, who is dying, and reconnect with his oldest daughter, who's befriended a deadly enemy from his past.

title: Save the Wedding
description: A bridesmaid must work with her college nemesis, the best man at the wedding, in order to save the marriage after the bride gets cold feet.

title: Charm Of Love
description: An art historian on a quest to find the Lovers Stone in the Caribbean for a rich benefactor falls in love with a hotelier with trust issues.

title: Finding Love in Saint Lucia
description: An Ornithologist and a Journalist partner up to save an endangered bird species in the jungle of Saint Lucia. They immediately fall in love with the nature, and in the process, they also fall for each other.

title: The Wine of Summer
description: James quits his job at a law firm to realise his long-held dream of becoming an actor. A play motivates him to go to Spain where an encounter with a playwright changes his life forever

title: Forever My Girl
description: Liam Page, a successful country singer, returns to his hometown after several years and encounters his high school sweetheart, Josie, whom he had once ditched at the altar

title: Tell Me I Love You
description: Desperate for money, three best friends devise an outrageous plan to get married and inherit money from a trust fund.

title: Richard The Lionheart
description: King Henry II chooses his son, Richard, to be his heir and in order to prove his worth, he sends him to a prison in which the captives must keep fighting enemies to survive.

title: A Cabana
description: Após o desaparecimento de seu filho mais novo, Mack Phillips fica severamente deprimido. Sua vida toma um rumo improvável quando ele recebe uma carta misteriosa pedindo para ele visitar uma cabana.

title: Crush
description: An aspiring young artist joins her high school track team and later discovers what real love feels like when she finds herself falling for an unexpected teammate.

title: Bleach : The Diamond Dust Rebellion
description: Se desata una batalla campal para recuperar un artefacto robado que contiene poderes misteriosos. Mientras Ichigo cura la herida de Toshiro, una multitud misteriosa aparece una vez más y los ataca.

title: Amor De Media Noche
description: Una adolescente que sufre de sensibilidad a la luz solar se enamora de un chico. Justo cuando empieza a vivir sus sueños, su condición empieza a empeorar y mantenerlo en secreto se vuelve mucho más difícil.

title: Romance Retreat
description: Dana decides to spend some time at a yoga retreat where she falls in love with the person who is at the heart of a big scandal she herself exposed.

title: Mr. Manhattan
description: Mason Bradley's life turns upside down when he unexpectedly becomes the sole guardian of his late brother's kids after prioritizing his law career and ending his engagement.

title: Before All Others
description: A young woman's world is turned upside down when she is struck by a paralyzing disease and forced to live with her estranged grandmother.

title: The Bad Orphan
description: Focuses on Jessica and Karl, Rhiannon's loving parents, whose family, after many years of striving to expand, is thrilled to adopt Gabby, an 8-year-old orphan born with special needs.

title: After.Life
description: After meeting with an accident, Anna wakes up to find herself being prepared for funeral by a funeral director. The director tells her that she is just in a limbo and will soon transition to death

title: Bloodslinger
description: Billy Bloodslinger is resurrected from the dead and begins the search for his missing gold, killing anyone who gets in his way.

title: Shadowlands
description: This autobiographical film chronicles the life of a world-renowned writer, C.S. Lewis and his romantic relationship with an American poet, Joy Davidman.

title: The Unwanted
description: Carmilla travels to a small rural town to find out what happened to her mother.

title: Deviant Love
description: After her marriage falls apart, a vulnerable woman falls for a new man's seemingly perfect facade and she soon discovers the shocking truth about him. He is an obsessively possessive and dangerous paranoid

title: Love At The Lodge
description: Sparks fly between an uptight lawyer and an indebted lodge owner as she tries to get him to sell it to her boss's cousin.

title: A Deadly Adoption
description: Robert and Sarah are a married couple who are doing very well in their respective careers. They want to adopt a child, so they take in a young pregnant girl into their home hoping to adopt her child.

title: Exit Strategy
description: James must move in with his girlfriend of three months after being evicted from his place, and soon he discovers that he doesn't want to be with her any more. His hope is to get her to break up with him but still let him sleep on the couch

title: Joe Dirt 2
description: Joe Dirt, a family man from the heartland of the USA, is transported back in time. As a result, he sets out to reunite with his loved ones in the present.

title: The Devil Conspiracy
description: A powerful biotech company has breakthrough technology that allows it to clone history's most influential people. Behind this company is a cabal of Satanists who steal the shroud of Turin, putting them in possession of Jesus Christ's DNA -- the ultimate offering to the devil. Hoping to save mankind, Archangel Michael soon comes to Earth to stop the devil's conspiracy once and for all.

title: Amy's F-It List
description: A young woman who suddenly learns she's dying sets out on an expedited mission with her relentlessly honest sister to right the wrongs of the world.

title: Dirty Teacher
description: Danny and Jamie are a happy couple, who attends high school together. However, things turn bad between them when their schoolteacher, Molly Matson, starts interfering in their relationship.

title: Legend Of Gobi
description: The king forbids music in his kingdom and is cursed. His right hand man secretly plots to take the throne for himself by killing the king.

title: Cronus
description: A genius who suffers from amnesia tries to find out about his identity using a memory extractor machine he built. Soon, his mission turns reckless.

title: After The Wait
description: Ginny is deciding to stop and commit herself to God's plans, After a bad break-up. Ginny's sister and brother-in-law are setting her up on a blind date.

title: The Royal Nanny
description: Working under cover as a nanny, an MI5 agent must resist the charms of Prince Colin while keeping the royal family safe during Christmastime.

title: Another Woman's Husband
description: Laurel bonds with her swimming instructor Susan as she helps her improve her marital life with Johnny. However, the two are unaware that Johnny is in a relationship with both of them

title: Edge of America
description: Kenny, an African American, accepts a job as a teacher at a Native American school. He faces great difficulty to fit in, but things further worsen when he has to coach the girls' basketball team.

title: For the Love of Money
description: When shadowy figures make the mistake of threatening her daughter, a woman gets pulled back into the life she never wanted.

title: Change of Heart
description: Helen owns a lovely hotel, which unfortunately attracts less costumers due to the remote location. However, everything changes when a reality show producer visits the hotel.

title: Broke
description: Ben Kelly, a sportsperson with a terrible reputation, struggles to deal with his gambling addiction. However, through all his troubles, his ardent fan stands by his side and helps him.

title: Where's the Money
description: Del learns from his father that there are one million dollars hidden in the basement of an old house. When he goes to collect the money, he sees that the house has been turned into a fraternity home.

title: Dance Battle America
description: A successful businessman finds himself with the task of training a group of misfits for an underground dance competition. Having no dance experience, he calls a professional instructor to help him.

title: The Engagement Plot
description: After getting her heart broken on a wildly popular dating reality show, teacher Hanna Knight returns to her small-town Colorado life.

title: Caged Birds
description: When an innocent prank against a white bully goes horribly wrong, three Black high school students from the suburbs are forced to commit a cover-up.

title: Children of the Corn: Genesis
description: After getting stranded in a remote area, Tim and Allie seek shelter. When they encounter strange happenings, they investigate further, only to discover a bizarre cult-worshipping church.

title: Every Day
description: Maddie, who was raped in high school but not believed, attempts to rebuild her life ten years later

title: Animator
description: An artist gains the power to draw the future. When his girlfriend commits suicide, he learns he can also erase the past, with chilling consequences.

title: Miami Heat
description: Days before Christmas, the daughter of a retired Spetsnaz operative is kidnapped. In order to save her, the agent must rely on his old skills.

title: Honest Thief
description: Tom Dolan contacts the FBI to confess to stealing a large amount of money in the past years so that he can start his life with a clean conscience. But he gets double-crossed by two FBI agents.

title: The Substitute 2
description: After his brother is killed ruthlessly, Carl becomes a teacher in a school, hoping to find the murderers who he believes are members of a gang.

title: A Stone in the Water
description: Heartbroken by the death of her only son, an eccentric farmwoman mistakenly believes that Alex, a young city girl, is pregnant with her son's child. What Martha doesn't know is that Alex was involved in a robbery that ended in murder.

title: China Salesman
description: Yan Jian, a young Chinese engineer, competes against Michael, a French spy, in a contest that allows the winner to control the first mobile technology in Africa.

title: Nocturnal Activity
description: A woman learns that a malevolent spirit is trying to seduce her in order to possess her body for a vengeful missio

title: Mr Crispin
description: Eileen Daly and the I See The Dead team are sent to investigate Mr Crispin, and will potentially unearth a terrible secret!

title: A Tiger's Tail
description: A tiger cub runs away from an animal sanctuary and enters the home of a boy. When the cub's naughtiness begins to damage the boy's home, he and his pal decide to return the cub to the sanctuary.

title: Sweet Taste of Souls
description: Four musicians battle a sinister force after they become trapped inside a deranged woman's painting.

title: Blood Widow
description: While exploring a dilapidated boarding school that was destroyed during a massacre, Laurie and Hugh find themselves tracked down by the incident's sole survivor, who doesn't wish to be disturbed.

title: Dark Lullabies: An Anthology by Michael Coulombe
description: A thrilling horror anthology by Michael Coloumbe to tuck you in and rock you to sleep.

title: Rapturious
description: A drug-addled rap artist, Rapturious, is unable to tell whether his horrific visions are just that or if he's actually committing vicious crimes.

title: Finding Hope
description: Pastor Roger Minassian leaves the security of his pastorate and takes to the streets to help disadvantaged youth gang members; he transforms the life of a 16-year-old gang member with no future prospects and a pregnant girlfriend.

title: Comfort
description: A courier boy escorts an important client's daughter for two days. They develop a close connection, and even a romance, as they explore the Los Angeles food scene.

title: Adventures Of A Boy Genius
description: When a series of thefts take place in school, and Emmett teams up with an older person to crack the case. He must get to the bottom of the case to clear a loved one's name.

title: Angels Fallen : Warriors of Peace
description: Called by a higher power, an Iraq War veteran embarks on a mission to stop a fallen angel from raising an army of the dead to take over the world.

title: Summoning the Spirit
description: Carla and Dean decide to escape the city, only to find themselves on the remote land of a strange cult claiming a connection to the flesh-eating Bigfoot. They must save themselves and uncover the terrifying truth of the cult's prophecy.

title: Rust 3
description: Seven years after Hotel Fear, Heather faces its reopening and Travis's return.

title: Live Survival
description: After escaping a homeless shelter infested with flesh eating zombies, cops discover the whole world is in chaos. They team up with more survivors and fight to escape the city while still searching for a way to get rid of the zombies.

title: Blood and Oil
description: A small village in Nigeria does not have drinking water, sustainable farming or fishing. However, its fate changes when big corporations learn that it has reserves of oil.

title: First Contact
description: Two estranged siblings meet at their late father's farmhouse and open a portal allowing an ancient monster into their world.

title: Why Women Trip
description: Zori Johnson falls in love hard and fast, yet always seems to be hurt by those closest to her. When she meets the man of her dreams, their love connection spurs her to open her heart once again

title: The Stepdaughter
description: A woman seeks revenge on her biological mother after spending her childhood being shunted between various foster homes and institutions. Having charmed her way into her mother's family ranch, she waits for an opportunity to exact vengeance.

title: Planet Dune
description: A mission to rescue a marooned base on a desert planet turns deadly when the crew finds itself hunted by the planet's apex predators: massive carnivorous sandworms.

title: Black Easter
description: When a billionaire gives a group of young scientists unlimited resources to study the science of matter transfer, the scientists unlock the secrets of time travel. But they soon find out that the project is backed by a militant extremist group, and the billionaire plans to go back in time and prove that Jesus never rose from the dead.

title: Kiss of the Tarantula
description: Susan loves collecting tarantulas and lives with her parents in a mortuary. She uses the spiders to scare her classmates who constantly torment her.

title: Second Chances
description: Following an accident, Sunny Matthews, a 10-year-old girl, moves with her overprotective mother. While adapting to her new life, she develops an affinity for Ben, a rodeo star, and Ginger, a horse.

title: Iron Brothers
description: Fur trappers Abel and Henry Iron live in the Rocky Mountains. An encounter with Shoshone Indians leaves one Indian dead and the Iron Brothers on the run. In the end, they will learn if the bond of brotherhood is enough to save them.

title: The Supreme Fighter
description: This is Action, Thriller movie about supreme fighter.

title: Deer Crossing
description: Maggie Chancelor and her son Cole are on their way to visit family when they are involved in an accident, they are found by Lukas, a farmer, who takes them to his farm but they are never seen again. Eight years later the father gets a call

title: Run for the Dream
description: An Olympic sprinter (Charlayne Woodard) overcomes Graves' disease to win the gold medal in the 1992 Summer Games.

title: Forbidden Empire
description: Cartographer Jonathan Green discovers a mythical village inhabited by mysterious and strange creatures when he sets out on a mission to map the uncharted territories of Transylvania.

title: Orphan Horse
description: A young runaway hides out in the barn of a retired horse trainer and is offered shelter in exchange for her help with a troubled horse.

title: One Last Night
description: On their first date, Alex and Zoe venture out to see a movie at a local cinema. After becoming so engaged in a heated discussion, they do not notice the cinema closing, leaving them locked inside.

title: Wind Dancer
description: A young girl, who suffers from an injury, is helped by her family and her supportive horse to ride again

title: Jack and Jill 3
description: 10 years after the last vicious killings on the hill, Jack and Jill are back to slaughter the cast and crew of a live streaming internet show who are looking to uncover the secrets of the legend.

title: Guns Of Eden
description: Four weekend campers witness an execution in the woods by the local sheriff and his deputies. The campers attempt to flee, but the deputies seal off the mountain, and the sheriff gets an armed militia to hunt the strangers.

title: Scream
description: In this fan film set twenty-two years after Scream 3, the daughter of Sidney Prescott returns to Woodsboro and is terrorized by a new Ghostface killer.

title: Crated
description: A group of six people mysteriously wake up in crates in the middle of nowhere. Their memory is somehow wiped from their minds with the exception of their names and the group is left to question who put them there, and why

title: The Alphabet Killer
description: Detective Megan Paige investigates the murder of a young girl. She becomes obsessed with the crime, causing her supervisor to take her off the case, until years later when the killer strikes again.

title: Deadly  Patient
description: Hillary Spenser, a young doctor, saves the life of Gregory Lipton who meets with an accident. Things change when he becomes obsessed with her and tries to kill everyone in her lif

title: Weight
description: Dub's crew is made up of Rob, Turk and Junkyard. Together, they run the west side drug business. The boys are not pleased when Charlotte takes over. But she isn't phased and quickly shows them why Dub chose her to take over.

title: Ex Next Door
description: Katie and Dan's life becomes hell when his obsessed ex-girlfriend Louisa moves in next door. She tries her best to separate the couple by any means necessary.

title: Need For Speed
description: A street racer is framed by a rival who is also a wealthy business associate in a murder case. Upon his release, the street racer devises a plan with revenge in mind.
