title: Street Code Broken
description: Two lifelong friends come to a crossroads when one decides that street life isn't what he wants. Loyalty is tested when the unwritten rules of street code protocol are broken.

title: Making Moves
description: Making Moves that risks everything over comfort and stability.

title: Hope of Escape
description: An enslaved mother and daughter in the antebellum U.S. desperately plan their escape after learning they're about to be sold and separated forever

title: An Uncommon Grace
description: Grace Conner, an army nurse, returns to her grandmother's farm to live a peaceful life. However, she soon has to investigate a murder in the region while falling in love with her Amish neighbour.

title: Seven Angels
description: Seven Angels, a famous Girl Band from Indonesia, consisting of Stella, Carla, Dian, Anggun, Amy, Tari and Mika go on vacation to Melbourne, Australia, where they socialize with a local singer named Mark. Mark takes the girls of Seven Angels to Aradale Lunatic Asylum, a former haunted asylum with a dark and horrific history.

title: A Pinch Of Portugal
description: When a celebrity chef walks off his show, prep cook Anna must step into the spotlight and make the show her own, with help from her cameraman and Portuguese location scout.

title: O Garoto
description: Uma mulher abandona seu filho recém-nascido junto com um bilhete para quem o encontrar. O Vagabundo tropeça na criança e, embora inicialmente relutante, o acolhe e o cria como se fosse seu.

title: Rapiña
description: Dos vecinos presencian un accidente aéreo y deciden confiscar cualquier cosa de valor al fallecido.

title: A Incrível História de Adaline
description: " Adaline, que tem 29 anos há oito décadas, conhece e se apaixona perdidamente por Ellis. Ela é forçada a tomar uma decisão que mudará sua vida depois que uma reunião com os pais dele ameaça expor seu segredo."

title: Smart House
description: An online influencer is trapped in a smart home by a sinister hacker, and forced to start a strange live stream while her family and friends fight to get her free.

title: Sea of Lies
description: A couple desperate to save their marriage after both having affairs, set out on a sailing holiday, but their best laid plans backfire when they encounter a stranded yacht and what then becomes peril at sea.

title: Hell Ride
description: Pistolero, a biker, and his brother, The Gent, and another mysterious biker, Comanche, set out to avenge the death of Pistolero's lover at the hands of a rival biker gang, the 666ers.

title: paixão sem limites
description: Uma garota rica e sofisticada que respeita os outros se apaixona por um garoto relutante que adora participar de corridas ilegais de bicicleta e tem fome de perigo e risco.

title: Relação Perigosa
description: Um casal passa a lua de mel em uma cabana em uma pequena ilha no meio de um lago na floresta. Não há energia nem conexão de celular. Ele começa a se comportar de forma estranha, não deixando ela sair da ilha. Ela não sabe nadar

title: Ghost Graduation
description: Modesto, un maestro que posee habilidades paranormales, ayuda a algunos espíritus perdidos a completar sus graduaciones y deshacerse de ellos de la escuela para siempre.

title: Los SICARIOS Del Cartel
description: El Jefe del Cartel de los Sicarios, Don Aurelio, es desafiado por "EL COCHILOCO" ya que su hijo Luis, es testigo de un secuestro y es identificado por uno de los plagiarios y desata una persecucion agresiva para silenciarlo.

title: Under Spanish Skies
description: A reclusive artist invites old friends to her farm in Spain and tells them about a suicide pact she made with her dead husband. Her friends must reveal secrets from the past to change her mind.

title: Flor del desierto la película
description: " Waris, nacida en el seno de una familia nómada en Somalia, decide huir a las tierras de Mogadiscio a los 13 años cuando descubre que su padre está interesado en casarse con ella"

title: Un Don Exceptional
description: " Frank, un hombre soltero que cría a su genial sobrina, Mary, se ve envuelto en una batalla legal con su madre, Evelyn, por su custodia. Sin embargo, Evelyn hará cualquier cosa para que Mary complete el proyecto de su madre."

title: 12 Horas Para Ei Fin Del Mundo
description: Una lluvia de meteoritos detrás de un asteroide que pasaba estaba destinada a ser un espectáculo. A Lera, sin embargo, no le importa nada mientras lucha con sus propios problemas de adolescencia. Los meteoritos son mucho más grandes de lo esperado y se dirigen directamente a la Tierra.

title: El Cuervo
description: Eric Draven y su prometida son brutalmente asesinados. Cuando misteriosamente regresa de entre los muertos con la ayuda de un cuervo, este comienza a guiarlo hacia sus asesinos

title: Indiferencia El Profesor
description: Henry, un profesor suplente que intenta no encariñarse con nadie, involuntariamente ve su vida transformada por tres mujeres con las que se cruza, una alumna, una compañera profesora y una prostituta.

title: Enamórate
description: Enamorate es la historia de dos jóvenes almas enamoradas, Celeste y Yahir, quienes enfrentarán obstáculos, pero su amor mutuo los ayudará a luchar por alcanzar sus sueños. Celeste es una chica joven, audaz y llena de vida. Ella es la alegría de su hogar.

title: ABC de amor
description: Gabe, de diez años, vive en Manhattan y se enamora por primera vez de Rosemary. Está confundido acerca de sus sentimientos ya que también lidia con el proceso de divorcio de sus padres.

title: Atrapados Bajo El Agua
description: Atrapados bajo el agua cuando su avión se estrella en el océano, los supervivientes deben encontrar una manera de escapar mientras los tiburones comienzan a rodear los restos.

title: Malas Madres
description: "Cuando tres madres con exceso de trabajo, Amy, Carla y Kiki, se ven empujadas más allá de sus límites, deciden eludir sus responsabilidades y llevar la vida que aman."

title: Second Act
description: Maya, una mujer con poca formación académica pero mucha inteligencia callejera, consigue un trabajo en una empresa corporativa cuando un amigo le crea un perfil falso. Ahora debe vivir la mentira de manera convincente.

title: Double Dad
description: " Enquanto sua mãe está no exterior, uma mulher de 18 anos que viveu toda a sua vida em uma comunidade hippie foge para o mundo real para encontrar seu pai biológico."

title: Bem Bom
description: Quatro garotas que formam uma banda pop em 1979 desafiam a atitude da sociedade em relação à cultura pop. Eles alcançaram grande sucesso e se tornaram um grande sucesso.

title: L'enfant
description: Após o parto, a adolescente Sonia (Déborah François) volta para casa e descobre que seu namorado, o irresponsável criminoso Bruno (Jérémie Segard), sublocou seu apartamento. Sônia rastreia Bruno na rua e, depois que o casal passa a noite junto, decidem começar uma nova vida com o bebê. Mas na manhã seguinte, Bruno vende o filho por dinheiro, deixando Sônia em estado de choque. Abalado com a decisão dela de prestar queixa contra ele, Bruno sai em busca do bebê.

title: Sanitarium
description: "Sanitarium" is an original series that consists of segments based on particular patients of a mental institution and what drove them to madness.

title: A Night in Old Mexico
description: " Después de verse obligado a vender su propiedad y mudarse a un parque de casas rodantes, Red Bovie decide emprender un viaje por carretera con su nieto. Sin embargo, no están preparados para lo que está por suceder."

title: Memory
description: La vida estructurada de la trabajadora social Sylvia queda destrozada cuando Saul la sigue a casa después de su reunión de la escuela secundaria. Su encuentro sorpresa los impacta profundamente a ambos al abrir la puerta al pasado.

title: Sombras de un crimen
description: " El detective Phillip Marlowe se ve envuelto en una investigación con una familia adinerada en Bay City, California, después de que una hermosa rubia lo contrata para encontrar a su antiguo amante"

title: La boda de Rosa
description: Una mujer atrapada en el drama de su familia y su trabajo decide finalmente hacerse cargo de su vida casándose consigo misma.

title: Dead Easy
description: An adulterous ad executive decides to have his equally unfaithful wife killed.

title: Curse Of The Mayans
description: Dr. Alan Green an American Archelogist leads Danielle Noble an her team of cave divers on an expedition searching the Mayan ancient records. Instead of finding glory they will find hell hidden in the underwater caves of Xibalba.
genres: Action, Drama, Horror, Mystery, Thriller, Sci-fi

title: Island of the Dolls 2
description: A documentary crew visits the Island of the Dolls, where they encounter Santana, a sinister spirit inhabiting a powerful doll, who begins to hunt them down relentlessly.

title: Pet Graveyard
description: A group of teens are tormented by the Grim Reaper and his pet after undergoing an experiment that allows them to revisit the dead.

title: Agua y Fuego
description: " Hasmet escapa de las leyes no escritas de Oriente y se enamora de Yagmur, una joven ingenua sin experiencia en las amargas realidades de la vida."

title: A princesa e o sapo
description: A bela, mas arrogante, Princesa Iria, a única filha do Rei, se esforça para encontrar pretendentes que correspondam à sua alta autoimagem. Preocupado com sua atitude excessivamente criteriosa, o Rei se preocupa com sua felicidade futura e com a perspectiva de que ela pode perder sua herança se não encontrar um par no tempo prescrito para a coroação. Buscando clareza, a Princesa Iria confessa seu dilema para a noite e ouve uma voz em troca! Ela encontrará magicamente o amor verdadeiro por trás da ilusão de reflexões vãs ou um casamento arranjado será seu destino? Todos ficarão encantados e divertidos na busca da Princesa Iria para encontrar o príncipe encantado neste filme de animação altamente divertido do conto clássico, a princesa e o sapo.

title: Paixão sem limites
description: Uma garota rica e sofisticada que respeita os outros se apaixona por um garoto relutante que adora participar de corridas ilegais de bicicleta e tem fome de perigo e risco.

title: A Girl From Mogadishu
description: Based on the testimony of Ifrah Ahmed, who, having made the extraordinary journey to escape war-torn Somalia, emerged as one of the world's foremost international activists against Gender Based Violence and Female Genital Mutilation.

title: Kal Ho Naa Ho
description: Naina, a girl living a dreary life, finds herself a new person when Aman walks into her life. Even though she loves him, Aman claims to be a married man and convinces Rohit, her friend, to woo her.

title: Awaken The Shadowman
description: Two estranged brothers, Adam and Jake, set out to search their mother who disappears mysteriously. Things change when they discover that a supernatural force targeting their family.

title: Monster
description: On their first wedding anniversary, Lucky Singh, an entrepreneur from Punjab walks into the lives of Anil Chandra and Bhamini. Little do they know that this man will change their future

title: Comboio de Sal e Açucar
description: The Train of Salt and Sugar : Uma viagem de trem muito perigosa através da guerra em Moçambique. Passageiros civis são protegidos e assediados por uma tropa de soldados indisciplinados a bordo para lutar contra um exército rebelde no mato. Todos devem trabalhar juntos para consertar trilhos sabotados e chegar em segurança.

title: Exhume
description: Based on true events, Patrick and his wife Karen Connor are hired by the state to exhume bodies resting under a closed down reform school known for the sadistic torture and murder of young boys in the early 1900's. During this horrific excavation they are met with unnatural forces causing them to question their sanity and will to live

title: Black Widow
description: Journalist Mel is suspicious about the woman her pal Danny is dating. So, with the help of an assistant, Mel gets investigating the rich but mysterious woman, all the while endangering her own safety.

title: The Facility
description: In a facility, seven strangers are invited to participate in the testing of a new drug. As the medical trial progresses, the side-effects of the drug causes the patients to descend into madness.

title: Her Best Move
description: Young soccer player Sara juggles her life at home, romance, school and sports while she struggles to reach her goal of becoming a part of the US National Team.

title: Safe
description: Mei, a 12-year-old girl, is chased by Russian mobsters, Chinese Triads and corrupt policemen for the information she holds. She finds relief in the form of Luke Wright, a fighter who shields her.

title: Sky Sharks
description: A team of geologists who uncover a Nazi laboratory in icy Antarctica must protect the world from the lethal attack of zombies.

title: Cabin 28
description: A family's day of fun at a remote getaway cabin turns into a brutal battle for survival as nightfall brings masked strangers to the cabin.

title: The Shepherd: Border Patrol
description: A former New Orleans cop arrives in New Mexico to take a job with the border patrol, and discovers that he has to battles ex-navy seals who are trying to traffic drugs from Mexico into the USA.

title: Redwood Massacre: Annihilation
description: The hunters become the hunted after a stranger obsessed with the Redwood Farm murders convinces bereaved family members to venture into the wilderness in hope of proving the existence of the notorious burlap bag-masked maniac.

title: Three Weeks, Three Kids
description: Tasked with taking care of her nieces and nephew, a carefree woman struggles to parent her young charges. Until a handsome neighbour steps in with some unexpected gifts.

title: The Surrogate
description: A married couple, struggling to have a child, hires a young woman to be their surrogate, but soon discovers she has a bizarre and deadly agenda.

title: The Magic Of Ordinary Days
description: An educated young woman becomes pregnant out of wedlock during World War II. Her family experiences acute embarrassment. They compel her to wed a lonesome farmer to give her baby a fatherly figure.

title: Time Changer
description: A Bible professor from 1890 is taken 100 years into the future by one of his acquaintances to show him the effects his manuscript has had on the world.

title: Left Behind
description: A TV journalist chances upon a biological invention that coincides with a massive destruction on the other side of the earth. He suspects it to be the end of the world. Could the two events be linked?

title: Where The Heart Is
description: Abandoned by her boyfriend, Novalee, a 17-year-old pregnant girl, takes shelter in a supermarket. However, when she delivers her baby and becomes a national sensation, she tries to rebuild her life.

title: The Opportunists
description: All Victor Kelly (Christopher Walken) really wants is to be a responsible man, earn an honest living, and in so doing, redeem himself for the lifetime of trouble he has brought down on his small, fractured family. But Vic's skills as an auto mechanic are not nearly as marketable as his safe-cracking skills, and he soon finds himself risking everything for a chance to make an easy score

title: Samantha: An American Girl Holiday
description: When Nellie, a domestic helper, and her sisters are sent to an orphanage with a cruel matron, it is up to her friend Samantha to help them escape.

title: Picnic
description: Seeking work from a wealthy college friend, a drifter (Josh Brolin) arrives in Kansas and falls for his pal's girlfriend (Gretchen Mol).

title: Stormy Weathers
description: Private detective Stormy Weathers is beautiful, intelligent and has a knack for solving crime. She uses her skills to put crooks behind bars.

title: Python
description: After a military plane crash near a small American town, a giant man-eating snake set off on a killing spree. The locals must find a way to eliminate the snake with the help of a scientist who can kill it.

title: The Terminator
description: The Terminator, a cyborg assassin from the future, attempts to find and kill Sarah Connor, a waitress who is destined to give birth to a man who will save humankind from extinction.

title: 100 Days
description: Devi, a clairvoyant woman, has a vision of her sister, Rama, getting murdered. After her sister goes missing, she tracks the clues to identify the murderer.

title: Zulmi
description: Raj is hired as a bodyguard for Komal, and the two grow closer to each other over time. However, things get complicated when he comes across Nihal, the man who molested his sister.

title: Zaalim
description: A law student who is short-tempered has committed murder in his childhood. Years later, when his sister is raped and killed, he goes on a murderous spree once again.

title: Zakhm
description: A boy, born into a family of varying religions, finds himself embroiled in communal riots. Soon, his mother's death becomes an issue raised to fulfil political agendas.

title: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara
description: Friends Kabir, Imran and Arjun take a vacation in Spain before Kabir's marriage. The trip turns into an opportunity to mend fences, heal wounds, fall in love with life and combat their worst fears.

title: Ziddi
description: Deva, a short-tempered man, is a protector of justice and is greatly feared. He saves the CM in an assassination attempt and wants to punish the culprits responsible for the death of his siblings.

title: Zameen
description: When a few terrorists hijack an Indian aeroplane and demand for their leader's release, ACP Jaydev and Colonel Ranvir Singh team up to punish the perpetrators and thwart their evil plans.

title: Zamane Se Kya Darna
description: Since childhood, Vikram has held a deep grudge against his father for deserting him as a boy. Will his attraction to an unlikely love interest cure him of his resentment, or will it make things worse?

title: 16 Wishes
description: A teenage girl makes 16 wishes before her 16th birthday and is amazed to find them coming true. However, her happiness turns out to be short-lived as all her wishes start backfiring on her.

title: Sleeper Agent
description: A man's dream comes true when he finally gets the opportunity to work as a sleeper agent. Unaware of the ramifications of working as a spy, he gets caught up in a web of espionage and betrayal.

title: Dimensions
description: Stephen (Henry Lloyd-Hughes), a brilliant young scientist, becomes obsessed with finding a way to go back to the past after a tragic event.

title: The Magician's Raincoat
description: Three kids discover a magical raincoat that transports them into the body of its owner, a cursed magician. With a scorned witch hot on their trail, they must solve the mystery of the raincoat and break its curse before it's too late.

title: Solver
description: Luke Williams, a young man, embarks on a quest to solve a mysterious puzzle, which leads him to a web of dark secrets after the death of his grandfather.

title: Unsettled
description: Two returning college students, Andrew and Jesse, move into an old off-campus house and experience unexplainable things due to a past tragedy that remains "Unsettled".

title: Perfect Sisters
description: Sandra and Beth, fed up with their mother's alcoholism and abusive boyfriends, plan to kill her and put an end to this unrest in their lives.

title: Teenage Girl: Skip Day
description: On senior skip day, the cool kid convinces the class nerd to skip school. They run into the school fashionista and a punk rocker, and the four get into all sorts of trouble while avoiding the school principal.

title: City Hall
description: An innocent boy is killed in a shootout between a policeman and a member of a mob. Even as tensions escalate, the Deputy Mayor steps in, only to discover that uncovering the truth has consequences.

title: The Atoning
description: Haunted by ghostly apparitions, two parents try to protect their son from a terrible secret from their past that could destroy their family.

title: Where Angels Fear To Tread
description: A widow meets a young man when she visits Italy and marries him. She dies while giving birth to her baby. Her relatives travel to Italy to take care of the baby, expecting no trouble from the father.

title: Aged
description: After taking a temporary job as a caregiver, a young woman realizes her employer and the house have a dangerous, dark past.

title: Zameer
description: Pooja gets married to Suraj but feels guilty for separating him from Supriya, his former fiancee. When Suraj learns the truth he abandons her, oblivious to the fact that she is pregnant.

title: Killer Mom
description: Allison, a 14-year-old girl, inherits $40 million after her father's death. At the funeral, her birth mother, Jessica, reaches out to her and promises to be the mother she needs for her selfish gains.

title: Murder At The Manssion
description: When Deanna starts preparations for her wedding, which is to be held at her fiance's countryside house, she stumbles upon some murky secrets about his family.

title: The Visitant
description: Actress Samantha tries her luck as a psychic out of necessity; however, she does not believe in the supernatural and spirits; however, when she comes home one evening after work, she learns otherwise.

title: Just Breathe
description: Sydney a troubled teen is sent by her mother to live with her father and his new, pregnant wife. Whilst there she befriends a girl who has lost her mother and realizes the meaning of a family.

title: Dangerous Attraction
description: A successful businesswoman finds herself in a dangerous position when she discovers one of the two men she is dating might be a murderer.

title: Family Vanished
description: A happy family finds itself in unprecedented trouble when they return from a vacation and realise that some criminals have stolen their identities and are living in their house.

title: Yalgaar
description: Two childhood friends, Mahendra Ashwini Kumar and Raj Pratap Singhal, turn foes when one of them becomes a policeman while the other gets involved in criminal activities.

title: 14 Cameras
description: When a family of four rent a beautiful house for their summer vacation, the price seems too good to be true. Unbeknownst to them, the lascivious owner has set up a series of spy cams throughout the house, streaming their lives onto the darknet.

title: Touched by a Killer
description: Nikki, a reporter, agrees to investigate the case of Tyler Nash who has been convicted for murder. After she manages to overturn his sentence, she finds herself falling in love with him.

title: Trophy Wife
description: A young woman suffering from amnesia is urged by her husband to stay at home. But as she pieces together her memory, she discovers, he isn't who he says he is, and neither she

title: The Banker
description: When a serial killer begins murdering prostitutes around the city, a policeman attempts to find the culprit before his ex-wife becomes the next victim.

title: A Night in Old Mexico
description: After being forced to sell his property and move to a trailer park, Red Bovie decides to go on a road trip with his grandson. However, they aren't prepared for what is about to happen.

title: Tinker Bell
description: Campanita :- Cuando Campanilla se entera de que para visitar el continente necesita tener talento natural, se propone adquirirlo con la ayuda de sus amigos.

title: Una entrevista con Dios
description: An Interview with God :-  Un periodista prometedor ve su mundo y su fe cada vez más desafiados cuando le conceden la entrevista de su vida: con alguien que dice ser Dios.

title: Sikandar
description: A young, passionate individual challenges a widespread corrupt system, advocates for the rights of ordinary citizens and disrupts established power structures in a country marked by unfairness.

title: Into the Spotlight
description: A gifted young songwriter finds fame but loses herself along the way. Her parents and friends try to help the artist find her way back to what truly matters.

title: Stalked By My Doctor: The Return
description: After Dr Albert Beck miraculously saves a teenage girl from drowning during spring break in Mexico, he shows up at her school back home in San Diego to check on her and pursue his obsession.
A vengeful, mentally ill woman blackmails three friends, threatening to reveal how they obtained their fame and fortunes. They commit a horrific act to keep their secrets hidden.

title: Saved By Grace
description: A retired cop mourning the loss of his family considers making a drastic decision until he meets a mysterious woman who gives him a reason to re-examine his life.

title: The Good Witch
description: Cassandra Nightingale is a stranger in the small town community of Middletown. Multiple occurrences believed as magic cause some of the town folks to think she's a witch.

title: Stalked By My Mom
description: A daughter accuses her mother of killing her boyfriend, but was it really the mother who did it--or was it someone who has always been there?

title: Betting On The Bride
description: Damon, a womaniser, bets that he can get a woman to accept his marriage proposal after only a month of dating. However, the woman he chooses, Melanie, turns out to have serious commitment issues.

title: Midnight Driver
description: When a driver comes across a woman who has an abusive boyfriend and learns that she is a victim of human trafficking, he tries to save her life.

title: Love Wine & Salt
description: Amidst the hills of Tuscany, three friends embark on a vacation that turns into an unexpected romantic adventure. They discover love with three sisters running a picturesque bed and breakfast, igniting the fury of their grandfather.

title: Deadly Sibling Rivalry
description: Jana and Calie are twins who get into a car wreck. Calie walks away while Jana falls into coma. Calie uses this opportunity and starts living the life of Jana in order to evade the police.

title: About hope
description: Thomas McKenzie is in search of the perfect woman but always finds problems in every woman. He meets Hope Sanchez, a widowed mother, and realises the real meaning of love.

title: House of Thaddeus
description: HOUSE OF THADDEUS is a drama about the reality of living in a place with a dark past. A couple buys a beautiful old house not knowing its troubled history -- one that includes mass murder and enigmatic residents.

title: Finding Sara
description: Sam searches for his wayward daughter on the Las Vegas Strip after she's been missing for a year.

title: Outlier
description: A woman escapes her abusive ex-boyfriend with the help of a kind stranger, but his intentions are not yet clear.

title: Determination of Death
description: A couple is in debt and in order to free themselves from the debt, they make a plan. The plan consists of them faking the husband's death but the conspiracy goes terribly wrong.

title: Snowbound
description: Liz tells her friend Barbara that she fears her ex-husband may be stalking her. Barbara accompanies her on her getaway to a cabin in the mountains, only to discover that she may not know the true Liz.

title: Tick Tock
description: Rachel is married to an older and wealthy businessman. She and her friend Carla plan to obtain his fortune by carefully murdering him. But he has hired a detective who is keeping an eye on her.

title: The Lost
description: Plagued by grief, self-doubt and issues of identity, three troubled lives become inextricably linked as a much more powerful force begins to set in.

title: Alone with a Stranger
description: Max, a criminal, has been down on his luck. One day he discovers he has a twin brother who has the life he covets. He kidnaps his brother and pretends to be him.

title: Demon Baby
description: Rose and Theo's peaceful weekend getaway in the Scottish Highlands is ruined when Rose confronts chilling memories of a secret past. As the weekend descends into a living nightmare, Rose is forced to confront her demons.

title: Baggage Claim
description: Montana, a flight attendant, is pressured by her mother to get married. Her friends vainly strategise to find a partner for her before her sister's wedding. William, her best friend, offers her hope.

title: Love and Deceit
description: A young woman thought she married the perfect man, but soon finds out that he is not who she thought he was.

title: Transference: A Love Story
description: Katarina, a Norwegian nurse in London, embarks on a passionate affair with a fellow immigrant nurse that suffers the consequences of unresolved mental health issues from the lovers' secret pasts.

title: Last Chance Cafe
description: A young woman realises that her stepfather was bumped off by a network of dishonest cops and her ex-husband. She flees with her daughter to a nondescript farming town. Love and danger visit her.

title: Haunted Valley
description: A family must do whatever it takes to survive the horrors of Rio Grande Valley, a haunted place where an unbending evil spirit sets its sights on them.

title: My Divorce Party
description: Xan gathers her close friends to celebrate her impending divorce, only to reveal she intends to blow her settlement money since her husband gets half of it. Chaos ensues as each friend has a wildly different opinion on what Xan should do.

title: The Best of Me
description: When he gets back to his hometown to attend his surrogate father's funeral, Dawson reunites again with his former high school sweetheart.

title: Love Sick: Secrets Of A Sex Addict
description: Sue Silverman, a housewife who feels neglected by her hardworking husband, starts sleeping with strangers in motels. As she struggles with her sex addiction, she seeks help from Dr Robert Gardener.

title: Wildlike
description: A molested fourteen year old girl runs away to a deep forest in Alaska and befriends with a stranger who helps her finding a new life.

title: The Last International Playboy
description: New York City playboy and professional charmer Jack Frost is shattered to discover that his one true love is about to marry another man. As the news sends Jack spiraling into a self-destructive cycle of reckless behaviour, his best friends decide to find a way of cheering him up.

title: The Luring
description: A man tries to recover a lost memory by returning to his family's Vermont vacation home where an unspeakable act took place leaving him institutionalized as a child.

title: Bury Him
description: After his controversial acquittal for murder, Michael Kenny must lay low. This becomes difficult after accidentally killing a man with his car. Zach Lazar Hoffman, Cael Adcock.

title: Mommy Would Never Hurt You
description: Riley's mother and younger sister are confined indoors due to her ailing sister. However, Riley soon learns a truth about her sibling that shocks her.

title: Shadows Side
description: Delving into the harrowing journey of Sophie, a young woman who, while seeking a romantic retreat in an isolated chalet, finds herself trapped in a supernatural nightmare.

title: The Donor
description: With two months to live, Allie Graves faces a four-year wait for the kidney transplant that will save her life. In desperation, they turn to James Dolan who charges recipients exorbitant fees, while harvesting organs from needy donors like Maria - a terrified Mexican teenager, who’ll give up a kidney to help her family get across the border. Allie catches a glimpse of Maria in the makeshift operating room they share inside a downtown hotel.

title: Bikini Nuns
description: A fearless trio of nuns is out for revenge. After being wronged by ruthless men, they trade their habits for high-powered weapons, taking justice into their own hands. These deadly women will stop at nothing to clean up the crime-ridden streets—one target at a time.

title: Flower
description: Erica is a rebellious teenager who lands in trouble when she sets out to expose the teacher who molested Luke, her mother's boyfriend's son. However, things do not go as planned.

title: Friday the 13th: Vengeance
description: Elias Voorhees, Jason's father, returns to Crystal Lake and a string of grisly murders soon follows his arrival.

title: The Babysitters
description: Seventeen-year-old Shirley  is a good student who works as a babysitter in order to make money for college. One night Michael, a father Shirley works for, confesses he's unhappy with married life. Shirley has a crush on Michael, and seizes this moment to kiss him. Michael is so happy he presents Shirley with a big tip, which gives her an idea. Shirley plans to make extra money by setting up her teenage friends with other unhappy fathers.

title: The Neighbor
description: A middle-aged man, who is facing problems with his married life, gets obsessed with a young woman after she moves in next door along with her abusive husband.

title: Rogue Angel
description: A young woman runs away after a traumatic experience and becomes a war hero. But when she finds out her grandmother is dying she returns home to protect her sister and get revenge on her abusive family.

title: Sinful
description: A newlywed couple go on the run after committing a horrific crime and find themselves trapped in a mysterious house.

title: Frozen With Fear
description: Katherine Sullivan  is a severe agoraphobic who takes permanent shelter in her home. But, when she witnesses what she believes is the murder of her husband, she is forced to confront the outside world, including a detective investigating the case. When the detective mysteriously disappears, Katherine begins to fear for both her safety and her sanity. Bewildered and petrified, she hires private eye Jack Mize to look into the strange sequence of events.

title: Holy Terror
description: Haunted by the ghost of their dead son, a young couple tries a séance to make contact. But instead, they summon a wicked demon seeking revenge. Now they must enlist the help of a disgraced exorcist to send the evil spirit back to hell.

title: Wrong Numbers
description: A chance encounter in a restaurant leads twenty-something Emma and middle-aged businessman Jack into an intense one-night stand that becomes complicated and destructive beyond their imagination.

title: It Ends with Us
description: Kip, a boy from Kansas, moves to Los Angeles to get out of his small town. Shortly thereafter, he falls in love with a Persian girl and becomes immersed in the zany world of Iranian-Jewish culture.

title: Twisted Seduction
description: A mathematical genius (Tom Broadwell) uses his precise calculations to find a woman (Caroline Brassard) who he thinks is his perfect match. Hoping to make her fall in love with him faster, he kidnaps her.

title: Kill Me Later
description: Shawn Hollowway is in the midst of a suicide attempt when she is taken hostage by Charlie Anders, a bank robber on the run, who promises her that he will kill her once he escapes.

title: After Dark, My Sweet
description: Kevin an ex-boxer, after escaping from a mental hospital gets involved with a widow Fay. Her uncle talks them into helping him kidnap a rich boy for ransom but things soon turn sour.

title: Sorority
description: A college-bound woman and her sister reflect on the past and ponder the future as they spend their last few days together.

title: The Grotto
description: A young man is the sole survivor after a serious accident in a forbidden cave. Four bodies are found in the cave, and forensic examination reveals that the same man killed them. He denies it and asks a nun for help.

title: Smothered by Mothers
description: A football star feels like he has it all, until he loses all of his money in a Ponzi scheme and finds out that he has impregnated three women.

title: Night Shoot
description: T.J. joins a documentary class at Southeast Art Institute. While exploring a fascinating shanty town for their project, the group attracts the attention of dangerous drifters, leading to a horrifying night of bloodshed.

title: Sister Code
description: Three foster sisters come together after the passing of their mother and soon find themselves fighting for their individual goals and dreams.

title: Turbines
description: As part of a government policy, immigrants Jana and Attila resettle in an isolated Australian town, where they work on a wind farm; when bad things start happening, they suspect the wind turbines could be the source.

title: The Tormenting
description: A medical researcher begins experiencing horrific visions of a young girl's death. She becomes determined to seek justice for the girl's death and put her soul to rest.

title: Broken
description: Uma jovem foge de seu passado e segue para a Inglaterra em busca de uma nova vida. Lá, ela passa a cuidar de um paciente paralisado, um homem difícil, que leva uma vida desregrada. Desestabilizada, a jovem cuidadora passa a reviver seus traumas e isso deixa tudo muito perigoso naquela casa.

title: A Paixão de Cristo
description: The Passion of the Christ : O salvador da humanidade, Jesus Cristo, é traído por um de seus discípulos e é crucificado. Apesar da morte torturante, Jesus mantém a pureza de sua alma e derrota o propósito de Satanás.

title: Pelé: Birth of a Legend
description: Pelé mora em um bairro pobre brasileiro e faz trabalhos braçais para sustentar sua família. No entanto, ele continua a aprimorar suas poderosas habilidades futebolísticas que eventualmente o tornam um ícone nacional.

title: Twilight
description: Cuando Bella Swan se muda a un pequeño pueblo en el noroeste del Pacífico, se enamora de Edward Cullen, un misterioso compañero de clase que revela ser un vampiro de 108 años.

title: Night Shoot
description: T.J. joins a documentary class at Southeast Art Institute. While exploring a fascinating shanty town for their project, the group attracts the attention of dangerous drifters, leading to a horrifying night of bloodshed.

title: Girls Will Be Girls
description: In a strict boarding school nestled in the Himalayas, 16-year-old Mira discovers desire and romance, but her rebellious sexual awakening is disrupted by her mother, who never got to come of age herself.

title: The King Maker
description: Fernando De Gama, a Portuguese mercenary, sets sail for the Orient, where he reaches the Thai kingdom of Ayutthaya, in a bid to find the man that murdered his father.

title: Bastard’s Crossing
description: One of 12 Westerns in 12 Months produced during 2020, this film tells the story of Cam Talcutt, a man who won a trading post in a card game. Now, he's stuck in the wilderness trying to run it when he learns the freight company who supplies his store won't be coming anymore. Cam is in a bad spot and might have to do bad things to survive.

title: Closer to God: Jessica's Journey
description: A mother struggles to keep her life under control while her daughter is dying of cancer, her estranged father returns, and her faith in God wanes.

title: Hidden
description: When a woman disappears, one man decides to face the reality that all others try to ignore-that there may be a serial killer among them.

title: A Mother's Testimony
description: Once Kenny Carlson, a convict, is freed from jail, he returns home and gets employed, much to the delight of his family, except his sister. But he gets implicated in a murder case with an ex-inmate.

title: Fast Getaway
description: A teenager (Corey Haim) masterminds bank capers for his father's (Leo Rossi) gang, then must get him out of jail.

title: Striking Poses
description: Photographer Gage (Shannen Doherty) is being stalked, so her assistant, Casey (Tamara Gorski), convinces her to hire security expert Nick Angel (Joseph Griffin). Angel manages to keep Gage safe, but Casey is abducted and killed. Furious that the crime took place under Nick's nose, Gage gets hit man "the Badger" (Aidan Devine) to find and rub out Casey's killer. But Badger knows more about Casey's death than he lets on, and Gage and Angel get caught in a complex web of murder and betrayal.

title: Murder RX
description: A young and single mother moves to a quaint town with her daughter in order to live a peaceful life. But little does she know about the mysterious crimes that will entrap her.

title: Hush Little Baby
description: Edie's baby girl, Susan, was taken from her arms when she was put into a mental hospital for attempted murder of her baby daughter! Thirty five years down the track, Edie is released and tracks her daughter down. She enters her daughters household and destroys her relationship with her adoptive parents. She is eventually found to be evil, in Susan's eyes and must face

title: Forgotten Abduction
description: Karina, the owner of a boutique, befriends Lena and her three-year-old daughter Mallie. However, she soon suspects that Mallie is a girl named Emily, who was abducted from her biological parents.

title: The Perfect Wife
description: Dr Robert fails to save Ruben after he is hit by an inebriated driver. Ruben's sister, Leah, changes her name to Liz, marries Robert and goes on a killing rampage in order to destroy him.

title: Death Clique
description: Three high school girls fight over friendship but their rivalry turns into a terrifying act of violence. One of the girls is found dead. The dead girl's mother wants to get justice for her daughter.

title: Third Falcon
description: An agent from Brussels heads to Estonia to find a missing British intelligence officer.

title: If I Had You
description: After Sharon, a police detective, returns to her hometown, she immediately becomes embroiled in a murder investigation. However, she soon realises that her married ex-lover is the chief suspect.

title: Deadline
description: While working around the clock to finish a script in time, Alice moves to an old Victorian house. But a series of strange events begin to distort her psyche.

title: Maggie's Passage
description: Maggie is taken in by a group of unconventional characters that God places in her life to help her.

title: Presumed Dead in Paradise
description: Madison meets Blake, a local guide, on a holiday and goes paddleboarding with him. When she falls off the board, she miraculously survives and makes her way back only to see Blake with her stepmother.

title: Killed Herself Twice
description: " A young single mom, Emilia, invites Sophia- the upper-class student who drove her daughter to suicide- to her place."

title: The Three Worlds of Gulliver
description: As Gulliver, a surgeon, sets sail across the world, several circumstances lead him to different islands where he meets people of varied cultures and sizes.

title: Dark Asylum
description: A serial killer known by the moniker "the Trasher" (Larry Drake) is apprehended unintentionally by the police. They confine him temporarily to a wing of a nearby asylum that is on the brink of closing and devoid of other inmates. A psychiatrist (Paulina Porizkova) arrives to examine the Trasher -- who promptly escapes -- and gets herself locked in the abandoned asylum while the killer roams free. As the Trasher chases her through the dark corridors, she struggles to survive until dawn.

title: Taffin
description: Cutthroat developers are intent on building a chemical plant in an Irish town, and they'll use any means necessary to silence their opponents. In need of more help than the law can provide, the town's citizens turn to Mark Taffin (Pierce Brosnan), a debt collector and martial-arts expert who's accustomed to getting his way. As Taffin battles against corporate goons and hired thugs, it's clear he's a force to be reckoned with. But is one man enough to win the battle?

title: Children of Darkwood House
description: Desperate to find answers to her children's disappearance, Florence Taylor enlists a paranormal researcher to find an entity called the Nursery Man.

title: The Redwood Massacre
description: Five adventurous friends visit a legendary murder site, and fight for their lives when they discover the legends are true.

title: The Sounding
description: On a remote island, Liv, after years of silence, begins to weave a language out of Shakespeare's words. After a neurologist commits her to a psychiatric hospital, she becomes a full-blown rebel as she fights for her freedom.

title: Take Me to Banaue
description: When a gawky American engineer discovers the real truth of the stunning woman he falls for, he must seek the help of his best friend.

title: Lyvia's House
description: A young journalist links the disappearance of an Italian artist to murders that took place 20 years earlier.

title: Halloween 3
description: Michael Myers is loose in Haddonfield again for one last night. Can Maxwell Loomis stop him once and for all? Will Judy strode and her friends survive?

title: A Mind Of Her Own
description: Sophie, a determined young girl whose ambition is to become a doctor, is obstructed by the fact that she is severely dyslexic.

title: The Music Box
description: Lawyer Anne Talbot must defend her immigrant father, Michael J Laszlo, in court when he is accused of war crimes. As the trial progresses, Anne begins to question whether she truly knows her father.

title: Foreclosure 2
description: A new family moves into a neighborhood in hopes of meeting the ghost that lives in their home.

title: On The 3rd Day
description: After being in a car accident, Cecilia struggles to find her son, Martin. While she desperately tries to find him, she must face a religious fanatic who hates her.

title: Donovan's Echo
description: After he discovers events from his past are repeating, Donovan (Danny Glover) is convinced his young neighbor and her mother will die on the same day his wife and daughter were killed 30 years ago.

title: Asylum of Fear
description: A team of paranormal investigators go on one last job to a haunted psychiatric hospital where children have reportedly gone missing. While searching for evidence of what is haunting the abandoned building, they stumble upon clues that reveal what made the former head doctor snap and go on a killing spree.

title: From Dust
description: Researchers put their lives at risk to discover an ancient artifact.

title: The Good Shepherd
description: Edward Wilson, a spy, lays the foundation for the CIA as he works in the OSS. However, as the Cold War begins, he realises that he has to pay a price for his dedication to duty over family.

title: Mouse of Horrors
description: In a seaside town, chaos erupts as Doctor Rupert's monstrous creation stalks the night, harvesting body parts for a sinister purpose. No one is safe.

title: The Cradle
description: Frank (Lukas Haas) and Julie (Emily Hampshire) move to a small town with their infant, Sam (Ellisa Madeline Marks), seeking a peaceful life. But their neighbors are unfriendly, and Frank is plagued by terrifying dreams about the death of his son. When Julie falls ill, Frank turns to a local midwife, Helen (Amanda Smith), for help with caring for their baby -- and he begins to uncover the story of a child buried alive years before, whose evil spirit seeks vengeance on his family.

title: I know You're In There
description: Following the death of his mother, Tom discovers about his paralysed sister. However, Tom's sanity is threatened by an evil spirit when he takes his sister to his mother's house.

title: Dead Mary
description: Kim and her group of friends decide to go to the woods for a holiday weekend. Once there, they summon a witch who begins to possess them in turns.

title: Day 13
description: A young man investigates a mysterious neighbourhood house that holds dark secrets.

title: Red Letters
description: Two private investigators embark on an assignment that leads them into the hands of darknes

title: Bright Hill Road
description: A deeply troubled alcoholic comes face-to-face with her past misdeeds while staying at a boarding house run by a controlling woman.

title: Self Isolated
description: A woman awakens from a coma to find her husband has gone missing during a pandemic. With no recollection of past events, her search for clues leads her to the doorstep of an overly friendly neighbour who may have something to hide.

title: Ten Miles Back
description: People make decisions that have unexpected consequences

title: An Unkept Secret
description: A married couple contemplates whether or not to report a violent crime they witnessed, as the reasons for their hesitation lead to a shocking discovery.

title: Devil's Revenge
description: An archaeologist returns home from an expedition after unsuccessfully trying to locate a mysterious relic.

title: Toolbox Murders 2
description: Samantha Forester enters a world of torment when she is kidnapped by a hideously deformed killer known only as Coffin Baby. Locked up and tortured beneath an abandoned hotel, Samantha's sanity soon begins to slip away.

title: Silent Night Zombie Night
description: During a zombie outbreak, Officer Frank Talbot (Jack Forcinito) and his partner get trapped in an apartment with the woman both men love.

title: Mandy The Haunted Doll
description: A young woman named Amber is asked to babysit her neighbour's little girl but during the evening she hears unusual sounds coming from upstairs. When Amber goes to investigate she is shocked to discover a strange doll in place of the missing girl.

title: Outer Darkness
description: A spaceship captain becomes increasingly paranoid as she suspects a mutiny by her clone bred crew.

title: The Blazing World
description: Decades after the accidental drowning of her twin sister, a self-destructive woman returns to her family home, finding herself drawn to an alternate dimension where her sibling may still be alive.

title: Child of Mine
description: Tess and Alfie adopt two daughters from an unrecognised Canadian agency. One of them, Heather, proves to be rather depressed and difficult, which leads Tess to believe that she is harbouring a secret.

title: Cabin Pressure
description: A disgruntled ex-employee of an airline hacks into the system and threatens to crash a fully automated commercial jetliner. A former discredited Navy pilot is put on the task of locating the culprit.

title: Girl in the Garage: The Laura Cowan Story
description: Struggling to make ends meet, Laura Cowan and her children temporarily move into the home of a family friend. However, they soon find themseves held captive in a cold and dark garage, enduring years of abuse at the hands of the man who betrayed them.

title: The Nature of the Beast
description: When drifter Adrian (Eric Roberts) strikes up a conversation with a man named Jack (Lance Henriksen) one night in a restaurant off the main road, Jack uneasily agrees to give Adrian a lift. As the two drive, Adrian starts making Jack increasingly uncomfortable by repeatedly alluding to a secret Jack is keeping. Meanwhile, news reports are spreading about a vicious murderer known as The Hatchet Man -- who seems to be committing crimes wherever Adrian and Jack turn up.

title: Into the Outbreak
description: When a dangerous outbreak starts turning people into cannibals, a group of survivors must deal with their personal issues as they attempt to survive the outbreak.

title: To Hell and Gone
description: A crafty drifter and a widow rancher cross paths with a gang of murderous thieves on her land in the middle of the Arizona desert.

title: Hook
description: After murdering John Darling and losing his hand to Peter Pan, Lily the daughter of Peter and Wendy, now will face carnage from the drug induced revenge seeking James Hook, her biological father, until he marries Wendy Darling.

title: A Mother's Crime
description: Arrested for her husband's murder, a woman gives custody of her daughter to her rival and sister, Nikki. After her release, she is determined to get her child back from her.

title: Freddy's Fridays
description: A detective begins to investigate a series of mysterious murders that are connected to a demonic book that brings dolls to life. As the body count begins to rise, the detective soon learns the curse of the demonic Friday and must find a way to stop.

title: Decoys
description: Desperate to lose his virginity, Luke Callahan attempts to woo two beautiful girls, Lilly Benson and Constance Snowden. However, he soon discovers a secret about them.

title: The Bad Batch
description: Arlen is sent to a fenced-off wasteland where undesirables are exiled to when she is kidnapped by a group of cannibals. She escapes and ends up on a journey to reunite a missing girl with her father.

title: Sand Angels
description: Esperanza endeavours to reveal Tom's truths and save young people globally from Christmas-time depression, aiming to convince Tom to seize his time.

title: Love All You Have Left
description: A woman who is in mourning for the death of her young daughter finds a girl in her attic who claims to be Anne Frank.

title: Cartel War
description: LA cops are determined to dismantle the most powerful narcotic mob in the United States. As it is not easy to do so legally, they resort to disregarding the law to achieve their goal.

title: Animus
description: Five students travel to document the paranormal activities in a legendary hospital. In the process, they experience strange incidents and find themselves being pursued by a maniac.

title: Lost in Tomorrow
description: A young girl struggles to get back home when she starts inexplicably waking up as a different person everyday.

title: In the Eyes of a Stranger
description: An overworked woman encounters a pair of armed robbers while riding home on the subway. When one of them commits suicide --- apparently as he divulges the location of some stashed money to her --- police place her in protective custody, even though it appears that she has no idea what the man told her prior to his shooting himself, as she was wearing a pair of headphones at the time. She meets up with a disgruntled cop (Richard Dean Anderson) who decides to join her in searching for the money. A strange twist makes their hunt possible.

title: Sounds of The Streets
description: "While a drug kingpin floods the streets with Fentanyl laced drugs, overdose rates are through the roof. Detective Richard Haynes and Trevor Jones take matters into their own hands, but personal battles will push the detectives off course and cause loyalty to be questioned.

title: Earthstorm
description: The moon is hit by a violent meteorite. Deep cracks develop on the celestial body and fragments disintegrate. Scientists fear that the moon could collapse as a whole on the earth and destroy all life.

title: The Bad Visitor
description: Couples quiet life in suburban Georgia is turned inside out when an old friend trying to escape a violent past shows up at their door.

title: Holistay
description: Two couples, who do not know each other, double book a vacation house in San Diego and strange events begin to happen. "Things are not as they appear."

title: Next Stop Murder
description: A woman discusses her family problems with a stranger she meets on a bus, but is horrified when her confidante suggests each of them kill the person making the other's life difficult.

title: Blue Hill Avenue
description: Quatro amigos entram no tráfico de drogas em Boston no final da década de 1970: Tristan (Allen Payne), Money (Aaron D. Spears), E-Bone e Simon. Com o consentimento de um chefão do crime do South End, Benny (Clarence Williams III), eles rapidamente ascendem no mundo das drogas, enquanto o líder do grupo, Tristan, mantém sua vida dupla em segredo de seus pais desavisados. No entanto, com a transição da década de 1970 para a década de 2000, uma investigação policial ameaça desencadear uma violenta rivalidade entre os amigos tão unidos.

title: Shuttlecock
description: During a memorial for his father, WW II hero Major James Prentis confesses a dark family secret to his son, something he has harbored for more than 20 years.

title: After the Storm
description: When a luxury yacht goes down in a violent storm the race is on to salvage the bounty at any cost, causing two couples to commit the ultimate betrayal.

title: The Hunted
description: Bob is coming to terms with his unsuccessful attempts at becoming an actor when he is bitten by a vampire named Susan - the daughter of a crazed vigilante slayer.

title: Exorcism in Utero
description: It tells the story of a woman who must save her unborn child and herself when she is possessed by a powerful ring.

title: John Wick
description: John Wick is a former hitman grieving the loss of his true love. When his home is broken into, robbed, and his dog killed, he is forced to return to action to exact revenge.

title: Bond Of Blood
description: A modern tale of the prodigal son. Here, Luke leaves family wine farm only to squanders all his money on gambling, drugs and alcohol. He learns his lesson, returns home where his parents welcome him back but his brother has doubts.

title: Gumnaam (Rakshasudu)
description: अरुण, एक नव नियुक्त पुलिस सब-इंस्पेक्टर, एक कुख्यात सीरियल किलर का पीछा करता है जो किशोर लड़कियों को अपना निशाना बनाता है। हालाँकि, उसके मिशन को जल्द ही एक भयानक कीमत चुकानी पड़ती है।

title: Brothers War
description: In the waning days of WWar II, enemies must become allies in order to deliver a message that could change the world.

title: O Peregrino: Uma Jornada Para o Céu
description: Pilgrim's Progress: Journey To Heaven : Esse filme alegórico acompanha a jornada do personagem cristão da cidade da destruição para a cidade celestial.

title: Chronology
description: The Lost Day : After witnessing a horrific sight, two men inexplicably claim to be one another at New Year's Eve parties...only the parties are six years apart.

title: La Cabaña
description: The Shack : Após o desaparecimento de seu filho mais novo, Mack Phillips entra em profunda depressão. Sua vida toma um rumo inesperado quando recebe uma carta misteriosa convidando-o a visitar uma cabana.

title: Don't. Stop. Running.
description: Two estranged brothers - thrown together for a treasure hunt - soon find that they are the ones being hunted. As they race across an island wilderness they soon realise that if they want to survive, they'll have to work together.

title: Guns For Hire
description: Detective Holt and Beatle talk about a murder with flashbacks added. Twists follow.

title: 3 Knee Deep
description: Six years ago a criminal mastermind hid one ton of cocaine in an abandoned warehouse. No one knows the location of the drugs except his violent sidekick and his beautiful but deadly girlfriend. Instead of giving up the stash to the cops or a rival gang, the criminal, a mysterious Jamaican named Ghost, takes his secret to prison. When he is kidnapped by a black box covert operative by the name of Cole (Bill Koruna), he escapes with the help of an FBI agent (Angela Williams). Now free on parole, Cole's only goal is to get the cocaine, sell it, and disappear into a life of luxury. But his actions have been closely watched by the DEA, The Russian mob and bad guys alike, and everyone is interested in following the trail to the hidden hoard of coke.

title: A Friend's Obsession
description: When Megan's fiancé is killed, she moves cross country and rebuilds her life with a new boyfriend and a closer relationship with her sister. Once she befriends one of her old colleagues, Lloyd, things take a turn for the worse. She realizes he will make her his - no matter the cost.

title: Grown Ups
description: When five high school friends reunite for their coach's funeral, they decide to take a trip to the lake house where they celebrated their last win and are challenged by their rivals to another match.

title: Mr. Popper's Penguins
description: When Tom Popper's father dies in Antarctica, he inherits six penguins. Tom initially decides to give them away, but his children think they are a birthday present and he is forced to keep them.

title: Soldier Boy
description: Six-year-old Seryozha Aleshkov loses every member of his family to the war. Afterwards, a little game to preserve his innocence leads to a heroic outcome.

title: El gran Stan: El matón de la prisión
description: Big Stan :- Un estafador entra en pánico cuando se entera de que va a ir a la cárcel por fraude, así que contrata a un gurú de las artes marciales que le ayuda a transformarse en un experto capaz de luchar contra los reclusos que quieran hacerle daño.

title: Shadow Witness
description: When a detective finds himself in the snarls of an Internal Affairs investigation, he has to turn to the only person he can trust, a young girl who holds all the answers he needs, the only problem is that she's been reported missing and he's the main suspect.

title: A Forja: O Poder da Transformação
description: The Forge :- Depois de se formar no ensino médio sem nenhum plano para o futuro, Isaiah recebe um empurrão para começar a tomar decisões melhores na vida.

title: Waking Ned Devine
description: Despertando a Ned: Jackie O'Shea, una anciana aldeana irlandesa, diseña un plan para mantener en secreto de los funcionarios de la lotería la muerte de Ned Devine, un anciano ganador de la lotería, y cobrar su billete de lotería.

title: Órfã 2 - A Origem
description: Após escapar de uma clínica psiquiátrica na Estônia, Esther viaja para os Estados Unidos se passando pela filha desaparecida de uma família rica. No entanto, uma reviravolta inesperada a coloca contra uma mãe disposta a proteger sua família a qualquer custo.

title: O Massacre Da Serra Elétrica
description: Sally, Franklin e seus três amigos ficam sem gasolina enquanto dirigem para a casa do avô. Um por um, eles são atormentados e mortos por um assassino armado com uma motosserra e sua família psicopata.

title: All Dogs Go To Heaven
description: Charlie is killed by his erstwhile friend Carface Carruthers and finds himself in heaven. Charlie then returns to Earth, reunites with Itchy, and befriends Anne-Marie, an orphan.

title: Den of Thieves
description: A group of elite deputies in the LA County sheriff's department has to stop a notorious crew of expert thieves from executing a robbery plan at the Federal Reserve Bank.

title: Un été d'enfer
description: Élisabeth est à la recherche de sa sœur Valérie, mystérieusement disparue trois mois plus tôt. Trouvant les hommes du commissaire Turielle trop lents dans leur enquête, elle engage un détective privé, Philippe Darland. Son enquête le mène rapidement dans le milieu de la drogue, où il découvre que le chef du réseau n'est nul autre que le commissaire Turielle.

title: Bunker Palace Hotel
description: Dans un monde futuriste imaginaire, une rébellion éclate. Les hommes au pouvoir se ruent vers le Bunker Palace Hotel, un bunker construit jadis pour parer à ce genre d'imprévu. Mais une espionne rebelle s'infiltre et, bien que sa nature soit très vite soupçonnée, elle se retrouve seule à observer les délires d'une classe dirigeante décadente, qui ne cesse de se demander ce qui est arrivé à leur chef, absent.

title: Johnny Mad Dog
description: Un adolescent africain (Christophe Minie) dirige une bande de jeunes combattants dans un saccage sanglant à travers les villages locaux.

title: Run
description: Chloe, a teenager, is forbidden from seeing the mail and is kept in isolation. She soon starts suspecting her mother of keeping dark secrets and decides to investigate.

title: Night Night
description: After waking up from a coma caused by a horrific car accident, April must find a way to work through her trauma and find the will to survive a recovery from hell.

title: A Killer in the House
description: When a psycho killer becomes obsessed with a beautiful girl, he does everything he can to win her over, including killing everybody in his way. This is a study of a psycho killer, his prey, and how far he is willing to go.

title: Til Ex Do Us Part
description: A separated Kyle and Sophia decide to reconcile but find that Claire, who Kyle has a past with, is not going to let it happen. When Claire's covert attempts fail, she goes on the offensive

title: Cliffs of Freedom
description: The story of an ill-fated romance between a young Greek village girl and a conflicted Turkish officer during the dawn of the Greek War for Independence against the Ottoman Empire in 1821

title: The World Unseen
description: In 1950s Cape Town, progressive and free Amina (Sheetal Sheth) co-owns a cafe with a black man named Jacob. One day, a beautiful housewife named Miriam (Lisa Ray) visits the cafe, and Amina is instantly smitten. Miriam runs a store outside of town with her husband, Omar (Parvin Dabas), and feels increasingly stifled in her conventional life. She cannot help but give in to her desire when Amina comes calling.

title: The Girl
description: A Texan mother loses her child to foster care and she starts to smuggle Mexicans across the border to make money.

title: Love Come Down
description: A gripping tale of two brothers in their early 20s, one black and one white, each the other's keeper since their family was torn apart by a decade of tragedy. One is a struggling comedian and the other is a boxer consumed with the pleasure and pain of his skin.

title: Ghost Webcam
description: While under house arrest, Nate goes on a virtual date with a woman who appears to get murdered on camera.

title: Love on the Run
description: A woman's (Annaleigh Ashford) optimistic attitude can't be shaken, even after being taken hostage during a bank robbery, especially since her captor is the most handsome guy she has ever seen

title: Scorn
description: Liam's girlfriend invites his director for a drink to talk about his new script and a role it might hold for her. Merrick suggests they improvise some scenes and the three begin a boozy night of creation, provocation, and retaliation.

title: Still the Water
description: Brothers try to reconnect many years after a domestic tragedy tore them apart.

title: Treasure
description: A new friendship with a geocacher has troublemaker Erica (Ansley Gordon) wondering what the meaning of life is and where she can find it.

title: A Case of Deceit
description: A cop investigating a crime boss uncovers a deep conspiracy.

title: Chavez Cage of Glory
description: Hector Chavez, an amateur martial arts fighter, struggles to cover his son's medical bills. Soon, he is given the opportunity to go up against the MMA world champion to pay for his child's surgery.

title: Soul Man
description: Esta es la historia de Iris, una bailarina de ballet que se ve impulsada a iniciar la búsqueda de Otis, un viejo amigo al que no ha visto en años. Sus investigaciones la llevan a un hospital psiquiátrico donde Otis ha estado hospitalizado durante los últimos diez años. Una vez allí, las personas a cargo del centro le advierten que su amigo ha desarrollado una misteriosa personalidad alternativa, que sin embargo han logrado bloquear gracias a las drogas. Tras el alta de Otis, los médicos advierten a Iris sobre su imprevisibilidad y posible violencia, y la imposibilidad de mantenerlo en el centro médico por más tiempo. Después de que ambos sufran un episodio violento, la personalidad alternativa de Otis, Soul Man, toma el control de la situación y le propone a Iris que ambos se conviertan en justicieros urbanos para cambiar las cosas que no funcionan bien en nuestra sociedad: crimen, abuso, corrupción, venta de drogas... uno a uno, los criminales se encontrarán con nuestros protagonistas.

title: White Crow
description: Alone and wounded Spy J.D, is on the hunt for members of a dark agency he used to work for, White Crow. This will push his skills to their limit, and maybe uncover a dark and sinister conspiracy that could change the world as we know it.

title: Rift
description: Jason Cole has a successful career, a beautiful wife, home, and works as an FBI Agent. He appears to have it all. Until his past rears its head and propels him into a situation that not even he, could have prepared him for.

title: The Architect
description: A couple solicits the services of a renowned architect to design their dream house. However, things take a humorous turn when he begins designing his dream house instead of the client's.

title: Restless
description: After going to extremes to cover up an accident, a corrupt cop's life spirals out of control when he starts receiving threats from a mysterious witness.

title: Prodigy
description: A psychologist engages a dangerous, young genius in a battle of wits -- unaware of the supernatural power the girl possesses, or that her life hangs in the balance.

title: Beyond the Woods
description: A gathering of friends is thrown into chaos by the opening of a mysterious fiery sinkhole near their secluded holiday home

title: Blurred Lines
description: When six friends get together for New Year's eve and a drink gets spiked, secrets and conflicts reveal themselves begging the question, who is really responsible? Who is consented?

title: Children of the Corn: Runaway
description: Ruth, a pregnant woman, leaves her sinister cult behind and starts a new life in Oklahoma. After ten years, she is forced to face her past to protect her child.

title: The Last Rescue
description: Three American soldiers are stranded on enemy territory after D-Day. Soon, they attempt to run away by taking a hostage from the German side.

title: The Harrow
description: Miller lives a lonely life in his house and gets visions of his wife, who was killed. When he and his daughter try to solve the mystery behind his wife's murder, they are shocked with the truth

title: Urban Vengeance
description: Skateboarder Jack Urban must avenge his sister's death. His antics ignite chaos throughout a reimagined Austin, Texas, set two weeks in the future

title: Kingdom of Gladiators, the Tournament
description: In a world with ancient magic, a king enters into a pact with a demon. After ruling for many years, the mysterious demon appears to the king to claim the lives of the court's descendants and eventually the destruction of mankind.

title: Monsternado
description: A tornado infested with prehistoric monsters forms in the Bermuda Triangle and makes its way toward land. Megalodon, pterodactyls, giant octopuses, crocodiles and other deadly creatures attack, and the city must fight to survive

title: Stonehenge Apocalypse
description: Jacob, a scientist, observes strange tremors in the Earth's orbit originating from Stonehenge. He tries to take evasive action, but his associates turning a blind eye over the issue creates a problem.

title: Mrs. Doubtfire
description: Après un divorce difficile, un acteur se déguise en femme de ménage pour passer du temps avec ses enfants détenus par son ex-femme.

title: Foreclosure
description: A young couple buys a home in the hopes that it is haunted by a ghost.

title: Going Viral
description: In a neon-lit backdrop of the 1980s, a nerdy teenager suddenly gets the popularity he's always wanted when a deceitful artificial intelligence makes him a video star.

title: Locked In
description: Josh decides to leave his advertising career at its peak and walks away from fame and success. However, his life turns upside down when a car accident leaves his daughter in a strange coma

title: Saving Faith
description: Faith fears she may have to close the Ritz Theater after years of struggling to keep it open. With help from friends, she tries to put on a big Christmas show to save the building.

title: My Bakery in Brooklyn
description: A woman and her cousin inherit a bakery shop from their aunt in a changing neighbourhood. They come up with different ideas to grow the business

title: Killer Tattooist
description: Eva is an undercover cop, who will stop at nothing to solve a case. On the hunt for a serial killer, who tattoos and skins his victims, she meets Nathan and starts to get close to him, unaware of who he truly is.

title: Vengeance
description: The daughter of a man on the run is brutally attacked, and with the police reluctant to act, he must return to a city he no longer recognises to deal with the culprits himself, relying on help from his last remaining friends.

title: We Had It Coming
description: In a world of faceless, anonymous men, Anna seeks to avenge her younger sister's suicide, which resulted from her relationship with a ruthless pimp. During this hunt, Anna encounters a mysterious woman who recruits young, vulnerable girls.

title: The Fourth Musketeer
description: At the behest of his father, young d'Artagnan travels from rural Gascony to Paris, where he becomes embroiled in a devious plot between the King's Musketeers and the Guardsmen of Cardinal Richelieu.

title: Life in Long Beach
description: A look into the people, places, and stories that go on in a day in Long Beach, CA.

title: Interviewing Monsters and Bigfoot
description: A forest ranger tries to prevent a vengeful college professor and a legendary hunter from capturing Bigfoot.

title: Spin State
description: A troubled private investigator plagued by strange blackouts investigates the estranged husband of a young scientist, which reveals a connection between her husband and his own repressed trauma.

title: Unwritten
description: An agoraphobic, failed writer who lives in a used bookstore becomes convinced that a mysterious customer is a villain from a story that he never finished writing. He is forced to overcome his fears in an attempt to save not only his estranged daught

title: Tinker Bell O Segredo Das Fadas
description: Sininho vagueia pela floresta proibida do inverno e conhece Periwinkle. Juntas, elas descobrem o segredo de suas asas e tentam unir as fadas do calor e as fadas do inverno para ajudar o Refúgio das Fadas.

title: Talking to God
description: A woman discovers the true meaning of life after travelling to Ukraine to search for a cure for insomnia.

title: Ascension: I Am Not My Mother
description: Elizabeth is haunted by her past and is trapped in an abusive relationship with her tyrannical husband, Caleb. She finds solace in her writing and an escape into a world where her imagination can influence good or evil

title: Like a Bat Outta Hell
description: When four young filmmakers are sent into the outback for a new project, they get stranded in the desert while a mysterious flying entity disables their vehicle.

title: Division
description: When a Z-list actress connects with a fan who has opposing political views in pre-election, pandemic-stricken America, will they come together or prove we're too far apart?

title: South of the River
description: Front man Aaron has it all. The mates, the band, a girl - and cancer. When he meets someone new, only he can decide whether to rock until he drops or grow up to survive. Life and love. It's all going on, South of the River.

title: The Appleton Ladies' Potato Race
description: Penny returns to her childhood home of Appleton, where she starts a cultural war after she learns their world-famous potato race awards the women's first place prize a fraction of the men's first place prize.

title: Rosebud Lane
description: When a middle aged Hollywood filmmaker receives an unexpected card from his young son whom he has never met, he makes the difficult decision to go see him in the Blue Ridge Mountains of North Carolina.

title: Run Away With Me
description: A former soldier is released from prison before the world's destruction and sent on a mission to save mankind.

title: Heckle
description: Fledgling female stand up learns how not to die on stage.

title: Desert Cathedral
description: Leaving behind a trail of VHS tapes, Peter Collins, a despairing real estate developer, mysteriously disappears into the Southwest in 1992.

title: Ashgrove
description: An overworked scientist needs to take a weekend off work, so she and her husband head to their farm, but something isn't quite right.

title: Extra Innings
description: In 1960s Brooklyn, a teenager struggles between fulfilling his baseball dreams or staying devoted to his controlling Syrian Jewish family.

title: Friend Request
description: Two detectives are tasked with apprehending a crazed, online psycho who tracks down and lures victims via a popular social media site.

title: It Came Upon a Midnight Clear
description: Jeremy Adams, a hopeless romantic high school senior, just scored a date with his dream girl, Amanda Lawton, but she is kidnapped causing him and his best friend, Minka, to go on a horrific quest to save her from a ruthless serial killer

title: Spring 1941
description: Artur, his wife and children search for a safe place to hide from the Nazis. Afterwards, their grocer and the wife of a veteran, Emilia, offer them shelter.

title: Absolution
description: A hit man who works for the Russian mafia is sent to Berlin to retrieve the watch that Yuri Gagarin wore on his first flight to outer space. Before that, he must deal with the consequences of the mess he left behind on his last mission to Berlin.

title: Sisters Grimm
description: Sisters, Esmeralda and Fancy Grimm, set out on the final leg of their journey to their ancestral village, but they need to get past a coven of witches, an amorous yokel and a storm that leaves them stranded.

title: Dracula On Holiday
description: Travelling from Transylvania to Scotland by train, the Count's two companions, Lucy and Renfield, try to get the Count over his many fears: sunlight, crosses, bibles, running water, garlic, food and drink.

title: Wind Walkers
description: A former soldier and his buddies fall prey to an ancient Native American curse while hunting in the Florida wilderness

title: Broken 2021
description: What starts as just another delivery becomes the catalyst for life-shattering trouble. With Brian injured and evidence mounting against them, three friends find themselves on the run from the law. In a panic, Brian turns to his mentor and ringleader, Bear, and together they come up with a perfect scheme of betrayal and murder.

title: The Beehive
description: When peat cutter Barry Drone tries to woo the widow Betty Queen, landlady of The Beehive Inn, he finds her unresponsive. He devises a plan for Ben Wasp to pretend to be a burglar so that he can save her.

title: The Avenger
description: After Matt Hollis wife is attacked and his daughter is kidnapped, he recruits his ex-special forces buddy in a violent rescue mission.

title: The Experience
description: A girl is sent to a ranch for juvenile delinquents in order to improve her attitude to life

title: The Alliance
description: Drug dealers call a truce and form an alliance, but after 20 years, one member is forced to kill the others.

title: Mia and the Dragon Princess
description: Mia, a plucky barmaid, has her life thrown into chaos when a mysterious woman turns up at her workplace, on the run from a group of violent thugs and unable to speak English.

title: The Perception
description: An inspired writer. An aspiring actress. A house with a dark history.

title: The Irish Mob
description: Dublin crime boss Val Fagan leads a violent bloody and ruthless gang who are the main target of Garda detectives after an audacious cash depot robbery.

title: Three and Out
description: A London tube driver considers pursuing a third fatal accident to collect a huge payout.

title: PawParazzi
description: A Hollywood starlet arrives at a farm with her pampered pomeranian to shoot for a film but she is in for numerous surprises and shocks before she learns the true value of people.

title: A Small Fortune
