description: When a desperate man finds a lost bag of money off the shores of Prince Edward Island, his decision to keep it turns his quaint fishing village into a growing crime scene

title: Lucky U Ranch
description: In 1953, 11-year-old Junior McCaully is ready to call it quits. Chubby, bullied, and stuck at a dead-end Arizona trailer court with his mum, nothing prepares him for the arrival of Melissa, a sophisticated Hollywood girl who changes everything.

title: Fare
description: When Eric's day turns to night, and he takes the evening's last fare, he finds himself face to face with the source of his troubles. Eric's unsuspecting passenger is a man who doesn't know this cab driver from any other. When Eric recognizes the man as the one who is secretly sleeping with his wife, the events that are set set in motion threaten the lives of everyone who sets foot inside the car.

title: City of Vultures 3
description: While community advocates urge him to leave the drug trade behind, Richard Steele dives deeper than ever into a life of drugs and violence.

title: Foreign Land
description: Two strangers with different stories find themselves in the dangerous border towns which are infested with ruthless criminal groups

title: A Prayer for the Damned
description: Thirteen years after the American Civil War, several mysterious characters converge upon a strange New Mexico Territory town on a quest for a lost Confederate fortune

title: Vengeance Turns
description: Vengeance turns Rebecca Falcon into a ruthless warrior following the slaughter of her husband and children.

title: Alice and the Vampire Queen
description: Ex-con Alice Oldman struggles to overcome the scars from her past. One night, a dark stranger gives her an offer she cannot refuse: she must make one special dish for his boss, the Vampire Queen.

title: Lou
description: Lou's life undergoes a radical change when her father abandons his mother and sisters. She blames her mother for this separation and grows up with a shell around her.

title: Against the Clock
description: Kelley Chandler gets injured while on a mission, making him grip for survival on life support. His wife Tess, a former CIA operative, does everything it takes to find out what happened to her husband.

title: Adam Resurrected
description: Adam, a circus performer, is spared from the concentration camp and forced to entertain a Nazi commander. When he is a patient at an asylum, he identifies with a young boy raised in a basement.

title: American Parent
description: Bette, a free-spirited new mom, begins weaning her 1-yr old daughter in order to return to work for a Chicago theatre as pandemic restrictions are lifted. Her wife, Elsie, hustles in the gig economy as an adjunct theology professor.

title: Sometimes Always Never
description: A family is blessed with exceptional vocabulary while playing scrabble. However, they cannot put these words to use on an everyday basis and hence, they struggle to communicate with each other.

title: Guardians
description: A charismatic minister's sermons transport his congregation back to biblical times while he works with guardian angels to save people in modern day life-threatening situations.

title: And God Made Man
description: Lindsay loses a scholarship to a transgender athlete. Her father fights for fairness, facing legal challenges. The case involves faith, science and political issues.

title: The Devil is a Lie
description: Blaming God for his son's overdose, a schizophrenic father teeters between salvation and destruction as an Angel and the Devil battle for his soul-while his wife fights to save what's left of their family.

title: Hong Kong '97
description: Hong Kong 97 takes place, appropriately enough, in Hong Kong right before the transfer of power from Britain to China. Reginald Cameron, an assassin affiliated with a large corporation with interests in the colony, guns down key members of the Chinese envoy which will take charge of Hong Kong the next day. Suddenly, he becomes a target for every two-bit mercenary in the city. With the help of his company mentor (Brion James), a clueless friend (Tim Thomerson), and his ex-girlfriend (Ming-Na Wen), Cameron must unravel the motives behind his sudden target status and escape Hong Kong alive.

title: Smile as You Kill
description: With only a few months to live, a desperate man kidnaps a successful advertising director and makes one demand: Create an online campaign to pay for treatment - or share his fate.

title: Cop vs. Killer
description: When Sheriff Bill Abrams is attacked during a routine traffic stop, the would-be Killer leaves him for dead, using his gun, badge and vehicle to terrorize the residents of a small desert town.

title: Busca Explosiva 4
description: Jake Carter precisa proteger Olivia, uma denunciante que está determinada a expor um contratante corrupto de defesa militar, enquanto uma equipe de mercenários é contratada para matá-la.

title: INTERCAMBIO DE PRINCESAS
description: Una semana antes de Navidad, una duquesa cambia de lugar con una mujer común y corriente de Chicago, que se parece exactamente a ella, y ambas se enamoran del pretendiente de la otra.

title: When Saturday Comes
description: Jimmy (Sean Bean) aspires to be a pro soccer player, but as a heavy drinker with a go-nowhere job in a local brewery, his dream of making the team for Sheffield United seems an unlikely one. However, after starting a relationship with the pretty Annie (Emily Lloyd) and catching the eye of recruiter Ken (Pete Postlethwaite) during an amateur game, the future is suddenly looking brighter for Jimmy. Unfortunately, to make it into the big leagues, he'll first have to win his bout with the bottle.

title: Freshman Year
description: The journey of two young people going off to college from their sheltered homes and different backgrounds to face the real world of battling peer pressure and falling in love.

title: The Path
description: A young woman returns to her childhood home and discovers strange circumstances surrounding her parent's death and the town in which she grew up.

title: La Nouvelle Locataire
description: Lorsque le mari de Karen est hospitalisé, le couple décide de louer des chambres dans leur nouvelle maison pour rembourser leur prêt. Mais l'arrivée de Miranda, la locataire, bouleverse leur vie.

title: L'amour En Trois Rendez-Vous
description: Three Dates to Forever : Maddie Mckenzie est une présentatrice travailleuse dont le dynamisme et le talent ont fait d'elle une animatrice radio populaire. John Reed est un entrepreneur technologique insouciant qui préfère organiser des fêtes. Ils sont totalement différents.

title: Le café de L'amour
description: The Proposal Spot : La propriétaire d'un café où tout le monde tombe amoureux risque de tout perdre lorsqu'une célébrité lui demande en mariage et se fait larguer. Elle jure donc de le remettre ensemble avec sa future fiancée.

title: Marcher vers L'amour
description: Stepping into Love : Lorsque son musée d'art rencontre des difficultés financières, une conservatrice conventionnelle collabore avec un artiste d'avant-garde pour concevoir une exposition originale. Elle apprend à sortir des sentiers battus pour sauver le musée et trouver l'amour.

title: Tu M'Epouseras
description: Girlfriend Killer : Une femme d'affaires qui crée des demandes en mariage parfaites pour des hommes riches devient la cible de l'obsession d'un client fou lorsqu'elle lui montre de la compassion après que sa petite amie l'a publiquement rejeté.

title: UNE MÈRE DIABOLIQUE
description: Killer Mom : Allison, une adolescente de 14 ans, hérite de 40 millions de dollars après la mort de son père. Lors des funérailles, sa mère biologique, Jessica, lui tend la main et lui promet d'être la mère dont elle a besoin pour ses intérêts personnels.

title: Une Amitié Malsaine
description: The Perfect Soulmate : Une blogueuse de poésie dont le mari est violent se tourne vers l'un de ses fans pour obtenir du soutien, mais elle commence à découvrir qu'elle a trouvé un compagnon encore plus dangereux.

title: La Vengeance D'une Mère
description: A Housekeeper's Revenge : Une étudiante soupçonne sa femme de ménage d'être la coupable d'une série d'événements étranges qui l'ont traumatisée.

title: Né Dans la Mauvaise Famille
description: Mommy's Little Boy : Après la mort de son frère, Eric subit des violences psychologiques de la part de sa mère. Mais la situation empire lorsque sa mère met tout en œuvre pour éviter de perdre son deuxième enfant.

title: Gentleman Menteur
description: Ring of Deception : Julie Stevens, mère célibataire, tombe amoureuse d'un homme nommé Martin qui s'installe dans son quartier. Cependant, ils se retrouvent poursuivis par Sloane, une ex-amante vengeresse qui veut tuer Martin.

title: Mariage sanglant
description: The Wedding Stalker : Jenna, couturière, envie les mariées qu'elle sert tout en subissant les abus de sa tante. Lorsqu'elle rencontre Marci et Glenn, un couple fiancé, elle décide de garder Glenn pour elle par tous les moyens.

title: Vitória Por Submissão
description: Victory By Submission : Um lutador de MMA problemático enfrenta uma crise de fé enquanto luta para se tornar o campeão.

title: Epifania
description: Epiphany : Mientras secretos familiares enterrados durante mucho tiempo salen a la superficie, una joven lucha por construir una relación con su padre.

title: El Compromiso Falso
description: Tras perder el corazón en El Precio del Amor, un popular reality show de citas que une a veinteañeras con un joven soltero con éxito económico, la profesora Hanna Knight ha regresado a su vida en un pequeño pueblo de Colorado y ha seguido adelante con su vida. Pero su tranquila vida se ve interrumpida bruscamente cuando Will Preston, el galán que le rompió el corazón en televisión nacional, aparece inesperadamente con una propuesta de matrimonio descabellada.

title: Primeiro Ano
description: O filho de um devoto pregador deixa o seu lar protetor para começar a faculdade e conhece uma aluna autossuficiente que vai testar o seu coração e a sua fé.

title: Encontrando Faith
description: Finding Faith : baseia-se numa compilação de acontecimentos reais que o xerife Mike Brown investigou através da sua força-tarefa de Crimes contra Crianças na Internet. Num recente anúncio de utilidade pública da Safe Surfin' Foundation, uma destas vítimas contou corajosamente a história de como foi raptada por um predador de crianças e como permaneceu em cativeiro durante três dias antes de ser resgatada pela polícia.

title: Rico en Espíritu
description: Um pastor da igreja local torna-se objeto de desejo de uma mulher cristã.

title: A Lista
description: Em depressão, Jack Stone decide assumir o controlo da sua vida, fazer uma lista como seu guião e partir para viver à sua maneira.

title: Mr. Barrington
description: A mysterious stranger (Brian McCardie) affects the welfare of an agoraphobic poet (Jennifer Nichole Porter).

title: O Circulo de Oração
description: Quando um jovem ex-recluso em busca de orientação se junta a um grupo de oração, os membros encontram um ponto em comum que muda as suas vidas.

title: Força Motriz
description: Um homem luta contra a fé e o perdão depois de um acidente de viação causado por um condutor embriagado ter tirado a vida à sua filha.

title: Pastor Jones: Mi Hermana Te Ama
description: Desde que murió su amada esposa, el pastor Jones ha evitado enredos románticos por dolor y respeto.

title: Periodt
description: A promiscuous businesswoman gets spiritual help through her friend's pastor's prayers, causing surprising changes in her love life. With Robert Ri'chard, Nicole Alexander, Patrice Lovely.

title: Pastor Jones: Hermanas en Espíritu 2
description: El pastor Jones (Jean Claude Lamarre) descubre que su mentor y consejero espiritual, quien acaba de fallecer, es en realidad su padre biológico. Y que las dos hermanas que han estado compitiendo por sus atenciones son en realidad sus medias hermanas.

title: The Stolen Valley
description: To save her dying mother, Mexican Navajo mechanic Lupe Reyes seeks help from the father she has never met. She accidentally helps an outlaw cowgirl rob a pawn shop and the two continue the journey together.

title: El Capitán Alatriste
description: En el siglo XVII, Diego Alatriste, soldado del ejército del rey Felipe IV de España, regresa de la guerra para cuidar del hijo de su amigo. Posteriormente, es contratado para asesinar al príncipe de Gales.

title: Nunca Ouvi
description: Never Heard : Enquanto o pai passa a vida na prisão, Jalen é atraído para o mundo da droga de Los Angeles. Tudo o que o impede de seguir os passos do pai é o poder da oração, enquanto uma rapariga que ele conhece na igreja lhe mostra que a vida oferece outros caminhos.

title: Pastor Jones: Voces Celestiales
description: Pastor Jones : Heavenly Voices El querido pastor Jones enfrenta otra crisis. Dado que la iglesia no puede pagar un préstamo, su famoso coro está en peligro. Para salvarlo, el pastor debe reunir a las líderes del coro, Tammy y Louise, quienes están en disputa.

title: A Ressuscitação de Um Morto
description: Dead Man Rising Depois de contemplar os horrores de execuções anteriores com recurso a novas drogas experimentais, um condenado à morte em busca de informações sobre a melhor forma de enfrentar a sua morte iminente vê-se a evoluir para um cristão fervoroso.

title: Aprendendo A Viver
description: Amazing Racer : Após a morte inesperada do pai, uma adolescente angustiada descobre que a mãe está viva. A caminho de a encontrar, faz amizade com um treinador de cavalos e recupera da melancolia.

title: Revolución Virtual: 2047
description: 2047: Virtual Revolution, mientras la gente pasa mucho tiempo en línea, terroristas matan a jugadores mediante un ataque viral. Las multinacionales dominantes contratan a Nash, un agente oculto que pasa tiempo conectado y desconectado, para matar a los terroristas.

title: Savage Girls
description: A gritty thriller set in the raw heart of Watts, LA, Savage Girls is the story of three women caught in a dangerous game of survival, betrayal, and the will to rise above their circumstances.

title: El Guarda de mi Hermano
description: My Brother's Keeper  Un veterano de guerra lucha con el trastorno de estrés postraumático y su fe.

title: I Am Not a Hipster
description: Brook is a gifted singer who is liked for his work in San Diego's indie music scene. As he copes with his mother's death and a breakup with his girlfriend, his friend Clark tries to cheer him up

title: Hart Blvd
description: A college dropout thinks he has life figured out until he runs out of options and is forced to move in and take care of his grandfather.

title: Messy
description: A crime drama about a reckless drug dealer and his unfaithful girlfriend. Caught between deception and lies they struggle to trust one another, while facing opposition from the police and their enemies.

title: Unfailing Love
description: Follows Hosea's memoir. God instructs him to marry prostitute Arianna as symbolic example. Spans 7 years in DC area with childhood flashbacks. Portrays struggles/hatred faced due to obedience to God's command, despite finding his wife.

title: Hit a Lick 2
description: An old-school gangster who got played out of his money goes on a highly personal crime spree in order to get his money and his street respect back.

title: American Trash
description: A war veteran suffering from PTSD finds solace in the company of a free-spirited environmentalist. Bonding over shared secrets the couple navigate the streets of Venice California in search of happiness. However, their romance takes an unexpected turn.

title: Mãos Talentosas
description: Gifted Hands : The Ben Carson Story, O Dr. Ben Carson, um neurocirurgião que foi criado por uma mãe solteira e enfrentou muitas dificuldades na infância, enfrenta o desafio de operar dois gêmeos siameses ligados pelo crânio.

title: Secretos de Otoño
description: Secrets in the Fall : Los campistas asisten a un retiro juvenil en las montañas de Carolina del Norte para comprender mejor el plan de Dios para ellos. Cuando uno de ellos desaparece, los consejeros y sus equipos parten a buscarlo antes del anochecer.

title: Os Reis da Noite
description: Kings of the Evening : Numa cidade na época da Grande Depressão, um ex-presidiário (Tyson Beckford) cria laços com quatro estranhos e participa numa competição invulgar.

title: Si Te Vas
description: If You're Gone : La noche de la graduación, la vida de Lillian cambia para siempre cuando su novio, Brad, desaparece. Incapaz de encontrarlo, Lillian se ve obligada a cuestionar su relación y su fe.

title: El Karma del Amor
description: Love Karma : Cuando dos desconocidos descubren que sus cónyuges tienen una aventura, unen sus fuerzas para mostrarles a sus parejas que lo que se da se recibe.

title: Caminando Por Fe
description: Walk by Faith : Esta comedia romántica gira en torno a una mujer llamada Pamela (LaRita Shelby) que deja a su prometido en el altar y va en busca de otro hombre.

title: La Princesa Karateca
description: The Karate Princess : Una película familiar inspiradora, basada en la fe, que cuenta la historia de una exitosa empresaria que regresa a casa para hacerse cargo del dojo de su padre.

title: Un Matrimonio Hecho en el Cielo
description: A Marriage Made In Heaven : Demetri Chicopoulos (Robert Krantz) vive una vida de ensueño. Presenta su exitoso programa de entrevistas, "Daytime with Demetri". Sin embargo, pronto descubrimos que, tras un divorcio reciente y el fallecimiento de su madre, la vida de Demetri es más dolorosa que feliz. En un momento de oración, Demetri se arrodilla y le pide a Dios que le permita revivir una semana de su vida. Sabe que las cosas serían diferentes. Demetri se levanta y de repente se encuentra con... su ángel de la guarda (Tom Arnold). Bueno, no es precisamente el tipo de ángel de la guarda que uno desea. El ángel de la guarda le dice a Demetri que Dios escuchó su oración... Demetri podrá revivir una semana de su vida. Lo que suceda después cambiará la vida de Demetri para siempre.

title: Corazón de Sombra
description: Shadowheart James Connor (Justin Ament) regresa a casa en 1865 para matar a Will Tunney (Angus Macfadyen), un asesino despiadado que asesinó a su padre.

title: Kiss Me for Christmas
description: After Cara's friends give her a new look for the holidays, she has a romantic encounter with a man on an elevator, only to learn that he's dating her overbearing boss.

title: The Kid: Chamaco
description: Dr Frank Irwin and his son Jimmy, a professional boxer, team up in order to train Abner, a Mexican teenager, to help him become the country's new boxing superstar.

title: Coming to Africa
description: Adrian has spent his entire life shunning Black consciousness and chasing corporate success. After a perfect storm of discrimination, Adrian finds himself in Ghana on an amusing adventure.

title: Goodbye, Hello
description: Nate Ryan returns home to Bundy Canyon to visit his dying father; Nate opens old wounds in an attempt to make peace with his incredibly unpeaceful father.

title: The Happy Camper
description: Sparks fly between a woman and a hardware store owner as they work together to restore a vintage travel trailer.

title: Raaz Reboot
description: Newly-weds Rehaan and Shaina move to Romania after the former is offered a job. When Shaina senses paranormal activity around her, she learns that her husband is harbouring a secret from her.

title: Água Viva
description: Living Water : Uma ex-festeira converte-se ao cristianismo, provocando tensões com os seus antigos amigos.

title: Ainda Tenho Alegria
description: Still Got Joy : A história verídica da Dra. Shonda Reynolds, que superou o vício após entrar em reabilitação, onde teve um despertar espiritual e um chamamento para pregar.

title: Levantando a Jane
description: Lifting Jane : Conmocionada por experiencias traumáticas pasadas, una sobreviviente de abuso doméstico cierra su corazón al romance hasta que el amor verdadero llega a su vida.

title: Cavalgando na Fé
description: Riding on Faith : Assombrado pela perda da mulher e da filha pequena, um homem destruído encontra um caminho de esperança e cura depois de um novo pastor carismático chegar à cidade.

title: Nuestra Navidad Soñada
description: Our Dream Christmas : Una mujer de Mississippi intenta traer a su familia a Los Ángeles para poder pasar la Navidad con su madre moribunda.

title: Lluvia Musical
description: Country Rain : Pete Ford es un artista de música country en la cima de su carrera. Le encanta actuar más que nada, excepto su esposa, Angie. Cuando ella aparece y le dice que se acabó, Pete tiene que decidir a qué está dispuesto a renunciar para formar una familia.

title: Once Upon a Christmas
description: A modern-day multi-millionaire Scrooge is sent back to high school in order to learn the true meaning of Christmas before his fate is forever sealed.

title: Eu Sou Gabriel
description: I Am Gabriel : Um jovem chega à cidade de Promise, no Texas, com a intenção de ajudar as pessoas. No entanto, o xerife e os moradores não acreditam nele e juram descobrir a sua verdadeira identidade.

title: El Milagro Navideño de Megan
description: Megan's Christmas Miracle : Cuando el padre de Megan la aleja de la única vida que ha conocido y se muda a un pequeño pueblo minero de Virginia Occidental, le cuesta encajar. De hecho, renuncia a su única y verdadera pasión: bailar. Pero el mágico pesebre de su iglesia local podría ser justo lo que necesita para cambiar su vida.

title: Una Navidad En La Granja
description: An Evergreen Christmas Después de la muerte inesperada de su padre, una cantante se debate entre seguir su carrera y salvar el negocio de árboles de Navidad de su familia en un pequeño pueblo de Tennessee.

title: Fuerza Espiritual
description: Driving Force : Un hombre lucha con la fe y el perdón después de que un accidente por conducir ebrio le quita la vida a su pequeña hija.

title: Awesomest Christmas Ever
description: When Ollie learns his parents are planning to divorce after the holidays, he and his friends plot a series of wild schemes to keep them together.

title: At Your Own Risk
description: Hoping to make some money and get hired for a job, two women volunteer to take part in a unique treasure hunt in the New Mexico desert. Their adventure turns into a fight for survival

title: Most Wonderful Time
description: Before her mother sells their family home after the holidays, a 30-something struggling author reunites with her three best friends to reminisce and re-create the glory days of their high school years.

title: Anger Has a Secret
description: EJ Henderson uncovers truths and betrayal. His only refuge is writing, but with a haunted past, can he control his present or future.

title: Never Let Go
description: When the daughter of a single mother is mysteriously kidnapped, she decides to take matters in her own hand. As she goes deeper into the case, she discovers a web of organised crime.

title: Gracia y Misericordia
description: Grace and Mercy : Mientras ascendía en la escala corporativa, Grace Lawrence se ha matado trabajando... literalmente. Pero entrar al Cielo no es tan sencillo. Ahora tiene siete días para aprender todas las lecciones de la vida antes de encontrarse con el Misericordioso, quien determinará su destino final.

title: A Stranger in the Woods
description: A young film student is about to make a documentary about an elderly man who has been hiding from the world for many years. But as secrets from his past come to light, their strange relationship takes a fateful turn.

title: Último Ano: O Amor Nunca Falha
description: Senior Year : Love Never Fails CJ e Marcella lutam para proteger a sua relação contra a pressão da família, da fé e dos amigos quando uma descoberta devastadora vira as suas vidas de cabeça para baixo.

title: Esperanza
description: Hope Después de la devastación de perder a un hijo, la fe de una familia se pone a prueba cuando su hija, Hope, regresa como un espíritu guía que solo su hermana puede ver.

title: La dernière danse
description: La dernière danse Un afecto inesperado se forja entre la pareja menos probable: una joven y su secuestrador. Con pasados ​​igualmente inquietantes, la joven bailarina comienza a reconocer la humanidad de su secuestrador mientras se adentra en su creativo mundo de escapismo.

title: Milagres Existem
description: Miracles Are For Real Uma famosa estrela de televisão encontra o seu ex-marido abusivo para jantar e percebe que ele mudou consideravelmente desde a separação. Mais tarde, ela tem de decidir se volta a confiar nele ou não.

title: Colombes du Badland
description: Badland Doves En quête de justice pour les meurtres commis par un homme que toute la ville protège, ces filles sont en quête de vengeance et sont prêtes à se battre.

title: Mes Deux Amours
description: Hadrien part à la recherche de sa femme Barbara, une journaliste à succès, soudainement disparue. À sa grande surprise, il rencontre Emmanuel, l'amant de Barbara, et Juliette, sa fille.

title: Trahisons passionnées
description: Passionate Betrayals Deux femmes riches concluent un pacte pour assassiner leurs maris respectifs lors d'une escapade d'un week-end, mais les choses tournent mal lorsque leur sinistre complot est découvert.

title: Mon copain virtuel
description: My Online Valentine Un jeune homme et une jeune femme tombent éperdument amoureux l'un de l'autre, cependant, alors qu'ils commencent à s'installer dans leur relation, l'ancien amant de la femme arrive avec son propre plan sournois.

title: Flashbacks d'un fou
description: Flashbacks of a Fool Après la mort malheureuse de son meilleur ami, une célèbre star hollywoodienne, connue pour sa personnalité narcissique, rentre chez elle et réfléchit à sa vie.

title: J'aime ma mère
description: I Love My Mum Un duo mère-fils est embarqué par inadvertance dans un conteneur de Londres au Maroc, avec pour seul bagage leur pyjama. L'aventure les mène à travers l'Espagne et la France, dans un périple pour rentrer chez eux et reconstruire leur relation fragile.

title: Amour De Jeunesse
description: Agnès, architecte, est surprise de rencontrer son ex-petit ami et sa femme Luisa, qui se trouve être maire d'un petit village où elle s'est vu confier un projet de reconstruction de la salle communale.

title: Le courtier du coeur
description: Good Advice Ryan est un coureur de jupons qui perd son emploi de banquier d'affaires. Par la suite, sa petite amie, chroniqueuse, le quitte. Il décide alors de devenir rédacteur fantôme de sa chronique « conseils ».

title: Attraction Dangereuse
description: Human Affairs Un jeune couple prospère de New York a du mal à concevoir un enfant et décide de faire appel à une mère porteuse.

title: La Época Más Maravillosa
description: Most Wonderful Time Antes de que su madre venda la casa familiar después de las vacaciones, Bria, una autora de unos 30 años que lucha por salir adelante, se reúne con sus tres mejores amigas para recordar y recrear los días de gloria de sus años de escuela secundaria.

title: Como Flechas
description: Like Arrows Charlie y Alice intentan cambiar su estrategia de crianza cuando el conflicto, la rebelión y el resentimiento abruman a su familia. Para su sorpresa, pronto descubren que las soluciones efectivas y duraderas estaban más cerca de lo que jamás imaginaron.

title: O Perdão
description: Forgiven "Forgiven" acompanha a vida de uma sobrevivente adulta de abuso infantil e a sua luta para superar a dor e o trauma deixados pela sua turbulenta educação em casa.

title: Esta Oportunidad Navideña
description: This Christmas Chance Chance Phillips es un empresario exitoso con un futuro brillante y un pasado oscuro. Mientras intenta construir su negocio y corregir sus errores, conoce a Gabriel Dupree, una hermosa doctora que guarda sus propios secretos. Ambos se llevan bien, pero no todos apoyan el éxito de la nueva pareja. La amargura, el dolor y la placa se han aliado para destruir la oportunidad de la pareja de encontrar el amor y disfrutar de una feliz Navidad.

title: Premonição
description: Após um violento acidente de carro que quase lhe tira a vida, Jack Barnes começa a ter premonições inexplicáveis ​​e aterrorizantes de desastres horríveis. À medida que suas premonições começam a se concretizar, Jack logo é procurado pelo FBI para interrogatório.

title: Blood Star
description: A young woman driving through the desert alone is drawn into a deadly game of cat and mouse with a psychopathic Sheriff. The game escalates to dangerous levels, and she must use her street-smarts to turn the tables against him.

title: Le rêve de Sara
description: Her Best Move :- Sara Davis, prodige du football de quinze ans, a la chance de rejoindre l'équipe nationale américaine, mais elle doit jongler entre le lycée, la romance, le sport et la pression parentale tout en décidant de ses propres priorités.

title: Le triangle amoureux
description: Three Night Stand  :: Carl prévoit une escapade romantique avec sa femme, Sue, pour raviver leur flamme. Cependant, la situation se complique lorsqu'ils apprennent que le gîte où ils séjournent est géré par l'ex-petite amie de Carl, Robyn.

title: Dutch Kills
description: A desperate ex-con is forced to gather his old crew for one last job to pay off his sister's debt to a dangerous local criminal.

title: The Shooter
description: Cowboy Michael Atherton intervenes on behalf of a prostitute, Wendy, who is being terrorized by a gang of thugs. He guns down the attackers and shepherds her to safety.

title: The Circuit
description: The dynamic between a father and his estranged daughter spills over to the race track, where the duo go head-to-head.

title: Eye of the Beast
description: A young scientist arrives to a small fishing town to fight against the creature living under the water.

title: Wedding Cake Dreams
description: At 12 years old, Carrie Watson places a piece of wedding cake under her pillow when her mother tells her about the superstition that doing so will ensure you dream of your future true love -- and that night, Carrie dreams of a handsome man meeting her at the altar. Fast forward a couple decades, and Carrie, now a successful chemist (and amateur baker), is prepping the wedding cakes for her little sister, Lydia's wedding. Carrie is shocked to discover that the groom's best man, Jason, is the very same man from her wedding cake dream.

title: Do amor a vingança
description: Quando o coração e os olhos estão encobertos pelo amor, é muito fácil se enganar e não perceber que as emoções e ações podem ser falsas. Nastia é uma médica de ambulância, o que significa que nos momentos críticos ela não deve perder o controle. Ela tem um bom coração e um caráter compreensivo. Um dia, Nastia encontra Serguei e se apaixona por ele. Começam um lindo relacionamento cheio de flores, presentes e amor. A garota não acredita em sua felicidade.

title: Final Approach
description: An action filled account of an Ex FBI negotiator who uses all his skills to save a jumbo jet headed for Los Angeles California from the terrorists who have placed a bomb on board.

title: Fever
description: A struggling artist (Parker) is implicated in a string of macabre murders.

title: Nightmare at the End of the Hall
description: A writer teaching at the school she attended encounters a student who seems to be the reincarnation of her dead classmate.

title: The Judge
description: Steve Martini's The Judge... Defense attorney Paul Madriani is hired to defend Judge Acosti, arrested for soliciting a prostitute who later turns up dead. Madriani faces threats, corruption, and doubts about Acosti's innocence as he navigates this challenging case.

title: Operator
description: Joe, a programmer and obsessive self-quantifier, and Emily, a budding comedy performer, are happily married until they decide to use one another in their work.

title: L'éducation de Charlie Banks
description: The Education of Charlie Banks :- Se déroulant dans les années 80, il s'agit d'une saga de passage à l'âge adulte qui commence dans les cours de récréation et mène aux environs d'un collège d'arts libéraux tout en explorant le changement, l'inévitabilité et le courage face aux peurs personnelles.

title: Women in Trouble
description: Women in Trouble Lorsque 10 femmes de Los Angeles issues de différents horizons se retrouvent dans des situations difficiles, elles recherchent désespérément un plan d'évacuation.

title: Elle : Un conte de Cendrillon moderne
description: Elle: A Modern Cinderella Tale :- Ellie Daniels rêve de devenir une star de la chanson. Mais une terrible tragédie survient dans sa vie. L'arrivée de la pop star Ty Parker marque un tournant pour elle.

title: The Messenger
description: The Messenger :- Will Montgomery, un soldat, est blessé au combat et rejoint l'équipe de signalement des pertes. Il se retrouve alors dans une situation délicate lorsqu'il est attiré par une veuve.

title: Spiral
description: A recluse telemarkets at an office, where his boss is his only friend. As he befriends a new, social colleague and sketches/paints her, his dark mind surfaces.

title: Un séducteur en jeu
description: When It Comes Around :- Une belle femme est recrutée par un jeune et brillant cadre sportif. Il tombe amoureux d'elle, mais elle l'utilise pour son propre développement.

title: Sacred Cargo
description: Vince Kanevsky is a US Marine who finds out that his brother has been kidnapped by ruthless ex KGB members, he will stop at nothing to find what really happened.

title: L'amour à nouveau
description: Falling in Love Again :- Ricky et Tara, un couple récemment divorcé, doivent surmonter les difficultés de la coparentalité de leur jeune fils tout en se remettant des blessures de leur relation ratée. Mais après avoir changé de partenaire, ils se rendent vite compte que l'herbe n'est pas plus verte et qu'ils pourraient bien vouloir retrouver leur ancienne vie. Vont-ils tenter une seconde chance avec l'amour ?

title: Rain
description: Rain:-  Un berger allemand nommé Rain est entraîné pour combattre pendant la guerre du Vietnam et son intelligence et son courage face à l'adversité lui valent le respect et la loyauté de son peloton.

title: Depth Charge
description: On his final voyage a commandeer aboard a nuclear submarine is making a shocking bid for world peace. With the help of mercenaries he takes over the sub in order to hold Washington D.C. and the world hostage.

title: Une femme d'action
description: A.T.F. :- es agents de l'Alcool, du Tabac et des Armes à Feu (ATF) du gouvernement fédéral effectuent une mission au sein d'une opération qui est peut-être impliquée dans la vente d'armes à feu et le meurtre d'un agent.

title: Haunting Sarah
description: As a mother (Raver) deals with the death of her young son, she learns that her niece is being contacted by the boy from beyond the grave.

title: Two Eyes Staring
description: Zwart Water :- Christine et Paul s'inquiètent pour Lisa, leur fille de neuf ans, une jolie fille calme qui passe la plupart de son temps seule. À la mort de sa mère, la famille quitte les Pays-Bas pour la Belgique et s'installe dans la grande maison où Christine a grandi. Lisa se lie bientôt d'amitié avec un autre enfant qu'elle seule peut voir.

title: Claustrophobie au sommet
description: Avalanche :- La policière Leah n'a jamais poursuivi quelqu'un avec autant d'obsession que Martin. Elle est convaincue qu'il est le fou qui a tué plusieurs femmes, dont sa sœur. Et maintenant, elle l'a traqué jusqu'à un chalet de montagne isolé.

title: Amour et trahisons
description: Everything That Glitters :- Victoria Robinson semble mener une vie parfaite. Mais son mari infidèle et un jeune homme séduisant aux intentions sombres vont l'entraîner dans un dangereux jeu du chat et de la souris, où elle découvrira que la vie parfaite a un prix.

title: Jusqu'à ce que la mort nous sépare
description: Til Death Do Us Part :- Deux amis d'université, Olga et Maxim, se rencontrent après 15 ans de mariage. Olga affronte la dépression de sa vie conjugale après avoir réalisé qu'elle aime Maxim, tandis qu'un meurtrier maniaque rôde dans leur ville.

title: La Primera Apelación
description: The Last Appeal :- Los presos condenados a muerte a veces se enfrentan a batallas legales insuperables, luchas familiares y, en última instancia, a su propia mortalidad.

title: O Padrasto
description: Step Dad :- Um solteiro bem-sucedido acredita ter encontrado a mulher perfeita. Mas, depois de a pedir em casamento, a relação entre ambos complica-se quando ele descobre que ela tem filhos.

title: Papa à l'essai
description: The Dad Test:- Moritz Kaiser, un jeune homme, demande à Nina Schmitz, serveuse et mère célibataire, de se faire passer pour sa femme afin qu'il puisse obtenir un emploi de designer dans un magasin de meubles pour enfants.

title: Liebe auf den dritten Blick-Un amour en éveil
description: Un amour en éveil :- Lorsque son mari se rend à Vérone pour réaliser ses objectifs commerciaux, Dianne Schonleber reçoit un message anonyme l'informant que son mari a l'intention de rencontrer sa maîtresse à Vérone.

title: Die Kirche bleibt im Dorf
description: Die Kirche bleibt im Dorf:-  L'énigmatique étranger sait que quelque chose dans l'église du village a une valeur particulière, mais les habitants ne permettront pas qu'on l'achète sous leurs pieds aussi facilement.

title: When It Comes Around
description: A beautiful woman is recruited in the office where a young and successful sports executive works. He falls in love with her but she uses him for her own progress.

title: Tearsucker
description: Emotionally vulnerable women are preyed on by a charming psychopath who wants to suck their tears.

title: The Last Ones
description: Following a virus that took the lives of most of the population, John and Micheal have spent their days trying to survive and make sense of their new world. But when they meet the mysterious Karina, who has knowledge of the outside world, their friendship and everything they once knew about the virus and each other will be tested.

title: 13 Souls
description: An evil creature attacks a small mining town. A college student and a cranky outcast must uncover the mystery of the creature's past to put an end to the bloodshed.

title: 2/11: Day of the Dead
description: Un joven es encontrado vagando por el bosque a las afueras de un pueblo, desnudo y cubierto de sangre. Resulta ser el hermano del alguacil local. Una serie de sucesos inesperados comienzan a ocurrir y conmocionarán a todo el lugar.

title: Behemoth
description: Scientists discover a legendary creature which has existed on earth since the beginning of time. When the creature unexpectedly awakens, it causes worldwide destruction.

title: Stranger With My Face
description: After the shocking untimely death of her husband, Shelley Stratton (Catherine Hicks) moves her daughter Alexis (Emily Hirst) and her adopted daughter Laurie (Alexz Johnson) to their remote summer house to give her family a fresh start. As Laurie begins to settle in and put her life back together, she gets the eerie feeling that she is constantly being watched. Her uneasiness grows when people start claiming to see her in places she has never been. The family's delicate state unravels when Laurie unearths her dark past, discovering a twin sister that she never knew she had. Laurie is forced to delve deeper into her twin's secrets, for it turns out her twin has been locked up for years. Laurie must now understand their strange connection in order to prevent her sister from taking over her life and harming her loved ones.

title: Son of the Dragon 2
description: The 'Arabian Nights' tale "The Thief of Bagdad" retold and relocated to ancient China.

title: Prairie Fever
description: Drunken ex-sheriff Preston Biggs gets a ticket out of the jailhouse and a fistful of cash to escort three half-crazed rejected mail-order brides to the nearest train back East.

title: Shark Killer
description: A shark exterminator must retrieve a rare diamond from the stomach of a massive black-finned white shark; however, the powerful local crime lord has, too, set his sights on the gem. Will the fearless shark killer live up to his reputation?

title: 20,000 Leagues Under The Sea
description: A ship sent to investigate a wave of mysterious sinkings encounters the advanced submarine, the Nautilus, commanded by Captain Nemo.

title: Moonshine Highway
description: A moonshine runner tries to make a better life for himself by becoming a stock car racer. Unfortunately, the local sheriff is out to wreak revenge on him for having an affair with his estranged wife.

title: Black Fox II: Price of Peace
description: In 1860s Texas, a man whose abused wife fell in love with a Kiowa organizes a hunting party to recapture her.

title: Cat 8 Part 2
description: An untested global defense system triggers a swarm of devastating solar flares, resulting in catastrophic earthquakes and ferocious magnetic storms; an unprecedented CAT. 8 Armageddon. Can we stop the annihilation of the human race?

title: Kung Fu Killer 2
description: A Caucasian monk in Shanghai infiltrates the underworld to find the killers of his spiritual female Grandmaster.

title: Sea Beast
description: Mythic creatures emerge from the sea to feast on the residents of a fishing village.

title: Ela é o Cara
description: Quando seu irmão decide se afastar por algumas semanas, Viola vai para seu colégio interno de elite, disfarçada como ele, e começa a se apaixonar pelo jogador de futebol da escola, e logo descobre que ela não é a única com problemas românticos.

title: Patient
description: After escaping a cult suicide, a paraplegic hospital patient is tormented by malevolent spirits and cursed to kill whomever hears her voice, unless she offers up the soul of her innocent nephew in place of her own.

title: Zero Hour
description: Following the death of her husband, a young woman is stalked by those responsible.

title: Dead of Winter
description: In the wilderness of Colorado teams compete in a Geocache treasure hunt that suddenly becomes a deadly game of survival.

title: The Black Mass
description: A serial killer stalks Florida college girls during the winter of 1978, leading to his final, unhinged rampage.

title: La vida al revés
description: Life upside down... Aysulú es una rica heredera, en la víspera de la boda se entera de que sus padres fueron asesinados por su prometido. En estado de shock, ella sale del registro civil en taxi, el conductor comienza a acosarla. Saltando del carro, Aysulú encuentra un bebé abandonado. Junto con el niño se muda al pueblo. En la ciudad vivía con comodidad y no estaba acostumbrada a las condiciones rurales. Ahora le toca empezar la vida con una pizarra limpia y aprender a ser madre.

title: The Eastern Front
description: During World War II, a rag-tag group of German soldiers get caught up on the Russian side of command and attempt to rejoin their troops with two Russian female prisoners.

title: Devlet Sırrı
description: Secret Defense... N'obtenant pas un poste potentiellement lucratif, Diane se voit proposer un autre type d'emploi. Pendant ce temps, Pierre devient la proie de terroristes fanatiques, mais le destin leur réserve un autre sort.

title: The Night Before
description: On the night before Halloween, a single mother and her daughter are taken captive in a strange home.

title: Exposure
description: A traumatized man is convinced someone is trying to poison him, so his skeptical wife forces him to face his fears head on with exposure therapy.

title: Penumbra
description: A woman hesitantly rents an apartment to an eerie man who she soon realizes has a part in the solar eclipse that is taking place.

title: Shadows of the Past
description: Four teens target a wealthy mansion owned by a lonely host. In exchange for safety and the freedom to take anything within the mansion, the host compels them to listen to haunting stories of the past.

title: Cornered!
description: During their nightly poker game, a group of lowlifes are terrorized in their own convenience store by a masked killer.

title: Zid
description: A journalist, who is still in love with his ex-girlfriend, becomes the obsession of his landlord's daughter.

title: Blackout
description: A fine arts painter becomes convinced that he is a werewolf wreaking havoc on a small American town under the full moon.

title: Blood Thirst
description: Blood Thirst - A vampire who works at a blood bank meets a detective investigating blood-draining murders, she must choose between revealing her true nature and keeping her secrets safe, even as her own desires become increasingly hard to resist.

title: Wolf
description: After heading to the country to sell his childhood home, Kevin finds himself caught in the middle of a missing persons case while he also begins developing visions of a wolf

title: Water Horse
description: A paranormal investigator links a bizarre string of seemingly unrelated events to the disappearance of her mother.

title: El diablo me dijo qué hacer
description: The Devil Told Me What to Do - Un joven con problemas mentales secuestra a un médico dedicado a la venta de seguros médicos para que confiese sus pecados.

title: Final Days: Tales from the End Times
description: Presents a horror anthology that features five visionary directors offering their unique perspectives on the end of the world.

title: Another Cabin in the Woods Movie
description: A group of horror-savvy friends must sift through a web of murder, mystery, and red herrings when a wedding weekend at a cabin takes a sinister turn.

title: Patient 27
description: La salud mental de César comienza a deteriorarse debido a un misterioso paciente después de que acepta un empleo temporal en un laboratorio.

title: Don't Peek
description: A professional YouTubing couple - whose career is starting to fray their marriage - grapples with how to leverage the discovery that the previous owner of their new home was not only a serial killer who taped his crimes but also believed his victims were haunting him

title: Coffin Rock
description: A woman makes the mistake of sleeping with a young stranger. Her troubles begin when the young man goes to terrifying lengths to prove his paternity.

title: Buenos Aires BZ
description: Buenos Aires está invadida por los muertos. Los cadáveres reviven, hambrientos de carne fresca y con extrañas y grotescas cucarachas que excretan de sus cuerpos. Rubén es oficinista; Julián es cadete y Camila es enfermera. ¿Qué tienen todos en común? Cada uno enfrenta el día de la BZ a su manera, corriendo para sobrevivir, luchando contra los muertos que anhelan devorarlos. Pero el destino de todos los une con un solo objetivo: llegar al Palacio Pizzurno, el último bastión libre de zombis de toda la ciudad.

title: Halloween Candy
description: Spending her first Halloween alone, a recently divorced writer searches for inspiration from trick-or-treaters who come to her door. The night becomes a nightmare when one surprise visitor makes this Halloween one she will never forget.

title: Game of Death
description: Seven millennials must kill or have their heads explode. To survive, they may turn on each other or target innocent townspeople in their secluded town on a fateful day.

title: El diablo blanco
description: The White Devil - Un viaje de campamento para un grupo de amigos se convierte en una pesadilla inesperada cuando uno de ellos se encuentra con un misterioso extraño.

title: Las Vegas Frankenstein
description: When popular Vegas hypnotist Victor Van Pelt inherits Mary Shelley's journal, he believes he has the key to the next greatest Vegas show - bringing life to the dead, live on stage.

title: Clementina
description: Después de sufrir abusos a manos de su novio y un aborto espontáneo, Juana comienza a escuchar ruidos extraños y misteriosos dentro de su casa.

title: The American Ripper
description: As soon as Bobby and Lola, a newly married couple, move into a new house, Bobby transitions into a delusional maniac murderer who turns into a disturbing psychopath, torturing Lola and killing anyone who comes his way.

title: Torment
description: Newlyweds (Robin Dunne, Katharine Isabelle) and their young son find themselves at the mercy of sadistic madmen who secretly took up residence in their remote country home.

title: Rust 2
description: After the horrific ordeal and the loss of her friends, Heather is forced to return to Hotel Fear where Travis prepares for his next victims, Heather must fight once again.

title: I Am A Ghost
description: Sylvia helps Emily, a troubled spirit, uncover the mysteries of her past so she can move on.

title: Return of the Salem Witch
description: A group of students stuck inside for the holidays, unable to drive home due to bad weather conditions, soon find themselves conducting a modern day witch trial.

title: Zombiefied
description: A zombie outbreak begins at a club, leaving locals to fight for survival while a brutal serial killer ads to the body count. Only 2 people know the truth & the infection is just beginning.

title: El Amigo Visible
description: The visible friend :- Juan hace un pacto con un hombre misterioso a cambio de recuperar la vista y el habla. A partir de ese momento, la realidad y la fantasía ya no tendrán límites claros.

title: St. Patrick's Day: The Sluagh Awakens
description: A man is determined to get revenge on the legendary Sluagh, which killed his wife years before.

title: Compulsión
description: Una joven tímida sospecha que su enigmático novio la engaña. Al buscar la verdad, descubre un secreto siniestro que convertirá su vida en una pesadilla sin fin.

title: Heir of the Witch
description: An underprivileged seamstress, haunted by her past, seeks love and acceptance in high society but is faced with the curse from her evil roots.

title: Skin Creepers
description: Onsuccesvolle filmmakers proberen een film voor volwassenen te maken, totdat de hoofdrolspeelster door een demoon wordt bezeten.

title: Astaroth
description: Encoberta pelas brumas do tempo, ela foi esquecida — mas sempre há alguém para lembrar. Gregório é um tatuador obcecado por Astaroth, uma entidade demoníaca que espreita nas sombras com promessas de desejo.

title: Rerouting
description: When a rideshare driver is wrongfully framed for the abduction of two women, he must navigate a relentless pursuit by the law while uncovering a chilling conspiracy, risking everything to clear his name.

title: Beautiful Prison
description: A brain-damaged man awakens after a violent accident with the ability to control happenings in his world.

title: Don't Fall Asleep
description: When Janice and Sam move into a new house, she starts to sleepwalk again, and people start disappearing.

title: Turn Back
description: Lost in a haze of memory from which a truth is nowhere to be found, Lucy searches for a place to belong while constantly running from everything she cannot remember.

title: Punto ciego
description: Blind spot:- Ulises es un documentalista que filma desde su ventana. Busca la objetividad total y, poco a poco, una serie de pequeñas historias cotidianas empiezan a tomar forma. Sin darte cuenta, estás poniendo la cámara donde no debería.

title: Daemonium: Soldier of the Underworld
description: In a universe where magic and technology coexist with humans and demons, a wizard becomes involved in a full-scale war with hell and its demonic inhabitants.

title: Love Again
description: A broken heart consumes Nathan with bitterness, blinding to the true love of his life and stifling all his dreams. Sometimes finding love and happiness is as simple as opening up your heart.

title: Category 7: The End of the World Part 1
description: Across the world an unprecedented Category 6 storm descends. Violent winds, hurricane-level pressure and unprecedented "tornado alleys" develop across two continents. For years, scientists have been expounding theories - and warnings - of global-warming effects. It's disaster Code Yellow, as the "storm on steroids" is only just beginning to rend the earth.

title: The Way Home
description: An inspirational true story about how a rural community rallied around a distraught family to search for their missing two-year-old boy, and changed the lives of many of those involved through doing so.

title: Category 7: The End of the World Part 2
description: The warming effect is creating new regions of extreme weather, but something else is triggering it; something that when combined with record-breaking heat waves creates explosions in the sky. With time running out, discredited scientist Faith Clavell, teams up with storm chaser Tornado Tommy (Emmy nominee Randy Quaid, "Elvis") and Judith to discover the trigger.

title: King Solomon's Mines Part 1
description: Renowned safari hunter Allan Quatermain is lured back into the unknown recesses of the African jungles to find a man who disappeared while searching for the fabled King Solomon’s Mines—a destination of legendary riches from which no soul has ever returned alive.

title: King Solomon's Mines Part 2
description: An adventurous quest for a treasure hidden in King Solomon's mines, based on H. Rider Haggard's timeless tale.

title: The Deported
description: A U.S. Italian actor is deported to Mexico by crooked I.N.S. agents, and a pack of orphans help him find his way back to America.

title: Jules Verne's Mysterious Island Part 2
description: To escape evils of the Civil War, Cyrus removes his small family and random war prisoners by way of hot air balloon. Once landing on an island, the group finds they are surrounded by danger from giant insects and gold-craving pirates. Turned away by the only safe haven on the island, owned by Captain Nemo, played by Sir Patrick Stewart, the group is forced to find shelter and survive.

title: Citizen Jane
description: Based on a true crime story, Jane, living in San Francisco's Pacific Heights, is happily in love with a handsome, intelligent financial analyst that she has known for many years. She finally introduces him to her favorite Aunt who lives in San Jose yet Within days, Her Aunt is murdered in a home invasion. Jane is determined to solve the case on her own when it finally goes cold , interviewing friends and suspects to no avail. Then, the case is picked up by a new detective (MeatLoaf Adair in a great role) on the force who asks Jane for her help. It finally gets solved and Jane, with her now amazing crime solving expertise, helps solve 20 additional cold case murders. The downside of this true story, is Unfortunately Jane died just 2 days before this movie went into production on the Hallmark Channel. Thankyou Jane for your service.

title: Red Dirt Rising
description: Based on a true story about the early days of stock-car racing. A story of love in the time of moonshine as three of stock car racing's earliest heroes come of age to find escape from life's challenges on the track, ultimately shaping the future of their families and auto racing during the Fighting Forties.

title: War Flowers
description: North Carolina 1863, the Civil War is raging. In this inspired story of tragedy and love we follow the lives of Melody, a precocious seven-year old, and her young mother Sarabeth as they struggle on their farm to survive the war.

title: Go Away
description: During a family gathering, dinner is interrupted by a knock at the door. 5 intruders take the guests hostage and put them through a series of sadistic games. As the night goes on, the intruders realize they also may have something to fear.

title: Mother Superior
description: A nurse and her eccentric patient share a longing: the old lady's memory contains the secret to Sigrun's past; the young woman's life force holds the key to the future for the Baroness.

title: Wolves
description: A young social recluse comes across a series of unresolved cold cases and is drawn deeper into society's dark underside.

title: The Daniel Connection
description: After her best friend, a reporter, is killed, a woman finds herself caught up in a tangled web of conspiracy theories, an apocalyptic scenario, and federal corruption.

title: Ripped
description: After smoking marijuana developed by the CIA, two stoners from 1986 are launched into the year 2016 and must learn how to adapt to present-day living.

title: Duress
description: Haunted with nightmares of his wife's recent suicide and struggling to mend the relationship with his only daughter, Richard is caught as a witness to the violence of Abner Solvie. He finds himself at the mercy of a charismatic killer and plagued by his involvement in the city's recent murders. As Abner's new found protégé, Richard is forced to adopt the mind of his sociopathic mentor in order to protect the one he loves. Richard must decide if he's willing to kill in order to keep his daughter alive.

title: The Bet
description: A down on his luck man gets into an absurd but high stakes bet where he has one summer to find, and hook up with, every girl he had a crush on from 1st to 12th grade.

title: Yoga Hosers
description: Two teenage yoga enthusiasts must do battle with an evil presence that is threatening to rise from its underground lair and endanger their major party plans.

title: Virgin of Juarez
description: While on assignment, Los Angeles based reporter Karina Danes meets Mariela, a rare survivor of one of the vicious attacks taking place in the border town of Cuidad Juarez.

title: Girls of Summer
description: Jake McBride bets his best friend he can win the league with a team of models. Together, Jake and his model cousin, Holly, recruit an athletic group of pampered princesses and attempt to turn them into a well-oiled softball playing machine.

title: MOBY DICK
description: 2010: Moby Dick... Movie features the underwater mission of a submarine captain, to eliminate a massive whale that bruised him in a fatal encounter decades ago. Determined to hunt down the creature, will he succeed?

title: Jurassic World Rebirth
description: Zora Bennett leads a team of skilled operatives to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park. Their mission is to secure genetic material from dinosaurs whose DNA can provide life-saving benefits to mankind. As the top-secret expedition becomes more and more risky, they soon make a sinister, shocking discovery that's been hidden from the world for decades.

title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba
description: The Demon Slayer Corps are drawn into the Infinity Castle, where Tanjiro, Nezuko, and the Hashira face terrifying Upper Rank demons in a desperate fight as the final battle against Muzan Kibutsuji begins.

title: Grown Ups 2
description: Lenny decides to move to his hometown with his family and friends. On his arrival at the hometown, he faces many hilarious situations while his friends struggle to cope up with their own issues.

title: Final Destination 1
description: After getting a premonition about a plane crash on his school trip, Alex, a student, saves a few of his classmates. However, their situation gets complicated when death starts chasing them.

title: Superman
description: When Superman gets drawn into conflicts at home and abroad, his actions are questioned, giving tech billionaire Lex Luthor the opportunity to get the Man of Steel out of the way for good. Will intrepid reporter Lois Lane and Superman's four-legged companion, Krypto, be able to help him before it's too late?

title: Final Destination 2
description: Death is stalking Kimberly Corman and multiple survivors of a deadly highway accident.

title: Lilo & Stitch
description: Stitch, an extraterrestrial entity, comes to Earth after escaping prison, where he tries to impersonate a dog. Things take a turn when a lonely Hawaiian girl, Lilo, adopts him from an animal shelter and he helps mend her broken family.

title: Final Destination 3
description: After Wendy has a premonition that her friends might lose their lives if they ride on a roller coaster ride, she manages to save them. But her friends continue to face life-threatening situations.

title: The Fantastic Four: First Steps
description: Mister Fantastic, Invisible Woman, Human Torch and the Thing face their most daunting challenge yet as they defend Earth from Galactus and Silver Surfer.

title: The Final Destination
description: Part 4 : While watching a car race at a stadium with his friends, Nick has a premonition of a car crash which kills all the audience. However, he manages to save his friends. But how long can he cheat death.

title: My Fault: London
description: An 18-year-old girl named Noah moves from America to London with her mother and wealthy stepfather. She meets her stepbrother, and an attraction brews despite their efforts. Unaware, her estranged father tracks her down after release from prison.

title: Final Destination 5
description: Death returns to claim the lucky survivors of a deadly bridge collapse in this fifth frightening installment in the series.

title: How to Train Your Dragon
description: On the rugged isle of Berk, a Viking boy named Hiccup defies centuries of tradition by befriending a dragon named Toothless. However, when an ancient threat emerges that endangers both species, Hiccup's friendship with Toothless becomes the key to forging a new future. Together, they must navigate the delicate path toward peace, soaring beyond the boundaries of their worlds and redefining what it means to be a hero and a leader.

title: Final Destination: Bloodlines
description: Plagued by a violent and recurring nightmare, a college student heads home to track down the one person who might be able to break the cycle of death and save her family from the grisly demise that inevitably awaits them all.

title: KPop Demon Hunters
description: A world-renowned K-Pop girl group balance their lives in the spotlight with their secret identities as demon hunters.
